[{"Name":"Socorro Ament","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGUaYV-4GsBmIL_KaU1Ef_2EGa7JOAhRD_QIdbP978r6nFSas=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Located right outside the post office this quaint little place definitely serves a delicious cup of coffee. The menu is extensive with lots of choices from savory to sweet. There is also a baked goods selection for people on the go. The service is quick and friendly. Great value for money.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-xkZuzG0oKi4X7KcKglfCMFbKBdj2FBc0ZMEP"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"R S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKQilTd1Iv-Kg_9M0v6cF9CQxmuvX3QxXIpc7t9_QE9-B79Nbv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Consistently the best food. Had vegetable laksa today and have to tell the world about it. Creamy, spicy, beautiful presentation, filling (had to eat it in 2 batches), fresh ingredients.
Consistently great customer service.
Support this local business! They deserve it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOz7SBftslxw_dNBe0Oq9Rgkg0YxpS2iNvRvZd5"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"Jan Matthew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVHV_fi29twCP3TJxh0gkO9FVrTIdnQJBmAB88YTc_gh4RAkI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"served with the best customer service from the workers there. food is excellent and well prepared with the freshest ingredients. will recommend to anyone looking for a quick bite. coffee is also very good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuTl7n_TIhWzepFAmJF0ctt0m-Z3cQn2TbXsHy"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"David France - ExploreFeelGood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-kbI4LTlzcRv1MRphBFeuYxTMne4E0JJNO54LNVtGCmRDvmZT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New in town, I had passed by yesterday, but it wasn't the right time for me, so I came back on purpose today
And what a great move!

First thing you may notice is how busy Alberto's Cafe is, anytime you come, you're likely to see lots of customers around

Second thing, is the numerous and VERY welcoming staff. Friendly, smiling, I even heard them call several customers by their first names, which shows those were returning customers, and that the staff cared to ask for their names and actually remember them. I even noticed some guests coming back in just to say bye and wish them a good day, that means a lot about the mood they've built up

About the place, it has different sections, with some stools and a bench by the kitchen (convenient when waiting for your food to go to be served for instance), tables inside, and outside
It has nice decoration, with plants, nice lighting, and other nice touches
Newspapers available too

And the last but not the least, the fooood, and drinks, indeed
Lots of elaborated food options, with acai bowls, gourmet toasties, savory crepes, sweet crêpes, laksa etc
For drinks, hot coffee, iced coffee, chai, smoothies, milkshakes, cold pressed juices... For your hot drinks you can choose the type of milk, if lactose free, add some syrup...

I personally started with an avai bowl, which featured, on top of acai indeed, pear, apple, banana, strawberries, muesli,  almonds, dried goji berries, pumpkin seeds
Then a smoked salmon brie avocado crepe (for French people, this is not a galette, but like a giant blini in a crepe format, well worth trying)
And to drink a mixed fruits one (apple, pear, orange, ginger and lime)
It was all appealing, yummy, healthy

An attention to details on all levels

Definitely the perfect place for brunch, once you'll have tired it, you'll want to come back, again and again

Highly recommended!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIXY52dcZw1MPr3M8QaRQGEbT8J7CrQ_ANeJtP"],"When":"2024-3-9"},{"Name":"Dev Anggraini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkvMB8xcaMsTyPiesl12Kzzf8no0TjKsdAV73ydpsdO0o_N2o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I forgot take picture of my food but I had to review this place because of the warmth and friendly service of the staff. The food was served in a generous portion, quick and fresh. Will come back if I had more time in Darwin.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMpTTDBpK1TCVFw8WL8ekiFb4otOtpPz9w-bwNa"],"When":"2024-3-7"},{"Name":"Jett Mahmud","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWl4saQpaUF0DgXtuVMAuu-y3btXvnrZ66Xd04fKX_XjkWIwUfvOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Darwin's breakfast game just got upgraded – stellar coffee, mouthwatering toasties. Pics fall short; it's a feast that words can't capture. Pure yum!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhOCOOodgcg5_OOrdkUVpQSHQgO_YzfVE_tMHS"],"When":"2024-1-26"},{"Name":"Tanuj Arora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9Q3i-ZoMGy71EH5DfG7AkqE9613TIS9Go055l5HfxhsgLw7wM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love their Laksa. Easily the top 3 Laksa’s in Darwin. Good staff. Good coffee and good brekkie deals.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOC68B2F9LejGMz_j1sKLPlp_9lRzan4Dnr50t_"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"Protozoa Zoe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWo4sF6hj2MgFE2g9PfHWA9CihISnyQaWEY1bOXp8u2VPT0pEhPDA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was delicious and healthy. The staff are wonderful. The coffee was okay, not my favourite howevever maybe just not what I'm used to in Melbourne. The portion size was also very generous. Ill definitely go again next time im in the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWvD8VJK1ad9ZmXPzlX2AIVI_rwuCNlB7MoRUN"],"When":"2023-9-11"}]

[{"Name":"Chad Harper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-kZcfd4GMEWXpEieU5RY9DKD3jmjR3imX-_lMcqWdu0UWr-9WHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came for morning coffee and breakfast. Location is central, easy to find and access. Venue is neat, comfortable and open. Service was friendly. Coffee (mug cappuccino) was good, though a little less warm, though I could've asked for it to be hot (I prefer a hot coffee). Coffee art though was spectacular, if that is what your in to, which I am not so much. But it was pretty good. (I believe Duke's cafe was running an coffee artwork comp. So far this art was leading. IMO.) I also ordered the Yoghurt Parfait. I usually go for a more savoury breakfast, but felt like yoghurt. Unfortunately this option was greatly sweet. Fruit was nice, but soooo much jam and they use sweet yoghurt (as opposed to the preferred Greek yoghurt). I didn't really eat much at all. If you're a sweet tooth - go ahead. Price is standard.

Comparing Duke's cafe (@Pandanas Hotel) and Rabbithole, I prefer Duke's. But they are comparable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNydHpSlWpt2K1U9FjRFcy2uL-wpPoUWOgcZF6x"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"B.S. David Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLg7tA3A13ejrBP8jUeCxUB3kwGXkInqRDXRLqWIRXH-W50CiFu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After arriving in Darwin, I was drawn to my first cafe, Rabbit Hole, and went to a cafe located in a park where huge tropical trees grow.  As soon as I entered, a tropical squall poured down from outside, but I was drowned out by jazz music and the sweet scent of coffee made me feel like I was in another space. I took a sip of a cute cappuccino filled with milk art and felt the tropical morning.  First of all, 5 stars for the coffee taste.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPQ52Mv4Yu0Y8qRzP_QIDiUzgFYUdJJEdGfM67"],"When":"2024-1-22"},{"Name":"Dev Anggraini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkvMB8xcaMsTyPiesl12Kzzf8no0TjKsdAV73ydpsdO0o_N2o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Walked down for a quick lunch from my hotel. The staff are friendly and love the quick service. Ordered baked eggs (vegetarian option) it was served hot and filling. Good value of money.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP19YSa8dxLVT_NyNFStAK3IubxVO3hxSyu4Vdq"],"When":"2024-3-5"},{"Name":"_freddyfeeds","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7f9u5cFiTKIVXlHcwJufo_OKYU1EFvHIA5yKWVFXvV2wDTYHF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had the cacao smoothie and big brekkie. Food came out quickly and tasted mean. the staff were friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsu58Jf5CsKgXWGecPFihTmwnsVCZrYF8h0Di1"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Michelle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTMKERZ4s5yN9tABH8qIZyiaNiwN5kaPjjHDQ5aKhjMAzOFtk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We went in around 8.30am on a Saturday, and there were still many tables available. However the tables fills up quickly after 9am. Good selection of dishes on the menu. You order at the counter. Food service was slighty slow. We tried the smoked salmon and the miso benedict. The dishes were a good portion size and tasty. The matcha was milky and too sweet, matcha wasn't strong enough..would not recommend the drink.
We were visiting from Melbourne and were happy with our breakfast overall, would recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGFvRCtrpjX0DO1hGgJnTJNZAAPBCjFfouM-HY"],"When":"2022-8-30"},{"Name":"Katherine Tomelty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXV5E5hG1aHveE9k1oMWZuwPj3l5iJEGV-NwEFPAMLl11jnA6pC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I am so grateful for the person who recommended I come here. I came here recently whilst up in Darwin, the food was divine!! 😍 Located in the 'mall', we came in with a table ready to go (walk in) and we were seated straight away, the cafe is very chill and the workers are super nice, the wait time is just the right amount and so is the price! The only problem I have to pick out is that there seemed to have been no gluten free bread available when I ordered. The menu does have items with gf options, however, luck just wasn't timed well. I ordered the mizuna salad with the green juice. All in all, a great place with aesthetically pleasing dishes (worth a shot for your Instagram stories).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNchwTiwp1yfVDYHwMLmqltVpni6rRu1PR_FDmN"],"When":"2023-1-21"},{"Name":"Ian Frew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0E3aPt82ixz_VBELU9MhoUUxJWb3Ji7Fi5AsN7GymdW8zJA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Looked it up before arriving and definitely lived up to the reviews. I wanted good coffee but also good food, but not a burger.  I had the big breakfast and my partner the mushrooms. Both delicious. Coffee was excellent as well","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPA4yhKR_fehJDa-IfRYX88zda7hzGrSCzPk0ze"],"When":"2022-6-30"},{"Name":"Avijeet Sen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2O-Ka2qb-gc-yeDiMN99jHPTtgbAMroDxss7J3Zu7wwUmlKob=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Visited in Dec 2022

Great little breakfast/brunch joint located in the city centre mall. I ended up ordering the Korean Toast with bacon and a cold brew with tonic. Liked both of them. Service was friendly and helpful.

Would definitely recommend this place for breakfast if you’re staying in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLRg6Cg2kd7GcFNZi7PTD70YN9JR86Lbjeys3Q"],"When":"2022-12-31"}]

[{"Name":"dewy putu swan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZQxmq7KejGqv96TfLP2fWiuVfZFHHNLz-EMSr3zqaA-h_TSGi2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Coffee was great, and the place is cool. Lots of old stuff to see","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrL1zutfDlRcCBPXLbYgXdb3AP6j3-mlYUEERM"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"darshizone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGYuR2ylga1FAbocgxohpL7BTv2YDanxe64JmaWrSi2T1QYt66Tg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Heartwarming Hub of Community, Compassion, and Culinary Delight

Stepping into Sam's café is akin to entering a rich tapestry of community spirit mingled with a dash of historical charm. Nestled in the heart of Darwin, this café blossoms under the diligent care of Sam, whose multifaceted service to the community is nothing short of inspiring. Every Friday, the cafe morphs into a sanctuary for the local veteran community, offering not just free coffee, but an atmosphere of camaraderie where stories are shared.

The collectible fair run by the café is a quaint voyage into the past, offering a platform for enthusiasts to exchange and purchase unique treasures. As the holiday season approaches, Sam’s initiative to organize a 'Feed the Homeless' event reflects a deep-rooted empathy, creating a conduit for locals to contribute food and services, fostering a true sense of community.

The verdant charm Sam infuses into the café’s surroundings is a testament to his eye for beauty, making the space a verdant retreat amidst the urban hustle. Moreover, his recent election as a councilman for Darwin City Council showcases a level of trust and respect he has garnered among the locals.

The café itself is a delightful time capsule, with fascinating artifacts adorning every nook, inviting patrons on a nostalgic journey through time. The inclusion of a vegan menu was a pleasant surprise, offering a modern culinary touch to the otherwise vintage ambiance. Every aspect of the café, from its community-oriented services to its charming décor and diverse menu, resonates with the warmth and dedication Sam and his team bring into this beautiful venture, making each visit a unique, heartwarming experience.

A definite must visit, and absolutely would recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxSXyAwokLx7s9GPaCCu1ox8KbyrWfTBkJbJiW"],"When":"2023-10-30"},{"Name":"Sera Koth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsFVeZUQt7zAuOwgOVjITA1cAf5XihTWLxbusdL1wPuYYFgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mad Snake has great atmosphere, coffee and food. Keep an eye out for a variety of community events they organise. Good folks doing good things. They also have great vegan options!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaHLDSYH4PdmYTKT5ah1YZc5RO9Y5rOq-AqyNy"],"When":"2023-6-26"},{"Name":"Jenny and Troy Jackson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhVcD4vuWg7hZCTQXVWOhdikm2seQ2eFE_1XPKVT2GyZeSUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little cafe with awesome coffee and entertaining conversations with the owner Sam. Doing great things for veterans supporting a range of community events and selling veteran owned coffee products. Keep up the amazing work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cliff Wheatley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU73GSJt9KY4P0OxzziwqxMradl1i8qzZJAsTy1bE_ty9QVEoSPsg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is the best cafe in Darwin.  Awesome iced chocs, great people, 80s pop culture, retro video gaming and plenty of memorabilia.  Love it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNnoLX9E8XL1FMTpUI_IAnQdp2YQhkh05Z6NcWw"],"When":"2022-7-6"},{"Name":"AC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocInvWeysqcUlume3kC2hMDxXMY8BbBN8BwKjXbQacnYtUJKUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"What a place! The owners were awesome and a great local cafe to support. Coffee was good 👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCgvg3cR79e_xu8hL3BRUHZ0zyQv_GJ9Goejym"],"When":"2022-6-27"},{"Name":"Jurgen Hein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUeE5UfP2Wsr_yjcoyT8kfRTDms4573cuIEjHQ0XOf3UNYpg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One unique place to visit and plenty of things to look at or play game. The coffee was excellent and service was extremely helpful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgVCbvgGEgKvzPqXz7pEBh0pGN7DahWYPzBrmI"],"When":"2022-7-16"},{"Name":"Mighty Brown Mouse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGIuoP6N4PQ_e2zFBpnqnYEqrEdrV1E8AjuNUPBegdeehijQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"No doubt the best coffee in Darwin although inside is a bit musty. But coffee will not disappoint.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNp3z6lGi2wDyQHktCTxcLl03Bd9WFgODmEFZjV"],"When":"2023-8-2"}]

[{"Name":"Ipin G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnKmSunSkHvxaUhiXyBYbvUi3MU1-ZZcxA4kdP7rNogwr2QSo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food wasn't a surprise to look at but definitely surprised at taste! The combinations within a dish was delicately designed. When I first look at them I thought I could have made them at home. When I tasted them, I was glad that I came to this cafe.

Ordered salmon bagel and pancakes. Portion of the food was a bit small but I would say it deserved the price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMybhK2r71-2A4OWHCYvO4GFGJ2AQf-LhrIL5Uz"],"When":"2023-7-25"},{"Name":"Lissy Phetiam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW19NEQZVvA2v5J7BERyKr-s8NUZ8Z5ScB5tiNci_388H3PLM0dbw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you haven't heard of kaya (coconut jam spread) and you love the combination of sweet, salty, and savoury, the kaya toast is a must! It's serves with a soft-boiled egg lightly complimented with a dash of soy sauce. The coffee is amazing, and the service is professional and friendly. I highly recommend Quarter for your next dine-in experience in Darwin.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKIAOJiVHFb_94zk6vTeb_fSYOaPai7wYAUXR-"],"When":"2023-7-9"},{"Name":"Suzanne Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4JznvGn7ti3aFeYRXFoK30gLvDj4CL3X0l4R9UrYMTgDAKhi8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A great little Cafe for a coffee and a snack. Very polite and efficient service. Best flavour and price for an iced latte that I have found in and around the cbd. Indoor air on and Al fresco seating available","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Liza Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSoIjG_7wb5b9V6egg3pKO9gTgGcfSc5DP4Mmm0ZZXGUDcWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s a new cafe on the block - highly recommended! The chef who is also one of the owners bakes the Oreo cheese cake in the shop and the homemade Oreo cheese cake tasted as good as it smells! I love the Oreo cheese cake is low in sugar as I find cakes in Darwin are way too sweet for my taste. I tried their Hong Kong Milk Tea and it tasted exactly like those Cha Chaan Tengs in Hong Kong. Love their butter kaya toast set too, very Singapore-style. Will continue to visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbFZ-Dcq9fvXj5wZFJv9BdMd95833cQVCZYXah"],"When":"2021-3-30"},{"Name":"Maryam B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjacKu7jYTjMb7Rg4dRFWOATvjt8W3wTrXovvQe9xTof7R12LY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quarter Cafe - my daily delight.
Very friendly staff, great vibes and nice coffee...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFsQUkmpsGsQ6oMshiisCvwe35hWFoW3F-EEEQ"],"When":"2023-11-21"},{"Name":"love","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLiwnVg79pBaSarMQD-H8uOFs2E8qjdVrdzvsYW-Rxzok-GYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great coffee and best customer service. The cakes look beautiful and fresh I’d love to see a vegan cake so I can enjoy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxv_bxeeNW_X5ynj3DZpK17IaqNNnCkMFDMgs8"],"When":"2023-10-11"},{"Name":"4chillies","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUbuM7i6TizD07cpYhi3L15rBKlGWpBEh5uDKeTUIGGDZsR800=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We needed somewhere cool to grab a drink and have a chat and Quarter looked really inviting. The mango smoothie was delicious and refreshing and we couldn't resist their cake selection - just the perfect couple of mouthfuls to reward yourself without being a glutton.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGVk96O6hPQu1tGKhFL4XYFtszSiEW-wcDQhAd"],"When":"2022-9-30"},{"Name":"Jiyeong “Helen” Jeong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0v19ppKGYCRnPtkv931SRF8EmSoTbEa3Dmt3hEssyXiRLkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee, grabbed a fresh orange juice and coffee with my son. Lovely cakes and sweets. Friendly team! Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkZkVKcX457zgaOR-lCKc63n_JCJpzV-1nLWfS"],"When":"2023-4-8"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alexander Zhdanov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaehpTTsabl5IBdRaUZLERl0WjZUCD9Ae45ZHlVoO9DB2fOxN6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Ray’s Cafe and had an absolutely delightful experience. The coffee here is incredible, crafted by a very skilled barista. The pastry selection in the cabinets is impressive, and the menu boasts an extensive array of food options, ensuring there's something for everyone. The staff were all exceptionally friendly and attentive, which added to the warm and welcoming atmosphere.

The location itself is fantastic, offering both indoor and outdoor seating. The indoor area is well air-conditioned, making it a perfect spot to relax on a hot day, while the outdoor seating is comfortably shaded and cool, ideal for enjoying the beautiful weather.

I went to Ray’s for brunch and was blown away by the food. I tried a dish I wouldn't normally go for, and it was so delicious that I left nothing on my plate. The coffee complemented the meal perfectly. The ambience of the cafe is cozy and inviting, making it a place I will definitely return to soon.

The portions at Ray’s are generous, which is great for those with a hearty appetite. I particularly enjoyed their organic sourdough, which was springy and delicious, and the scrambled eggs, which were buttery and rich. The fresh juice was also a refreshing addition to my meal. The corn fritters, while a bit dense, were flavorful, and the poached eggs were cooked to perfection.

Overall, Ray’s Cafe is a gem that offers amazing food, great coffee, and a charming atmosphere. Whether you're looking for a place to enjoy a quiet breakfast, a leisurely brunch, or a quick coffee break, Ray’s is definitely worth a visit. I highly recommend stopping by and experiencing it for yourself!

Alex","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsTBUrzHUXgCkxk6871eodFe9OjwwJizMnFEkb"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Otta Orsya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_TXUO8zl-SRak2g0x-HSA17jJsuh_r4bKk7XfnBwcijbRkc0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to Ray’s for brunch and the food was amazing! I never thought i’d like this type of dish, but it was so good nothing was left on my plate. The coffee was also good. I love the ambience and will definitely come back soon","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNBWWyRDZQIyTrTxhVmzfj2YULr7DISmehmVWN"],"When":"2024-4-10"},{"Name":"Luke Fraser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtr6aNvqfp6CP6Of8ZvOwa8lRv1tBMCw1JV7DQX9DJlAhDIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best coffee I've had in Darwin!!!!!

Great music and atmosphere, plants hanging from the ceiling and amazing food.

Who wouldn't want waffles and chicken for breakfast.

Did I mention the best coffee in Darwin ☕️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-F5w8jvAU_BqX4GivwWq9_fFN-i7As6wHPj8v"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Katherine Tomelty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXV5E5hG1aHveE9k1oMWZuwPj3l5iJEGV-NwEFPAMLl11jnA6pC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went here in the morning looking forward to the food. Best to say, it was quite underwhelming. I eat a GF diet, and was dissatisfied with the range of GF availability. I got excited when the menu had a croissant with eggs/halloumi and stated that there was a GF option available,  to which I was shocked when the dish came out and it was on 2 thick slices of bread. I think it is quite misleading to do that. The prices of the place are a little pricey for what you get. Though, I will say, the hot chocolate that I ordered was very delicious and I'd definitely come back just to order that drink again. The staff were nice, the place was semi clean (chairs were dirty from being outside), the service was fairly good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOI1qDNAwzhLxm84MxBslowvP21JTQxA7xFdnDm"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"C T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaU92h9-1OVEHFGRsJfxQJ8rNIDhL-YyDWG_ypWUkzVAMMUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee and big food servings. Their organic sourdough was springy and delicious, scrambled eggs were buttery and juice was refreshing.
Corn fritters were quite heavy and dense but the poached eggs were perfectly cooked.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPI9wAhwK2ALJiTOTYJug4XdRzyNmx4YfXqYItg"],"When":"2024-1-17"},{"Name":"Andrew Richardson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3HpETHdb6QCz4jyhjT-a8ZQKFum6Z1jJ4PEcQ3UrjJF64fNS0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ray's cafe was recommended to me by a local. I visited for breakfast, hoping to find somewhere air conditioned and with good coffee. The coffee was good, but the air conditioning left a lot to be desired. The menu has a lot of options, but even cold meals like granola are a little on the expensive side, perhaps due to including a panacotta. Granola over $20 is not in the 'affordable' range. There is no table ordering, so you line up to order and pay (which is fine). The inside table and chairs were very flimsy/rudimentary, going for a varnished plyboard look. That'd be fine, except every time I tried to cut my meal (ricotta toast) with a knife and fork shook the table and almost spilled the coffee. My ricotta toast had a good covering of ricotta, fresh fruit and a drizzle of honey. It was good with the exception that the actual toast was more like bread than crunchy toast.

Overall, Ray's cafe is fine. Darwin is blessed with lots of cafes and coffee stops, so try what's local to you. I'd be happy to eat at Ray's again, but explore what else is on the menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaubJ5L60s1viyqWLI8er4HAzVJjl8BG49nMvu"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"Don Bensted","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIguNptTPh08DE8PoryIpeXFoxDjsyWqFboJD-q0SfLsnyUbnq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tommy Toast for breakfast was divine! It was incredibly tasty, and the perfect start to the day. The coffee was great, and the almond croissant was fresh and delicious, completing a delightful morning treat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqnxq1Kd3wzghlZkxj0ArRXSCYlX9zGvasbVmV"],"When":"2024-3-22"},{"Name":"Melissa Leong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWI4LfgSU945Lf5cnsPQ5Md2F6lYSYhIoiYeV-TJ6QwaJ50Osd1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice iced black and atmosphere. Very airy and spacious cafe. My partner loved his juice of the day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODh_wES5raAPJO5tarLN5a-4bkt2b8scDYbu6n"],"When":"2024-5-27"}]

A nice setting and good place to chill.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeJbIpO1xw6m_TEXZCgbvTW7YEpTHnWrzyqerj"],"When":"2023-8-2"},{"Name":"David Maddison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFyPx9z-tDVuyNWsqNCdGUEXJQr34sGR_wnKlh-nIdlk2E_R8mrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We happened across this quaint cafe whilst exploring Darwin’s various arcades. In fact, this location is unique as it used to be the old, open air cinema. The butterscotch muffin was decadent and delicious and the special, four cheese toastie is worth the extra cholesterol on your arteries - yum!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9aN5O7wfT7sCG_PfXga2hN064Yvv_S8vDPtiX"],"When":"2021-2-20"},{"Name":"Janna Nystrom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrfG-6aI-nWHG5aUHEQgl169GDdk074lNY_YNBqBFBnRTG0D0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been to a few places around Darwin for coffee, and this is by far my favorite. The food was incredibly delicious. And I was really surprised by how good the salad dressing was. And that’s coming from someone who isn’t a big fan of vegetables. I wasn’t going to eat it, but it was that good I wanted to.  Not a bad menu selection, either.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMa34RUem7sB8sdeucRIUFShHniMpjtbxkZQyLU"],"When":"2022-7-18"},{"Name":"Paige Kosik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVr9apFtLQkx59dAPtFLYf5KHS1SwvZe7UrpYtb_aTkXKuApvvAHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"No wifi, but really friendly service and in a really cute location ! Indoor and outdoor seating! Lots of vegetarian and gluten free options !! Great chai latte !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTS6MaU66m90salRDpZLS_zuXqqd5inVxn2pvS"],"When":"2023-2-24"},{"Name":"Raffa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJnwXgDxv6o5DlE4dHrW7QftMm9QRxz0E0Tkn3u3A8nfLvOBZpIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quality ingredients make the food here so good. Coffee excellent, and I’m a good coffee addict! Tucked away, not always busy but worth the search.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOROCJnBY97QLD38_XZ1-h0NbY6hvGMlXqqaFkQ"],"When":"2022-10-3"},{"Name":"Brightone Nik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWqlWLiowRjxIqSLwTNAH3a9h0HM86SGSNb2avf0_dXp3RhScK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Located in the #StarVillageArcade. Friendly, romantic relaxing. Good coffee delicious cakes and sandwiches. The #nuttycoconutvegan slice is thick moist and sweet ($6.50) large coffee is creamy and bitter (not acidic) /not campos/- good menu range, managed by friendly welcoming staff. Located in the Smith street Mall. @fourbirds is a clean cool and great place to come play chess and a cup of coffee.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSsZvF3wieWLGUE_RDPHNZRqTGBVdPdZxzjeGK"],"When":"2019-4-23"},{"Name":"Ross McHutcheon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXWML6-W-Kcw31PUfJeEwHI3T3Xqz_KkxvA0oc04r2xF7kXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After another busy week - halloumi included with breakfast ! What a great treat at Four Birds Cafe in Darwin. Excellent, hot coffee as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNN63dXecy0lP1cHG8SOgdvZFQYbeNa1H7_u91t"],"When":"2023-4-1"},{"Name":"Mickey P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKORf3s_kHtPUI68BoNvv7J9BSx8LeT0ekEa2UVVN0Q2rEOTA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best coffee I’ve had in Darwin and the Japanese Pancake was delicious, great friendly staff, highly recommend","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Suresh bogati","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSl-uCpwTwslZFyUh1ip_OgN09ROg8kODdSl-0p9f3E7G0JkBf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Even during the busiest times, the staff go out of their way to make you feel welcome and attended to.
The highlight of the cafe experience is undoubtedly the coffee and the barista who are passionate about what they do. Reed consistently goes the extra mile to ensure everything is perfect, from the quality of the coffee to the overall atmosphere. Their attention to detail and genuine care for customers set 1995 Cafe apart from the rest.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWsWasw-fbX9PgfpklyvLbThZq0XSZ27_FMULL"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Haley Clay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXczBREuRUZ0aMpU4BSPMmAv7fBR81dtZBiVsjVCFC1YhJfwrO0TQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hidden gem in Darwin! Great croissants and coffee, staff was welcoming and helpful! Great vibe -- not the spot if you're looking to work & wifi, but definitely a place for enjoying time with friends over good coffee!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6sUkjWSqx4zalZbRQvibQ-en1enV6VTRC_V8C"],"When":"2024-2-9"},{"Name":"Odilia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoDAYJJ-92fMRZbS5JIzO6hkOI5SmPEfPpZXB8EVh-6OChl5I1iQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Best Ice Chocolate ever.. and the staff there are FAB.. alot of my colleagues love the coffee aswell. Some different cakes or fruit tarts might be nice to add to the menu..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMC-gE2seM0uZXtpBJmzC69niw18aqZxawPskhW"],"When":"2024-5-1"},{"Name":"suvapat D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_hJyvTXpcvN47OXgsmNJbOhts6VbQ2PiyDPT2WMfAQ1ohBj8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today I had an amazing meal, juice was so good. I love to stay here and relax. Atmosphere is so relax and lovely lovely staff.

Would definitely recommend coming here.

Coffee is no question, Always Great! 👌🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGdciA8Wra7Md1fevweLkgeR2bO2GJkSQn-3U2"],"When":"2023-12-12"},{"Name":"Nick Wareham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_Wz-svTHMH5W9X0NxEkS7RYRb2om6pSaOgjOLmMYEEv-bxiXWrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What can I say, this place is a hidden gem, strong Melbourne Vibe, beautiful Cafe and great music.. Now down to the important bit, the coffee. We tried an iced latte and a cappacino. Coffee was amazing! Not strong, but an amazing taste! Have yet to try the food but will definitely be back. I can highly recommend to the coffee drinkers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2MlXlwie_OqL2uhtYtQn0xSITxr18qkEXvfRv"],"When":"2023-7-15"},{"Name":"Lesley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKKfWeiWaeTLo1_ieQL9Qc5u38FvXYqWFNPi6NZhmnDFzCKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful coffee shop - I thought I was in a trendy Melbourne side street! Lovely atmosphere- great staff.
I usually can’t tell one coffee from another but knew their coffee was brilliant as soon as  I tasted it, soooo smooth and well made.
We had a pastry that was lovely!
Will be back to try their breakfasts.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kitchen Insider","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCa9Ovt5QTHL0DFA-hZiWxc3dxpx6guwo0qDkwdf2HkVfd3mxp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Patissiers must hate Darwin. There's more humidity than anywhere south of here, and many places north. In the case of this perky little place, they've opted for the heavy croissant butter approach (as opposed to the French traditional "so light I swear it's a hologram" approach). The result is a buttery taste, with the air moisture transforming its once considerable weight to...well...more considerable. The coffee is well made, but very weak for an extra shot order. Otherwise, a place to come and be happy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrgIwmB96DHHLVgHrpCb1FcG3vB3HjWg_XFVmv"],"When":"2023-10-4"},{"Name":"Cheyne Grace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXldNz8Fm4l4jPw9n0Ve_O8zbKg9UKAojFsZ9q1gbxjpD1pfXy4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best coffee I found in the Darwin CBD. Super friendly staff and cute indoor decor perfect for catch up or meeting. Limited food options but the fresh juices and coffee is exceptional.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNrjht-8A0QtEDrqQsKkp7a2_2NF4CkGkd2GlNP"],"When":"2024-1-15"}]

[{"Name":"Michey Moo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwe8wGjYpr0d7uwEYXQKeX6rTDBFX-RmbwG9I7FeDiHI2raLCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fabulous coffee. 😃 This coffee snob couldn’t fault their almond latte. The beetroot juice was also great! Very beety 😉
Delicious food options for a wee little place. The avocado toast with poached eggs was a very generous serve! My friend really enjoyed their pulled pork toastie too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjfNCmb5TXfTSVcD75QAy7L6z1lhyrmNe0P1YD"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Melissa Leong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWI4LfgSU945Lf5cnsPQ5Md2F6lYSYhIoiYeV-TJ6QwaJ50Osd1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"No-frills breakfast cafe selling tasty toasties. So good that we forgot to take a photo and already started wolfing the food down. Iced long black was good too, not bitter.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXkyTn9NWccCGQccs06OlRLcywGjUj0sgG_7PL"],"When":"2024-5-24"},{"Name":"Jean Teo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzZB3OYIdl82xs18TPx9FyFK6n9sunkLIEjehK_LDIk7VCkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to have brekky. The mushroom cheese toastie was delicious. Eggs Benedict is good. Coffee is nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNik8cgtTrvv86xBa1k2VstwT_4n4Fos9bmqrzT"],"When":"2024-4-18"},{"Name":"Areej","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgJnAqOPiABipKJEbH-qjewpUGSDOTr2jfxP4lV1YRx_Z4_-MM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After hearing numerous positive reviews about Coffee Man on Mitchell Street, I decided to give it a shot. I was pleasantly surprised by the positive and lively atmosphere of the staff. It turned out to be one of the best cups of coffee in town. Had Matcha Frappe, and cappuccino with banana bread. The place also offers a great selection of fresh juices. If you're looking for high-quality coffee and friendly, prompt service, this place has it all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPt-syK9Tuq_9zzwqPcT5cDAkbK7CHvxseUBCq-"],"When":"2023-8-26"},{"Name":"Yulia Kulikova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS0he81fYB9MLXj4brw59LcnwTuPrcw7fXgGsMcKly4HuxDZIn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely best coffee in Darwin! You can also get amazing coffee beans there. Food is ordinary, but I go there for a coffee. Thank you guys 💚","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dean Murphy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXL7ZUr9gN080ojz6M7f_VXrVnxY7SBzeHqDbVAv3R0WFkySgvo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have to say the coffee man does the best coffee in Darwin! Their chicken cheese melt is the best I’ve ever had, staff are amazing and always so smiley and polite! Would highly recommend anyone looking for a good coffee and some food to check them out! Great atmosphere to relax and chill out also!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jana Landong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIADJAyvUFrkjWfuyiAV3SNjZ2cjdnu3B98H08J-5wIWoo8_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best coffee in Darwin!! Will definitely come back. I had their pulled pork eggs benny and it was such a generous serving 😍 coffee as always made with passion by the man himself!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoLdkZP7UFdovJ5jn6fOpXY9otXk8c_WAZND4R"],"When":"2023-7-14"},{"Name":"Michael McRoberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwRc3Rft9ujgj_5ryhAciMIk7U4iEgGFwRGM26GksuozrAE6eP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Popped in this morning, the coffee was lovely!

Coffee Man is also located close to the main esplanade and hotels, making it an idea location to pop into for a quick morning snack or coffee.

Plus an added advantage, the coffee shop was also open a smidge early so I didn’t need to wait around at 7:00am!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0Mm7_39AUYv8iB8YMG-Iutw3uJr69PlzZUN6V"],"When":"2022-11-14"}]

[{"Name":"Franklin Righês","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsDj448cEgnoaYY996rgxeEW2EzAejw7P8rzOw9ViOXYPI0CY3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The fries are real and crispy, delicious.
I’ve got the B.E.L.T and didn’t regret at all, but wifey went a naughty and the Pullet pork burger is a blast of flavour. Worth the visit for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8if9XADRVYyrnfEKTWV_1gpS6bbTtxjeBQuxR"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"chris chase","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuX6-71WVtLmKsHl_KPVSM4TS8D5_1GmcCuzvJM7I5SxHvOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An excellent cafe with fast service, fantastic food and delicious coffee. Dog friendly with a relaxed vibe. Seating is available inside or outside. Even when the cafe is busy food arrives quickly. Highly recommend 10/10 will be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karl Tattersall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_UKnkcDJdIuobALddfWnOpguU-nYyQiuUGm4RiM7PMnQUR3m9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a nice joint! The chicken in the chicken super salad was super tasty, good coffee and the vanilla slice... cor blimey! Can I move in?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOV1jC0tz17l4VqIEvugOz6Py_0aMTyP8PluouA"],"When":"2024-2-6"},{"Name":"Susan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPmxUf-nGBvrB7R6hBnlDWAHxEPhVIZeq8uTQ73t8F5CGS2p8_Dw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a busy little Cafe with a great vibe. Tucked away in the suburbs so no noisy cars of the city. I counted about 8 staff members so that gives you an idea how busy and popular the place is, and they were the ones I could see. Staff were happy and friendly and took our order as we stood in line which made getting our coffee much quicker 👍👍. Do yourself a favour and grab a great coffee.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMssHXryufutMEfB5th61uBNuULdJMt8hXDUDG1"],"When":"2022-2-11"},{"Name":"Brightone Nik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWqlWLiowRjxIqSLwTNAH3a9h0HM86SGSNb2avf0_dXp3RhScK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Number4 bus corner #Ryland & #Rossiter then short walk. Noisy (bad acoustic). Large coffee creamy and smooth (4.5$). Hollandaise with salmon and spinach was tasty ($18.5) but not memorable. Friendly staff, efficient service, clean presentation. Popular with locals. Relaxing outside setting. Good for Sunday date short walk to nightcliff shores, but no views.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOz0oUEIAwxbwuqm3yVz6YWIzA40nVVvBkWmih5"],"When":"2019-6-15"},{"Name":"Frederic Meyering","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqONzSln52uBiWF4rHtDw_cScyVmA3IKJbZ-UnKHDDRR_9uWIntg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There was a good range of dietary variations on the menu from the humble bacon and eggs to Tempe burgers and very good coffee. I was impressed by the speedy service. Being new years day and arriving during lunch hour I was prepared for a wait but my coffee arrived within 5 minutes and my Tempe burger probably 10 minutes after. There was plenty of staff and friendly as well. Very impressed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMMKmJv_SQCcO0D7feunmhmHXajr8suOYn2wpK"],"When":"2022-1-1"},{"Name":"PILAR GL","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6bpdxmgTRYrOSQ_TXaKs2apa9MvGA-usLoIj_zo7D2KhwAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My breakfast was absolutely delicious! The special mushroom toast with rich flavours and the ice coffee was the perfect combination. The owner and the staff very friendly. The atmosphere very cozy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQDWfwUhEIKgvhOPsvlEwN8u3vTgCBkiazXFfi"],"When":"2020-10-22"},{"Name":"Pooja Parikh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtEamqP-TdCyTXmwbCe-a5VLoyR1WivkG1pap2mXsYWgojT1yU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden gem found!
One of my friend suggested me this place and it is truly worth it...
Being a vegetarian very rare places serve good breakfast and lunch.
Must try the mushroom and halloumi roll...
The super salad was great too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPY3guW-ki__wwsZpEdiMDImwQHX2x2Ktn3r_Qg"],"When":"2020-7-16"}]

[{"Name":"Jiali Guo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1BGZojklUM5W9Uo7yjnP1oDVmyIvVFfDeuwVoHUCQxj0Neg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"KOPI is always go-to place for me on Weekends. I love the coffee and super friendly atmosphere in here.
The only suggestion would be that  if the veggies in Laksa are fresh instead of frozen ones would be perfect! ( in May)

I am not sure if they saw the comments I left last time, but they had totally fresh broccoli today!!! It was fantastic!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvPRxO3kXJDr0R4_GpMi18ZuKUwORjHX6An5yt"],"When":"2024-3-29"},{"Name":"ReyN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDaSaG5vHOa04jf0zYw0t7_RDk1wgq7XS0yC-LTHtEtEeHWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ever since I moved here a year ago, KOPI Stop has been a comforting spot for me in Darwin. Their coffee and food are always delicious and the staff's positivity brightens my day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaL7OPFiOf5HmlOjytuuQtdjX5R3iJER0V5lQ8"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Maggie Dong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkOieoqVaizTowfZXOMc-9TSrTZuG0c_mGU2dzMO8dfK_fAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"KOPI Café is truly a hidden gem. Their coffee boasts a rich and robust flavor, their curry noodles are exceptional, and their cakes and pastries are authentically delicate with a hint of sweetness. What truly warms the heart is the enthusiasm and sweet smiles of every staff member, exuding a genuine sincerity that resonates deeply. Each staff member, friendly and supportive like a family, embodies a passion and love for their work that transcends mere profit-making. 🌹🌹🌹","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYyUJJ37vzrYtCq7j8exQOZ09rJPpyfGggDnL3"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Polly McGee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAHSIMHLHETWVirlJeBiau6Zi4dope3ZjgeE6K1lTs1PmfvsA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"KOPI Stop is EVERYTHING! Highlight of food in Darwin, every Singaporean dish hits the mark perfectly. So great to also have coffee at the same
level of quality as the food. The coffee is Ona so it’s good, but is expertly handled by the baristas. Everyone who works at KOPI Stop makes you feel welcome and invited to the not so secret society of makan makan makan! Thanks for making my trip so delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvpWtJW6jJWI32IS_SUTMXfLtJJa2WN9djsup1"],"When":"2024-2-17"},{"Name":"Ben Rowland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVV9v1-2TzmcigIihm-ClVmHTVcVFEgPT1gx7Ts1KprDkGsc4Fdqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is our favourite coffee shop since moving from Melbourne. The staff are super friendly and put a lot of effort into preparing high quality food and coffee. They also make my new favourite breakfast (Kaya toast)!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8opHrqEd5kM5QT-rIzYRZKa12ISfqK247tNnS"],"When":"2024-1-17"},{"Name":"sithara dilnuwan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIAv1pBkY-DSC5xKSk3cdp3df_QRZy1FOozEF6wX-qDLBVm8oF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Do not buy !!(Malaysian BBQ Chicken Jerky)
Just wanted to let you know that this was a terrible product and smelled really bad once the bag is openned. Paid $29 for this and absolutely  disgusting!  Loved the coffee and the chicken wrap though! Nice staff as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPq7oyZ__B9wd_hLULRTpMbgs3j5EGpBYovVdVn"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"Valerie Q","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnFNNmX5lKBZPsu0t05nMbl3raCSLyv9guL0f4zPdqtVq84DjF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always make a stop at Kopi Stop when i’m visiting Darwin. It brings me back to my childhood of having a kopitiam breakfast and kaya toast. Delicious chicken rice too! (generous serving)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPNnNgTsyRbmhnOnnkfavvCagLbNrXQ8lsPTb0"],"When":"2024-1-26"},{"Name":"C T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaU92h9-1OVEHFGRsJfxQJ8rNIDhL-YyDWG_ypWUkzVAMMUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We popped into Kopi Stop for lunch and ordered the chicken rice and laksa. The chicken rice was delicious and savoury with the chicken cooked perfectly and the soup a perfect accompaniment as a tasty palette cleanser.
We also had the laksa which was well balanced and fresh. Probably the best laska we have had outside of Asia.
Also ordered a coffee and milosaurous which were lovely.
Friendly service and atmosphere. Would definitely reccomend as a must when visiting Darwin.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOco3HmEZtenUSGomYpQyGOz_Pl8LVBQwNZE9Ru"],"When":"2024-1-19"}]

[{"Name":"Jack Gomboc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqZqNRjm0pyCCTRkvhqf09yqswQQPWri2_1gO0Pan_GySu0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place. I have worked next door for 4 years and this was my escape place. Super service from all past and present workers, too many to single out and mention. My only compliant is seeing a handful of customers can treat the lovely staff whom are always smiling and cheerful despite the busyness! Like my coffee today, I am sad to no long be “a regular”.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOegZWvJZVyO6Z31walbEaJuxwqoS-Vt-9EEUuk"],"When":"2024-5-3"},{"Name":"Hai Minh Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4dfDRHaZ3Mh4SZBK5KFGvlZl-mdBA7uQZBpB0O6W8sKPAA4Xw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Coffee here is great. I have tried it twice and will come back again. Haven't had a chance to try the foods, but definitely order some next time. Service is excellent, very friendly staffs. Location is at the corner, so very easy to recognize the shop.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwboZx2dnhsE4izTu1RGsxvzQATjg7SLhww8U-"],"When":"2023-12-30"},{"Name":"sonjanan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL24IKDzhNXOXCMe5JuqlmBucIEAoTiZnGRVwL1W7s9uDDn3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Laneway Coffee is just the best in Darwin. We had a wonderful breakfast. The atmosphere was great and the service amazing. Definitely going back there. Thank you Laneway Coffee 🙏👏👍🍀","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYWZ0j-QDH0uN8VmdM87wix_bNThsUd3evGk_b"],"When":"2024-4-5"},{"Name":"Gisella Galloni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxUJoMUgYj_Ts6EYjjQq0uHJ5Zi_6P401mChkHX-zi8Eqk4D3k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best breakky ever!! And service is great too! Would love to have this place in my city, but nice excuse to come to Darwin again! Thank you :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYrOGCK4M7EXla1c2Ahw4o7AlNFOswWQ0DL96J"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"Craig Marquis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdC--0G_qS2o_9ccdtn_i3wzwgNe9uMFHwSfkRQN6VNrzUiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic food, especially the poached eggs with bacon and mushrooms, a large enough selection without having an overload of selections. The coffee was the best that I had whilst in Darwin. The Staff are very friendly and the service was prompt and accommodating. Justine and Emily were very cheerful and looked after you with your meals. Although it was a little noisy it added to the atmosphere of the Cafe. Keep up the good work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeanne Lamp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqS1a9VnzybpQfhW2oaMh7HZK-edJP1b-YEbOwN9MgGSoBFaSj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good single origin coffee and freshly made juice of the day.
The food was delicious - we had the Heirloom mushrooms with added poached egg, and Eggs your way with their award winning Gotzinger smoked bacon","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPr14oDapVJEAFzK1Y73oeEhgIAfUqSGvEx8TGx"],"When":"2023-10-13"},{"Name":"Hendy Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIBT2Y1vmgc-273amh1utbRW8SY3c7sCQpIIThs4ZnumEXr58=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Coffee was good and breakfast amazing with acceptable price, but the service was outstanding. One of the list have to go if visit Darwin 👌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6PzNY2m-P_opyEGHG077DAdaG95QDWO9Zvpo"],"When":"2024-4-19"},{"Name":"Culinary Palate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYS1x07OJyLncOkflZMcjyVe8P2uJFcch1l3B5IhatTeUVeuY1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It’s been a while since I’ve visited Laneway. Last time I was here I left dissatisfied as meals weren’t very filling and was pricey. Not much has changed in decor and setting but still looks cosy and busy.
We ordered breakfast and waited a little bit. My partner was surprised how delicious and colourful the meals were. Coffee and fresh juice was great too.
The staff were attentive and accommodating. The only down side was it was a little too pricey","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPN7Zqq9qa9did--bfQ4WsjtkExnF3q9Qkf3k9G"],"When":"2023-8-11"}]

[{"Name":"John Stacey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLv0Wv1GPrFAT6KxEM261PpZ8iYiFywKqM308Z5EQNm2Vj2ag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"2 locations - one in the Mall (lots of outside seating) and one at the end of Smith Street near Fish feeding/esplanade end  (that is bigger). We went 7 times in 10 days for coffees, lunches, breakfast.  By and large all was excellent. Great coffee, salads and chicken schnitzel. Home made. Friendly service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kay Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXqWs2EyJR5c_RnalgtVMbxnWJyflw_YN9jEgfK4BDyJ8P9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really enjoyed our brunch at Cafe 21. The menu is extensive, and the food cabinets  are impressive. The staff were very friendly and polite. We had open grills that were large enough to share...very generous servings and nice coffee. Appreciated the air-con.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUepHaWyHikJ3HGueUqseqP-7DyjsWAeVh7ov5N51_vDLklNXDX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Perhaps I came on a bad day, or maybe we just ordered the wrong thing, but our meals weren't that great. Firstly, I dont really understand why the egg was served ontop of the sandwich, the aesthetic looks cool for picture, but the practicality of it made it awkward to eat. There was no sauce served with the chips, maybe im just silly and should of ordered extra, but I kind of just assumed there would be sauce added to the side already like they do in other places. Thats my bad. The burger was quite oily and although it didn't taste totally bad, it's made us never want to come again. Im sure its a great breakfast place for other people, but we genuinely didnt enjoy it that much. Im sorry.

I will say however, the drinks and smoothies were great. And I remember eating a chicken salad there years ago which was delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBUAhq3WpiBDetAhoEZ98loaKPCIrizv4_2lXT"],"When":"2023-4-30"},{"Name":"Ca T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQZP6aL8kKrYwDlfN9O3ut39l3ezGgXW1ViVVaEWKDlXGNbLuM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Lovely spot on the edge of town. Always great food and good service😁 you can choose from the menu, the counter display or build your own sandwich.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiRBQCs2RAwFTEzjTTTnc5C_GQ8g6kI6qyR3tE"],"When":"2023-2-23"},{"Name":"Jonathan Haslett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8enPx9W_SwNediu_Ku-imso9PL67a9zeBtOgx4b_0enIF1wgweg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Kitchen actually closes before 1:30 p.m. on a weekday so don't believe what they say with the opening hours.

Spent all day trying to organise a lunch with my grandmother at her favourite restaurant.

Once we finally got her inside we had to then start packing her up and go to the cool spot instead.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brightone Nik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWqlWLiowRjxIqSLwTNAH3a9h0HM86SGSNb2avf0_dXp3RhScK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Popular with locals, this is a great place for a lazy Sunday brunch. Large clean venue with modern appeal and efficient friendly staff. Service is prompt. Carpark available, no Wi-Fi. Freshly baked sausage roll (6.5$), bacon egg roll with coffee combo (9$ !!!). He desserts are dellliiicious! Walking distance to city, great for business or date.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_Kl3AlQvtORB7Rx-HLhGU6HcVKALSybsdkU_G"],"When":"2021-8-22"},{"Name":"Lauren collette parker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWv0rspJdOPkRh0BX-cJL1EbTt1AfYkfRAIZ4V31R0s5AC8Y6Np=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"After requesting no nuts or sesame for catering due to severe allergies the catering provided had both in (see photos).
when I called to make them aware and come to a solution I was met with hostility and told that she doesn't believe there are sesame in there, when I was looking directly at it, after trying to impress the importance of what and why I had requested she put the phone down on me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPP9y_TbsWJeU8JxdBEH1vY9sudtP7sZhv6_Uic"],"When":"2023-3-8"},{"Name":"Hunt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1ucyHXuE57MypfDacEFLUBnxFVA3l2W7-JGArTaT-LpAqPEsV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I don’t get the point of the egg on top of the brekkie burger- just makes it awkward to eat.
The entire thing was just oiley and sloppy without a real flavour beyond grease and bbq sauce; Darwin has so much better to offer than this. Go anywhere else.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGQmppc_pu3kElCxjM_wNZXGnFaiB--yFcfiPQ"],"When":"2023-5-29"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Tiffany Zheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnlIqRI7nu4CmOmqsLEbIYNoH9gnlYg5xy7K_WYKPQzXo7et23=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I think their breakfast and ambience is one of the best in the Darwin. You can see that the owner has put his heart and soul into the decoration of this place. The dining area is divided into indoor and outdoor, and indoor there is a children's room where kids can play games and draw pictures. Outdoor there are free bread for diners to feed. Overall, very recommended!

The only drawback for me is that they don't serve a bowl of fries for breakfast.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhe5vvG8tv3HBq76Ak0Sb-mW4q24hCmOfXd3lv"],"When":"2024-3-23"},{"Name":"Tania Paraone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQiTxhK3fuKfjgdtNOalu9iyux1I1veFpBzvbUfLFvj_-iFqgf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been here for breakfast 6 times each time has been a great experience for me. Invite people you care about to join you and you are sure to have a great time eating , laughing , sharing stories. While taking in the environmental free gifts. Such as the fresh sea breeze, the visual feast of the sparkly greenish blue water, the sight of boats floating on the water, and the fish who choose to visit. I love The boat shed its my favourite place for breakfast in Darwin. Next time I'm there I will take photos. I've been having too good of a time to think about photos. Oh and the food! Always satisfyingly tasty!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Derek Jemerson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKNfD82eA5ygXqsaG-Etz5QzdfUmXEwQM6m9yAIRIPHfFxyg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I had the Fatty Boomba breakfast, it should be called the mediocre microwave or the Bain Marie mix up.  Toast was cold, everything else was either greasy or sloppy. Only positive is the eggs are good and the meal comes out in a flash.

On the plus side, the reason I gave 3 stars is the staff, absolutely top notch, great service, friendly, helpful and cheerful.

Beware the large coffee. They’re not joking. It’s a soup bowl.
The coffee is good.
Atmosphere is good, relaxed and easy to have a conversation or just listen to the music and chill.
I recommend coming for  the coffee and the service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0JTXStPdF4VWX_UyaiWhzZXIxx0ycRkb1S1k_"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"Phil Langdon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5KoMNc7ky6H831tuLE9VhwaOF_wol7mtbQsQlcd5GaWp1r8M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very nice coffee shop at the marina.   Sit inside or outside watching the boats in the marina.   Coffee is good and the fattening cakes are delicious.   Good table service.
I got an eggs benedict which I thought was a bit exxy, but is was very big and filling.   Delicious thick shake","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_u4FBByf8CTXt7obYsjl_MQjCXHEgTTOg4Qa-"],"When":"2023-11-16"},{"Name":"Tammy Grimsey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ34rqFR4GHk31MA2JoCS21bRYK2Zsmr9tL6UIYK_ewaB3EFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a fabulous morning coffee and breakfast here. This business is very popular so patients is your best friend. But once you have ordered the services is very prompt. Beautiful views over the marina even fish feeding is an experience in its self.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stuart Hamilton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWlMAO6ffuK663hAjUUZOo8l3EeHyRhziriZxWqnzsDUm3Mw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been to Darwin for the V8’s the last 2 years. We stay in Cullen Bay, right over the road from Boatshed Coffee House. I can’t recommend it enough. Sensational coffee, lovely breakfast’s and tasty lunches. Fresh squeezed juices and just spot on. Feeding the fish with the free bread is fun as well. It’s relaxed, great food & coffee. Definitely worth a stop for brekky or lunch. And special shout out to Jamie! She is the best hostess!! Fun, friendly and a hoot!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dimity Cottle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzy4I2gw5TdEQzt6BfpuzDWJhT5OYWckvmdJqK_hbAHLmASbb2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Great location but unfortunately had a very negative experience when visiting for breakfast. Friends' meals came out in good time - I had to chase up my meal and by the time I got it, it was cold and my friends had finished theirs. Staff were friendly but not overly concerned about customer's experience. Disappointed as was highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Jayawardena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMSQlEGN8aJppo5mjaImVkBIlXQt1ZSQHPNaLF65kuFWaJyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Wonderful atmosphere. Highly disappointed about the food. After visiting the place for more than 5 times last couple of months, highly disappointed about the food. Not worth theprice! No complains about the coffee.ordered poached eggs see the pic. Bread was stale.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjfWqkQkgCmh2UNFXplpl_YZF4GD5UvLVWbJXT"],"When":"2024-1-3"}]

[{"Name":"Zoshna Pariyar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKSkM5GwT4mDb5ElE446d_SUj417cq3KHvMEqoJ-vTP8nuIGw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing coffee with breaky really enjoyed it zucchini taste horrible but everything was delicious loved it 😃","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9tgSLg9iAe5K0chk7OIBA6MyNPb1POAZbuK51"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Odilia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoDAYJJ-92fMRZbS5JIzO6hkOI5SmPEfPpZXB8EVh-6OChl5I1iQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Attended TFBC and once again experience was exceptional.
Breakfast was the occasion and they did not disappoint.
Food was amazing, staff friendly.

Great service, coffee was good and their fresh Lemon 🍋 cordial was refreshing. Staff friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObI3jUS6nWeox1_uCmItgKiPWuLuJPKL8owVbc"],"When":"2024-1-13"},{"Name":"Claudell Goodrich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk_imppb2-19Evb43HeHmjmTlna1S4Fk1upzjY41ei8EKoh0hjBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome spot, friendly and efficient staff.
Breakfast was exactly as I wanted and came to the table  surprisingly fast. The parking area was minimal. Quirky setup that gave a sense of space and privacy.  Prices are top end. Positioned with ocean views.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNr4yuphQRNn06E-OW6EpIvGbLvDYVfoU2QlmSV"],"When":"2023-11-24"},{"Name":"Donella Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSlQ9h9Q7E-gqDi4igI5kCufJTktnIxpuCG1abSntJ6z7ZFreL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Extensive selection of tasty food options .. generous portion sizes .. friendly staff .. nice location .. absolutely recommend The Cool Spot .. it will become a regular for us in Darwin","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYgO29yWKXsBitFOT0mqkxWeeGgNQ3jjhEyQjN"],"When":"2024-1-13"},{"Name":"Britt Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLU9dnP01cBtcw1cBzauHc3FLXfrYkNE9OFSI_9BesqQifJ9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great location overlooking beach, great layout, and fit out. Despite being quite open, it had enough corners that it was not super noisy.
Menu was extensive, good df and gluten-free options. Lunch was divine, chicken & avocado open grill with delicious salad & chips, yum.. i would return for that routinely! Sandwiches are good. Juice & smoothies were yummy, too.

Service was friendly & fairly efficient.  The only reason I gave it 4, not 5 stars, was that service could be improved. Table service would be an improvement. Also, when we went up to order, we were enquiring about menu items & she was not super helpful. The food was a bit slow coming out, but service was ok, it just seemed rushed (it was busy). Table water.. filling jugs yourself was a pain.. can they not be prefilled in a better container? This took ages, it was a very slow filter, gave up after halfway.  Small matters, but resolved, could make it a 5/5

Overall, I enjoyed our lunch & would return.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Barrows","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_3oQ5jqhp7X_xfOdhTP0vpjlkRYXSUTdN12gVmh6Uc2_ArJMcUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Hark, what tidings of the new menu's arrival!
'Tis a day of change, with fresh staff in attendance.
We hoped, nay, expected, excellence in each dish,
Given the prices, a king's ransom, in sooth!

Alas, the service, slow as winter's pace,
Did stumble, and mistakes, like autumn leaves, did fall.
The meals, a feast for eyes, did promise much,
But, alack! The meat, o'er-cooked, did lose its gentle touch.

The parmi, hamburger, steak burger, and taco, too,
Did suffer from the heat, and emerged, o'er-done, anew.
The seasoning, lacking, did leave the taste buds dry,
And the meat, tough as old boots, did defy the knife's sigh.

The knife, a buyer's tool, did fail in its design,
Unable to cut the bun, let alone the steak's fine line.
And the ice cream, gourmet-priced, yet flavorless, alas!
Did leave us wondering, if the kitchen's magic had passed.

Yet still, the coffee and cakes, a saving grace,
Did bring a smile, and a glimmer of hope to the place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFHNkyzRDeH9S4TIxepaj3JwAX_I7HNxcZNdy5"],"When":"2024-5-5"},{"Name":"Culinary Palate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYS1x07OJyLncOkflZMcjyVe8P2uJFcch1l3B5IhatTeUVeuY1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This cafe is located on the top end of Fannie Bay and is a favourite among the locals.
The service was quick and easy.
The big breakfast was filling but the cheesy potato hash was cold and only received 1 egg instead of 2 eggs.
The Halloumi bowl or vegetarian bowl was a disaster and disappointing after eating most of meal, we found a piece of ham on the bottom.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxUZ7LApMEejldxhmSxDbzfuCi0a7dEy82bmVu"],"When":"2023-7-27"},{"Name":"Lady Bug","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYyheV-aiJ756eECyukhOMb64Iq3qOksaHckbECbtlu03QKW4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We have a love hate relationship with this place. The food is sometimes on point and other times disappointing. Not great with amending orders and try to add on surcharges wherever possible. Not like cool spot I’ve known years prior. Good aircon and I like that there are private seating areas around the corner.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alishna Maharjan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoH1E24jGy-cvUk6k5ZGL0CnXnFsWdztLd1BfL5-jQX4Teh0hwtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely love this cafe! From the moment you step in, the cozy ambiance and welcoming staff make you feel at home. The food and drinks are top-notch, with a great variety to choose from. Whether you're looking for a quick coffee or a leisurely meal, this place delivers excellence every time. Highly recommended for anyone in search of a delightful cafe experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoudwqkuqHicrXYoe3DnkIEdcFOPimD4dwUAtk"],"When":"2024-4-1"},{"Name":"Culinary Palate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYS1x07OJyLncOkflZMcjyVe8P2uJFcch1l3B5IhatTeUVeuY1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cafe has established itself as one of the most popular breakfast venues in Darwin, with its great selection for breakfast/brunch/lunch menu. In addition they bake their own delicious breads and pastries on premises, if you’re lucky you might see a stall around the local weekend markets.
This versatile venue also cater for evening and weekend functions.
Can get very busy on the weekends if you dine-in but takeaway coffee and pastries is quick and easy.
Chilli scrambled eggs is my favourite very filling, full of flavours and satisfying.
Friendly staff, good customer service and great coffee.
The juices of the day is a great alternative, if you don’t drink coffee.
You could easily compare it to a trendy Melbourne cafe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_kIFxWarQHs8_jhDVC-xNi24ORojSwQ-yAakf"],"When":"2023-7-27"},{"Name":"Phil Langdon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5KoMNc7ky6H831tuLE9VhwaOF_wol7mtbQsQlcd5GaWp1r8M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Large coffee shop in Stuart Pk.  Good coffee, large choice of cakes and fattening dishes.  Banana bread heated and with butter is very nice.    Service is good and the waitresses are attentive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpY_ZiLTryCHY-rlqNLbIHHleHl5po3uOR8D1z"],"When":"2023-11-7"},{"Name":"Rich Kendall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQlJHiH7dDLq4Gi7JxKpBrjUov1Mi5fJruGnp2MlRoYonq5diRIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"By far my favourite eatery in Darwin and I'm blessed to have it literally around the corner from home.
Friendly staff, great coffee, awesome tunes and a menu that caters for everything.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKPtbYcfqK9uSFEQ6xne70V_9i9V-NAMllh87p"],"When":"2023-7-18"},{"Name":"Zack Klein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWf1fyQdCCoqfyV2YBRT036G9_-Olr78fh7nyl5yprN50XnN0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a great place.
3rd time here and thoroughly enjoyed each time.
Great coffee and food.
Water service was great, was greeted with a cold jug of water and glass shortly after sitting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPLy0ZF5BPuQsbVlkk3aLu29OwsWlSwNCa0qIW"],"When":"2023-12-17"},{"Name":"Sarah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlogpuvhvE_3ox9wjGtwtZOX8im7ARZxEh5GpUWwdJpx1jwCfp0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great sandwiches and coffee! Such a yummy breakfast and really well priced. Had the bacon, egg and avo sandwich, only 14 dollars. Well priced and delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNX7fM3Rk2kz1KUMuIMdS9beBc9nGzQyuC_FdIC"],"When":"2023-7-18"},{"Name":"Dilhan de Silva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLasSpy2c_ONsqtcL5OfGeJA3gXLL2m8YlpVGZLlrmOwhsLHg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First visit to Sweet Brew and it was great. I had the Okonominyaki (got the vegetarian option) and my partner ordered the Chili Scram. Both plates of food were delicious. The pickled ginger in the Okonominyaki balanced the whole dish and the flavours were popping. The Chili Scram had a good amount of crab and the sliced red chilis gave the dish a good hit of spice. The croissant was one of the best we have had in Darwin - buttery, flaky and melts in your mouth. Coffee was good and excellent service. First of many visits to this place!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM36KQKBMDOaLwn5V6nGcHuj_dRH7KvBwSwjoPD"],"When":"2023-6-24"},{"Name":"Sevi Donlon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXPWA93DeSfi_hqvndkfQ8kd9r0SdBM7TMmP4GHMPA9vyF1Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands Down - THE BEST - dining and vibe in Darwin.
I don’t remember the last time I was this turned on by food..

Service is also exceptional, staff is gorgeous, groovy and super friendly & I’ve already planned my next choice for the start of next week!

A little slice of Melbourne here in Darwin 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlE1wRdSLhKy_uzfIoqULH3oj_2Ia-E8ZIL0XT"],"When":"2021-9-30"}]
