user_reviews: [{"Name":"Laura Stone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDegxfw8l2ttoYjwnA4FJmysKWWoa_Gp3iEPgnVyFnqz0SuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been in Darwin for a week and this was the BEST coffee we have had. The food was also incredible. We are a family of 6, visiting from Sydney and we all had something different. The customer service was 10/10. They split the milkshake for the kids and gave us extra fruit for after our savoury breakfast (which were all delicious). The atmosphere was lovely, too. A five star dining experience in a relaxed cafe style setting. We couldn’t fault it ☺️ It was inside Parliament House, so we went though security at the entrance, which the kids thought was fun, and the staff were all really friendly 🤗","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_MUQQCznWN_6TiyIbvWuvZ6wP15a3TIsr8wyp"],"When":"2024-3-14"},{"Name":"Rebecca Lavis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAOBTdSNno7aycndL_khMULkUqjKrrIwfZk4ka0SEdrfYPKIF6oA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely service, delicious food and a spectacular view. I habe eaten here on multiple days and not been disappointed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zelia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvDbH_wQx9_56bePX54WyqZTyhEI1qEclVX7mZODqXRHXv3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious deli fare, excellent and friendly service esp from Flo! Great atmosphere with view. Second visit in a week!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsq_WXdSnHh8WQEHLp2c2yp0R150GThoX5pjpO"],"When":"2023-10-25"},{"Name":"Grady","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFH9b-NzHIa31WR6xTVFOqGhj4TiDQGbfKuw0j3nwb575TBm6F=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Friendly staff, not unreasonable prices, decent food and pretty good drinks (coffee is a bit weak so order an extra shot).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOR5JacOoO2cQfP4NpUoanGkiJ4aPTZf7LmXnBN"],"When":"2020-9-11"},{"Name":"Lee Thombley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCyjO0INOJZ-0GTH4goAlKFSGz3W6DE2VswROjACp55LAUPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small cafe with great outdoor seating in the back corner of Parliament building.  Very few people when not in session. Two small scones with jam and coffee $8.50, but food in Darwin is generally expensive. A fountain provides nice white noise ambience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBOe4ytHpyRJWKrTYshAk-wcyC4csbS2BTGRhN"],"When":"2019-4-16"},{"Name":"Josh Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbZETqBs-3Kf_ML7Fc3o0i5o2vZUISn3IPoinWSe8tOTAgCBc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely little spot! Enter through security at the parliament and walk straight through. Great little cafe with great indoor and outdoor sitting options. Food was fresh, substantial and excellent. You can see why Karen has won some significant awards! Had the smashed avo, long black, croissant and some toast for the kids.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBFBMXypALAdMR2FZkmY4JrROxEc7NmOcLYnMd"],"When":"2022-9-28"},{"Name":"Nadia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVx7iYWuptbHJEFxqt0rI_XFBs99GWWpWKg497N5SQEDGXOfiYL-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It’s quite expensive compared to other cafes around town but view outside is super peaceful. Coffee was decent","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqki3CkyiNNMlD5VqHQOlmrg2KSFUlxMU4vQfC"],"When":"2022-10-9"},{"Name":"Rolf Nilsson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2ZTdlwTC1cKgJLheGytWM61agH6EfRaKKP76xqxwLWGbnUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Darwins best kept secret cafe. Don't let the Parliament House security checkpoint put you off. Those guys are friendly and helpful. Go through to a wonderful hall with stunning views and fountain as well. Then go to the corner of that hall and find the best Cafe seats with shade umbrellas and with an unbeatable view over the harbour, manicured lawn, great coffee, good food and no crowds. Go figure!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Alyssa J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrrSrbPMMwABgQKgbpPHbABtje66cuoOLPL4Y4u8D2gzhFag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I walked here for the picture of the pancakes with fruit and ended up getting the avocado. Zero regrets, had no idea what I was ordering but the colours on the plate the flavours and the textures were all top notch. Pretty sure my juice was also fresh squeezed. Happy surprise :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbU7UoUzD_3ozC3Yti3xRLh9oFVaEGSlFguPpm"],"When":"2024-5-3"},{"Name":"Ally VM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4HcEyKTSLpXhQisQm3H08VXck89rsqXRp-1k_TSnMfSxptw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a customer of Dukes for years and I have seen it getting better and better. They keep upgrading their menu and aiming to improve every time, the presentation of the food is amazing, staff are always friendly and welcoming. The head chef has done catering for a few of my events and the results are always outstanding. Do yourself a favour and visit Dukes Cafe!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLIZfzV9XNPdVGhV8ZoBOYQOuokltej3iTmvle"],"When":"2024-3-10"},{"Name":"Being Goh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfQlMg5hqAHSyVdpIaqKbRp0YPrq2-cK8y6J81hIJwj0vXKcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Walked past, very happy with my mini egg Benny and great coffee!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN54shzCjihg93QySePrvchG5VHH-43hL7KIl_z"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"lana banana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNYHI5qa6by4AqnjMmXcPc1gKf3ZEIVwYDzbIigda42iVIVTlJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"paid 10$ for an orange juice!! and only got a cup the size of a small?? i understand times are tough but this is ridiculous. The juice was tasty but only lasted 4 sips. atmosphere was so chill too","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxx1e1-JycTEOnI_iJU4zD5LdN617jRxq--BZe"],"When":"2023-8-30"},{"Name":"Scott Lusted","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnE8Tn_jrxBdHH2HhUdER38o5eoPf0-iYIcpU64_rTLDKLA_-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"$13.80 for large (really a medium) coffee and a very thin H&C toastie.  Average value. I was going to eat-in but walked past uncleared tables that were fly-blown. One girl delivered a single coffee to a customer at a table beyond the mess and returned without clearing... also with a sour look on her face. Bad training and management. Coffee was made with a smile 😃  but whole episode soured the vibe.  Finally, need more non-egg selections","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKyX-GN0Hvr4GGMmh3zemgZqAO1vuhqjigD5uP"],"When":"2023-6-17"},{"Name":"Fantastic Avi and shubi YouTube channel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVduU1h0DkiOU_Rmt6jH9Q1xFdO4lUZ9DnxGQ4EUKcEWdeU9vFKtA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The enjoyment of any food is observed by empty plates.. we finished each and every crumbs of course food was great and friendly staffs.
We had great Anzac day breakfast at Dukes cafe+ eatery","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brightone Nik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWqlWLiowRjxIqSLwTNAH3a9h0HM86SGSNb2avf0_dXp3RhScK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wi-Fi available, ask for password. Coffee delicious but a little mellow. Staff very welcoming and friendly. Prompt service. The eggs Benedict with ham on soft toast, spinach and light because but spicy sauce is scrumptious and reasonably priced, so is coffee. Walking distance to centre of town and main bus stop. Great atmosphere, different decor, good for date, must try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvGUXZB1vXtCFlzuTGK0QwDwn6cmKrUkO9f5dB"],"When":"2020-5-22"},{"Name":"Zoe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2MDHfrox5f-D28Cs8WSPdtw95agEpsYbHM_1tYd1eZY0T-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Came in for Lunch 12:10pm.

Customer Service: Excellent, FOH was able to provide queries quickly.

Order the lunch special - chicken parmi/parma with chips (chicken parmi doesn’t come with ham thank goodness). Wait time for drinks was long at all, about 2 minutes. Ordered the banana smoothie - it taste delicious with cinnamon (an ingredient I don’t usually put in when making my own). Asked for the wait time for food - 10 minutes FOH said after checking with Kitchen Staff. Nope. Waited 30 minutes. Got my meal, chicken parmi had ham. Not happy now. Chips were yummy, nice and crunchy with chicken salt. The chicken was moist- thank you.

Overall I rate my experience a 3 out of 5.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4DIL9F3S6Z2s14tI8tlH2LQSKafg5S_65yKFF"],"When":"2022-7-25"}]

[{"Name":"Phil Langdon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5KoMNc7ky6H831tuLE9VhwaOF_wol7mtbQsQlcd5GaWp1r8M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very nice coffee shop in Cavanagh St.   Good choice of breakfast and lunch.   Coffee is good and the cakes are fattening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPd05UVfZWVrapWIMkDlviqPzeJsQ73_wk6cIF2"],"When":"2023-11-10"},{"Name":"Narelle Standen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyHQuu39JnXg1gP1jfkA1oeqZVF3EbK9JA29r1RdIZ9OgyfCyP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We had the Eggs Benedict. Food was okay the hollandaise sauce was so salty. I felt like I dipped my mouth in the ocean. Great atmosphere. Loved the plants by the balcony.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVmDKRJMYPftN4L-_-dXAnKEX5vpiDEj3DvL4P"],"When":"2023-6-9"},{"Name":"Justin Ngahere","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2Hb23nc-n-XL9ur1qAKmkcZ9VXw4LNpOMbT0mod0Bcm1YBftY3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice friendly place.. a good Cafe, ordered the big brekkie. I Recommended it, ... nice coffee
all round excellent","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kitchen Insider","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCa9Ovt5QTHL0DFA-hZiWxc3dxpx6guwo0qDkwdf2HkVfd3mxp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Coffee only: super service and well made coffee...do you know your arabica from your robusta? No, nothing to do with Syria or Dolly. The arabica bean dominates Cafe coffee while robusta is cheaper and is in many powdered sorts... One big difference is the caffeine, higher in robusta. If you're still reading, I raise this as my heart is still on the precipice of arrhythmia many hours after my coffee. Yes, I have a double shot daily. From the slightly empty mid palate and my hyperactivity, I'd say there's robusta in the mix here... just in case you do or don't want the meth hit it brings.
Geez coffee is pricey in Darwin!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjJWDBZBX68JUwKm1UFPcF7NrOh-t5HuozZzXG"],"When":"2023-10-6"},{"Name":"Charlotte White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrVM4Xc4BPH5vSKVdN52r8t-xh1xMJBzm0F4cZboihQ02Cnw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great cafe, quality of food and coffee was up there! Portion sizes were on point, value for money
Lovelg breeze when sitting outside and all shaded, inside seating also available","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel Fuller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMaTfddUs2Vo0T7gnRR-RjJyycyAsv2vczGUtRhWG_hB4taA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered breakfast and it was soooo good. Plenty of food for the price and so tasty.
My partner said his coffee was the best one he has had since we arrived in Darwin.
Thanks!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMbmPM0HKpdzmsTF-1laGpYCqP_2hOufJOsQzS"],"When":"2022-8-26"},{"Name":"kritika soni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJM_GQJpkaq1B5GD4sYOSuqM5YzsmZsiRCqyhH5pKO2Q-2ACg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Superb Coffee ... The place is bizzie but worth a wait ... I normally don't drink coffee or tea outside( prefer making my own specially in the morning - to have parity between water coffee and milk if you know what I mean so it's not too milky or just flat taste but this one has the perfect taste aroma to kick start your day) I donn work in city but whenever I will b around will always wish to drink their coffee even thou I m a tea lover...","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nim Ja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOVUilUaqKOOtU9gLPACsfSuumEwS1tOAZRz96S9F9kmQTwwLU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Unfortunately I was too excited to drink my coffee and only photographed it post quaffing! Make sure you check the specials menu. The other day I had a very filling Hash Brown Brekie, where instead of bread the eggs were served on hash browns with salmon and hollandaise sauce!

Today I had a savoury mince breakfast. If you're are after a small breakfast the half breakfast is perfect. It's literally have a breakfast: one egg one piece of bread etcetera.

The morale of the staff here is high and they are all friendly and efficient. It's a pleasure to see a place obviously run in a supportive and team oriented way.

The Roma Bar is an iconic Darwin establishment. Midnight Oil even mention it in their song "Truganini". Make sure you ch eeck out the artwork around the place. I love this place and always feel happy after seeing the happy staff enjoying their work!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyutZv8Ri8hh9kuG360Vz3nyxlzM_BlJmKbO28"],"When":"2021-3-17"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"HoiC咀叼叼","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4O7q5yd5-GsbnKTk5zisp3FZYN1Ao7XKdIgby62TxdJu367E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice place for coffee as their coffee is so good! We had lattes and it was the most tasty latte I had so far.

Food was okay but only the dumplings were not the type we like .

And the staff were really friendly and nice :) I would recommend this place if you want to have a nice Sunday brunch :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNL4ikVipN3nYujW86PJqyNf3-WgkQiQXtfORUt"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Mighty Brown Mouse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGIuoP6N4PQ_e2zFBpnqnYEqrEdrV1E8AjuNUPBegdeehijQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The name wasn't that appealing but a look at the menu told me different and I am glad I gave it a try.
Walking inside the tiny little place was like walking into a European Cafe/bar, very quaint with knick knacks scattered around and the back shelf crammed with homemade pickle jars.
I had the Ukrainian style borscht which I found was made of chicken stock instead of beef. It was pleasing and am returning for the homemade dumplings.
If the weather is nice, take the outdoor seating so you can people watch as you enjoy the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgWr_L2FWVu9_iuNslngc6cE6lGiPzSnt-Zbfc"],"When":"2024-1-18"},{"Name":"Rahul Rao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVedQl4I2-k8QgL5C01UxsbKOsQZ-8fgImoU9MHX9BvOQ-lEtUMUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brilliant food. The host is so friendly and funny! Makes the time spent here so good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAdW2aYLmsag2KtxpWXWINyRdx9pfv7WQJaX7p"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Inna M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIn-btQsserkFQLRKWFNPQlLH1XRGPSXEL7_45RIbEjdcVow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I found this place when went to the Markets and very happy about it. Had the most delicious breakfast and will be definitely back for dinner. Thank you so much for delivering a great service and a great food. 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSTdzZ3E6yO36nMyNfjzN3-sSIj_o2iK9GHVSR"],"When":"2024-3-3"},{"Name":"Sadia Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAwTiYHwndtRbnzQ-LDLMLAB8Z9mhk5ZixL0JxrKIDYZKsuJrZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visited this spot after seeing google reviews . We came all the way from Canberra and wanted to experience something different in terms of the environment and food as well.
The owner, who reserved our table, was incredibly welcoming. The cafe's interior created a fantastic environment and gave us that unique to Melbourne vibe. The food was not only amazing but also reasonably priced. The shakshuka was perfect, and it turned out to be our best breakfast experience in Melbourne. We're definitely planning to come back; highly recommend this gem!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5yD-X5W4A_c4IHHOS5MpuFMNrdw9orMzU1nNq"],"When":"2023-12-28"},{"Name":"Dani L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMPxBqUp2UxRTA-XQOrraB2hUMU4CKu_5xg9MEa_8eWKeWrg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Found this hidden treasure!!! Such a lovely restaurant, can tell from every corner every wall that are full of dedication and passion. Indoor and outdoor seating are both lovely, the menu is full of surprises! You can order those typical cafe breakfast but highly recommend you to try the Polish dishes! The food was presented with perfect plating and the right portion. I was so fascinated by the bar and its wall of jam/ fruit. Staff members were amazing, very helpful and friendly, all of them seemed to love working there!
Went back again for dinner, mind blown by the authenticity and quality of food, we were recommended to keep ordering and sharing the food so we can try more. It’s definitely the way to go, we have had so many dishes and they are all perfect!! The vibe and environment is perfect for a date night with plenty of drinks to choose!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbGbe7VVIWMcRQB26IrxRR9kTsk79C7C1bn6S-"],"When":"2022-5-26"},{"Name":"Roza Janowska","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmMuzoSIgELm2_izbptzfQjLdR6yoyFXIKxKGWp0SJiRTlHThh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best European restaurant I’ve been in Melbourne! This place reminds me of my childhood on my grandma's farm in Poland.

Perfectly balanced flavors, they really cook with passion.  I recommend Russian dumplings, “bigos” and white sausage.  Excellent!

The owner is chatty, very professional though. Everything was served on time, we also had a great chat with him and learned a lot about the way they prepare the dishes.

They have wide range of bear and spirits, not only Polish

I am delighted, I will definitely come back here many times!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJwmO8trPtFCohaC-F3C7tk9o4BTLpXV1kCTRe"],"When":"2023-1-23"},{"Name":"Andreea McLaren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw86cOHPgGQUgjkjSsL-S6lc-DVVqANJs7ONbj6AhNziVusKpR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a lovely lunch with such friendly service and the most delicious and authentic Polish food!

The owner was so friendly and we had a great chat about a few dishes on the menu. Loved the vibes, service and food!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGjz2LaYJ9t-pIdT9sBxtm5oh6tBflQSFOg5tK"],"When":"2023-6-10"}]

High quality and authentic flavours. Will definitely return and highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQEKyfRI8GcwbiLgKJ6-ZWmElmPzdnfwn2DEcY"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Dillen Selvarajoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0AqVnD-fUP4OT8KY-qwLoMWyIB6pSLIborQmPMhQuhWn1pCU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great Thai food with authentic flavours in South Melbourne! We had the fried chicken wings which was super crispy yet juicy inside. The Tom Yum (Prawn) soup was done right based on request for Thai style spiciness. We also had the Pad Kra Pow which was flavourful and a great portion. Service was tops! Will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAth_IJRKqV3w22RCO12xOsh4oMhA4GgdILwyK"],"When":"2024-1-14"},{"Name":"Abhay gopi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1z-wc2c3QpNw_8Dt998EZaM3EGBjcodEJ-iBpfVGdX0Vrl22j=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’AM GONNA BE BACK..!

Indulging in the offerings at this place was an explosion of flavors in every bite. From fragrant curries to sensational fried chicken wings (with Thai herb mix seasoning- Laab) , the culinary journey was a delight for the senses. The harmony of spices, fresh ingredients, and impeccable presentation showcased the chef's expertise. A true haven for food enthusiasts seeking an authentic and unforgettable Thai experience.

I’m really gonna need to get back there sometime to try my hands on rest of their menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTd0NQhbzlgp_EPj_UR8eslCK0sZP4c-HRV0rV"],"When":"2023-8-27"},{"Name":"Lore Gutierrez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB9lI1dYTY6ANoT-7Vjw0vlvA2J76BhSfM81b8_n3qgeGw2qxjxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down, this Thai spot is a winner! The pineapple fried rice is a flavor bomb that’ll have you craving seconds. The vibe is cool, and the staff are super friendly. Can't wait to come back for more tasty dishes!
🌟🌟🌟","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNG3bdeDUXOx6wHjRJkZbunbzqfaRaAc1Soy5b7"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"OH Ginny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLc0tBPs4CIdAUKW8_l6J7TlPPN2ylxLu6OJUa1kJyHxMDwAx1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice food ! Bit hard to call staff (to order) if you sit outside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSX7tj0r5IxERPWdg4bZzjTPUer519p0oWhY_u"],"When":"2024-1-30"},{"Name":"Heidi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdkfqZRHddzpPRUpPEn-Wb3pUJCE14_-lwt33fmPq3ICf3-iCE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was the first time we came here and we were satisfied! The space is full of sunshine (we appreciate it much in winter cold days!). Staff is friendly, food is good. We ordered tofu salad, tom yum soup and fried fish. I strongly recommend tom yum soup, love it!
If have chance I will come back here and try other dishes 👏🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNu4GAnuqiYGMjO50M5cKenrRBnCHWXR_VHSWls"],"When":"2022-6-15"},{"Name":"DD Melbourne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeZdH8QBxyUuBb-VfQeUl0VNaU6Z6mZuLKPy15C3di8SOOgp6lFg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The restaurant is small and cozy, service is fast, friendly and efficient. All the food are big portions and full of flavour. Parking street is convenient and easy to arrive. Despite this toilet is just next to the kitchen, so that's not really convenient for customers. Anyway this restaurant is beautiful, for sure will come back soon","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Payam Fazli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWokwubwFZNvweciaNyRklQ1DhVQewN69eN50H5a5nX1rlqH_KS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Super friendly staff, great range and amazing dishes BUT hygiene is missing. There was a garden insect in our salad which meant that the leaves were not washed properly. There was a big bee/hover fly flying around our table and there didn’t seem any measures in place to control insects.
The staff are really nice and cared for our needs.
The food is delicious and prices are reasonable.
But, hygiene is so important that unfortunately I won’t be visiting anytime soon.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Aishwarya Dongre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZrNQZBI9XwQRzlAy1mPHGZIdvPtZ9ZAgbI1LNvwqfrJxmGM2x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I found the experience to be decent overall. The concept of offering fresh pasta, pizza, and drinks is appealing, and it's great to hear they have vegetarian options available. I tried the vegetarian pasta and the pesto pasta with garlic bread and potato wedges. While the overall taste was okay, I appreciated the generous portion sizes, which made it very filling for one person. The variety of sides like garlic bread and potato wedges added to the meal's satisfaction. Despite this, for anyone looking for a hearty and filling meal with plenty of options, Etto Pasta Bar could be worth a visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPQhrC7P_GyQXezSlnNtuf--CfsEuA-1OAbUeg"],"When":"2024-4-3"},{"Name":"tiffii_c","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWId58jZaWrig0PBJslYcNVegejS5N6fNhv87A94bAXRk-W6B6r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love how the pasta is made fresh in-house and served with delicious healthy sauces. We built our own pasta dish with our own choice of sauce and pasta. Delicious Napoli Pizza made in house too. Delicious classic and healthy Italian cuisine ! definitely recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8KkozineQjgKJQp3Sq5XRkd0hnVMcCeaNffLv"],"When":"2024-1-28"},{"Name":"Linh Doan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9bl8o33wvN5G4PXWX2rjijqtyFJ1KMW6_v81Odq4r0koh08k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"pretty nice pasta. I add mozzarella cheese and it’s so good. the pizza (3 cheese with mushrooms) is pretty good tho, could be better if it go with the honey as a sauce. big portions, friendly staff. food 8/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlnDyj9QZOqbGgL7wh_rKLNyth4vU9z-bri_bc"],"When":"2024-1-9"},{"Name":"Pragya Gupta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc-pLR_zguKwzF2CG9ziUjzIIA39xiqMY9AuaPWoLSRLfsRH5e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Get your Italian cravings sorted @ettopasta 📍various locations.
We visited their South Melbourne store recently and tried all the variety.

-Pasta / ravioli
- Lasagna
- Pizza
- sandwiches
- Milanese salad
- Cannolis

Everything tastes amazing and is prepared in no time.

We definitely recommend you to try out @ettopasta
BON APETITE!! 😊😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0V6NCx01HChLrLj3nBvAVhfayh7EN6eTTN8Uu"],"When":"2024-1-14"},{"Name":"Athena Tse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDLFpbErBHeETrgFAvIU2R3TrMv-QbyaeqKqZlyiLdW4mofZW3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The serve is small but the price is high compared to other pasta shops doing takeaway. The taste was just so so as the ingredient and sauce are not enough while the pasta is not fully boiled. On their website, it said $16 for bolognaise as they charged me $21. Across the road, Patony Pizza restaurant was selling much more tasty pasta with bigger serve, more meat and sauce at only $17.
I will never go back Etto again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYcLSXxaOtbSg3RTi7Q4G_9zOqvx2u8rrAvVLT"],"When":"2024-1-12"},{"Name":"Angel Khong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUclkqITYfc7Hb5-vgjuDeacBepTyuu5kLvxhAdtl1YqD-OIEdR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had their bolognese pasta and prosciutto/gorgonzola pizza. Both were great comfort meals (though I did find the pasta more filling than the pizza); pizza base was crispy, sauce in pasta was generous and truffle parmesan chips was deliciously crispy. The venue itself was not the most comfortable - the chairs were either too low or too high for me, I’d takeaway next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7H49WRY-qSu8FslFUwvFaKXkSuZPnwiVR4QRe"],"When":"2023-9-13"},{"Name":"Gaurav Vithalani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeK7idfHgu_mj3-1uX3VPqoOQG2BQ2PwXU_uK3nd9d1sKoaiM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The service was good but the pasta was very under seasoned, the pizza crust was kind of chewy. Overall wouldn't recommend going to this place.

Edit: Changing it 1 star because it turns out the lack of seasoning and chewy crust isn't a mistake, it's just how their food is according to the person who replied.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fulvio De Vita","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbgHpNKrTAPgTfouZ9RoqprD5BTquo1yx8Uc7uPSeNi7q_Mg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"That’s not the way to cook Italian pasta at all, the pasta is too soft, too white and not enough tomato or meat or veggie to mix with.

Chips doesn’t have Parmesan and truffle oil flavour at all.

Croquette and mozzarella sticks acceptable

I feel so sorry how can a place like that can say Italian food and is not even close.

Never again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmDAenxSzPTXb1EKBIAHJscNwyz4-3li3xMvtW"],"When":"2023-1-14"}]

[{"Name":"M O","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJWyj27diLZVT8pZdwSaQc0xR7VlzXbDdvOjwAjo574Tghgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s very nice and cozy space. If you are sick of eating meat, I would highly recommend you to go this place. So much different types of fish and different style of cooking! Also their prawn is good and if you are going in winter time don’t forget to order clam chowder! Their tap beer from Germany is must order!!! It’s sooooo good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPB1SP1fhL1yXqrDskSRp2bZJeDnmlbpcgmrmDP"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"Tess Scully","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdI80p-VLIIjRb1qv6Z6cr5IgivjmBcRryp3MejC7Ye0tAOZ8EYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best seafood places I've ever encountered in Australia. Excellent seafood, live music, reasonably priced extra dry Italian prosecco for those who don't like sweet prosecco. We ended up having a bottle. Succulent, fresh oysters for $2 each, we ended up having 20! Real king prawns, sweet moreton bay bugs, beautiful stingray, you must try the middle eastern eggplant. Mmmmmm!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWschYxISYQIrrKCliyr593hrLL83yBnWZYoKo"],"When":"2024-4-20"},{"Name":"N Marriott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmMxFiPg9_r32bE6ciZpVaKJW8bbk4gv-wpZoMx3PhmObQRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great seafood and atmosphere. Had a live jazz band in on Mondays who were fantastic. Ginger mussels and king prawns were beautiful. Chargrilled. Foccacia bread and good German beer. Quite affordable for 2 beers, 2 glasses champagne, olives, bread, chowder, mussels and king prawns all come to $130. Very relaxed atmosphere with good vibes","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBLZAFX_s_2-j6c10RsS3hziEPIDFFtigJqiMl"],"When":"2024-4-29"},{"Name":"Pikuan Susanto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTfk6GTFGxMcRWQvx9bSmq-NdAFHlVJ7xvdwUdn3KuDwU00A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Coffin bay oysters were fresh
Grilled king prawn with coriander sambal: prawn was fresh and sweet. Sambal was delicious , however I prefer plain garlic grill.
Green lip abalone: grilled, quite tender.
Lobster tail with sumac butter: lobster was grilled. Sumac butter was interesting.
Marinated field mushrooms: outstanding marination. I'll order again.
Octopus pintxo: octopus was chewy, tough.

Service staff were very good, explained the menu cheerfully.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFQ8gGQRmzFOBfPLGfQZT-xf7_R4HoJwia2l5Q"],"When":"2024-4-14"},{"Name":"Charlene and Ronny (Fitness Foodies)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzmw9UDsD5isHrR7ARD6-HRqJH0vx9M35mieydr3B9woLP75wmqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The seafood peddler outside serves up some quick lunch bites. We ordered the ‘bread and fish’, which is lettuce, parsley, sumac, onions, and a trevally fillet in a tossted Turkish roll. One roll with two fillets, and one roll with just one, as it comes.

Fish was grilled there and then, and the bread was also toasted on the grill. Flavours were great and a good lunch time fix. It’s a relatively nutritious lunch when on the go. The chilli sauce however needs more chilli, not enough heat. But other than that enjoyed it but it’s a messy feed, so take a few napkins.

We sat next to the peddler on the bench seat to eat which was fine, but the restaurant really needs to sort out its cleanliness for their peddler stand outside, needs a good sweep (from all the food droppings next to the grill and stand, and the bin needs to be emptied more often from the empty boxes overflowing. Just a basic tidy up would make sitting outside more inviting and pleasant. But anyhow. Sandwich was good, so grab and go and enjoy the market.

Can’t comment on the food inside the restaurant so this review is limited to the peddler and outside atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlwkR18zzCKfFkIyvdVSxPbinCfhAhq8L95PO5"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Michelle Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUuFNSWzjeY9w7rDhFSJAUTZTaqDwl9f414_k5YlKWFPGpD7UK3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Nowadays I think an email booking system seems quite dated, but that was the procedure listed on the website for Claypots Evening Star. I emailed January 24 for a table of 10 on February 15. As I was booking for a group of 10 I wanted to be on top of the booking. In the following days I called at different times, again with nobody picking up.

I messaged them on Facebook on January 30, and they responded a day later saying “we do not take bookings”, despite the website saying “book a table for 10 or more people.”

I messaged on Instagram, also on January 30, and got a response on February 11 saying “we don’t take bookings for less than 8 people” and explained there were some issues with the telephone.

I finally got a response to my email on January 31 confirming my booking.

Come time for the dinner, food was overall delicious, but considering we went across the road to Schnitz for second dinner as some of us were still hungry, the dinner coming to about $85 per person was not worth what we paid.

With all the stress that came with booking (I had 9 people wondering if the dinner was going ahead!) and leaving the restaurant with less cash and still hungry, I don’t think I’ll be coming back.

This experience was a shame, especially as my time at Claypots Barbarossa was a clear 5 star in comparison.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwvB6J91NFDDZCfCoFBa834p5GHWhZR-GcM6S-"],"When":"2024-2-15"},{"Name":"Mo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJolVgilBBriVRZehZQWUcuMcWdPai0mXvEPhf9qvHzqZaIh0_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Recently went here with a group of 10 and was appalled by the service. We sat outside and wanted to use 4 small tables so 10 people could squish in. Originally, the waitress with the dyed blond ends pushed together 3 tables for us but refused to add an extra table because she claimed all 10 of us can fit on 3 little cafe tables. We ended up pushing another table for ourselves and all the food we ordered and people barely managed to fit on 4 tables. The food was decent and some dishes made up for the poor service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_V7mR5b0y5FVqwI2FfBPPj2fh56JQE9Qq1Dv2"],"When":"2024-2-25"},{"Name":"max koh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdor5LPFbYXL-zYEj9LcDhmmMJQOZWI9rUlZkS2LopSSQiFA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I really want to love this place but i simply can't

The good: the food, the pasta is like their best seller.

The consideration factor: price is a bit on the higher side.
A bit slow on the food even during less busy period

The ugly: hygiene, sticky table top ( very sticky and gross even after a wet tissue wipe down by me )

Broken dishes ware. This is a big big no no! It was serve in badly chipped ware. See picture.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRy2IYkBmBa9G5JsnuBKdpweossZ4LU339RW9c"],"When":"2024-5-29"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Maybelle Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPPk7d2WnI4F-nUPuV0WDB6uTTBvBBZIRLaE89U8LNwSK62iXr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried on a few dishes for a company lunch here. The cured fish is pretty good. The flathead is great, not too fishy and plenty of flavours. Charcuterie is a little salty for my taste but the sausage rolls are amazing. Very attentive service here, didn’t really the wine was filled up util later.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOJb10agNveaP73Rxpa4JJh6pW1za4q9JqM8dk"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"Andrew Barrotta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUUCG6BJdr9aROUzBBvph0KkOpvNhuz-TjEBzUCZUdkA0dnmwC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here a few times, never disappointed. Quality food, Excellent service. Steaks are always perfect.
Will be back whenever I need my steak night fix, keep doing what you're doing, it's beautiful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPELMFs7b1aZ1OWBs7rzAPudVrReufv72PZXnxQ"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"Mo Bamba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqSxznJEsc3leavl2dSTL-o9TONaBewlu1E2WDqPxynoNM0JWH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered the $25 steak special on a Tuesday evening. It was ordered medium rare but it was closer to medium. A little light on the chips and the salad could have been better with a bit of dressing or pickled onions for acidity. The offer of different types of mustards was a nice touch though.

Still a nice pub to have beers outdoors when the weather is nice ☀️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMp4_r5VL1S4L00_ppomOA7_QHVCUgWVcp7nG-L"],"When":"2024-2-6"},{"Name":"El F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwVghnnTK5eg7pOobTQ3uCUrUwMIAwYrA7HYlZMVH8RB6WDP2w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice quiet pub off the main streets of South Melbourne. Enjoyed the ambience outside and the historical feel inside. Food and cocktails were good. Really enjoyed the three cheese croquettes. Everyone enjoyed their meal. Didn’t realise the salad leaves would be so bitter even though the menu did mention it, so I put the leaves to the side. I love beetroot so I still enjoyed it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_jVCkYdw_8TrrtlJjdLpxeR40Jt9flU35zK1O"],"When":"2023-2-25"},{"Name":"Jan Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI25KG5VHtBflIW_oO1LAMmPNvlo20gKtvL_24S2N2qXRre0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice bar and restaurant in the neighborhood. Some oysters had slight fishy taste to it. Overall, soft and plump. Fish and chips was delicious. Batter was just enough thickness, fish was fresh. Hostess were attentive. The lack of one star was just the oysters. Will recommend to visit for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRJ5GLqNXxuALVVwgL-mNJOjHNabVxGThxIdBB"],"When":"2022-9-22"},{"Name":"cze low","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_3dTSyD_ZVOgc1YjQ93sD2fPGZ_sJ5b-4rQODLErAY_lzV2rT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice ambience, small restaurant,  booking essential","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhdAUtTfQ-O1Gl8VxWOWEBnZnzIA0q32ktl715"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Mary Answerth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdtPb7ZVwtm5SVQgwT16_IUuck6QJafYbM-t5oNjof8aAZUUUG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"So disappointed how this venue has changed. We have been here on many occasions not so recently we thought it was a go to for good food great staff and atmosphere. How things change. Manly the menu. Menu not clear what your ordering. So went for a chicken pie with vegetables.  I could have cooked better at home plus my side vegetables would have been apt least warm not cold. Won't be back unless menu changes to something the average person knows what there reading.  Staff also couldn't answer my questions. So disappointed. We used to love this venue.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Jiang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXA0fdRYQC0HLoNRmNNHVpVLIA4dSFIibZSG7EWDoF_zPae61yP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great service, we had the 1.4kg tomahawk steak between 3 people. MUST TRY! The steak was very well cooked and came with 4 sauces. Sauces could do with a bit more variety or choice, something with mushroom perhaps? Decent wine selection, the portion size of the fried squid dish was lacking. Overall a good experience and will be back to try the other steaks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIEWXnuNZNMTHwX352gILVzv2tOhvC9J-Fm3_C"],"When":"2022-6-18"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Dilek Toygun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjdKw1JTYrK2WNGFVukmy52PXyOMkO83VLYAQhuLVdSV_G7AvE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yes i love Grill'd, though even more when it's done on point! ☺️
By far, the absolute BEST, juicy, ingredient filled Grill'd burgers we devoured 🤤
The team here were certainly pleasant, and the kitchen was pumping out orders, without delay 👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVQVzMC_IY1eOOVhVvccLuqyg5WqveW4ixhisC"],"When":"2024-1-24"},{"Name":"Maria Belen De Giacomo Zoppi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX79jgZPYjeQ9l4RbrUvIXAxGkY8RtXMfa5WOKor66t43HKB6P7CQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I’m really disappointed, i was expecting more. We order 2 hamburgers with 2 sides of sweet potatoes and zucchini. The bread was dry and without flavour, the crispy bacon wasn’t crispy at all and the zucchini was oily (pictures).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3QzQAKP80j43zgVtDq6Tb3pCWGQ-EcptSGy2x"],"When":"2024-3-18"},{"Name":"Angel Khong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUclkqITYfc7Hb5-vgjuDeacBepTyuu5kLvxhAdtl1YqD-OIEdR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered through ubereats for lunch the simply grill’d, summer sunset and chips. Burgers were flavourful with juicy patty, loved the pineapple slice in the summer sunset. Thick cut chips were not well seasoned with herby salt.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP19q_xQUET3SwJXLzqu9cmM7SLGLu2l5nOtM0X"],"When":"2023-12-4"},{"Name":"Ha-Dieu Ford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOXrySmIV5otI-QASg9FgDyowczO7c4llRZ5SJzEhqNMnFp78d=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"All 4 hamburgers and patties were cold. Seems like they’re cooking in bulk and leaving patties to sit for too long. We let the team know and they did offer to recook but we didn’t want to wait and shame they would just serve these patties which had been left to cool for too long. Chips, sweet potato chips and chicken were right temperature and stayed warmed as it should. Be good to see the team get the burgers right.

We’re regulars but from another Grill’d location.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gopi Bala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7ZzaudFcbdAGlKH6kwZCFzR8Me9ksnqE8OnLeAzyXe9hGDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered the chicken burger and cheeseburger with bacon.  Both burgers were delicious. This was dinner on 11 October 2022.

The fries were also great as was the service.

The only issue was that the restaurant had poor ventilation and a very strong meat gamey aroma.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4lfwRqEjguqypaOSHwD2VTmdKMOGO3KSXwKHo"],"When":"2022-10-12"},{"Name":"Kurt A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNs-pBetr-mFZsKwH7SuErcE1o7bbgJ3Vwek9NyHlsfTrRO7S-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Grill'd venues around, particularly after the recent refurbish. Staff are always friendly and onto it. Food is always fast and fresh no matter how busy","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joyz Lio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXB7mWcllam6Wxt1mqpXgSO495SWGSz7yaeBGLmiKvT8PcVma85sw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered 2 plant based burgers using the 1 for 1 deal. Grill'd burgers don't disappoint, always juicy and tasty. The zucchini chips were tasty but a little too salty for my liking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBn1K0Ait2h2Eq-CxbuVzdf0Q_PuHJnWUhuVzP"],"When":"2022-7-18"},{"Name":"Philippe Lemarchand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLibZqAGVn4Z4o-QynWm8Mwi_cRCXML3wHh_jXCOthrtkfCww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I give it 5 stars because it's definitely worth more than the 4.1 they currently score. They do make an effort to offer you more than traditional burgers.
Burgers were tasty, good sizes and at a reasonable price. As they give the expectation of calories it is really good if you are watching your food intake.
Got the potato fries snack size with herb mayo and those were really good. Good herb taste, salt, not too oily, crunchy outside and soft inside but not too thick so it has a better consistency.
Staff and space are friendly.
Toilets could effectively be cleaner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqimkKEoo0QiyRex8abxNzWSoy33iicjRC9nSC"],"When":"2019-11-15"}]

Went there at my 14 year old daughters request and it was a great choice. She had the chicken burrito and I had a regular naked burrito … yum yum yum. My pics don’t do the food justice so give it a go. Good honest food. Happy to eat there again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsfiqmmuSzwZEqr6sXCvs8ji_0nwozV3iRnTEW"],"When":"2023-5-9"},{"Name":"Kat Peacock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRr8y6FwMnMWbAijjEM_a658xFN0sx5ZT2Gh7lRb477wL_TiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just a shoutout to the girl working today (27/06) at 2pm. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rudrabhishek Bansal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlgGhzdk91FAS5jJuYjeAY7SECHIJkz-cr-p_gX5fQRqdL-QSP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"GOOD AND HEALTHY.

You can mix and match from a variety of options to have a delicious and healthy meal.

Service could've been better though.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"samantha taggart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgZZZPtyrSQbSMc9bKPDvtn1bJdR7f4EiC6Rypox3UQKIkJLU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Got a burrito and burrito bowl, paying for our food found a dying cockroach on the floor, half way through food found hair in burrito and the stuff look unhygienic. Sadly we love mad mex but  this is the first time at the south Melbourne restaurant will never visit again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diary of Life","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAmdjz8a6zk5pjljF5PmE-_bvvcJ3KzyWis1SMsVg0Wcejuq-R=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place for a quick and tasty Mexican meal . The ambience is accomodating and welcoming, with Staff that are very friendly, providing fasrService.
Definitely a place where you can enjoy the taste of Mexican fast food with a Touch of Tex Mex .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgERzIc5rKMMDkS4YjRb3uAq5tN83ENSMjuAqL"],"When":"2021-10-24"},{"Name":"neha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJp4pB3SnXtkfpolO2xQ7zLTJF0TluV11Y6JF9MolLAxlmZOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My son did the order burrito  but he put the chicken it’s smell very bad not fresh .After eat the burrito he  has too much stomach pain and start voamting.I talk with manager but  he  give me excuses for  council came here before two weeks but council didn’t try your meat and bread. i suggested never  go this shop.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Amelia Tan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLo5TBjc4Yx_zrQSYU1KyzD59durxKxSa2ypusiX2vfZtB72w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If I could give a zero star I would. I ordered through EatClub for takeaway. I picked up my order and walked all the way home to realise they got my order wrong, they gave me the curry laksa instead of the omelette. I walked all the way back to the shop and got them to swap my order. The man serving me did not apologise for his mistake. I got my order replaced with the right order and went back home to eat. While I was gobbling up my food, I realised there was a bug that looked like a cockroach in my food. I am never coming back to this restaurant again. Please clean the kitchen and have better service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMq1vwG2mbidz_PxRPgcooHeW_1oLa9301-ZrLH"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Z H C Kong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhAwLkQ-HrHX15-D2jnYKBgoKDNpctVqvCUEpd2cxElKYxTbw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant in South Melbourne is like a home to us, with all their staff including the kitchen crew mingling with us like a family. And yes, we love all their Malaysian dishes as always.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjR-4lXB4j8fwFDqrAIG-l3oOx_YdyibqiCuMn"],"When":"2023-12-14"},{"Name":"Sam Soo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPRBtKoZC_upWnhXj9tEIqsbgtiiOPH3qBh5BnG3CPAIFaklnW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Reliably good Malaysian cuisine with a pretty extensive menu. Then all walking on the floor.   The idea of washing the floor is that it’s clean - and usually you should smell disinfectant - which was not present …. Anyway I guess they need to check the cameras for 820pm onwards and see if this is as per the Nando’s franchise handbook.\n\nThe food was good.   The service not so much.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZy-N6hgyqhjCvVoGXJQmmvEwxF49PoGh-bWU3"],"When":"2024-4-25"},{"Name":"Dipti Grover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrxaYU_POsu5VA7uDUukLgToEMvDImhkplI3wvdou2TeJbNAa9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The chicken was super yummy... as well as the chips were crispy... overall delicious food. Reasonable price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNnUthunl4GA0SiA7D07e5QiUTEMlSFUTdNcBtl"],"When":"2024-4-6"},{"Name":"Shirley V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeApfuiswtpRavj8DYI0U-QCfrkXTiMl-HB5zrgx0YhamLZf02=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered Beef Pho and prawn & crab spring rolls. Pho average and meat a bit tough. Spring rolls was good and crispy outside","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhvAvULklnCK9Uhu8BFrM7HWWmh_SepxYPIdwE"],"When":"2024-5-3"},{"Name":"Tommy Lim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_pYKfvDDmKILoiI1EhIcS_e7HRJ9zSqCiLFQD9QiimE_KZYwzvw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered from Ubereats and it arrived fast. I love the beef pho. You get a nice umami taste from the broth, a slight sweetness from the beef slices, and a refreshing taste from the herbs and vegetables. The Shanghai pork dumplings aren't bad either, but I wish the skin was thinner. All in all, a satisfying meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvcF-0NV-x3jbzDQRRyaPJZV2QaC-2N85bbE5y"],"When":"2023-8-15"},{"Name":"Debadrita Ghosh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkLqa9r-twziLnBbR7bssWJIv3f7EI-gR2lD7he7Aza_53gkfGVg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The location of Misschu is incredibly convenient, just a stone's throw away from my place. Situated near popular establishments like Woolworths, Aus Post, and the Goodlife Gym of South Melbourne, it couldn't be more aptly placed.

Upon entering Misschu, the entire ambience exudes a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The staff members are exceptionally friendly, making you feel right at home. One unique aspect that sets them apart is their commitment to providing refreshing drinking water to every guest, a delightful touch that adds to the overall experience.

I have had the pleasure of trying various dishes from Misschu, and I must say, I am thoroughly impressed. From their delectable dumplings and succulent pork bao to their flavorful salmon noodles vermicelli and refreshing chicken salad, each dish is expertly prepared with just the right amount of spice to suit all palates.

In addition to dining in, I have also availed their services through Doordash on numerous occasions, and they have consistently delivered exceptional meals right to my doorstep.

Overall, Misschu is more than just a restaurant; it is a haven that provides a cozy atmosphere where you can gather with your loved ones. Whether it's a casual hangout with friends or a family get-together, this place offers the perfect setting to create lasting memories. With its convenient location, friendly staff, and mouthwatering dishes, Misschu is undoubtedly a must-visit destination.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYWN2iehgE_tELmdTCnmcPBYD3bgAymJiqvgbg"],"When":"2023-8-23"},{"Name":"Madeline Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDhF7Uk06rERfZjJ0mL9mr3s-i785g0yRNPOzJaB32jlxVYIP-uw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bloody delicious 😋
Will order from here again.
Ordered Uber eats and price was good , food was yummy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBbir9Z5LHi4e60Wncwm_He726W0QH7dXK-81Z"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"Black Mamba535","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYR5s4kwgdwi28jpIJpiaRtkKxM-ivwzzHPM5ylT5eAiKMsA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great lunch place with plenty of vegetarian options. I loved plant based 'beef' curry and mushroom soup the other day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBPLUKAImttxOSmQPfk2wGQhlBrjkh8_Lh3Vfh"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"J H (jawz786)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3u4ywRqoc6T1yjK_aFdRaEq8IgP4kbdBj68_egTWOUf50bpFdgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First night in Melbourne after a 20+ hour flight we were too tired to go out for food.

Got an Ubereats from here to the hotel.

Food was very well packed but missing utensils despite being requested (necessitated a request to the hotel for cutlery).

Everything was very tasty and large portions. Food is good, spring rolls were very different than what we are used to in the UK Vietnamese restaurants but were nice. Did work out quite expensive though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLYkHcq70lWLY8KL-Z2ctVlZjulP0sbBIda2M9"],"When":"2022-9-9"}]

[{"Name":"Konni Starr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUigBZSAtzZGUda377-GnSpGroidlMg6RLarSoo5svVg06wXayAcg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything was cooked to perfection, the beef brisket was really tender, the prawns were juicy and fresh.
The only thing was that we ordered the beef rib thinking it was going to be a rack but it was one piece of beef that we had to share between three of us, we were given the impression it was able to be shared.
Other than that we could have ordered more because it was really yummy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-w3RKhVWJ2vgmbiVfolRjm5R1diC2QeXIPjyt"],"When":"2023-12-19"},{"Name":"Mark Donovan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcN9ywThDz2wla7zV1ERYZPdBZIQamKUE9Jhj0Ka_qNL5bJK8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amongst the best service I have experienced in a very long time! Great food and very tasty beer too! The spud fries were perfectly cooked and the meat itself was superb! Will definitely be back! Thanks for special birthday treat too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPp2PBhag-jQlzu-6HKV8V-AG7ObEAFHWJRSUg"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"Ellie May","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsbkcLSNVEOK_ecETyNj41-n18ryh7OZuLfoClOZp-W6RthVNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was absolutely amazing! We loved every bit of our meals. We got a mixture of meats and sides to share it was perfect. The meat was beautifully cooked falling apart/tender and the sides paired so well with it all. We had no complaints at all, was very well priced and the meals came out super quickly as well. We most certainly will be back and recommend to anyone in the area to try!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOZe4rbYfUEPWYCGH8ffvmwwAQUALmkdhBBs5Z"],"When":"2024-3-27"},{"Name":"Min Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFDdREMheaumKfYIYBchxgLj5yg4YRFWbRfacdFdEyQ2OF5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at a remarkable restaurant that left a lasting impression. The ambiance was warm and inviting, creating a cozy and relaxed atmosphere. The ribs were cooked to perfection—tender, succulent, and beautifully glazed. The menu offered a range of delectable options, and the attentive service elevated the experience. The attention to detail and commitment to excellence were evident throughout. If you're looking for a restaurant with amazing ribs, enchanting ambiance, and outstanding service, this is the place to be.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9wmj2GN_pHNTncRwCjqr7MAiH85BFk0eJxqGK"],"When":"2023-12-4"},{"Name":"J “Ryan” C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWQq1WTznh66FxGqD26bYsGYGX1ZywXw65o5fmcIPsK-EtB4Qm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you're a meatlover, Meatworksco is a great place to visit.  I enjoyed catching up with a friend over some burgers, prawns and ribs; all were tadty but I inhaled the burger 🤤  freaking soft buns and delicious flavour.  Service was good. I liked that the waitresses didn't come check in on us a lot.  The place had a casual atmosphere with some banquet tables for big groups.  The seating is quite packed so may get loud when very busy.  Prices are on the higher side. Overall, recommend you dine in at Meatworksco.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvYh5Zv7iLK7pegfXC1MNFae1_3NNwthFdQ9s2"],"When":"2023-12-30"},{"Name":"Leo CJ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUY3LoXvT0QyJHNW4HWmPBt37M-p2BmaEUR4L1eTwxT4b-U3jgI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A gem found in South Melbourne.
Food was delicious, abundant and with their pun special touch.
Special thanks to Philip that made sure our drinks kept flowing and for helping me out with my special cocktails requests. Excellent customer service and knowledge.
And the German waitress.. omg se was so kind, friendly, professional, cute and smoking hot😅. I'm sorry I forgot your name 😬, but we won't forget how well you took car of us. 👍
Bravo team, way to go 👏👏👏
Hint.. that's not an Aperol spritz, ask Philip 😎","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvbEwAmorrmhaoP5D7U-hRQ7Cb3KSQF_GM0LXC"],"When":"2024-1-28"},{"Name":"Saige O'Brien","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWx1H-XdawEfKLvjkYwOF-GCAMZOwH3pAShoauwcP3E6FPr9Fc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly service. We enjoyed the platter for two which was a great cross section of the meats.
The steamed greens could have been more on the crispy side as they were a little soggy but I am a big fan of crunchy greens.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1wczaN_GQXMn0RMHZoalZNJkUTfwLtZYRyV27"],"When":"2024-1-30"},{"Name":"glen InMelb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIncRZ6xTmb00QkmMqI7gls0gX7W1fgERl2jRtQPtYMPWYPSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome BBQ platter for two. Great service. Highly recommend if you are a "carnivore" love it ❤️. Even better than the original Texan BBQ in the good old of USA. Crowded on a Saturday night.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSOrt9U9MhRVoS3CYb8yQJHeigAaSB6pWi5jZv"],"When":"2024-2-10"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Mo Bamba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqSxznJEsc3leavl2dSTL-o9TONaBewlu1E2WDqPxynoNM0JWH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious and affordable food!

The fried chicken 🍗 meal set was around $20 which includes a side of soup and a drink. Be very careful ordering the garlic chilli unless you can really handle your spice! 🌶️🥵

The beef ribs had a nice, smoky grill flavour.

Both dishes were equally great. Would definitely recommend if you’re in the South Melbourne area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEkBnGdOm2cTdWxEX2pyEvlgHZwU9APY5sWZmp"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"Joel Ch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1eXi1lmy24iIqTiG6RmkyVdIix6XDHzJi37xwqxbtVI3sz6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I spotted on social media that this place was claiming to be one of the best Indonesian restaurants in Melbourne, with a few locations in different areas.

I tried the satay chicken, which was a little too dry for my liking, and I had to order the rice separately. I was uncertain why it came with a salad instead of just cucumber cubes. Unfortunately, the gado-gado was sold out for the night, which was a shame. Instead, I ordered the soto ayam, which came with a lot of protein in a bowl of soup. The chili that came with it was incredibly hot, so I had to watch out for that.

As for the iga penyet, it was quite dry to me. Maybe I should follow what others do and squeeze a lot of kecap manis on top before eating. Overall, it was a bit hit and miss.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPi9gWwjWjnIMjz_-QN5CgPqEjL0GTaE-iLK5d"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Whitney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhEMHoizpkHB1g0d_KVlcjUOStzxSeE79NCw3i-sViJ7b37g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is legit here and so delicious! The Soto betawi and the beef ribs were delicious! The duck was a bit dry and we wanted to try the chicken but it was sold out :( gado gado was average. Beef stew was also not as good. The sambal was hectic. The garlic one was especially delicious but careful as it was pretty hot!

Really casual take away place with self service water and self order. Service as chill and friendly. Too bad the chicken was sold out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZvH9c388KYoAvTJ-lXxwlgmvibazcbklMx5zd"],"When":"2024-4-10"},{"Name":"E L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQN4dg6XZsMCg-L38lcitWOzmUp8JQiq_u2UD6NvtAy9PajtPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food!

What they do incredibly well:
1.  That chilli sauce on the side. So lethal and you can tell from the amount of seeds in there that it’s going to be hell. But you just keep going back for more - not just spicy but full of aroma and goes so well with everything.
2. Meats have great flavour - the aromatics around the meat are very fragrant and get extracted very well from the process of deep frying. Nice crispy bits at the top as well.

Comparing the ayam (chicken) vs bebek (duck) penyet, I would say there are parts on both that are a little too dry (but understandable given it’s the crisp and flavour they’re going for) but there are parts of the duck that have a nice fattiness running through it that helps keep the meat more moist and tender. The dry parts of the duck were drier than the chicken overall though.

Rice was also slightly dry. But all in all a great plate of food, and at an affordable price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLWqGqOKyLCwD7hDuuftAz2dq4t7Afok9ZJ664"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Dexter Medusha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVY0IRkZhc8WoArNno-NeLdlNyiHxp8LK94lI4RdS-kmOnet28=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have shopped at Penyet Ria with uber several times, and some of my orders were incomplete. Firstly there is no sambel, secondly there is no rice. Now I buy meatballs, but there is no soup and sauce i just get meet ball and noodle. Sorry, but if it happens once or twice, I can still be patient. but not the third time, i am sorry i cant eat dry bakso with noodles","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSpoQqxtZpnStCnrEJSekMXnjJdO1t8pxRXWzL"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Puteri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXxtrgOpmdpXsBrjYlIaJIOh54P1SfqLsuMK7RuDSOco6FvSby=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered ayam penyet, ayam geprek, empal, and sayur asem after our visit to South Melbourne Market one afternoon. One of our top-pick Indonesian restaurants here in Melbourne! :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWOIojr44fEr37Q3k-fYdG_LU1PXatSy6SOdMN"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Eyie Zhang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVD3BA3UsC1ZNf3ZZ-7mu1ceAYrs0QH7PXro7ZO0l14HEcI4UzJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best penyet in town, the sambal is excellent!! Many options can be picked, and all are authentic Indonesian dishes. My favourite is bebek Madura, crispy tender duck, love it! Their soto ayam is still the best (compared to the other places)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRmBs57WSdRldb-pSUiY6x-RahD7cpcCxLg-Ux"],"When":"2023-6-10"},{"Name":"Nianna Chandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsFEzQOS1vwQv62nmIKXMkPfBpnzRBvkP6uvL7tDZ6v3sx4Dnu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is by far my favourite authentic Indonesian 🇮🇩 restaurant located at South Melbourne. Their ayam penyet is the best, so delicious, tender and flavourful and is goes really well with their sambal belacan sauce 🤤🤌🏻 Yumm!!! The service was quick and we got served by Angel, she’s very friendly and polite ☺️ We will definitely keep coming back here! I highly recommended you guys try this place out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCQlht7OZadzGMkXNJpf2ieCq8mcUasLdaJg4T"],"When":"2023-11-14"}]

[{"Name":"Narida Ear","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLKfbBe5bGQLwMaKV9g1O2Amn1bHYlkvN13vEARHQBk4Mnqaw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came to Lamaro's to celebrate my and my partner's 30th in the Atrium function room and we cannot recommend it enough! Great communication from the venue in the lead up, wonderful service on the day and the food and atmosphere was of an impeccable standard. Will definitely be returning for any special occasions in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhZIYVtQmvk_ULTEAi6zxO7TluvYqwviVuwmT_"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Marika Unger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkoSoyLEviu4HjkW312qIhKtmR6LZU2YvQFqe4897IgAh8Hg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came for dinner late January for a networking event and was incredibly impressed by both the food and service. I’ve since come back for work lunches. The pork belly scallops are one of my favourites on the menu. The combination of flavours is truly something else. The Scotch Fillet, and the Vietnamese chicken salad are also to die for. Highly highly recommend checking this place out. I have since come back for multiple work lunches. See you again soon Lamaros!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGv2cEfb3h1qcUuC4aetbiEq0aEBSu5WvQkVNU"],"When":"2024-2-8"},{"Name":"Maral Tecer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWlmoNKAj5tmdndvpybjxKzA6xni1M2BgTQrwYcOAqsyMPyaxr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I’m coming back for the red duck curry! I had one mouthful (friend’s meal) and can’t stop thinking about it.
The steak, risotto and veal schnitty were pretty good too. Great red wine selection also 🍷","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaSSU1bCA4Nc272wXPDDIs6vL5N7U5_6K0Bciq"],"When":"2024-2-20"},{"Name":"Ani Covini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXezK44Jqxcij2FCy42Z9askWgmxMZRhmLc2R_ptpSYWVUqSYm6xQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice! The free bread came warm and tasted amazing. Not sure if that's just my love of bread, but I think it was great. I don't normally like scallops, but the scallop entree was amazing. All the flavours complimented each other and it was delicious. The sourdough crostini was a little odd, but that's just because I'm not a fan of anchovies. The goats cheese did cut through that strength so it was alright. I ordered the steak for the main and it was perfect for me. I wish there was a mushroom sauce, but I can't complain too much over the Diane sauce. Some complimenting salad would have looked better on the plate, but overall it was great!

I should have ordered the pudding for dessert. It was delicious! The brandy snap basket with ice cream/sorbet was still great, just not as good as the taste I had of the pudding!

Service was also amazing. Very attentive and friendly!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0vnRKX9S4jaBRPnbqhqth7YliCRdacg5E9D86"],"When":"2023-6-10"},{"Name":"Bella","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVziAsTZrgYCsjojKwpKDpW8CB2aMFuiisI_l_bnskJsIS3f9ZRw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful hotel, atmosphere was very nice, and the service was great. Food was beautiful, although I didn't really fancy the King Grilled Prawn Spaghettini. I feel it lacked flavour. The twice cooked octopus and the veal schnitzel are a must. The schnitzel was huge !!! Would definitely recommend this place and am looking forward to visiting again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3y6fqztN_VK9UQEvfQGHiRPgarV5aoNNabgeb"],"When":"2023-10-14"},{"Name":"Edwar Kartio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJL1A0TThvJIHeyMfzo3v10AhlGsjiRHFS9Mf2DrJBg2wVitw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We came for Wednesday dinner service and it was busy! The waiter told us they can sit us in but the table must be cleared within the hour for other bookings which shows how popular this place is. The food offering is mainly Italian dishes and steaks with few asian twists. We ordered the salumi Board, linguine and beef burger. Except for the burger which is only average, the other two dishes are great. Especially the linguine as the sauce doesn't taste like your traditional Italian pasta. Price is definitely higher than your typical pub pricing.
Food - 8
Service - 9
Vibe - 7
Price - $$$","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeOB5lYvOI6XD6v_6xMpNQNMqS2PK28iMzDTBe"],"When":"2023-3-29"},{"Name":"Jeffrie Trika","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtNG_SBHYfa3FBC0zUL4VkTXFlMh75f2WxcnGm_rKXfjiB791liQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Not your average Melbourne's pub ...

Impressively restored old pub ... from the minute you walked in ... you can feel the warmth and grace in modernly restoring this old pub ... dominant white marble bar, dark timber ... yes, don't worry, Gents, there are plenty of faltscreen TVs with sports on ... even on a Thursday night ... no rowdy crowd, just a pleasant ambience and good vibes.

The menu complements this modernly restored gastro-pub ... not your typical pub menu ... I'm not a salad person (sorry Mami), but I did enjoy that Red & Yellow beetroot salad, with presentation to match👌 more importantly, their famed schnitzel ... not to my liking, but generously served $44.00 ... 4/5 ... my perfectly cooked medium-rare 300 gms scotch was good $56.00, and the most impressive was their pepper sauce ... that was divine! Thank you Chef ...

Drink wise ... a book FULL of alcoholic drinks ... I started with the O'Leary's Riesling ... and if I didn't have to drive, I could surely enjoy a few more of that Voyager Estate Cab Sauvignon ... went down well with my scotch fillet ...

Just don't wear Fred Perry dark blue shirt when dining here 😊 ... you could be mistakenly taken as one of the wait-team ... they look smart, vibrant, attentive, and very pleasant, kudos to the team.

Thank you and I'm sure we'll be back ...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiZXZiVU9WeBGHFfdxkFGSOpGx_SzvfdWDYoV2"],"When":"2023-8-17"},{"Name":"Mina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4gucXakW7t8_UOd5kxL8f_3tOIjaNAD_AFPGR1N6MvWSnOOyNGg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I attended in a group and we had booked to sit outside, not knowing that it would be a cold and rainy night in Dec.

The staff were great and couldn't do enough for us.

I had prawn linguine which was delicious. I received 3x very large prawns with this dish. These were yum and enormous!

The others in the group enjoyed their meals and we all had a good experience.

It is a lovely spot to sit outside and enjoy beautiful South Melbourne.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKhWkT7Pd_A4dXkcg2QuuUIgNf1mqDUia0HBLn"],"When":"2022-12-14"}]
