[{"Name":"Jane River (ta.be.tabi)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXThFW_vdkFYe5GkNOfjhVWDWMU-_NpTMZ8yAtUoCfXaW4Bjy3I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quick, delicious and affordable eats! Many options to cater to anyone’s tastes. My fave is definitely the Wagyu 63 degree Egg Bowl, but can’t go wrong with anything Chicken Katsu too!

Overall amazing food and service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwZsGfbQm0K-2CdLmaqzEgPNgZWvb6R7fEw53n"],"When":"2024-1-19"},{"Name":"Anwen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvYPJ-yrwkXRWlFVg7uagYBBGq_3x_nnejnV1kH71AuWH7Gg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food! Generous serves! Excellent service with a smile. This place will be our go to in South Melbourne. We had the wagyu bowl, salmon poke bowl and chicken katsu. Ninja burger was a hit with my son- almost too cute to eat but was so tasty 😋!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5UlyquKFhc8ofW5wPV9_jL5Hbn3oa6gTv0YD5"],"When":"2023-8-6"},{"Name":"Anand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6Dlom4kizAnh_eprqwXDZAf9ulxZJY1Hy8ZhtJ_4SJYq3HsXa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great Japanese style fast food, the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtle style burgers was a highlight, along with the croquettes. The katsu curry was rather ordinary though. Note that seating is very limited, maybe enough for 10-12 people max","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsbBXBq2QeMLanDof9XE3nNyUGReI50hNBDZwB"],"When":"2023-8-19"},{"Name":"Kenan M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOfN0jPpaa_ERIm096dIz_By1aYqyN41CnxGVL6f6jZI-Z_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to try the limited edition Ninja Turtles Burger and i wasn't disappointed at all. Crunchy Juicy fried chicken with fresh salad and a fluffy bun ... will be back to try the bowls soon.
Service is top too 👌🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQ9tUlbmcAMiyxilN4dCQBH_CBEE9Jf_-LYcpr"],"When":"2023-9-4"},{"Name":"Mary Schalken","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfx4FmpjybmhFrIsqElk-lLGhws8rRDlmu5PhVzJYP3KoXmgSE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The burgers were nice but my favourite would have to be the chicken katsu. I also tried the chips which were really nice! It’s such a great addition to South Melbourne. I love their bubble tea range. The staff have always been kind and welcoming.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHOyIHk5Qla52D3pJng4XTJm2HrED8_h0wMpZn"],"When":"2023-8-9"},{"Name":"Thao Pham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpG5gDPKTOZlgqo2OObaGbzpfS81vX69oK5stMqUXh3Co8cmc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A good addition to the strip of eateries in South Melbourne. Nice & healthy Japanese inspired meals with lots substitute and also has bubble tea. Fries with a side of miso sauce to dip is too delicious to share!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCBNBZ7m_IzEbGAbHDBr0HBJHDwgWzIEaNQYJr"],"When":"2023-10-10"},{"Name":"2 Good Forks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULBaux-42xgwL65KCuBqkbZLakZ_XPC9D44HOetXwk04BVMKrh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"📍@future.canteen @theclarendoncentre, South Melbourne

We have finally visited the recently opened sushi restaurant called Future Canteen at The Clarendon Centre in South Melbourne for dinner 😋

They make bowls, super cute Ninja burgers using buns from @soninlaw_melb, sushi and bubble tea - we both loved the curry & poke bowls we tried here 😍

This is a great option for a quick lunch or dinner under $20 when you are in the area, also a good spot for a bubble tea break - I recommend trying their siganture flavours 😚

What we ordered:
🍤 Prawn Katsu Curry $14.9
🐟 Aburi Salmon Poke $18.9
🐢 Leonardo $15.9
🍔 Raphael $15.9
🧋 Taro Milk with Brown Sugar Pearls $6.8
🍑 Rainbow Peach Tea $6.8","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOA_HNCbAd21d5Jk06yZ1F67FNT0j2RuUXCr5Kr"],"When":"2023-10-16"},{"Name":"Sarah Melbs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYQzIKFLQofNENBGGeU9hYzAkN-fZyI-t330rG8-QkSAek6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came for the ninja turtle bun!!
The Rice bowls were also huge. Wagyu bowl, Aburi salmon and chicken Katsu curry rice!

Chips were very fresh and crunchy!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOF7w5r14KQd4f2RyUIaTiwPUZ7Hkqxxp3t5PE"],"When":"2023-8-13"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Shayan Soroush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlDQ2ES5kJPq_EidPjDT8pk4bXcwKHhh4dLCqXurGSkHFB_GI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good pizza place along Clarendon in South Melbourne. Pizza prices are ok, not too cheap not too expensive. The family size is quite big and can comfortably fill up 2 people, can also mix and match different pizzas in one for an extra $2. Taste was excellent and they were open past 10 pm when we went and everything else was closed, so good for that time of day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvz81EGZayeSJSmOkawXP5MSTcoppgADyM_IVO"],"When":"2024-3-3"},{"Name":"Carl Bronkhorst","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXz9HZvIgrcIMl0C72dfSzae2-63ohTU6TELfn1i3EsQZuVUfIqEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Everything was over salted, pizza salty, pasta salty.

The pizza was nice, nothing super exciting or fancy. Just the average local pizza shop style. The Lasagne had a good flavour,
ratio of pasta/meat, and the flavour of the sauce was great but very salty once again. The Al polo penne had no salt. The paster tasted cheap and flavourless.

Look the place was OK, but I have been to many other pizza/pasta places that were much better in quality and price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhRImBZMG5W2JUZIjD_slWHx_WnoxqWofs3Z2_"],"When":"2023-9-14"},{"Name":"Ram V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgPj3pJ1XXJvjl0KxG7qpCS5aVrDOBZtqXbyC37k-GTh-FRT8q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing food at a great price.
Perfect little pizza place in South Melbourne if you're after good taste and nothing fancy.

The service might be bit off if busy, which is understandable.

The only improvement ...they could do is to clean up the place and present better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Saigon Bread Shop Sbs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2hS-03M0u_Y3S5XeQZIq2W8rqSTt-atCUOcUSR1mDJeoFa9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed family time with lovely foods
Our fav is lasagna which we take a way 1 more meal to take home
Its so good","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMM7hLNftrByIZdu9TjAKXmkHIsoE4ilG23Ezr-"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Debadrita Ghosh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkLqa9r-twziLnBbR7bssWJIv3f7EI-gR2lD7he7Aza_53gkfGVg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is perfecto to hangout with your friends and partner. I would not recommend it for the first date because of it's old school ambience. Food are really reasonable in respect to it's tastes. I ordered Meat Lover pizza (large) for dine in and Aussie (medium) for take away.
Must try pizzas.
Friendly natured","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8O2MXFPR_6mlX5lo7dIQRS4Afu9hywrCERR8g"],"When":"2023-7-4"},{"Name":"Joyce Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLrarLXPsllnomcYc__yTz8Tiq22oLDncx30RQZ9X5_kkdaIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every time back to Melbourne we always to go there, the pizza always good, Jackie the lady was so nice to chat. Highly recommended..  from Mororo NSW","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuPSFlttIKG1cM5UYWABbRD9--Z2uqiyHu8MSs"],"When":"2023-12-12"},{"Name":"David Saab","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWTe-rm9nTdR4FvmcLnR0QphPN6ZJoJh2AObANTE2cnbY8Hz4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Purchased no.13 the lot. Strangely I ordered the family size which according to the menu says it's $24 but they charged me $25. I guess they must of raised the prices without updating their menus.

As to the pizza itself, when I opened it it looked fantastic.  Generous toppings looking fresh but when I tasted it, it was surprisingly bland. Maybe they should put more sauce on base or cheese on top? Don't know but was a little disappointing.

The restaurant itself looked and smelled great. Very authentic and a great smell. I'll try again with another pizza in the coming weeks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYxkt8vUsKGC5Nzpm-2N0Ae6BustQE2ZAWcwLM"],"When":"2023-2-26"},{"Name":"Mark A Woolrich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdqk4fJa-scV8rmsBCkJ4pG_awu4wDm1AscjlAwwJLMq0qn8LK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always drop pass here when I’m in the area of South Melbourne. Pizzas taste great original recipe and the same ladie been here for 30 years. You know it’s gonna be good…thanks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNA4ESAH5JVw1o2S8FPdR5VDPQaJncOv9Izp1QB"],"When":"2023-6-27"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Z L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUX_3_hqlhe3buz3dczsa0mp7h7KJyck7t9YUgjBzsU4kka7Hf9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I used to eat at Glenda’s Pho every weekend when I was living in Port Melbourne. Then Covid hit and they sold their business. And I moved to Richmond.

By chance while attending an event in South Melbourne, I bumped into familiar faces - Glenda and her husband, at their new restaurant, Huy’s Kitchen in the heart of South Melbourne.

The food is still as delicious as I remembered. I highly recommend the beef or chicken pho. The chicken spring rolls are also yummy.

Service is wonderful. Shout out to Henry, the very warm and kind-hearted waitperson who treats me like family. I always leave feeling happy after each meal there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyk94vxBofTteOISvtQOiOmHB-cPIGINBsQDwd"],"When":"2024-1-14"},{"Name":"Melody (mellu.dines)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEgPkBifQeiOq4x7j8EpxCxevPKVD3pC2wCoa2kQk4GbZsyZNZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We really enjoyed our visit here. Not only was the food affordable at lunch but the staff were really helpful. Loved everything!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNJiAqhLSoZ4yTDOEvPIkLpxE0YIrXXnlhEA_d"],"When":"2024-4-3"},{"Name":"Shirley V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeApfuiswtpRavj8DYI0U-QCfrkXTiMl-HB5zrgx0YhamLZf02=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food and service was good. Just a little comments the beef with lemongrass does not have much lemongrass flavour.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQ0G5cH7nHkdb_ho21QGS2zy94yPoJ63JQWLkL"],"When":"2024-4-16"},{"Name":"Edwar Kartio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJL1A0TThvJIHeyMfzo3v10AhlGsjiRHFS9Mf2DrJBg2wVitw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Recently there has been a growth of Vietnamese restaurants along Clarendon street. This one is situated within the same block as Coles. The menu is extensive ranging from rice, noodles, and main dishes. The beef pho has a nice, flavourful broth. The Tom Yum noodle soup comes with thin rice noodles (beehoon) and surprisingly pretty good and doesn't taste like instant tom yum that you normally get from an Asian takeaway shop. Would definitely come back next time to try other dishes. The service is friendly although it felt a little understaffed as it took them a while to clean up the tables before us.
Food - 7
Service - 8
Vibe - 6
Price - $","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9fyJvxKVp5eLDM2Ce5w0rZplThEdD-l_4Z2zp"],"When":"2023-5-26"},{"Name":"Tatiana Lukiyanova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYFmJ27H2OsZESYvTuOJ5vjEfDIVG9X9U4MQHN5Rm4IdTmig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We discovered this beautiful place and what a treasure! The steam fish with ginger and spring onions is our favourite! Highly recommend! We love their pho and seafood stir fried in black-been souse. We love the service , friendly atmosphere and great value. We are keep coming back again and again …","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angel Khong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUclkqITYfc7Hb5-vgjuDeacBepTyuu5kLvxhAdtl1YqD-OIEdR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered through EatClub from Huy’s Kitchen their prawn spring rolls, grilled pork balls & banh hoi, and the pork chop & fried egg with rice. The porks were deliciously tender and so flavourful, the spring rolls actually had prawn bits in them. Both mains came with a lot of vege - wish they’d put the vege in containers/boxes though instead of plastic bags as the vege got a little squished during transport.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7OeqCUf6KqDWXP7kf_IF5cCXxn_AyprOllJPf"],"When":"2023-4-30"},{"Name":"Angie Goh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1W8EOVf1kza7DKGSXX0kPujE-yT4ZB16gQmb9HIqfXG9wGFJ0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Broth for Pho Ga 🐔 was goood. Fragrance Fried Pork 🐽 Chop rice with  egg... not forgetting Prawn Rice Paper Rolls.. 👍🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyjft2ZFQ8KMurQ8RbUVts0mGwKJKkjyGo3b9w"],"When":"2023-7-19"},{"Name":"Olivia Elliott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8z45JiQxNuxo5e82o8MCzs5ThIy43mTzoCY0HglEwzxIJI7E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The biggest 5 stars ever! Not only was the food insanely fresh and delicious the service was 10/10. I had accidentally put pick up on the order and tried calling to resolve for delivery as I am pregnant. I did not mention this on the call but the lady said it was no issue and she would just deliver it herself. 20 minutes later our very yummy food was hand delivered with a beautiful smile and we are so grateful for the kindness. We recommend the honey chicken and the laksa!! Thank you again :)","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Rebecca Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMDQKT-L-EJqgtxkrsd8FtkUe5Tdhtn-uM6gOwA_BjI5Mi_A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's been 5 years since we visited Hobart and had breakfast here, and loved it so much we came back, and we were not disappointed. I had the corn mint fritters and added Halloumi. This was so good. All our food was generous and tasty and presented nicely. Coffee was great. The staff were very friendly and beyond helpful in helping us with queries about the area. We will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMThd6aQ8gG2Ma5RAn9uM3ezG_W27RvcCRGF0Bc"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"Bella","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2fZamRZH3L7HsuqKyozuONFb3zJ2pTS_uvYlUmUwjkq7gKkO5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a great little cafe! Off Collins street in a little lane.
Super friendly service by an adorable Spanish speaking girl. She greets everyone with the same enthusiasm. She’s so pleasant and polite.
The 3/4 latte coffee and mocha was exceptional, Melbourne coffee snobs quality! The scrambled eggs were hearty, the bacon plentiful and the rustic toast thick.
The granola was crunchy, fresh and the yoghurt tangy. The almond milk was warm and delicious. Nothing was too much trouble for them. Highly highly recommend and will visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3V6E6osqCA5B9sKgf8CAJreFzdK6_AsYl40p7"],"When":"2024-5-24"},{"Name":"Jo W (TheStick)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4mSlJGLw4Xd_j3MeVw18_v-TBxr8h-xbMm3UIs-5ZYhCszXE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a hidden treasure. Attentive staff, fast service, good prices. Not just your usual menu either. Felt like a real treat with something everyone in the family enjoyed. Food was very tasty and filling.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-Jby00zg0K0pl6TqbU8qOHlhRSrbpzq31NVYn"],"When":"2024-4-1"},{"Name":"holly gregory","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1VLibq2jZEtlgZ7JdewT5vtGzxpZ-CR_uRTDJNfh-8nACq_8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Does not live up to the hype. I chose this cafe specifically for our holiday, we encountered rudeness from the waitress, long waits for menus, and over 30mins wait for food, despite the restaurant being half empty. We did ask numerous times how much longer our food would take and while the waitress would say she would ‘go and check’ she proceeded to continue what she was doing without checking at all. The food finally arrived, the presentation was rushed, I ordered the Granola vegan option, expecting vegan yogurt but got a dry bowl of granola with only a small side of milk, which was not worth the $15 price tag and basically inedible. Don’t offer a vegan option and then just take away items.
Awful cafe. Don’t waste your time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJ9Vd0a9lLf1prvsN4xwhdUxrrTgCPUijJRwMr"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"Tea-Maria Constantin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrVad2tulq7kA3c1Iu3DIR4V3A1wO_hNEa8z0SrnLM8LI3kIeA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very cozy place, located in between two busy streets in Hobart.
We had lunch at Dandy Lane Café and it was great! Nice service and yummy food, good sized portions and decent value for money!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcLrCntfZk5xfwCl9ZCQlX2s7xlI_ZOF2H5gfC"],"When":"2024-2-21"},{"Name":"Michelle Valastro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYYL-XYT7HWjClQYq3HxlchPdgmKcpooJIL0UI8ZaTtrONhFn8mQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visited this Cafe for breakfast as it was closeby to our hotel and had great reviews. The food we had was super enjoyable!
Would return for and would recommend the Double Cheese Chilli Eggs - YUM! Tasty and slightly spicy and fluffy scrambled eggs in a bun. So much flavour!
The Croque Monsieur was also delish, crunchy fresh bread and can't go wrong with this take on a ham and cheese toastie.
Love that the menu had some variety aside from the breakfast basics.
Would recommend stopping in for a brekkie","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM41_b28yKEPnQoCHH5OdiyK8JNaQ01fzc7tHag"],"When":"2024-2-5"},{"Name":"Rohit Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbYc63lYm4Ss4K_hpJ9mgoR8j63C1KRZzMseEUvjTm3lHN_uY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is extremely good. Was pleasantly surprised to be honest as the ambience of the place(cafe is on the ground floor of a building) wasnt that great.
Truffle mushroom toastie and fried chicken burger is recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyGAunPR1EPWHuJLfN2oDmTJXVfvfsk4FRrPew"],"When":"2024-4-17"},{"Name":"Jamie-lee Harding","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX56jqvfK_rPNpR9YCn2dI4SO9J1LjEwK3KEb5YulkeMfNJxSHucA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Perhaps one of the best eggs Benny I've had in Australia so far. The ratios were on point! Plenty of hollandaise sauce and not too tart, plenty of flavour as well as great serving of bacon! Fried chicken Benny had a great serve of chicken and the sriracha sauce was on point, enough spice.

Coffee on point! ☕️

1st - Eggs Benny with bacon
2nd - Fried Chicken Benny","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2beUwmd6d4kui05Ly2bPNIA9gTlthpIfNam8k"],"When":"2024-1-11"}]

[{"Name":"Milane Mahendrarajah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPavnDN_9qfNyyAxDmLjcWlAvVDXg15ngO51fRT2r9RrHQaSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A friend recently introduced me to Song's Dumpling Restaurant, and I've already visited twice. The food is delicious, with reasonable prices and generous portions. The pork wontons in chili oil and the fried spicy chicken are must-tries. They also make fresh, in-house dumplings, which are fantastic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBDMUgMN-RPKNHVK7PkJqz7ZO-XJCwX3dL1kS6"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"sventek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLeijEDrYy2MJt1mV1zKigia9MXTzxSYCXmQo3965Sme1Bxb1Il=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We've tried a number of different items from here - chicken fried rice, meat and seafood hotpot, black pepper noodles, fried pork dumplings, chicken & prawn dumplings, chilli wontons, spring rolls, Singapore noodles, wonton noodle soup, and none of them stood out as amazing or brilliantly delicious. However, considering their pricing, portion sizes, and their Eatclub discount, it's not a bad option to get over the hunger especially when you find the right condiments for some of them.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMk5PTp8j4_cgPufKAlJeDam5Y3Oem2QXiC5kB5"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Lloyd Smyth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJO73zP8fsm01W-SAdN2zsTkTfpqxLYY4H2ASnShCMTC_XL9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tasty, value for money, great portion sizes! Really enjoyed our pan fried veggie dumplings and stir fried noodles. Noodles could have used a little more char in the wok but still very tasty. Would come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtRXgOntzPfNC1XZ36QfOBiz7qvYObGG3Mh4jv"],"When":"2024-3-29"},{"Name":"Kelly Eats Out","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXzk_0Bt0g9I49mv7TzpsdhDH-4ehgr2ACocttZg7ai8x_9A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food Ordered:
🍛 Special fried rice with shrimp
🐷Spicy pork belly in sichuan sauce with rice
🍜 Pork wonton noodle soup
🥟 Pan fried dumplings

Dumplings are handmade at this place. My fav was the spicy pork belly in sichuan sauce. An explosion of flavours. Overall, good food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRirm4JZuOzcXDviM77XTwTAgxC3Q8L9gqzNhC"],"When":"2024-3-8"},{"Name":"Annaliese Boot","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJ8nlTPsD0YqmE5PMd3wrJiFVoAerQR8xpWfJ3Bhx0xl_d3noa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow wow wow! Must visit when in Melbourne. I had the Xiaolongbao and Pork fried dumplings. Both were exceptional, bigger portions that I expected and the let me take away what I couldn’t finish. Great friendly service. Will definitely be back during my time in Melbourne !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoWxDnE-1WGzOB2t11_lHANudFgnM1ygISsEO1"],"When":"2024-3-30"},{"Name":"Bijan Shahverdi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLdATEFF4unEQS3azxAbkgSjPiJ0Eav4x0hCs0fkpeDXzJE7c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good food! I came here for the first time for dinner. All the food I got was great and I’m sure that everything else on their menu is good too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBf3Mrrf8tEfzldK7D4nOrSPwfLwQGlyNIouoh"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Miyuki Ishige","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWojA4MdSBrG_tBMIG2TR02syyJxcAzlM3LwO2ZDaYwniKS8XH6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best dumplings I have ever eaten in my life! The portion of Sichuan chili chicken was crazy for 2 people. But they allowed us to bring the remaining portion back as well :)) Will come back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAVK0bS7IcDiQNTaLVtJL_AnRO8CflgGDj8-A5"],"When":"2024-3-1"},{"Name":"Alexandros Papatsonis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6ENkR7Jn3X8iMgZxeBoknSJFTBOvWQGvxVI0AWboIqrfFyg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Don't buy the chilli chicken. $30 for the offcuts of the drumsticks, the ones that you throw away, cartilage and bone fried. These people give a new meaning to recycling. Not even a single piece of meat on it. If you like fried bones is your own choice but the kids will be left hungry.
Waste of money. Disgusting","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP452vTK1D6DFXftrbGa1nWjGAkNFXhLCutH7pN"],"When":"2024-2-4"}]

[{"Name":"Josh Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeCssENuWe_JZK1jxoBWG1Nicpo5_pcDQ6rWzbDGXtF8lKbgON=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely phenomenal egg and bacon toastie with the chives, nothing like I've had before. Definitely worth a go!

Edit: Had the Smokey BBQ sauce, I think I'd add that sauce to everything it was that good","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcd8qhRVinX-AyQ6gf2RolgybfR5X_y3uXw0c-"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"Chris Pittman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwBm55905E0LWOcq2r7rxcjDXPfi2Y0RWEk_qB2bcJHmghGY3oqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited on our Australia trip and I couldn't have been happier - the food was beyond excellent, the coffee was divine and even more welcome was the friendly employees.  We stopped by multiple times on our short Tasmania trip and were never once left unhappy.  Can't wait to return","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6IQQm-sUuSQVJhgkZokivV8uVjZvu04b1pvia"],"When":"2023-6-5"},{"Name":"Anthony Hood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-m8gSBFufp1vvmGNJyg0FkoszaiX4P1YnYR-WyXUteuqDDMs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Inadvertently,  yesterday morning,  I misplaced my review intended for another coffee place.
However,   today I am pleased to rectify my review. And, I have to admit that without Jono's prompting my in-error review (great,  in a very rare fairplay towards business competitors!, Jono proved his honesty).

Although,  today I had my 1st time coffee at The Stagg City  venue.
Services great, people fantastic,  coffee super!
Highly recommended.

Definitely,  I'll be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPC5K-Lj22jcWpzUsXMcfgAFynn-HBBHAqrDcyj"],"When":"2023-10-4"},{"Name":"Frank Jansen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfEdX3ehTATD-134Yq5FOYyA8KI9RQa8b5ScmS4XLgRLdapuU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee and service. Despite the fact that I’m an irregular visitor for business.  I have a mocha and the team here always seem to remember me and how I like it …. Lots of chocolate.  Also the sausage rolls are awesome…. [{"Name":"Prasad Falke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0Upu4KU0a59G3JD_zqIgNPG2MXRe6Ip0mW_ZRwfB9bWh4f03b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very close to the city and some really good brunch options available. I tried the Lamb Sandwich and it was delicious. Hopefully I will try more next time.

They are a 2-story restaurant/cafe and the second floor (first floor in Australia) is where you can sit, work, and/or meet people. Limited electric outlets so don’t rely on the power just in case.

Staff is good and they help you in deciding which food to order.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQRXGR0lw58wcmXjWTXp0OarFHdIlg6JqAo1Uj"],"When":"2023-11-26"},{"Name":"Sam Fariborz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgvtbejsgYOZkiRuP34EmiJnYmsu-MT6Q-sC5w494-H3WUno4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Coming from Melbourne, Criterion was an average cafe to me. My coffee was cold, the veggies were not fresh and I couldn’t eat them. I give 2.5/5 overall.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODWQB58XaINivAICmN05YRJbG4HlFK_H4ZIWBw"],"When":"2023-12-25"},{"Name":"June Death","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNzyELVsnQsiPvEEzpHfau9cJ69C4CnbaVd3u9Rttc2PjHzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Called in for breakfast. Lovely smiling staff, and quick service.  Fruit and Nut Toast with lemon curd was great, while French Toast hubby had was delicious.  Coffees just right.  Will call in next time in Hobart!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erin Jane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYAqRaj6ll5onkqfhl3ORXwEt6hpB2MkCqsuF4P6gi-7Z0tAPF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Criterion is always fantastic and one of my favourites. I went to breakfast with fussy eaters one time, and even though sweet waffles weren't on the menu at that time they still made sweet waffles for three of us (I had savoury, both delish). Also, best coffee in Hobart. Highly recommend to everyone who comes to visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"lachlan Stephenson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWP6iUaEBmQhDumeLz9qdnprHpe8noMVq1h0zwHEjNUIe4wu9It=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exquisite brunch and good coffee. Had the french toast with some scrambled egg. Portions were suitable to the richness but not large - flavour was great. Friendly and attentive service. The laneway was not the nicest but at least the sun could penetrate","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abi T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFQfPgyz_uk6vvYWFoeHvK52O2GV7Ya0aFHPI9L0ok6D-v2pw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down the best tasting coffee we have had in Hobart, all 4 of us were blown away.  It’s made exactly as you like it (especially if you’re into your specifics like double shot, 3/4, extra hot haha)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adele G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmCBb4HlM6WQtjbtLgEyRi3y_sfhzkgAfibHoD22xv8fPA59NRFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best coffee in Hobart , amazing food and fab service 🥰","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFOUdxP0fOiiSm4iq4mosikj4ukr5H_cdOUQx5"],"When":"2024-1-15"},{"Name":"Erin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWV0pwbXsVgiWSJ2mn-UFCMv-eUZyKOMF-AjbGkuZ3LGh6ujtHB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Found this cafe on our last day in Hobart and was very happy with the breakfast and service we received. Staff were very friendly, food was well priced, well portioned and we highly enjoyed. Coffee was great too. Would recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOrOYxgWTSgVCPu3M4cCQmSPwLZkMPo9kq5KcJg"],"When":"2022-6-14"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Denni Arli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMOyIPSGE-dyluKNy8Bll65q8XRWk7uZsqhzphWiDu50j3mHic=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A unique and small cafe, perfect for a solo breakfast or small group of friends and families. The meals are very delicious and full of flavour! More importantly, the coffee is one of the best in Hobart.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTdM8mzttNT5lhLNqxr6VBaQQUvKE45DuAecWk"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"A D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_HypPRZMx_Hxp_Aa3gIYKIeUlw8katsDXvxvRYUDdwHUlSuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We had waffles with fig, ricotta, honey, walnut and kale \u0026 bean soup with sourdough bread for brunch. Waffles were cold \u0026 ricotta didn't taste nice. Food was a bit overpriced. The barista milk leaf pattern on the coffee was a smudge. Had to wait for the tables to be cleaned. Preserves, jam, honey \u0026 other items from the farm for sale.  Got a small bottle of hot paprika for $16, hardly any heat, not worth the price. Bought some Madeleines \u0026 soft amarettis, not good, low amount of almond flour in the amarettis.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRztCAN8asAhKcGh8R6H5X1FguAjJk3JnWrmtx"],"When":"2024-6-4"},{"Name":"I Think","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5MmSNw5pQsom1kOCLIe_FqPAo1-Ap33j8XWuEARDVJjjrcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cozy cafe. Not very busy. We had a brunch after a morning run. The omelette with brussle sprouts was amazing, especially the brussle sprouts. Other dishes are good as well. Coffee is good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3XFuEk_ABpwLESzvnmxl3G8m8Ukd3b5hRuy3p"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"Diana Waines","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5Q9Vfqdx5R3vbPFQ-c4yE64UIYrIrVsTmDW_z6qYIE0f-lyg9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We noticed this cosy looking cafe on the way to our hotel in West Hobart. We only tried the coffee, but wished we could have tried some of the delicious looking food that surrounded us that morning. Unfortunately we had already eaten earlier! The coffee was presented beautifully, had good flavour \u0026 came out fast. The staff were wonderful too","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJ-rVjAPKJTYBzxV2FOiRBNAIgBYOKO6nk0FTp"],"When":"2024-1-27"},{"Name":"chutirat khongsantiah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs1Wg5dehhRDgk9ODJB_t_6UYuolrlWgOMsrnAj8IXqhkmYH1sqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my favorite cafe around Hobart ever!! I've been here 4 times, ordered different food and every time it was excellent. Don't forget to ask for daliy special menu! That's so fantatic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcWBaVth8-H-RB0l0yFGh_tgexqUb5vJkBKgwu"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"Robo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIO5kBuJXE3FJFeVOm1qss7etRe3Ib3htBcho16INUihW70bQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I googled for best coffee in Hobart, this place came up.. coffee was spot on.. stopped in here for a quick breakfast, had the house made crumpets with the house made peanut butter and fam made jam.. when I saw on the reviews that they served fresh produce from the farm I was like I must try this place.. you guys lived up to it.. keep up the good work, loved the vibe and the dishes that werecoming out of the kitchen looked beautiful. Will recommend and even visit next time I'm in Hobart","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZVn2dG6FzLuqQYwaB2Iqv9E2vuU-DCzhNtwK1"],"When":"2023-11-16"},{"Name":"Zhi Xiong Chong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXr2lhHyNK8DqIJfVm7gRrP2uEjquPqFRuv83hoBrOnVqC63qhEew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great choices of food. We were spoilt, but luckily the helpful waitress was amazing at recommending delicious food for us according to our needs. Menu has gluten free, vegan, and vegetarian options. Very inclusive. The homemade jam and crumpet is so delicious you can taste the farm 😜","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXG21dLr1y1e-SXos7T4qfSKs66wMAV-dhlIPP"],"When":"2023-8-17"},{"Name":"Moira K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTcbb5A_QKl71Ult2KoslMH3GqloJS-UTZjeYqEuLYQJPB-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a wonderful meal this was! I just missed the early crowds here on a Sunday, but this beautiful space still has lots of people enjoying its atmosphere over a cozy feed. I had the baked eggs with chilli and some bacon, plus a coffee. My word, it was delicious! Top 3 meal on my visit to Hobart. The staff were friendly and attentive too. If and when I visit this beautiful city again I will be back. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Darren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvm7I8OFs8G44HVqZHPQwkoUBiB0EnedFQESCXZaTGC_lzsZEmjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great cafe in the city of Hobart. Lots of seating outside and a small amount indoors downstairs and more upstairs. Great menu with lots of choices. Service is very attentive and coffee very good. When you ask for extra hot that is exactly what you get. I had the hotcakes which were delicious and presented beautifully. My partner enjoyed the bruschetta which was also beautifully presented and very tasty. A small selection of cakes available. They are open for breakfast , lunch and dinner and offer quite an array of pizzas. Definitely worth a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPG8p8gIdH_DFcMDeswFcaOpgA2ecXzR0K1qSQo"],"When":"2024-4-5"},{"Name":"illion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViqx0qMys5-bvxqOKuWKEU3_D-nxYBBlUozx3tG9oOUQPNPDSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The pancakes were amazing!!! Loved the setting that they didn’t put all the syrup and cream on too and you can eat it how you like. It got crowded when I got there at 11am but glad I managed to get a table outside over looking the habour!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzOeldGK_UEL6I5yz4DcQ8gXZlWdA4svIRKkJd"],"When":"2024-3-23"},{"Name":"Wolty Geoghegan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0OncRwdjgCrp1zXIW4AydI2R_6I3KAovWmT2wHgiy9Mb8AIMPcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our first meal in Hobart this trip and we think we've peaked early! Both scallop meals we had were outstanding. The service was great and the price was very reasonable. Can't recommend it highly enough.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxmo9g279_r0NKDDCDRnmGv_YLtN_VTvOdDeQO"],"When":"2024-4-3"},{"Name":"Bella","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2fZamRZH3L7HsuqKyozuONFb3zJ2pTS_uvYlUmUwjkq7gKkO5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brilliant service. Best eggs Benedict I’ve had. Absolutely delicious and plentiful. We sat upstairs on Sunday morning and whilst a little noisy it was served in a timely manner and efficiently. Would definitely visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOW_pt2ujHbQzsfFdj_2OUZScfLp9sYgzHCRB2F"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Anshul","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVN_WwwUQBXkKHC5j7Rj4Nrh-YoHmpJGrp97CJ0ZCidvz1hAamz3w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely thrilled with our dining experience—impeccable customer service, a divine "Breakfast Bruschetta," and delightful pancakes left an indelible mark. Should my travels bring me back to Hobart, revisiting this gem is a must.
Wholeheartedly recommend it to anyone in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPB4f_7cT8T5u2US-GZ2qX1QfrtdijnSlR3U06n"],"When":"2024-1-28"},{"Name":"Tea-Maria Constantin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrVad2tulq7kA3c1Iu3DIR4V3A1wO_hNEa8z0SrnLM8LI3kIeA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We went to the Harbour Lights Cafe in Hobart for late breakfast during the week. It was a nicely located cafe, with an overview of the harbour!

We ordered coffees - they were nice. A mango smoothie - tasty but not well mixed and one main meal each.
My partner had eggs on toast with a side of avocado, it was decent, but quite small and I had the Breakfast Bruschetta, which entailed tomatoes with onions, sautéed Mushrooms and Avocado. I also added one poached egg on the side. It was yummy, but it had a little too much seasoning - vinaigrette and oils.
Overall decent food.

As about the service, you just order via a QR-code or at the bar.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbJttLmG3frSp7XYZZEo9GXA4k34GRKOlkVLN7"],"When":"2024-2-21"},{"Name":"AT","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBpQmscjmppRXJqUcIeIzYLgMESPrQL93ucrNghpSS-k0vtg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great location and great food. We ordered bacon eggs benedict and salmon eggs benedic for our breakfast. Service was awesome and staff are helpful, quick, and kind. Unfortunately my partner found a hair on his salmon eggs benedict which obviously not his hair. But it’s not a big deal","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGsLcySGfsc4t2ogq63iSNWTrId7hEFD_xRfNT"],"When":"2024-2-13"},{"Name":"Bailey S (BattlingElk)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU33gy10TODOLIyxhchu776o-4GlyKvopnXoBhfKL8AZckUtfs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely loved this little restaurant, the customer service was on point. [{"Name":"surbhi agarwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQl0vIxe6SL6NQVtaawV-fOb0T-cev9zyk_dFcl38lTdTzFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My brunch experience was delightful. The miso tofu rice bowl I ordered was exceptionally flavorful with a generous portion size. The Strawberry Dream drink was a perfect blend of refreshing and delicious. Overall, I was thoroughly impressed by the quality of the food and the attentive service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPq4H8nSbcWzVXvvkjo7ZDbxHz3cxVrQ_4W7jn_"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Tansy Chau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeCWuKjhrLDcqIhkFWpljUYjTICMrGjdTff6DkENCzHXcS1GZb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic menu. Great variety. Lots of vegetarian options. Asian fusion.

Got the Miso Tofu rice bowl.

Rice was hot, Tofu very hot (fried)
Poached egg was medium-soft, perfect for me
My only criticism is that the edamame was near frozen... But at least it means the bowl assembled fresh! I think if I stirred it and let it sit amongst the hot things for a moment, I never would have noticed.

Beautiful bowl in presentation and flavours. Healthy portion. I was not left hungry!

Friendly staff. Easy location. Steps from the Red Decker bus stop.

Batch brew was aromatic and fruity.

Tuesday just after noon, there was high traffic but I didn't have to wait for a table. Solo diner.

Would come again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBZkx_S_zIQLCPtpGJqpTV6OxyH1XzGg-GZo81"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"Michael Royans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRN6kv4IbCQDS75GrYdv1nL2JmXeiBHh59a6JvaQTdQxrGGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a treasure. Magnificent delicious coffee and amazing brioche egg & bacon burger in our kind of place. Superb friendly service and carefully chosen staff. We will return when next in Hobart from Adelaide.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPs-UnwdmBce0qpGn02_2T5xaVW8joQOZL0lq6m"],"When":"2024-5-2"},{"Name":"Silvia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRZR8a9ioX2wmfZT7_WNbLOKfuBy7-fNCdK9KOu-DdTqPx84s=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best coffee shop in Hobart! Lovely service, amazing food and cozy atmosphere.
Can’t recommend this place enough, food is sooo delicious! 5 stars 🌟","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHl2AfVQr-nkB2jotn9xtm4cWMiMF0zVG27b65"],"When":"2023-12-3"},{"Name":"Jayne Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8ZFqEfPykGErWwDcyxC2CGrf6Olg11-po9BrtSSaqQdgJvY2iew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Lovely coffee, good brunch menu and friendly staff. Take a stroll down the Hobart Rivulet afterward into the city.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBPS3IPCe1GmMhCT8OK0Ul6wLaw99uQyRfI6g3"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"Sofia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf9aDRCvxR0HOJiG6aMT-dFRh-hAM0FPmlrSW0zQ6Z_GIibnsn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing coffee bar, the food and the coffee is 10/10. Staff is really friendly and the vibes are cool. Can’t ask for more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6uYtjbXlVNXg0kn66qxAerv0tkQO_3d0NlN2a"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Josh Weier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaUEl2UhRZmDbM4nnVQP8lCiA6iC3WU0a-DX4qLYIWHLgMeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I thoroughly enjoyed our breakfast here. Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5dHrQYEK7QgKQXOrHkquV6SliIpfgsf4wtbLE"],"When":"2024-2-15"}]

[{"Name":"Matthew Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX90_X79vJyoVbn6godo65__tdOy2aXoZdRMAOX7MDpsV4veCxR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent cafe. Superb coffee, Great food. We enjoyed eggs your way and eggs Shakshuka for breakfast, both were fresh & tasty. Many staff in the small kitchen space, but all working cohesively delivered friendly & prompt service. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVYSinZrkcYSRDLZnngJtp-FfXTKzClx77Ag1X"],"When":"2024-2-8"},{"Name":"Adam Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRel4gHHdm63q4Ubd-65En7g82_1YE6TACUf4DaS77kD7RjwnL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Crowdy place, filled with tourists and locals. We appreciated a lot coffee taste, toast was great too. We ate omelette (a bit to dry) and avocado toast - that one was perfect.
Staff was friendly, kind and had a time for a chit-chat.
I highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3Dl-3GBI_13BeMjjDLwPJ6Bhu9jikJepiyg4c"],"When":"2023-12-30"},{"Name":"Lisa Sutherland-Fraser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYX-aAckD0qXkseqeyrJgVDjoWvGzPtIMQdo79jxw6qaUURrWS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fabulous almond mocha & short mac. Wonderful warm staff even though the place was packed to the gills (it has seating for approx 20).

Cutest little brekkie slider with gorgeous ham, scrambled egg, tomato and chutney in a brioche bun. Delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMDQeSuHjCI46Rzn27nob4YFSsj31bljou1KkZ"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"Ebony Fawcett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWH5pPm8pCMLmtf-qpaNPl7vLvObCOzLORv6Qpj6iv2YqrCgv7NQw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"LOVED this little cafe!
EXCEPTIONAL customer service!
I only dropped in for a takeaway order so wasn’t there long, and boy were they hectic! But the staff were exceptional- still greeting everyone warmly, remembered my name & striked up a conversation while making my coffee.
I manage a hospitality restaurant myself and I was blown away by the customer service skills of every staff member there! I couldn’t help but think how fun it would be to work there- I think I want to put in an application! Well done everyone 🥰☺️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUWpjLk833as_Wo3SgrZSdzeksr8UwL6-JBHhS"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"Tom Law","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDarA6r2IYIKJ7-2t_WeQ7Eojmclw2JWQ7ORSGk0q90jkVMr0n4A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very cosy! Small, warm, yet professional atmosphere, delicious Breakky, lovely staff and convenient location. Not the cheapest but certainly worth a visit","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBtmmGZQe5Ova391Ahuy4UwbdhqPr8d1qSSXjl"],"When":"2024-6-14"},{"Name":"Krish","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQICOF6vI6rH0HNmwW3SMZd2YzbuO1dRueLwLe67nIMyOc-c8W=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Beam me up, Scotty, because I just found best  coffee  in Hobart! Forget warp drive, these roasters have a star trek door .
Inside, the friendly staff greeted me with smiles wider than a Romulan cloaking device.
So, if you're in Hobart and need a break from chasing Tribbles or dodging Daleks, beam yourself up a cup of this incredible coffee! You'll thank me later.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlohlNorsITw-LXhWwTVjEG5kcmadyusFEKQbT"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Brad Cooper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKE6u_ABIVGbh7BCD0cQcaqSfe4LnTvU_QrsiPWF1qNlbRH0VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing gem in the city, friendly happy staff, fast fresh service, food is colourful, wonderfully tasty and freshly made, take away or eat in, this is our new fave in Hobart. Strong great coffee and lovely fresh sweet treats too. See you there!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPivzL9oHIytgm63ZpgHDhyOwyS2G3Jpby3BzVW"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"Carlos J T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbBRIzb5moVhf3DVIpEr5ciOSKCUmsoIcS74poJfZMCGRDgPc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly staff, good coffee and good breakfast.
We had the avo on toast and the omelette.
Bread was good, felt a bit greasy, but I guess it’s the way they prepare it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvYeFrS_WAJ--4twIBfbjenGUvVBVwFOQaoyTn"],"When":"2024-1-24"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Lisa Scully","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzSQ-LN4mTjNETvqm74N_wCKYM5MIwSbEKtKt3XEIlm8ctww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved this little gem! Was beyond happy to find a totally gluten free cafe in Hobart and the food was just so good! The cornbread is amazing and will be heading back for another pretzel and donut for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZ2Cwi__Pox0KXt4HFxlt1BcBBSGZMAcATw4Z4"],"When":"2024-1-6"},{"Name":"Jeremy Smart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJ7UPqxdLQ1mK4_6qGpFFQUnx9-RuTBnXqFK3BViQfjuYRvfRU9g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic Gluten Free cafe in Hobart. Service is outstanding, friendly, knowledgeable and engaging. Watching people walk in and be greeted by their name is testament to the following and popularity of Straight Up. Their coffee is top notch, their GF doughnuts are next level. Delicious 😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTlbisfmq5LaXVC4V_zuoAC1cMw8VCcDy18jOF"],"When":"2024-1-24"},{"Name":"Krystal C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdxDyr-R9ClkX2c4xtcZen-2XcBTA9-5nIP9zVG4_NbeMAkQtN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a week in rural Tas with very little choice and lots of disappointment (food-wise), my cup (and tummy) is full again 😍 Amazing food and being gf/vegan I had more choice than I knew what to do with. Thank you so much for being the best part of the last few days for me (I’ve had a rough run and being catered for makes all the difference)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2XJbpr1RZyF7Cv6CZDjZhqi9OuPng0vU1I1_r"],"When":"2024-3-19"},{"Name":"Fair Dinkum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLdkfXDVdYk88jTRAgphJFlay4jM45sqlIcuF8AlZ_ykCaOg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Poteto Hash is delicious and so are their coffees.

Great service. Friendly staff.

Less waiting time.

Spacious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoKRx7gN876nvn6zzUREZ2kjEU2n1Ql6u-9MbJ"],"When":"2024-4-15"},{"Name":"P and F Rogers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKN_F2e20CAY5758g4xZMbs3oZB52ELTJzGvVEQF4UeAXgG3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Never managed to have a gluten free jammy doughnut before. Simply heaven, thank you. You need to open a branch in the UK 😉","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsq0KgAl2lr0hUZmiOAASmehEoLczaudeBN2_s"],"When":"2024-3-3"},{"Name":"Tavishi Khanna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULkA2XWZUPKACuqPhV3vFaxiWZDuxT8NHaD03AUym1tVsySecY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Straight Up Coffee and Food in Hobart is a vegetarian gem that has won our hearts. Back in 2019, when I called Hobart home, this was my go-to for the best beans in town. Returning this year was a joy as the cafe was just as exceptional. Their food is delicious, and the service radiates warmth and friendliness. And oh, the coffee - it's nothing short of spectacular. A must-visit for any Hobart trip!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPELQ8YF5W4VBaXutKeSNHT7qV0VuYxfidk-QmP"],"When":"2023-10-2"},{"Name":"Sophie Rochecouste Thorpe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiX3krbe9qkgIU8J_pYnRtIR31cx0sdF_A5-dAGScXUQiiBko=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The cutest little café with such friendly service! And 100% Gluten Free makes them a haven for coeliacs. Travel can be tough for us GF folk, but this place has me already planning my next visit to Hobart!!
Everything we tried was absolutely delicious - we got breakfast, lunch to takeaway and couldn't leave without stopping by for another coffee the following morning.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyDV9lKJidAKR21r4DpJ9wQACI1TT2CmuXIFhJ"],"When":"2023-7-10"},{"Name":"Anto Nella","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSvwe6_IYL_qsRh9XYtsviuw-QIaXl2HrXCCYgzrtIlXPXco98_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very nice coffee place with delicious food (vegan and vegetarian available), service is quite fast, staff are friendly. Location is good, pretty central. Seating arrangements can be a little bit tight if going in a big group but still ok. I recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNF0-gkg9cebFvipvdHdAX5kFtjtwBF8HLz2dFr"],"When":"2023-2-4"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ada Okenyo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2cFD4b9cxImzD8G1_XZnH58y44sMopyscfJ3DdgRFKzrI_b1Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The atmosphere of Born in Brunswick is just so nice. The staff are so friendly and you get to always feel comfortable and have a nice chat. The food here is out of this world, such amazing combinations that turn out so well. The drinks menu is also unique and always delicious. Love the plants lining this shop gives it such a warm feeling. The kitchen is also open but doesn’t feel too chaotic.
When coming here it is usually very busy unless you hit the right time so booking is advisable especially if you have a big group.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOi55MIsWcXYcYVHGaaqGRW-GqeRpRn8K-X9ipQ"],"When":"2024-4-19"},{"Name":"Vahid Shahani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcX8iQB182mf9aFofLVsT5fWJPGk1Opbpg110jWgCD7AtbkPTIzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Born in Brunswick in Hobart is a culinary gem offering exceptional dining experiences. I recently tried their octopus scrambled eggs and baked eggs, both fantastic. The octopus scrambled eggs were perfectly cooked and beautifully presented, while the baked eggs were bursting with flavor. Just be cautious of parking signs—I received a ticket for overstaying the 30-minute limit. Nonetheless, Born in Brunswick is a must-visit for food enthusiasts in Hobart.

Thanks 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-YbI59TU9XRs6kMP0HpPJpY2IksmYi2MprHvq"],"When":"2024-4-8"},{"Name":"Ben Trinh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl3MGkcTdv1_sUAS4h6JU6z6cjkBcO7Z1c3ihBDtxg9pGFZ3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had breakfast here during our stay in Hobart upon the recommendation from our brother and we were not disappointed.
Food was prompt and very enjoyable, especially the chill scramble and baked eggs being very well seasoned and coffee was also hard to fault.
The staff were very attentive and accommodating for our 1 year old whilst the decor was very aesthetically appealing.
Will definitely be back next time to try other dishes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9v8HK69FU5liUXwZnvAfZVQQXlUCq9K8ElqBR"],"When":"2024-1-3"},{"Name":"Mandy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYkKVCqvTuwVbOnzy-nlllQou-jaJphG7VRHq0sgGUtSCxsS40=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed a little brunch here with my partner today.

Loved my Tasmanian Octopus Scrambled Eggs. Very flavourful and delicious. Paired very well with the sour dough. My partner also enjoyed his Baked Eggs with a side of Chorizo. No flaws with the food and am happily satisfied. Coffees were great too.

Lovely customer service and a beautiful interior. The only down side was that the food were quite towards the higher end for a Cafe. Whereas the coffee prices were quite cheap. Nonetheless, would definitely come back for more delicious food. 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6MG0P3BWR2x1CF_9_dA1I8eybxi77G-SMpdAk"],"When":"2023-12-30"},{"Name":"Jakob Tate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLg5awN-3UTvtyyX1YIuRoAaFpAV4FSwIzk99ivD9NuknQWRnsj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down the best spot in Hobart for brunch! The vibe is fantastic, with friendly and attentive staff. The food? Unreal, had the Tasmania Octopus with scrambled eggs. A must-visit for brunch lovers!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvhfTXCsJLRlcyz9CoNs6yRlta6_EULDyH1D9e"],"When":"2024-5-10"},{"Name":"HanaYuki Mika","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3-RPYz6rESXMjHYRVcVLYHTMggXmBP8uN45YyE-a2LDzG9CRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"@food.whale1419

The soba and pork belly was to die for!!!

🐷 Didn't expect this brunch place to be so good!!! The soba was well-dressed, sweet, sour and savory. Even remembering it is mouth-watering to me! Paired so so well with the crispy pork belly, soft and crunchy, gave off so many different textures that played well together. 10/10 would recommend this dish.

🍞 The sourdough toast with homemade jam was bigger than expected. The jam was not overly sweet thank goodness, toast was too big for mouth size but other than that pretty decent side.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrHMPsm3WYtcnQQCAfUS9tMn-4J1F3_d8xyt3Y"],"When":"2024-4-15"},{"Name":"Julie Koh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2HPK1DvHch_ETPoPVgGMXfo6IuGE42M5SiWO9T2T69yyMB_UB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I enjoyed a creamy soy chai at a window seat, with the winter sun warming me up very nicely. The latte art was pretty special, maybe an orchid? It definitely made me smile. I also loved the whiff of cinnamon and intense spices in my chai. Service was friendly and very quick. I'll definitely come back for some food next time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMi8YDN6qwstPUk6BfF91eqiNNgEZZfQiIeSZXg"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Daryl “Dino”","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvJec9J6Zx8uHLlu0xz6TdKSUqddQ-0QDOiAdvMAzgFTnGXMc4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A vibrant, bright and modern cafe - very fresh and good lighting. Good service and friendly people -  everyone has been looked after. The food is delicious and was quite pleasantly surprised with its exceptional standard. Coffees were good as well, but food was even better. We really enjoyed our dine in experience here and highly recommend it. Probably the best brunch place I’ve had in Hobart.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqDwoYYzMYIwFR33uPCyf3rgQFtUxEpe2OJGmc"],"When":"2023-6-19"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Michele Gracia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUv3XzF8S0zNvz_zyJOvC2bFioviaYe-Ap8YajixZuLlux-I-EJmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good cafe to hang with friends. Warm ambience and super friendly staff 🧡

The food and the coffee was decent. It’s quite busy in brunch time but the service was pretty quick.  I was having fun with my ginger brown man by the way!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8_Enok5WZniurEQGyXDib1YvoLeCBOXX43evz"],"When":"2023-10-28"},{"Name":"S JJ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQ3Y7hO5QQrvcU3KPaoCDEaLe9ldHk4jrCRMYn6u_5Xn0IDBqtpA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Friday service was amazing and friendly and helpful. Food was fabulous as the photos depict.  Saturday service was not great, no smile no friendliness. Shame as food is amazing and so is atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAF6-d2zrKavxmF7Mqwv5_MfMfVaDOTd8CAWr-"],"When":"2024-4-12"},{"Name":"Megan Chism","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwLXxuLDYKYQyRzdQ4IKtJ5uVE8_26c_zw-xxI6qCtme-LgGznOw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Service was quick and efficient, food was amazingly good, my friend and I both really enjoyed our dishes, I had the breakfast tacos and she got one of the specials (chicken, bacon waffles). There was a young family in with a baby and they let her play with their keys the whole time so it was not very considerate of others dining.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMANl6fbCAe9BbMTealOFZX0NQCLZDeqLoOut6O"],"When":"2024-4-15"},{"Name":"Muaz Selim SOZEN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpECfiAfdTswkHA8Fazp76q259eeHPD-u1YqDlV8i2qYv6HyKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Im gonna do something different and post the empty plates to represent how much we enjoyed the dishes.
When it came to paying, the staff at the cashier got all aggressive just because I asked why they charged 5$ instead of 2.5$ as it shows on the menu. Although I asked how the pricing would be if I add and subtract items 2 times beforehand and just asked why the side was $5, the staff replied: “no mate, the side is five, I couldve added more fore the eggs but I didnt”. Although I had took out the avocado to add eggs and halloumi. Still everything was great overall. Def recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMm-4HDo5dPtVVAnH-g0oQA8NO0UVWal7xX8s3e"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"ELİF SARI","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNiVNL8rSrSc3J8Yx9Td-0XqgAOpVyU6acPDAD1QHw_tW1A0U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favourite cafe in Hobart. I am a grumpy person when it comes to food. I really love here. So delicious food. Service is friendly but professional. I'm GF, egg-free, vegetarian. There are healthy options for me in Ginger Brown that I can't find somewhere else in Hobart. Absolutely my #1 Cafe..Coffee is little bit strong for me-but my husband loves it. Juices and other warm drinks options are good, too.
The only thing I can recommend to the owner would be something like a water fountain that would soften the atmosphere sound wise( it might get so noisy). Some soft jazz/classical music maybe..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDDuQ8-MBc06qaxjF9U0Ri6D-MVUBx8dDRdJR0"],"When":"2024-3-26"},{"Name":"A J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzFr2zp3slGotR14nNJ9clfs3Q4Y8yZDtLOpPdQMPuymjxq6Ub=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Beautiful cafe in a great location, food was amazing. Breakfast tacos 🌮 was yummy. 🤤","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNgH5MMHquHt5TwkTHAl3cHXyex2r241GXjRXp"],"When":"2024-4-18"},{"Name":"Silvia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRZR8a9ioX2wmfZT7_WNbLOKfuBy7-fNCdK9KOu-DdTqPx84s=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hipster coffee shop in the heart of South Hobart. Delicious food and lovely service, coffee is great too.
Nice and cozy atmosphere. We’ll definitely come back 🙂","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfNFwX9n7iG_sCjeOqVj7vHAfMwxXriyovwvOb"],"When":"2023-12-22"},{"Name":"Linda Simpson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXU3v3quy7r63DMgcLvstU5D9RrZ2txlDjt6LJUUorV7hY1Fx6V=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were exclaiming as we ate. Best food that we've had in our Tasmanian stay.
The photos are of the Savoury Pancake and the Baked Eggs.
Also, for black coffee drinkers, best coffee. We asked for a strong long black and they provided it, in spades.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiQpyNhOizBCsZq1B51iOPnU5q4oHHvWdMFLfu"],"When":"2023-11-6"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Good Food Good Mood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrf6WmJWadAsyGM-_mRJiGHyQ0O4Vw9ACtLYSb77IRHutjyHl5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always come to Room For A Pony during my visits to Hobart. Service is quick and attentive – I liked that the barista checked my milk preference before putting my matcha latte order through. Vibe is cute with indoor and plenty of outdoor seating if you can brave the cold during winter.

During this visit, I ordered the huevos rancheros which unfortunately was overly cheesy on this occasion. The egg was also overcooked. Don’t get me wrong, I LOVE CHEESE, but this dish was pretty rich and heavy first thing in the morning… which is a shame given that I had it there two years ago and it was 💯","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAcNW5o5WnX_NuTRT5He_C-7Qb9W3euwtzYrY2"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Adam Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRel4gHHdm63q4Ubd-65En7g82_1YE6TACUf4DaS77kD7RjwnL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We visited Room in a very crowded day. There wasn’t a place for us outside so we took a table inside - there is a plenty of place in this place
We ordered pizzas - it came fast and it was good. Rich in ingredients, with crusty sides. I enjoyed Neapolitana.
Additionally, coffee was good. We didn’t try any breakfast or dessert menu.
Staff was nice.
I can recommend this place!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNq5njVEPobFYSKPOT7QCnhuAp4n31FJpb83_Nj"],"When":"2023-12-31"},{"Name":"Mark Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfd9tuy4_XxV07usy0CNMxXWIb3jsu-yETt_xwuNiCOLefALfOCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All rounder with sixes all the way! Great location, super cool atmosphere and set-up. My family and I were leaving Hobart on our long drive east coast and wanted something to sort us for the trip. Boy did they succeed. Absolutely lovely staff with great personality and accommodating. My wife wasn't feeling the best and the lovely lady came and offered lemongraas tea and ginger. Above and beyond!!! Thank you. Coffee was smooth and tasty and the food, oh my gosh. Beautiful. The best hands down huevos ranchos baked eggs I have ever had. Thank you so much and we will be back! 🤎","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhOZe4QLmcZFua65UVIwMGoYWfIoAuARiMtw6Y"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"Lakshminarayanan M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlKqSifd2k4nRxbGIFOiIo3DMUfNcdFALsPntaIlZguOCqe18z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A must try! Loved the food and vibe. Interesting selection of dishes and drinks. It was perfect for a dinner date with my wife during our Hobart trip. We shared a tasty wood fired pizza and some karaage chicken, both delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNZepWqA3g-B5ye_fQjp1BiaW3vLd_V8mvfJci"],"When":"2024-4-12"},{"Name":"Suze Peach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHjhBBBuLEsdm3unpdYMxwVgsQTpJfENwnelT_8vTV0IAMaytp0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been meaning to go to Room for a Pony for a while now and I am So Glad we finally did!
Cian, who served us, was Very Friendly and Attentive.  The food was quick and hot and tasty.... the only small downside was it was quite echoy in the room we were sat in so I would like to try outside!
Loved it
Thanks to all the Great Smiling staff....!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-5bcZ4-LAgYX5Im2ojaP2r_EMFTKAcNWADszv"],"When":"2024-1-2"},{"Name":"Ciaran Hyland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvhEb9RAWL0VIsQGRgS2p9rm5ceqnWXRpQJQNB97y7HY4yiFCuIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Dropped in on a relatively quiet Monday morning for breakfast and a coffee. The person serving me forgot about my food order and left me sitting around waiting for 50 minutes. I eventually had to ask another waitress if I'd been forgotten about before I was eventually served. I'd finished my coffee in this time and not once did they check in to see if I wanted anything else.
There were plenty of staff walking around. The whole experience ruined my morning, it's not a nice feeling to be forgotten about while people arriving after you are being looked after and served their food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4iqon86CPwWpPEBXspIqDy6K2t_2Og4GZh1to"],"When":"2024-4-15"},{"Name":"Tracy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEfWDDALyvIwtuS1JNt9bftAcNl_ZB1rYTnh-tZ2fQWgJPszD1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Room for a Pony, what can I say the staff Naomi, Cian & Bri were lovely, fun & had great customer service skills. The meal was good also. Only a 15 mintue walk from Hobart City was definitely worth the walk. Thanks again for a great experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM82hCQLa5Ame2A9AIQGqzLcQ6jib9AmnlRWL-w"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Ayisha Riswana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZ3jjSWqSCGqySuB8TaNTQy9z7bCZIYboVNL8GApRk0Dv0JrDM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A beautiful spot to enjoy breakfast! The Chinese fried chilly omelette is a must try item in their menu. Don’t miss it if you are going there! Very good service. This place gave me positive vibes. Will definitely visit again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCLewwgTDRoU5SWa1cj8EphREqBIYYfsa9Efr6"],"When":"2023-5-18"}]
