[{"Name":"Aaron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHekyHTCfzz3Cy1LtwHV_EZhWSu_3WJwOGFvjzXEXKMfgowctIGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sister restaurant to Tipo 00, Osteria didn't disappoint. Service was phenomenal, and their pasta was as good. Too bad we didn't order any steaks as I think it's their signature. Although the portions were a little small, it was delicious! A must try would be their mushroom croquette!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaMM_oV_DZAHpnUQWsP2N_lbWK1iN5thhUc_ni"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"life","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNNSXQ80absRts1C6HvVQZR9xK3DQkfbHi2Nxl0LKVKUzQDjaj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The ciabatta aniseed bread was lovely entree whilst waiting for our mains. We enjoyed the seafood pasta special, the lamb rags was deliciously smooth and tender and the mushroom risotto. We also shared the 500g eye fillet. We felt the servings were small and perhaps should have ordered 2 mains each","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeUP_1sjjAzV83z334umqBOMjGRoHJRnmLIidm"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"Maria Do","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLozF1cmz6RDcrJwFGHBVIxXFHETZKJTCUQwBPikgr_icm65U0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely service. Stand out dishes being the tuna and quince, the dish of the day - truffle pasta with mushroom infused tagliatelle, and the wagyu rump with bitter leaves. The Chef’s Menu is well worth it, especially as a solo diner. Was such great experience sitting by the front window, watching the bustling street as it rained outside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkW65CsQXNXOCUOu7iPqmCSh32u2ybh-KYNr3A"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Peau James Sommer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXExrv9fY3d4a8t5willB052NOCReB86Js7minr5wwBzStmTNw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had been looking forward to trying this restaurant for some time and had high expectations. Or was it too high? The food did not taste as great for what it cost. Many dishes were too sour for our palate. However, the service here was great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNw7HE4JmorLLc69pioraH5RULNO8N5U9sIkVa6"],"When":"2024-3-28"},{"Name":"Frank Fucile","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOjikH7IGk_DIKVQgvC3kbZ_6NyZkzSuYo1W3VYYwiob7F7MDz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Attended the Pride of Piedmont wine dinner in the private dining room. Food was exceptional, standout being the truffle risotto. The wines were also spectacular, paired carefully with every course. Host was friendly and not overbearing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDik9JlzKltyRRSb4wquwaS_YIBuntNGUBwfoC"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"E Chong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIR2oLuLk9fKykaDqQW-Sz43LbClwP1_YHBTCee67ltJP1GA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Like a lot of the reviewers here on Google, my first choice was tipo 00. But boy is it difficult to get a seat there. Osteria ilaria a sister restaurant is just a stone’s throw away, and whoa is this place popular too. Be sure to make a reservation before coming, however do note that there is a charge for no shows (but why would you not show up??)

I was seated by the kitchen counter and it was nice being able to see the chefs work. They were also really nice, and were happy to chat about their kitchen knives lol.

Being a solo diner, I liked that their starters could be ordered per piece. I loved the mushroom croquette, the scallop was good too but the mushroom croquette really stole the show. The lamb ragu with pappardelle pasta was rich and comforting, it really hit the spot for me. I didn’t want the dish to end!

The staff were friendly and helpful with recommendations and portion sizes. I appreciated that they checked in on food allergies as well.

I reckon this place is worth a second visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7Wze-cysNdOWLRqcChpWd0PI80G1OIqeCBDxH"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"Gurjeet Jassaddh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJeWmlRQSO3hvBlw0xES4Y-yVnVbS-jT-6ByfUhMEKTUnMNgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing and very quick customer service. Cannot appreciate enough. They figured out I was pregnant because of my questions, confirmed with me and made sure all the food that was being offered/suggested to me was safe for me to eat.
The food was delicious, tried a few different dishes and they all were good. Everyone just loved the Caramelised white chocolate dessert.
Would love to go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtFc7pZP7mHn3Qt4xVt5s0q5u_KX5FvmGRDmQ"],"When":"2024-3-30"},{"Name":"Mary JV","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsFIaHwmNRSYSFCJ-1wTyIC9AkoX13ZneX6sXxU0zGS4ElnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Our waitress was perfect. She was polite, very delightful and informative.

The food presentation was simple and elegant. I wish it tasted as good as it looked. We were with relatives who made authentic Italian food for over 40years. They were disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdz5N1txjoaH17Ds3yuwB9cm2ynI8cesnnvI_c"],"When":"2024-1-8"}]

[{"Name":"Theang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJL_Zzvrb9GbzajEtEOFml4hm9SQSW9XGBlcBH7yCXbJ_1e=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service and amazing food!
Got in without a booking on a Sunday night and got a seat straight away. Lucky we did, was packed not long after. The food came out pretty quickly, drinks were great with lots of options.
Would recommend to anyone!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKVjWPZYsd0qWrTMAK7N594HNG1MaVdOPf4jM"],"When":"2024-6-19"},{"Name":"Amir reza Hashemi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLw_gMAMNe8T11no7ixrD4183CGv5J1Z_Zb8L8vUDA4V-cSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food in this restaurant is unfairly great! I ate more than I should have, and none of their food disappointed me! Also, great staff. Seats in front of the kitchen give you a very good insight on the great orchestra the chef runs! Will be back for more very soon.

This was my second visit and I was even more impressed with the great food and amazing service. Well done.

And now the third visit sitting in the Kitchen Bar. Food was as amazing as always &  getting to watch the very talented head chef Jenna and the team make the most extraordinary culinary delights is always such a highlight of our visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUY7N0gP7NCi2mEVxzRrXmCT2c10JGNOSwDOAp"],"When":"2023-12-27"},{"Name":"Cici Wright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmIXqwbU2TQlsVXkFWWUxjy8j_wmaPZyHTb4fcBBAIFZkwPfs-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favourite Asian fusion in Melbourne. All dishes are so tasty, light and fresh. My third time here and it never disappoints. Great atmosphere, great service, great food. A Melbourne staple and it lives up to the good reviews. Must visit if you are in the city and looking for an amazing experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhjwcS7A8-3Z1f0lDXnevBQtc55PramJbGfVsI"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Jasmine Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKVfDQLsSoWV_aeOTijpJkrMvtteh6CtRi-7MeoBWKMw5Pwm_k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a lovely first time experience here for my best friend’s birthday!
Upon arrival they seated us promptly and took our coats, they had a large selection of drinks as they have an extensive bar range and we even got recommended some of their best selling cocktails.
We had the 7 plate course which costed us $78 pp, each dish was flavourful and unique with their asian fusion flavours (personal favourite being the stuffed eggplant) and was more than enough to feed the both of us.
The atmosphere was lively and it contained this open kitchen setting with ambient lighting, I thoroughly enjoyed the music as it keeps a bustling environment.
Customer service was impeccable - especially from the man with head tattoos! Always checking in on us and ensuring we were having a great time.
Would highly recommend this restaurant!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjKd3xOuEv8k6NqveonuVuxyRu-Z9yEiYah0O4"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"Jing Kuan Tan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxbeXFGJLyTwfRxsX1Y0IbEySiSTrdP86c_3Ybl8QzBTXWooaI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food. Loved the fried rice, and roti was pleasantly exquisite. Drunken chicken was good and went well with Jasmine rice. Crispy pork in the bun was crunchily superb. We will come back again.... and... Lucy Liu is NOT the actress 😀","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLDyAs0ZCNTZaqzHF3tsQkRdk22RNEKmYpbrSN"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Michael Kenzo Kennedy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURwUKX9sZO6OknBmJU1kr3xwl2VUhR6lyzT2VgWy_i6V-_QOSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm having a great night at Lucy Liu. We've got the 7 plates tasting menu and there's some bangers on it, like the Cauliflower, sashimi, and salad. The rest of the food was okay. Will definitely come back to try the other dishes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPGfcDv1x7T-3jgKEaMLNk0FLsaPkkfCzsFoiV"],"When":"2024-5-10"},{"Name":"CHOI YIHYUN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJktDAC6nRw6AVaVXlakCq8cV9tnN3LVj3Pqcw4SCZWiugeXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First of all, there are two doors. one used only as an exit and one as an entrance. I got quite confused about where the entrance was and wandered around for a while. To get to the point, it was just okay. There were mistakes with my order, and the staff seemed busy, so it took a long time to order. However, the service got much better as the meal went on, so the initial mistakes didn't bother me too much. Also, you can find the menu by flipping over the illustration on the table. I spent some time figuring this out because the staff didn't mention it at first. They seem to want to give the restaurant a unique character, but they should explain things better to the customers.

It was the weekend, and I was dining alone, so I sat at the bar table. Here, it seems the head chef informs the staff when the food is ready in the kitchen. The chef's voice must get tired... Anyway, the kingfish was not bad. The cream on top was unique, and it balanced well with the distinctive sauce. You probably don't need to order the oysters. I was looking forward to the pork knuckle dish... but I should have ordered something else. They served fried pork knuckle (similar to the German dish Schweinshaxe), and it was tough to cut. It would have been better if it had been pre-sliced in the kitchen. The dish is meant to be eaten like Peking duck, with thin pancakes and vegetables, but it was too different from what I expected, and I didn't enjoy it.

The apple kimchi pancake consisted of kimchi made from shredded apple and a thin pancake. The texture and sweetness of the apple weren't bad, but it lacked the distinctive tanginess of kimchi, which was disappointing. The hoisin sauce was too ordinary. It would have been better with both hoisin and chili sauce. Throughout the meal, I kept thinking the food just lacked flavor. Not that it was bad, but it didn't taste like much. It would be better to order dumplings, buns, and a small main dish instead. The dessert was delicious, though. As for whether I'll go back... I'm not sure; I'll have to think about it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDh2feqHGh3WL7wJn9pYazp0hREHi5T3VMopxY"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Alain Ludva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLM5tFYtY4l8uUOMCEMwBbGVrWoLKwXXuG7XztvAeIsmYKTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What an incredible evening! We chose the "Let Lucy Choose" 7 plate experience and it did not disappoint! Amazing food, incredible service, awesome wine suggestion by the friendliest sommelier (Thank you!). They easily accommodated our gluten free (celiac) requirement with no impact on the experience! The setting is beautifully done, great atmosphere! Thank you for a wonderful evening!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcAJhG4cU29aZZTbQszOnp_uOknq3-AEcngTAt"],"When":"2024-2-15"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jennifer Lum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3KjSyIL9afbNB9Mb7fVAqFCaamcjUMoujwMy69yTohI4hjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We recently dined at Farmer’s Daughters for our anniversary dinner. Having heard good reviews we had high expectations!

Service was great and timely and the restaurant upstairs had a nice ambience. I was obsessed with the La vie en rouge cocktail - from presentation down to its taste, it was delicious.

The first two seafood dishes were flavourful and had complimentary flavours.

However, the Pork dish was overly salted for my liking with the pairing sauce highlighting the salt - the pork was also raw in the center which in hindsight I wish I said something about.

The beef dish after the pork, came out rare which may not be to everyone’s liking however did taste lovely with the Jerusalem artichoke and side.

The dessert would’ve had a nicer touch if the sponge was moist.. it was well presented however lacked punch.

Overall, we were a bit disappointed given the price point of $135 per person for the Gippsland getaway, maybe it was just the off night!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxaSp3KmLb0rKX_kqNc1TxXNGNWI2jEDqc9eU5"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Stuart Mitchell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWB66XKuLjL4-5o8iyAvMyGy4MOBykKVL4tipbsPDeZctYN3fWI_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Farmers Daughter in Melbourne offers one of the best dining experiences I’ve had. The dishes are not only delicious but also beautifully presented, making each bite a delight. Paired with their phenomenal wine selection, the meals here are a treat for the senses. The atmosphere is warm and inviting, perfect for a special night out or a casual meal with friends.

The staff at Farmers Daughter are truly professional, taking you on a journey with each meal and wine from Victoria. Their knowledge and passion enhance the dining experience, making it not just a meal but a memorable culinary adventure. If you’re looking for a dining experience that captures the essence of Melbourne, Farmers Daughter is a must-visit. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0sZApMuaiYevIUcSm7rg-Lw73-WxNNvjjinBw"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"Sohee Yun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWukkCGeTkWyRiWns-HxRaDb1k2uFAkPpghv-E5BYwHuu5c4MwJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We did the dinner course menu. The service is superb and our wait staff were very knowledgeable and professional.

The dinner began very strong but when we got to the 2 meat course, the first thing that hit me was too much salt. I understand that we need salt to bring out the flavour, but the salt hit me so hard, that’s all i could think about instead of the flavour of all the things on the plate. I think it was just the meats that were salty not the garnish that came with it.

But anyways, atmosphere was fantastic.

The food was good, but I’m giving 3 stars because I’m taking the price into account.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3pPbaq9KTZIaLE3XS6jgth37igtODUR88faC4"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Mo Bamba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqSxznJEsc3leavl2dSTL-o9TONaBewlu1E2WDqPxynoNM0JWH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The 5 course menu costs $135 + $100 for the wine pairing 🍷

The food was good and very nicely presented. The trout dish was the highlight.

The only feedback is because it was a busy night and some courses were slow to come out. The timings of the wine pairing could have been better as by the time the corresponding dishes came out, we had nearly finished the glass of wine that was poured 😅

As other reviews have mentioned, it can get quite loud (think pub level noise) so be aware if you’re after a more quieter dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAgw8drn-WUjYdu0bIu5lEMvEZmzqwpNhD2IEJ"],"When":"2024-2-15"},{"Name":"Vitor Ten","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPRuX7yIVZV78qUuDcwc2BzG6n9fLQbE53e2vpTRCHMfeBFIY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Mains come on a small dish instead of a full sized plate just to make the portions seem larger. The beef scotch fillet $68 was chewy, the market fish $44 was too sour and the two of them lacked any veggies so I had to order a broccoli side dish at $18. Overall too pricey for the portions served and the taste. PS Also there was a 10% surcharge","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPs6nN2HN7pdZYTwUvhCyeE84COjz48CQbwHOva"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Anna Pritchard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5RYz_AlP83Mvk8IQER2ZqxvM1F5K4dSGHQtYpcsY6dDEKLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went for dinner and had the $85 set menu. It was so much food. We struggled to eat it all. Everything was perfect. The greens were so fresh and crisp. The meat was tender and juicy. The chips was seasoned and addictive. And that’s only one part of the dinner. I could go on!

The chefs and serving staff were exceptional. They worked so incredibly hard to make it a special experience. We couldn’t fault them. We would 100% go back here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuBikW0Wfy2V9FdT1EanF2SaryJXlFyTWD94Ij"],"When":"2024-2-12"},{"Name":"Shawn Wilmoth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSLt4k8dU7KIfiSA1FnZuHWhRnoSp6dXMwm68nVh9vPa0dQy7eBg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic service and food. Get a reservation is what I recommend but… We stumbled in about 8:30 as the vibe looked great driving by. The bar we saw had 2 settings ready and the maître d’ said she just had a cancellation.  Good for us!  I have a ton of food allergies and they avoided them all with the plates you see. Some of the plates are my wife’s. I you are in the city I highly recommend you try to eat here. ALL food is farm sourced from a large nearby farming area and has farmers owners ( ironically no daughters though :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMts7WRSs9GzDiCQj4vy4aUckvAF02ONLVhGW3T"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Chiliong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9AGKMvTyspIlfdQk271qQnucMRQVFWFxyYm69T5jIAiTxkA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A flashback review. Went to this restaurant recommended by friend. We ordered $125 set menu sitting on the bar watching how the chef making the food. Enjoyed the delicacy and creativity of each dish. It's my first time experience of such high quality food but the place is bit cramped and noisy for good chat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYvEhiS2nRr8aWo-LYd6WBZGxuSHzudKIvH5CX"],"When":"2023-3-2"}]

[{"Name":"Elle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWV0FujL2Yi1ocAN0_lUvwCjCjG-Ev2wX3D9ql_1-90xRKqQ1o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely a great experience! My partner and I were down visiting from Brisbane, and this was the first place we ate at once we arrived, and what a way to go into Melbourne’s foodie scene!
The food was phenomenal, so fresh and so much flavour! There was ample vegetarian/vegan options, which was greatly appreciated. In top of the amazing food, the service was exceptional! The staff were all so incredibly friendly, helpful and knowledgeable.
Will definitely be back on our next visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNR0nuk-dMOuLzEWe6lbaga2KUremKAfbtU_xyw"],"When":"2024-1-31"},{"Name":"Em Clare","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ70VbCetGRbJGCTAbIOV3izvFjoRdZ4XL6a5gzWbelNfgaOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"really great vegan options & and easy to read menu with the allergens stated on there. loved all of the dishes served, had several lovely waiters & waitresses who were all on the ball.

only thing is would love some more non-alcoholic options for drinks that aren’t super fruity!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhSbCreYWXW5BhqW7KL-wHdFPmACwjj-zs5Zbz"],"When":"2024-5-3"},{"Name":"Trang Ngo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFhPeR7nL0FFwIXR8RhIyR6WbHb2Pg8etv5dvWkNvWok9ZzussRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a delightful experience at Rice Paper Scissors. Their crispy barramundi was an absolute highlight, perfectly cooked and bursting with flavor. The coconut cups were yummy too. The crispy duck leg was a bit salty, recommended to eat with rice or sticky rice. The ambiance was cozy, and the service was impeccable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmHCKoFZ_jFPHvXUKOHO-uBp9J7AELteB2WVO3"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Lanie B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHg22SC-9KCHIYF66lECW1fLI8kFGa9eQVJAB-TI81Gvy_uQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food were tasty and good portion.I like everything on the menu. We were surprise their chicken spring roll is quite bigger than usual😁.
The staff were great, they were attentive and helpful.
I would recommend this place","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpyz-cffm7tZ-FjkTO465Q4fw0b6giuEnFKpB_"],"When":"2024-3-15"},{"Name":"LS W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKtmOQ-zLb8SB_PlDCm9x6nJX5LEHnQvA2atXWO6n4L3TnE9Ph=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came for lunch on Saturday at 12pm with no booking, was offered a seat outside. Ordered the feed me menu which came with 5 plates to share. Great gf options however not sure if coeliac safe. We ordered the:

Mushroom larb - was alright, needed more salt
Crispy king prawns 👍 - came out hot and crunchy
Thai fried chicken 👍 - crispy and tasty, can’t go wrong with fried chicken
Crispy barramundi - I liked the apple salad but the fish was a little tasteless, needed some salt
Yellow beef curry 👍 - delicious curry packed with coconut cream, beef cooked to perfection

Opted for the dessert:

Sticky pineapple pudding with passionfruit sorbet - unique flavours but a little too sweet for me

Service was fantastic, everything explained to us when we arrived. Felt very welcomed! Food also came out fast. Highly recommend this place!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-kmeeAshM91BYywJrv_XVjn5kYibIzVN5REqq"],"When":"2024-5-11"},{"Name":"Christina Huynh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyL-RLdaIOjA5hbaPZqnL2N9vfnHXKObk3ArCw0rHsjIJ-_v1DeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely recommend. Love the lunch option to get 5 plates to share for a set price. I really liked the watermelon dish appetizer, the snapper ceviche, and the thai chicken. My friend really liked the tofu. Friendly staff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONuCV-eooxylGcbEdmAS04wo3o8-KVfPe5OD8x"],"When":"2024-2-21"},{"Name":"niki_ yuv","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVACfnfH06wXvdaqnHC83vPFCJOiR2yNZ7MhJFmNdsb_jBxqJDh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Absolutely loved the food, very refreshing and delicious. The beetroot curry was flavourful. The crispy barramundi served with green apple salad was a good unique combination and the mushroom larb was to die for. Highly recommend this place for their amazing fusion Asian food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRbQn-_Ho3lvzEc4THRJC8cM-TPIwrCjlSED45"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"Tu Phan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvht1F1yElsKp6G9W6Azghkf38gN9WPtozrOn7ViFSeX_C1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We went here spontaneously on a Friday night around 6:30pm to which we were accepted without a reservation. The restaurant was for the most part full, so we were quite surprised they gave us a table. However, 15 minutes after being seated at the table, there was a long queue of walk-ins waiting outside for a table. So if you do decide to come here, definitely make a reservation.

From the get go, staff were beyond friendly. We had a waitress introduce herself and advise us she would be serving us for the night. We were seated outdoors and despite being a very cold night, we were kept warm throughout the dinner thanks to the outdoor heaters beside each table.

Food came out slowly and in our opinion, was average. We ordered the share menu with the following dishes:
- crispy coconut cups 6.5/10
- coconut snapper ceviche 7/10 (not enough ceviche for the amount of wonton wrapper)
- pulled lamb bao 6.75/10 (lacking flavour - some sauce would have made this 7.5/10)
- crispy king prawn 6.75/10
- Thai fried chicken 7.5/10

Cocktails on the other hand were AMAZING. Highly recommend the That Lychee Drink and  Vietnamese Espresso Martini!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0Sj-NcW3sBUlaFJ7jFypJy8JRGhGpF8ThUo9o"],"When":"2024-5-24"}]

[{"Name":"Deboo Chatterjee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUn0s7-8E1zb-_DMizXY9tTHeGdvfKvTVFbp2-Veo9yTjHG6DBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Dinner at Cumulus Inc. was an interesting experience. It didn’t start well. We had made a booking in advance for a special night, which was mentioned in the booking, but the host thought it was fine to seat us at the bar table along with others. This was very disappointing. When I expressed my dissatisfaction, he told us that we would have to wait another 45 minutes to get a table. At that point, I decided to go to another restaurant. He then suggested taking us upstairs, though he mentioned we might not like the place.

However, when we went upstairs, it was a totally different vibe. It was classy and quiet, unlike downstairs, which had a very basic and noisy atmosphere. I can’t help but wonder why he didn’t put us there in the first place, thinking the bar table was suitable for celebrating a special night.

Things changed for the better once we were seated at the table. The server was extremely friendly and informative, genuinely showing compassion and care about making our night the best it could be. She checked on us frequently and had friendly chats with us. The food was simply delicious. We chose the 6-course chef special, and it was worth it. Every item had a beautiful presentation and was filled with flavors. The cocktails were delicious too. The vibe was perfect, with beautiful lights and atmosphere.

I would have given 1 star, but thanks to the server and the food, I’m giving 3 stars. The team needs to reflect on why we were treated like that initially. It could have been the perfect night for us, but the initial sourness lingered throughout the evening and was the only topic we discussed at the table.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFNZ0xyDlqKtUiIeAGfjsn01EpEQ77ByhcEdDH"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Pete Sanders","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEw32AVd1aLlWSP-hWvYCuWTbuwFSAbFRFQHKmz_7zyTe_6XkoQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cumulus never disappoints and is a definite ‘go to’ in Melbourne. We had a lovely Tuesday night dinner. Great service as always. The slow cooked lamb was great, and we got the half serve as there was only 2 of us. The pleasant surprise was the tuna tartare was outstanding.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzZy9hZWw5hak-V9tc_doKppnuA1QJE0zqgY08"],"When":"2024-3-31"},{"Name":"Giacomo Pianta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdgJopgSQu3Si4B6LBf0XUCq7Gn6yprclC6aFebjrFXScudiNaCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"📝 Had lunch here with an overall positive outcome. Very polite service.

🍴 All food I had was good and really modern. I liked very much the ricotta pie and also found the octopus dish perfectly balanced in taste. Friggitelli were ok, personally didn't like too much how they had been marinated.

📍 The restaurant is pretty and has a cool open kitchen, however the room temperature was too low for me and I felt cold throughout the whole lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyMrpZhVeBf4LnZ9BrBUOcRHCoUg7uJAmWh_Dl"],"When":"2024-3-10"},{"Name":"Alexander Unkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMoMM0XSZ2F9SLs5_RuxBNueWM13L8tJjR_97uYQqvKoWcCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chefs menu was superb, one of the better meals I have had in Melbourne. The staff were amazing and put together a menu for my wife who is vegetarian. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIH8ctYi2WEjm9AO_ak2Uwt8urH3fHBpykiSPx"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Michael Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWo3mVchPqNY1efHNhBscTESHlfKG0oYV4dCVR2CnHtH-B9g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered a Chef Selection which has a very nice mic and balanced dishes.

The main course lamb is very good as well.

Although the dessert is a little small, me and my friend has a lovely dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxMo7cgqI-0kcLfkKHb8HrzXLLb191IWEB9xvL"],"When":"2024-2-4"},{"Name":"CHOI YIHYUN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJktDAC6nRw6AVaVXlakCq8cV9tnN3LVj3Pqcw4SCZWiugeXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered a selection of shared dishes. I realized it was a mistake, not just with the menu but also with the restaurant choice. I have no intention of revisiting, and here’s why

1. Noise like eating in the middle of a market

- I couldn’t even understand what the other person was saying, let alone hear the explanations of the food. It felt like eating in the midst of a crowded Victoria Market.

2. Terrible service

- First, I ordered a drink, and without a word or explanation, a bewildered staff member just left a can at my table. I tried to understand it might be because they were busy. Then, it took 20 minutes between clearing my plate and waiting for the next dish. Staff repeatedly passed by my table ignoring the empty plates. Meanwhile, they kept checking on other tables about their food but didn’t say a word to me. Was I just supposed to eat whatever was given? The main dish and side dishes were supposed to be served together, but I received the main dish and one side. The staff said they would bring the other side dish soon. I waited patiently, and it arrived almost at the end of my meal. Even when I wanted to pay, I had to wait 15-20 minutes more because the staff were chatting with each other. The restaurant wasn’t even full. What’s the problem here? Even the chefs seemed out of it...

3. Poor seasoning of the food

- The menu itself wasn’t bad, and the ingredients were fine. But the food was just salty. So salty that I kept looking for water. But then the main dish, lamb shoulder, was completely bland... How am I supposed to adjust to these flavors?

I dined alone, and the total cost was about $130. This was the worst restaurant experience I’ve had in Melbourne, and I don’t plan on returning. I’d rather get a sandwich and coffee from the cafe next door. it would be much more worthwhile.

And now that I think about it, I have no idea what I was supposed to do with the radish and miso sauce. Was I supposed to spread it on the bread, or just dip the radish in the sauce and eat it? Thinking back, they didn’t explain anything.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvFztRgup-z-e0-r8i40O-H076XiEEpf4HIqVr"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Foodie Files Melbourne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM5uVXT4DD1mNnhzCgfM7R2bueoDXnFhZpq01MdYcQrWvBRkUI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It’s been about 6 years since I’ve dined at Cumulus and after today’s lunch I’m asking myself why. The lamb shoulder was phenomenal. The potatoes were incredibly flavoursome. I loved the tuna tartare and the coconut cream pana cotta was a lovely light way to finish. Staff were very attentive also. I definitely won’t wait another 6 years before returning","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDssEEESvE82ls5Re5KTOb1g_7DhlsSw-suP2y"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Kim T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVboALQcvWxEuAY68W0Le5g51b6d0xq5d2tmYCjc6q3R11_KZmx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A truly delightful experience.

We ordered a selection of shared dishes.

Food: Each dish has been curated with careful thought and care - the depth of flavours were remarkable. Some stand out dishes were the heirloom zucchini and the tuna tartare.

Service: attentive end to end. Our server was fun, considerate and had excellent wine recommendations to pair with our dishes.

Atmosphere: kitchen bar seating was a great experience - it was great watching the food being prepared. Lovely ambience overall.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeVwOERwxfJbsyJSmlHnFg4Jx5WbHAey807svP"],"When":"2023-12-21"}]

[{"Name":"Aliya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPPeOobaIx3iSElgEDM6DY-65XW7TTiUImRsIRij0enCiI5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, good came out very slowly, we totally enjoyed it. It was my birthday and they had a little card on the table and even gave us the sharing soufflé  on a separate plate. It was so delightful. Best restaurant I’ve ever been to. Only this restaurant made my birthday special and enlightened our whole Melbourne trip.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_0JKgj4_0GIa6Q1isZ73wec9QTCQz9dmBDXFG"],"When":"2024-6-7"},{"Name":"TravelYoung_byDodong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwXMaKrH5c1VN8oDkJVYROSVwQptqJMRKDa-YyqglRwOnFXTS2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Are you searching for a sophisticated dining experience in Melbourne with excellent service? I highly recommend Florentino. Although I cannot speak for the food, the ambiance and the staff are simply amazing. However, the portion sizes may be smaller than expected, so keep that in mind while ordering. On a positive note, their desserts are a must-try, as they are known for their delectable taste.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBu5wNMXaAzLA6kp-aSKhyRt6lIo5cDEIsqWED"],"When":"2024-3-8"},{"Name":"Aaron Hurley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQcccbYKu0eEhPWmnUm6E_uwgGg0Tt4XKtKeJJS6U_umKZGSvM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Literally the best Italian food and service I’ve ever had! My photos don’t do the food justice.
While it may seem like the dishes are pricy, we got given at no cost - olives, breadsticks and fried tortellini for entree; the best freshly baked bread; and sorbet for dessert.
Our waitress was friendly, knowledgeable and so genuine.
I will go back as often as I can.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYMIMZFFKzqyGoXTQDrWzjNdGSK-6GWD-lhnhB"],"When":"2024-3-13"},{"Name":"Rafael Rodrigues","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXz439rMH9riCO8Bv0lZtkOC6wNnmXy8UxoyYKjmSqBIT44rGYH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honestly one of the best Italian restaurants we ever been. Made us feel like we were back in Italy.
The food was really delicious and the service too. Staff were very carrying and friendly.
Really recommend if you want a true 5 star Italian experience .
And thank you for the little present .
We Will definitely be back when we visit Melbourne again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqWPC5XCqZDPRzeSkwH354vXkgjMDZk-bcpE2B"],"When":"2024-1-30"},{"Name":"Karen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHDyK-arpPNiufvXXNdBCLdUme3mG9D1uvbrsciTXQLByIhvelDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely exquisite dining experience! The food was full of so much flavour.
I highly recommend the tortellini, it had so many layers of flavour.
The staff where very helpful and welcoming, and excellent in assisting us with the menu (I couldn’t understand most of it) and drinks.
The cheese cart is especially impressive!

Definitely a restaurant to wear a suit or a cocktail dress to ;)

I would also like to make a note that the anchovies and cheese puffs served with the breadsticks where delicious! I usually can’t stand anchovy, but it was very subtle and complimented the cheese well.

I also highly approve of the pre-dessert palate cleanser. It was just such a beautiful restaurant!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoe50eQn6y1Ip9JZx6VxhpS31xSj1XNgs9h_it"],"When":"2023-12-22"},{"Name":"Matteo Di Graci","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDvGkic82ve2geG4KuQF94SS5L777TAVVQKO-Jrvkr7k2Gbw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was on the evening of May 10th with some friends for dinner. We arrived as walk-ins at 8.45 and were presented with an unset table to start; the atmosphere and location are certainly beautiful and refined, but this cannot justify the low quality of the food and service.
Sorry for the Italian boy who served us but the maitre gave a super inattentive service as if we were second class customers (they made me taste the wine and then it was poured for all the other diners and not for me, which in a restaurant of this level I consider it quite serious to remain without wine for more than 10 minutes)
As an Italian, the pici with rabbit were completely tasteless, loose and perhaps 60 grams; the chicken perhaps even worse described as chicken we were served half a chicken not even cooked who knows how!
I don't usually give negative reviews but the previous night I also had a stomach ache probably from the rabbit!
Terrible experience and sorry because the boy who served us was very nice and probably very busy with other tables, given the lack of staff in the room probably!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPW4pQ7VEv7w46NoxL1wq5-tFnjYanUwzwlQzlk"],"When":"2024-5-10"},{"Name":"Sam Micich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9uVPgPVBc2ozsfnvd73OMnyfYIDxUfjgFzF3t8bsP7gTy06o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I hadn't been here for years. We were a larger group and the service and staff were impeccable.
I've given 4 stars for the food as some dishes were sensational: the wagyu special, all of the seafood starters, and the chocolate souffle (light as a feather). But I didn't enjoy the flavour of the olives, the potatoes in duck fat should have been amazing but were bland, and the batter on the zucchini flowers tasted oily and bland. So among plenty of hits, there were a few misses. At that price point I expect all hits.
The building is beautiful and the dining room has been very sympathetically renovated. It feels opulent yet intimate.
When we asked to share the souffle for dessert, the kitchen very kindly served us two smaller individual souffles. This was definitely a wow moment, and the perfect serving size after a big meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqd-uV0IlpaCEOq8QSciwta3rjcPcVY69yE0JD"],"When":"2023-12-14"},{"Name":"Eddie Limic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2gbVoBqeZgJEQwrzTv7Na26bS_KxKUqVgnP9VQxUSJe5g_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Menu items I felt were as if they were too fancy and the quality of it didn’t live up to the rest of the reviews on here, I do feel as thought if they had some more ‘typical Italian’ items it could have been amazing. The cocktails were amazing.

the service of all the staff was beyond Amazing, they were all super friendly, helpfully and wonderfully communicative.

Beautiful atmosphere for private dining, not anything special aesthetically but nice classy vibe.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Joanne Romios","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIIfJPEYrC1MXuVkTbQoDktPegDs_ow0ZACOXQEOmI_O_VPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food and amazing service. Thanks to the team here today, who went out of their way to accommodate our family (with a child who is autistic). We were moved upstairs to a quieter area and were even asked if we needed the music turned down- which we didn’t :) every single plate that came out was just perfect, beautifully seasoned, so tasty. Delicious. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8kN_ZP5JODKQ6fLJvDVMWTtigqWYbgrsb-_OL"],"When":"2024-5-11"},{"Name":"Anita Lyovic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtpg-r7QImbOmJs2WbSYBTD89ag2AIa_7KJTbTpzZdKs5sYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A thoroughly exceptional experience. The staff were friendly and knowledgeable and the food was superb. We had the deluxe set menu and everything was incredible! Incredible flavours and presentation was beautiful. Will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIoR2Y2wpgvBXpB8SF-o-CtVxtRHeIezW258OV"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"Emily Ge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQgcq5JXdIYnWLc4qgk8039m-GJWo8ez1b9aYJRIKxvy_bKTc3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food and vibes. Staff extremely friendly. Our waitress Natalie definitely made our dinner more enjoyable. She was very enthusiastic, approachable and professional! Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGwg-gT6iSM9LYOFZpIHI_rya4vGSqmLExhS_1"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"Sarah North","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXF9Nam0crlGMZlqKEjSIRF9t6hGlvVQi5GGBdGzREFmBl-rOH6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you haven't eaten here, go now.
Food: everything was amazing!
Service: attentive, friendly without being over the top
Atmosphere: relaxed and comfortable.

The beef empanadas were were crunchy on the outside with a tasty filling. The Foccacia was very light and lovely with the whipped butter. Grilled calamari was the best I'd had in a long time. The lamb was custed and well cooked on the outside yet very tender on the inside- so good! The sides of zucchini and potatoes were generous and great. We couldn't finish all the food so took leftovers home in a container
Would definitely return","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNal2jGdNgVox2aLZoHbF2dT9JH26sNwM51VKj5"],"When":"2024-4-20"},{"Name":"Justine G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHjnkw5-WrFzMhAWXfL2pJGH35fQuT7iQ_eIpXH50QF1dGMg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, food was fantastic so flavourful. Nice paced dinner didn't feel rushed. Welcoming environment
Steak was amazing and loved all the entrees","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmbRqzvSozen7PAqGVxjB5NMxDBUNp91h5RNYF"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"Anna Pietrolungo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxpgsjxkSv9ItS9GrR2yT7B4PCfDIPAy4U086MUDSIkn9eG70=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a wonderful lunch at Palermo restaurant. The food was delightful and plentiful. Tasty deliciousness in every bite. It was fascinating watching the very calm chefs in the kitchen and the staff were very attentive and accommodating. Love this place and well worth returning to.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiliWenZH3-VvyX6WEixnme7UTHd9Kuw3Xxv99"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"June Dang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2ITw-4DMFwfPfHtl8JHlfIYt44XCRWS1_pcpxIjhyWI58BA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What can I say! Delicious foods, terrific staff (Natalie) and cool/relax/ jazzy ambience. There’s background music but it’s played at a reasonable volume so we can still talk without screaming at each other.

We got the empanadas for entrée which is delicious with crispy shell and well seasoned fillings.

The Chorizo is great to have with the chimichurri and salsa!

Both the steak cuts and roasted carrots are all amazingly cooked! We do prefer the skirt steak more though.

Shout out to Natalie for being such a great host to us for the day!

Thank you Palermo for a great experience! We will visit again! :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMO74yIk2QMXS4rqBXxzDn9Bvo1OQj6jQDaPeXx"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"Joel and Sylvain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtS49-vtXEBcSWm4LR_Lo_WHYHi57Pm7XKlmCD5bCL9ZbzrYo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"💙💛 Chic Argentinian steakhouse featuring charcoal-grilled meats.

Indulge in the smoky allure of an authentic Argentinian culinary experience at this chic steakhouse. Nestled in the heart of Melbourne, the restaurant boasts charcoal-grilled meats that are tender, flavorful, and expertly cooked to perfection.

From succulent ribeye to mouthwatering tomahawk, each dish is a celebration of Argentina's rich gastronomic heritage. The ambiance exudes elegance, making it an ideal spot for a romantic dinner or a sophisticated gathering with friends. With impeccable service and a menu that showcases the best of Argentine cuisine, this steakhouse promises an unforgettable dining experience.  Also, Palermo offers a diverse array of wines to complement your meal.

You won't be disappointed with this restaurant.
This restaurant is definitely worth a visit.
You'll love this restaurant, I assure you.
💛💙","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWw2KO5Uup8ePGbGnmJVZs1IOfzFN_gMAZgHqj"],"When":"2024-4-14"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Nick Gentner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTJjJivrWzvOgZmWSzVIscL-uhoNrhXmB3I8nGESr6uTllpw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just awesome!

Basically everything was a highlight, from the service to the wine list, the setting in Hosier Lane and particularly the food.

Of the food, the anchovies with the tomato sorbet, the sardines, the mushrooms and the flan were the standouts. The verdejo wine was also particularly good.

This place definitely comes recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNguKPAxIDukl_BmizpveydYlVEBM591KPu2XZ"],"When":"2024-5-11"},{"Name":"Stephany Tanizaki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-M2fDtqgGjN0rg99buNSWxnLd7m-4nEH6atTSTfmI9JFvGatl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really nice place to seat down and enjoy some drinks with your friends! The service was on point, from the moment we book the table until the end! The food was overall really good, just the fish had too much bones. Would love to come back and try different tapas ✨","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4Bt05uoM2dwKbq3MbBmrx2pNLXuTZrC27iUrK"],"When":"2024-2-9"},{"Name":"Angel Khong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUclkqITYfc7Hb5-vgjuDeacBepTyuu5kLvxhAdtl1YqD-OIEdR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had their set menu for dinner; menu seemed to have changed a lot over the years and even though their food remained creative; they were all on the really salty side and there was less tapas-style dishes. Same amazing cozy atmosphere and good service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBPIjUC7UM4faL_1mvWNtaZ7EFWPj6Bt5Mp8L2"],"When":"2024-2-26"},{"Name":"Rachel R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAdIPN7YBIa8kmoQVV3IFUt6rnIl3WBK_3Lq1DssvA52ShY1-njQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Forgot to write a review back when I went in November, but I LOVED this place! Hands down some of the best Spanish food I've had outside of Spain.

I highly recommend the Cecina which is wagyu beef and truffle potato foam (posted a video of what it looks like) and this is probably the best thing I've had in my life, just amazingly delicious.

The venue is slightly loud indoors, a fair warning for those who get a bit of sensory overload like myself, but other than that I would absolutely come back here when I'm next in Melbourne.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbuHtV-LYXr6RltanN8gn2w3pDzpbkiub8UUp3"],"When":"2023-11-11"},{"Name":"Kai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXswVXk2UbPdtNS12Mja_GEv3630PMcWjjljGDNObllEE4gCW87=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"lovely service and food was bomb. jameson took care of us. just wonderful recommendations. can’t wait to come back next trip to melb! our warmest regards x","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiiMwb3_MNUiKLYIOz1KcEmzToc8MXNobuDULn"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Jeremy Riley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUX4CqA6d5JoLrYkXNlI2ycLMt4tMR_rstD-VNj1SapniQz_m2u=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had a long and delicious lunch here. Started with the 'must have' anchovies and sorbet which were as weird as they sound. The swordfish skewers for tapas were great and the lamb was excellent but the standout dishes were the grilled garlic brussel sprouts and the Setas - Lion’s Mane & Black Oyster Mushrooms with Crispy Potato, Sherry Vinegar & Egg Yolk. The service was impeccable - friendly, prompt, seamless and expert. Lovely atmosphere with some seating in a booth feeling very private and personal. It was an expensive lunch but the food, service, atmosphere and location felt worth it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9YBHGMXazPphtS5NKWvWUcb5HMMpcpkNdDCxB"],"When":"2024-6-14"},{"Name":"J B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeF89xdia-KbY2aVDnKk0vcaZPLjLmD15RQ1zLgIFxv58ir-E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The food was average, extremely small portion (including main) and very salty. $140 for 4 tapas (each), 1 main and 1 dessert for 2 of us and we were hungry still. The tapas came out quick but we had to wait 40 minutes for our main. The atmosphere is dark and very loud, difficult to talk/listen. Service was also average, i didn’t like how the eftpos machine didn’t show “no tips” option. Overall, considering i had to book 3.5 weeks ahead for a friday night dinner, this was such a let down experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPscl56Tw5EYrKQ319-D-CZU43LL4elyoFhhJU"],"When":"2024-5-24"},{"Name":"Piggy Eatalot","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWViqGQx8VrWCrwzd62Gdo_9VSRFQhIepVna9JMziKPKCt0d60=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Love the food there, everything is perfect, however, we got our entrees quite quickly, but then it look quite a long time to get our mains, which was quite annoying because we are the first table to arrive but it took ages.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOKHys7z1Fu28tMo0nCf7mS0wedvRAgeOAw2iC"],"When":"2024-6-8"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sarah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7rk2caQSqYaWCjZZMh86FmmWm7oSHV8u944iCgK9mDOBs88Q1nQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I popped into Hochi Mama on my last trip to Melbourne after an extended shopping trip as our day slipped into evening. The restaurant was buzzing, and we found ourselves seated at the bar. The vibrant atmosphere, fueled by lively music, suited the youthful vibe perfectly.

The food arrived quickly, with portions that were surprisingly generous and packed with bold flavors, beautifully presented. A bridal shower in the corner seemed right at home in this lively setting.

I tried the pork knuckle, impressively large (though it may have since been removed from the menu), which I couldn't finish—a rare occurrence for me! The bar was a focal point, surrounded by happy diners and plenty of empty plates.

There's some talk about smaller portions lately, but from what I experienced, Hochi Mama still serves up a satisfying meal with flair!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMn9XuO8SXBJCff9JUgLNhRJQA8NcVnIIN31uDG"],"When":"2023-1-21"},{"Name":"Chenny Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1A3mKuYv6l_VHgUi9cxD1PT0f1cpZigwmy3-V8FYB7aFU2Y0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Interesting flavours and an amazing atmosphere makes this a must go to. You're looking at about $60-$80 for a couple share dishes and a drink, which is quite decent value for what you're getting.

I was very pleased with the food options and the fusian dishes served. They were interesting and unique takes - although a little messy to eat but definitely enjoyable!

Service was very good and loved the recommendations our server provided.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkREFsnvhaaGqzoc_e3-5CwvqGsIMjyaK9HV0"],"When":"2024-4-29"},{"Name":"Peter Loh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVLzhtrub8y8ZpuqMEHuUX32wyPK4hmDEtGeRVDDSV-jr7lolQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hochi Mama is an inventive take on Asian food done well. Between both of us, we tried their chicken Pad Thai (larger), chicken bao (smaller), and vegetarian spring rolls (side).

The chicken Pad Thai was the highlight of our meal. When all its ingredients were thoroughly mixed together, the dish was flavourful (in a way that was seemingly even more so than typical Pad Thai) and moist to the taste. The chicken baos consisted of a piece of well-marinated chicken wrapped in a soft white lotus steamed bun, topped with kimchi and mayo for taste. The vegetarian spring rolls were prepared in the classic Vietnamese deep fried style, and were a delightful appetiser. Together with one non-alcoholic drink, we paid a total of AUD 60.50, which was a considerably reasonable price for the excellent quality of food.

Located just on the outskirts of Melbourne's Chinatown, Hochi Mama is popular with both locals and tourists alike. On a random weekday night, we had to wait almost 40mins for a table for two as we did not make a prior reservation. Service standards were high; the waitress was friendly and hospitable throughout, and took the time to introduce the popular menu items to us.

Overall, it was an excellent dining experience and well worth the (long) wait!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfxWIUjNBbtHhHNC9QLa-NPGy3xbDY_bKoGuPj"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"C & M Fraresso","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpnT2EKxAAYxch2owwKxaz4GM-miTQgozCpIAIGJDE1yI5Gg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience at Hochi Mama and will certainly be going back. Great food with a ton of exotic flavours and each dish was plated beautifully. Brilliant atmosphere. I couldn't fault the service by the staff who served the meals in ample succession with the name of each dish being mentioned on delivery. They were very attentive to whether we wanted anything else to drink as well as keeping our water glasses full. Suitable background music was playing. Would certainly recommend this place!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWvToMDib_3KDlEp4fbW6Kba5ijv0geRYW32vB"],"When":"2024-2-3"},{"Name":"Dror H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6o1BzcFa0J-0fldSoKAAc9IZSKxVQhdWLL99vKxkH358LBAKz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice Asian fusion restaurant.

I liked:
+good food
+some nice vegetarian options
+big portions
+cool interior

I disliked:
-very loud due to bad acoustics. I could barely hear the waiters.
-our main waitress seemed annoyed. Not sure why, we were friendly. Nothing she did in particular, just body language and face gestures.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9N49l8ayuqOy_83bxcY1JH_Ay5l3jh0DFwHE"],"When":"2024-4-19"},{"Name":"Meryem Celik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1HMYGuS0-hQecRYGdqedrJ8qlZDD-Eew8Dvzbni4meKES-2s1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything was fresh and tasty with great combinations.
We had the prawn betel leaf, roast duck wonton crisps and banh mi sliders for starters and mains included the pad thai, hanoi whole fish and chicken soutside curry. There were only tables outside so we went with that option but I felt there was a vibe inside but was too dark and loud for my liking. Book in advance if you want a table inside. Some things were on the sweeter side but there are other options.
Service was excellent with very attentive waiters paying attention to dietary requirements and Nadia was very helpful when we were selecting our order.
Would definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzfPFuQPJCA8xA8LRbhKx32K_o4LBDUBfGtMeS"],"When":"2024-5-24"},{"Name":"Natalie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIP24ZOSRdiUV8OW1UK7-LkdiHqCXUE5Ij_-LM7T3hRn5YI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The restaurant had a good vibe with a cool bar front and centre. The music was loud and the restaurant was quite dark but the food was pretty good. We had the feed me menu and were able to try a large portion of the menu. The cocktails were also very fun and tasted good. Recommend dishes that have raw fish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMroTNqxFfRmUJjkmLxB2oZ90NS_KOBGJqiXFc"],"When":"2024-1-12"},{"Name":"Dennis Tan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7hUcyUXvGTclY7Qzd9_2ckBsSK2H-NMvdz9onxHxr9m-UZPX_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I was disappointed with our meal tonight, our small dishes were hit and miss, the Chicken Baos were great and Kingfish Sashimi was also lovely. However, I didn't think their Betel Leave Bites or the Crispy Dumplings were anything outstanding. I wanted to be excited with the Betel Leave Bites but wasn't.

We had their whole fish, Pad Thai and Beef Ribs large dishes. The fish was over cooked, Pad Thai was lacking complexities and I found it overly sweet. The Beef Ribs' flavour was wonderful but the meat was a little dry.

This venue is a little on the loud side and seems lively for cocktails and drinks. Our seating of 6 was a little on the tighter side. Our wait staff could have been a little more attentive, however, they were wonderful and accommodating once you had their attention.

There are better modern Asian fusion food around.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMhzRzRoMkWBV-VpYrX-TV4fBv0KsUfkBfzC4Y"],"When":"2024-1-27"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Cristina Ainsworth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWf7DvN_jZiGVFw8zaEW9Sjj26wiWcS3dJcsoa4RYYgnkGrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Red Spice Road is a restaurant that we find ourselves returning to frequently. The diverse selection of dishes they offer is one of the reasons for our continued patronage. If you are dining in, we highly recommend trying their pork belly, as it is a true highlight of the menu.  Can't wait to dine in again!  Thanks!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0VVzKixvbxU7cSbuhxZn7QZJFeplgP4HiWPAL"],"When":"2024-4-23"},{"Name":"Yan Lai (RandomRabbit)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGDt9_2MTruPnQDV53SbQAKl4aPurdEBiksbqgjBgO4vDN9tT98w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is a meat lover's paradise with an Asian fusion twist! The pork belly is seasoned to perfection and cooked tenderly, while the lamb ribs are generously portioned and delicious. I also appreciate the ambiance and decor of this establishment. Definitely worth a visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6N0KmXfM4kwyA-Dt-j2QXASjAp2WMiBlUep7R"],"When":"2024-2-23"},{"Name":"Kim D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8AgzUXZS_exZC064Y8Hw_Oa1fNkyThmfZB0TlZ29sV3rko7mE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It’s modern Asian, but the flavours are not quite right. The majority of the dishes were salty beyond reason, and were not served with rice which is a staple for Asian cuisine.

The rice was cooked abysmally. It was mushy, and not the right texture at all. In my books, if you’re serving Asian food and flavours you need to get the basics right.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAhZ-nW3ilAw9x99HaspUpXd59HeeLsMyZ-ROv"],"When":"2024-4-16"},{"Name":"Courtney Mandel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGYgOEMc1vCGpvBR12gUh0YImKItLjwtfJ_PtRZ1QCcdmSnmxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely delicious. The best Asian fusion meal I’ve had in the CBD!! Highly recommend. Service was amazing and such a great vibe. Perfect for a date night or a group :-)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBP9wlG-7mJ7376PnyKG8PcRoOcV-ejDvI_t1K"],"When":"2024-4-18"},{"Name":"Lisa Galante","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViJdgmfuDCKQDt0SBZ1zGTJ-7RBrYmLY30USX-jp42RzBqbO8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Celebrated our 21st anniversary here. The entrance intrigued me with the long red curtains. It reminded me of a restaurant I went to in Milan where you would never know there was a restaurant behind it. The staircase ahead took us to the entrance of double doors that enter into a large ballroom style tables and chairs. A gorgeous bar in the middle and everything was red with wood. We were brought to our table and ordered our meals. Starters was corn sticks. Wow!!  Very tasty. Main was was the curry and a vegetarian dish. Excellent evening. Staff extremley courteous.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsXDzWOBNbKbbGRxG9OqTRJ9RzkN26cA3S8uCH"],"When":"2024-4-20"},{"Name":"keemekooh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEhWuAoVUT6cJSlyFvOA6H6mxiyULwTiyfPO8A7loI8K6npJQh6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We tried the one coarse meal and it was good specially the main pork dish , it was tasty and savoury but kind a bit disappointed due to one of the staff who doesn’t communicate with us properly when we are asking if we can move to another table and while they’re having arguments with the reservation person who agreed to move us on the table but the staff refused it because its been reserved but the main point is the reservation staff approved our request, although I understand the situation but there’s always a backup plan for any change’s that’s why you have a reservation staff to deal with it, anyway at the end of the day, it was a good experience specially food , kudos to all chef!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOfyNGkviKF5eY1G1hyURW6ot51M4BAMuWV4Dm"],"When":"2024-2-16"},{"Name":"Yvonne Amos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6-CiDV9bARXiq3Wldj1m3A_jRo7ugE7gikRAzyepZDgqU-1ti=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved our lunch selected the three dish option which was almost too much food!  Had the pork belly, bang bang chicken and crispy potatoes and it was oh so good.  If you’ve not tried Red Spice Road get on in there … don’t hesitate xx","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMECN2OICYfhUnu8w59Us95arA-5bLAbGTJdL8K"],"When":"2024-1-25"},{"Name":"Greg Lake","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7c8XGB4xroF3yeA9AGiWelYIUlGI57bSPg1jPOZ9TY9TndA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food. This place is super special. Perfect spice levels and great service. We had the 5 dish lunch special which was exactly what we needed.

Amazing atmosphere too. Good vibes!

Will definitely be back - either for casual lunch or a group party / table.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcHZtnu6JPqQkGcSXUf_IvGkKYjhX0eX84iZwR"],"When":"2023-12-14"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-l6rCjEZqGhJWR8u2QQcWE3DXPfGVhPLhROMvOaX9OqXE1cn5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"[Feb 2024] Highlight was hands down the fantastic service. Marc was warm and jovial. Very friendly and helpful throughout with a great sense of humour. Made the evening wonderful. The place had a nice cosy feeling, but the table space was cramped.\n\nThe food was good. The bouillabaisse was rich and flavourful and the toasted bread complemented the dish well, allowing the diner to alternate between crispy bites and using it to soak up the soup. It could do with a touch less salt, but that's my personal preference. The veal schnitzel was done well.  The potato gnocchi was on the firm, chewy side though. The wines (by the glass) that were recommended paired well with the food. All in all, a good dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuevSdQb76TAf5da4G7rPjjQnweWI5KHPruQ4x"],"When":"2024-2-21"},{"Name":"Sam Keir","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgusD3ARUlDfadBZUU3qqV0jSW2dSSEyA4z78AWTqzQ3Y29w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved Bistrot d'Orsay!  Four of for lunch.  Started with olives and nice crusty bread then I had vegetarian gnocchi, husband had steak frites, while friends had barramundi and bouillabaisse.  We had drinks (red wines and Proseccos) and coffees (flat whites, decaf long black and latte).  A very cosy, warm and moody restaurant.  Definitely book as not a lot of seating.  Would go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUlQUQhJw49gvv75ImrLld-6mNdEufP8FuV7me"],"When":"2024-2-16"},{"Name":"Gaya Balakrishnan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVj4clDkJLaR46yxECpSd-FTGyZ_O58pHWAIfhQzMTFnIiDKt-TMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stumbled upon this when I was hungry for lunch and loved it from when I sat down till when I left. The vibes were very cozy but elegant, not too lavish and felt intimate. I ordered the prawn and scallop St Jacques which was softly buttery and the seafood fresh and well cooked. Make sure you look up to appreciate the artwork!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Savannah Coates","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNoD5w5pR0OLVO2Cw8BgOKQKCtD_0Y1w0cRBg-GlTpEfAS6PJJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic food, atmosphere and service. Our waiter was so attentive and made our experience so enjoyable (gentleman in my photo). Food was 10/10 and Barossa wine was the best I’ve had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFy_UMnbWcBgnHY7PoisteXgo3ZSztPsin4l0q"],"When":"2024-3-16"},{"Name":"Ian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbyNiR2fJI1BiwzXH5FBdGkMJVVF8yYFV0iZwKZBekfBuEKgY2Ng=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautifully appointed small and intimate French dinning experience. Service was impeccable. Food choices many.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsPqP8aLg6JWW7ncj_DusOFwqKHtMGFjs9MIwv"],"When":"2024-3-14"},{"Name":"des hadji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5d78Q52fmCTkPhaM1cV_TMS2o_XXd1NnJ8-llbK3ap8Wi1Add=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The absolute best resturant I have been to. Service is absolutely the best I have experienced also. So kind, warm, welcoming and professional as well. Extra special shoutout to Max who is exceptional at his job and gives amazing recommendations. Couldnt recommend this place enough. If you want a special night with your loved ones, this is the place to go to. Amazing food and a beautiful seating area accompanied with the best staff to make the experience even better. Will never stop coming here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLRzP9DYjzE4UikKUSn8Sakd9emf6JduT2poGR"],"When":"2024-4-16"},{"Name":"Robert Summers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkCXMVVnPIs_-hmu_wFvo4HJv_-3YZG6dBu1qPKtHhQb8JFsw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is amazing. The food, service, and atmosphere are first class. The price was super reasonable. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcyR6C7kXMQLZMQiF6QJUtojr37SnScc8df4TF"],"When":"2024-2-3"},{"Name":"Don Ewart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLU13anIni-mZPNqTdeSEz77lt_UHU29ZDjbOjefwI3dIB7WA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very French vibe, with excellent staff and a commitment to quality. Definitely cosy. Excellent range of wines.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGWz9Ais-HWBxV0GCo4NHWDE1azG9uKRZ7pTzB"],"When":"2024-3-29"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Melissa Lobo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL1Xr0qVh8FsbXi6sw8pBAWdIkSSYLQuo62ILcGAtcr2aMwrg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Saturday lunch out with the family and couldn't fault a thing!  From the service to the food, everything was lovely. We didn't have to wait long for our food to be served which was great with two kids under 4 years old. There's also a small kids menu and high chairs available if needed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrMa9tExXn9W3GJ7-zYl9VOaXL7XSdvTBMJIzz"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Sop Khim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8nIvrnJFfrZlRIRt36I9hFzCcNRdNDV2xzSQ4HzGsZAAe4x-d=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Booked an early dinner here for 4 people on Saturday evening. We all enjoyed all the food tapas that we ordered. I didn't get the chance to take photos of the plates that came out, but I got some photos of dessert. The food was really fresh and tasty. It came out promptly plates by plates. The staff was very helpful and very attentive. The restaurant is in a nice location where you can people watch and parking is easy as well. There is also a night market on the same street, perfect for after dinner. Would definitely come back again for food and drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmD732Z8y6K82hqjDxt7sMcYsG-wpdDdAf_kCi"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"Andreas Ludwig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9lPBbV0sBWCGIIFUFygIFcyiKsOl-ONZzr1eulOOJTMeq-pUZPA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Excellent Spanish restaurant. We came without reservation for dinner and were pleasantly surprised. The pork belly was to die for, the meat balls were nice as well. Churros were OK, the cheese cake as well. But best were the lamb skewers.\nSeating outside was nice. Service friendly and quick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIhLBKsZZLJZc4hnQUfnSlsZN2q0SfX2Y3nnta"],"When":"2023-8-7"},{"Name":"Bron B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCRdEJO5Tl4MaB94kZx7_kSsUfsyXySTM9OP8Iv_HbV03wEnS_Ig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food was delicious, but expensive, and the portions were small.\nStaff were extremely attentive, service was prompt. The atmosphere was buzzing and it was busy, however you weren't sitting too close to adjacent tables,  so you could still have a quiet conversation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgvTWDp30vC0G9yzlrrvqtPVSoYwLfdgTsDFDi"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"Yeganeh Hallaj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfia3uuvxy2uAwNzWUFjWy5Zsia4OcTS4KaFmCgkXC3_XPoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This was my first experience with Spanish food and I believe that it was one of the best ones. Regarding the service I feel like they could have been better. We were not finished with the food but the waitress misunderstood us and cleaned up the table","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOL0r-U5P1vloKDa-oo2iWIpDlnwbWb5fVV_JCN"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"Sagnik Saha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGE5C_GvuKb9jJgs3L8QIbXNZ2ce8O9gcaUGldJUxKHLvEWZr0gw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I visited this restaurant during my visit to the South Bank for dinner as I was craving some paella. We went with a reservation so didn't have any wait times in getting a table but it can get pretty busy during the evenings. We got the chicken paella and it tasted great, the only issue being the dish seemed to have to been overprepped, resulting in the a large portion of rice sticking to the bottom of the pan which was hard to scrape. The price was fairly reasonable I'd say. The staff were great and we got our orders fairly promptly","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXvbbUPLl2bbZsiuIlWTsiTBMCL7U88k3WcchQ"],"When":"2023-12-30"},{"Name":"Iain Teo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8vi5fmshc0Hq4_gvk7KyN8d8hdUDRIW85u2HiKiHE0x59BSGfRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If the food and service at Ole is just like being in Spain, i can't wait to go. Staff was very attentive and the food ..... oh my gawd, i'm pretty sure it would be what heaven would taste like.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMv5BlzcwQUtn-KOM5qF7fpXVnYHA6AqFyM91Vz"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Jing Joo Bong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYT9EpP_STrzvhMEqMlDX_-KKXsdnRIPFCQTD46mNN4Giq8JqO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went there for a quick bite at 3-4pm cuz my friends and I were hungry around south bank. The food was delicious and environment was calm and chill. Had a great day there!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPS5hrfV410HgL_tDXHBgw8Jk2U0EXVnfEigBQc"],"When":"2024-6-23"}]
