[{"Name":"Jarred Funnell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVbOopuyJtINiK0mgIlpsj_RMOat1OYL-oLZZSs_y9tdrWhNwk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for an early Mother's Day lunch. The Pronto Banquet was well worth the money and tasted amazing. Our waiter was incredibly friendly and accommodating. Definitely recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPu1M8R28EuTXUqHlBtVAmHPMtnfYJGdk-m3xtb"],"When":"2024-5-11"},{"Name":"Ying Ang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqbUlDkkOAhdQBs60o0c36KW-okwvQ1_qTXeI_HkvnRp2pB92i=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"@massimo_restaurantandbar is a lovely Italian restaurant situated on the riverside of @brisbanecity with the most stunning view of Story Bridge!✨ 🌃 i’ve visited once before but each time reminds me that i must return to keep trying other delicious items on their menu🤤🤩

we got their✨🍽️

🦪oysters
🐙octopus entree
🥩eye fillet w/ beef jus
🤍burrata
🍝meatball spaghetti
✨sautéed mussels

their octopus, oysters and burrata are just the perfect way to start your feast off! all were super fresh, but a big emphasis on the octopus being the best octopus dish i’ve ever had!✨🐙

if you love seafood flavours, their sautéed mussels are a must get! juicy mussels with toasted bread for you to soak up all the delicious sauce🤤🔥the eye fillet (which comes with a side and sauce of your choice!) was cooked perfectly and the meatball spaghetti was so delightfully fresh and had such massive meatballs, a huge portion and another must try dish indeed!✨🍝","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4zEB9dv5xT8SRRCfxC0_aJtqd0mT1-yemzl63"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"kezia yepes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLU3N3jujgs6w-jtsBUrC2kRfHGEtsTsRLdxK0Q6ZQZzudqhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I  tried the $50pp lunch banquet. The service and atmosphere was nice, the resturant does have river views. The food was honestly a little underwhelming, the focaccia bread and pasta was nice. The  vinaigrette on the oysters was too overpowering, the calamari was cooked super soft but a little bland, they didn’t ask how we wanted our steak and it came out very rare, the potato’s weren’t seasoned it seemed but the sauce was nice. The food was still somewhat good but it definitely didn’t live up to my expectations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPHVsb41SCphQR4xtFBtCmsRQdtymkTZr8O4O0"],"When":"2024-2-7"},{"Name":"Brissy Aus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxp3L6mO7ogIPt0VL0m5foWbLlrRp2NGWxfTjUSiIctN4goA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was amazing! Salmon was spectacular. Entree zucchini flower and lamb chop divine. Only let down was atmosphere. It was very warm and there wasn’t much energy from the staff. Would definitely visit again though, a must try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP7-K6UST9Na7PFLf_Cf519jD-iuEF21BNtnPRq"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Con Costi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBx8zGuUPNbAMzc9dFo8s-JYU0WBwYRI5-WNBISdMpQTAFPAk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Magnificent service, delicious food and a great variety of drinks. The atmosphere is vibrant and the view amazing. Our maitre Giorgia was efficient, knowledgeable with all details of the food and super friendly. Definitely be coming back for more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMd-Obs8SjM0FoaiGVRPKYkXImLWm9BPmQXnd0i"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Lee Elwyn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3Gu6MW5fSOSLzCRjW8pWyRNwo68YeaTkNbO8HnkjfPcf2ns8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Was there on May 4th 2024 in the afternoon.

I've had lunch there before, which was quite lovely, but today we got their Pronto banquet, and we were very disappointed.

All pictures were taken before we even start eating.

Tiny oysters.
Both focaccia and Calamari were too salty, and calamari was only a small serve for 2 people.
Only 4 tiny slices of steaks for main as shown in the picture, each piece was about thumb size.
And the iceberg salad wasn't even chopped into smaller pieces, while dressed with too much vinegar, which makes the flavor horrible.
Paccheri was slightly under cooked to both of us, and they're an Italian restaurant where we didn't expect such a mistake to happen.

Service was good, so still gave 3 stars, plus I enjoyed the dessert.

But I've tried many other banquets all around, and so far this is the most disappointing one, which was a huge shame, since normally these menus were designed to introduce the restaurant to new customers, but not to push re-visiting customer away.

My advice is that, since there are table salts, and all dishes comes with loads of sauce already, the chef should stop pre-salting the food, as it's really too much and covers the true flavour.

Also, the table was only tiny, so you should choose plates which is not overly big for the table, since the food portion wasn't even that big, hence I don't know why you even need a plate as wide as a football field?

Anyway, I probably should have give the feedback while I was there, but I didn't quite have a chance as it would have been awkward if I'd bring it up.
Hopefully they will see this and make some changes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGRYcfD7kvdTmUzGD-grmZ-h_s7srnOqP-GsQ3"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Lewis Holder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw8ujqdqjF1DnIJ6gQUm3JeQpdw1vsmmIDFHl5bDIHBe2Jnqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came here for a boozy brunch and were not disappointed! We paid $110 per person for 2 hours of drinking, 9 courses of amazing food and superb service!

It’s located on the river near felons and the story bridge. Really amazing place and would recommend to anyone visiting Brisbane. The owner was very nice and gave us some recommendations as well.

The staff were exceptional and a credit to the company.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTZ1u62-JK03eCwO7HGihGausJh2GmwQ5_9H4s"],"When":"2024-4-10"},{"Name":"Kaylee Umbers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdp7ZRDMLkVeyT36XAfjj_A1W9VNRy3jmOeGcXMqpcnQcfP57Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came at the perfect time today as a lot of dishes and banquets are new. We tried the new Banquet Due and everything was fantastic, my favorites were the Salmon(raw) and Scallops from the Entree's. Rib on the bone was cooked medium, it was perfect and tender. Lastly the Torta desert was also absolutely delicious ❤️. Would love to try more dishes next time! Our server Jordan also treated us very well throughout our time there!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAvy-k_I4ma5XDLVUVNVOzHTIOuijZlTpqrhUB"],"When":"2024-2-1"}]

[{"Name":"Rook De Mel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_oCgpUeXwZEmPj_zWahy_SByBVQ2KYr7QNw_ECKxva4SrctXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Got the 'chef tasting' set menu.  Quite a few dishes came out (see pics), but there was nothing mind blowing. For the price and portion, I am expecting high quality, which was not the case. Leaving a 2* as I'm unlikely to return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcf5DrqH0_VtfJ_csGIhVix68kSV2BnFvWu9PI"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"tea S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwHy9q5Txz98c2hMyu5fvPpIb3c8-lwdRCcXtGRuibhqdMkA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We dined with the 75/pp banquet option. Food is tasty although very small serving size. As part of the main meal in the banquet they had run out of brisket so was replaced with lamb. Overall friendly service but was a bit too slow on serving drinks. Restaurant was busy which always is a good sign.

Downfall, toilets are out in the foyer as the restaurant is attached to the Hotel. Parking is limited in surrounding. However there is a paid parking building around the corner on Margaret St
Overall rating - 3.5 stars","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOC1FCiD1ur6Y8XEDpGnWhNVPTBvGatq6o4tGn7"],"When":"2024-3-19"},{"Name":"Ella Pert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4HkdNPdJAEYyqWnwGpo0jpiZxok2HqesC4i3Jdp_EGp0r0q7t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All I can say is WOW.
The staff were lovely, the food so incredible, the ambience - even though it's on a road - it is as if you have stepped away from the excited city into a calming new atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvq2DdMFImg2zGjB3sAAM3S-Zg_PqAjTdywu31"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Kijun Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKE7XzYomVCiDfddesBM49KaSXWv0IGOkFLZs9REMUbEmneug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first fine dining experience and it didn’t disappoint! Excellent service by staff. Entree came out quick one by one. Overall food was amazing, great value for money as well. Will come back again. 5 stars.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcNxDXnysHR9HQuSczLYwFRLuhGTpddzBYsKPP"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"Tyleisha Lloyd-Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsIikQfWWSQgvDDXfrYUmCVvTC7ugSF94T8__nK4nQqNbhIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is incredible. We did the set menu, and every single dish was unreal. Genuinely cannot fault this place, the service was amazing, everything was presented perfectly as you can see, and the food was 10/10. Will be back next time I’m in Brisbane.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPL0LLyxp5jgaPdGJMs3Z1UcMivcjxkQ-TrAY4A"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Matt E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgEhcjm1UNNXoA0YhE2_ztINrEHAoxmkOViUWwfjHFalD-Tw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"both the food and service were excellent. had the butcher selection. the entrees were great especially the chorizo, pork belly, prosciutto, and the scallops which we added on top of the set menu. also really liked the rump steak and the desserts","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMv2-V8Hyx-SR7iZwNSkwz6deOPhMxZLhz18Co"],"When":"2023-12-9"},{"Name":"Carolina Bocos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU33oUINH1wnDhL0cSnl0l7gykGNcDa1qpObnDeynSKhecWbb_K=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Blackfire restaurant offers a delightful dining experience that combines warmth, sophistication, and impeccable service. Despite booking last minute, they graciously accommodated me and my daughter in a lovely table inside. The atmosphere strikes a perfect balance, being welcoming and sophisticated without feeling overbearing.

The service was both friendly and attentive, ensuring a pleasant dining experience. The meals, including the duck and house pappardelle, were not only delicious but also served promptly. The cocktails were expertly crafted, with the strawberry caipiroska standing out as a delightful surprise.

We even had the opportunity to engage in a charming conversation with other guests, adding to the convivial ambiance of the restaurant. Desserts, such as the churros and crema catalana, provided a sweet conclusion to the meal.

The special goodbye from the staff further exemplified the exceptional hospitality of Blackfire restaurant. With the added bonus of my favourite Spanish tunes playing in the background, it was an all-around wonderful dining experience. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvJ4TSIrmYLv_rukXKkQxgItHC0b_vZ1qgbwh6"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Erika Patricia De Guzman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrJCboyVgxx7pgBrEvCoADiM_4nP64mDYtHsiW-YJ6fNzgJ14C6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Shoutout to Mitchelle! Such a lovely and energetic staff! We ordered his recommendations and everything was perfect! ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTuKe_PLK8UHMveJycgfF5a21is5rPFH52lWCh"],"When":"2024-6-16"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Bassem Aswad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkiIO1J8pD7HzLhVQXnZzT_2taQ-evLkmnJLXh4s9L7pbbBGhs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We tried multiple dishes at this restaurant, and I would highly recommend the Ali Nazik with Kebab and the Lamb Cutlets (though the latter was a bit fattier than expected). Both dishes were bursting with flavor and left a lasting impression. While most of the dishes were delicious, the presentation was average for most. Additionally, I would suggest skipping the banquet option, as you can enjoy a greater variety by selecting individual dishes for the same price. The vine leaves dish was average. We enjoyed the freshly baked bread and indulged in the famous traditional Turkish tea, which was a delightful complement to our meal. Finally, it's a bit pricey for what you get.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_Tj_dolcx3zwWtVJd6vRQnVtgkudNTo73AwrA"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"Jing Yellow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmPgIURwP6R6yOLck_lsy6fpJzmNGRReu5JR0cbIqTG7Mbp8kD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don’t miss this traditional and local Turkish restaurant when you visit South Brisbane!!!🇹🇷🤤

The manager and staff were very friendly!! The dining space was clean and comfortable 👍🏻 You could choose to sit inside or outside, both were good tho.

Their cuisines were so fresh, warm and yummy😋 Not to mention the decoration of the dishes, it’s amazing and beautiful to take a good foodie📷 No wonder they’ve got plenty of awards🏅","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdIjtf85Rsj1PSMPfS_K8kiTf6p9uKDNHP5p4p"],"When":"2023-12-27"},{"Name":"mustafa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeP6m2SmyUkSaHlGrph-JtvsGjMEh3VlFldYmY_CjI9hy7Im0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the most awarded Turkish Restaurant in Brisbane. It is in a very easy-to-go location in Southbank. The interior is furnished with authentic Turkish items. Many examples such as carpets and porcelain plate and vases can be found on the walls and floors. There are suitable tables whether you go with two people or a group of 20 people.

Duygu and Doğancan welcomed us very friendly and kindly and took great care of us until the end of the meal. I give them top five stars.

As for the food; As a starter, we tried calamari, stuffed vine leaves (Sarma/Dolma) and stuffed meatballs (İçli Köfte). The Stuffed Meatballs (İçli Köfte) were wonderful, the stuffed vine leaves could have been a little better.

As a main course; We tried Adana kebab, Chicken Iskender and Chicken Casserole (Tavuk güveç). All plates were quite large and filling. The flavors were quite good. We also tried juice sour cherry.  Finally, we finished by drinking Turkish tea.

A great restaurant to try Turkish delicacies, I highly recommend it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlpq5gWF6p2onBEc5Av8iqvDW4cXh8-3Pskga7"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Ailean Naidu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVscEekbRP6rRFLZMLyixuD5mldkRYlzqsFaj-m46RsTT6O1zO7eg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow what a fantastic dining experience! Dined here on Saturday night and was treated to a beautiful belly dance. Stunning performance and delicious food. Staff are super friendly. My absolute favourite was the Turkish delight which pairs lovely with the turkish coffee... so fresh and wonderfully made. Family friendly restaurant with such a vibrant atmosphere. Glad to have chosen this place for date night. I can see why this place has won many awards over the years. Thank you lovely team at Mado for squeezing us in last minute 😊 see you very soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9IillqLDtGuZRkPSilHa8I4KunZdH5vitmtmU"],"When":"2024-2-3"},{"Name":"Phyllis Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5FczMFVRE3N5DpwW3qygdQAieXpxp3ddRvUQTHXtV2oGxUfjqFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Such a cool and authentic place! Absolutely loved the vibe here, especially the belly dancing!
But the rating must be given based on my experience with the food, which was fine but not amazing. The chicken casserole was unfortunately lacking in flavour, and the Adana Iskender was ok but also quite plain.

Big shoutout to the staff tho as they were all super warm and friendly! Very quick and attentive service that was appreciated.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzPggyyyCJOL72BMlWlgX2EcsedVD8L4QFqFjt"],"When":"2024-2-24"},{"Name":"Noob From Afar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjA-dMtYTbgAHbfAlfi8NtcNI81Wrw4UM6mcJMVZhj_788Pg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Apologies for the pseudonym!

Great food, 4th time dining at this restaurant. Wonderful service from the waitstaff, the restaurant decor is authentic, great belly dancing performance last time I dined there.

I would highly recommend the Adana Kebab and Lamb Shish, if it is your first time dining there.

I will continue dining here every 1-2 weeks at least!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHwiYycYMqFTdGDkUB1yKBTxTC6m97DHh6XQa1"],"When":"2024-5-6"},{"Name":"Eman Mukhtar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvik2D68isjkNDnPrLyrP7xLK0F5tTy0YAhnEC0Ngd-s30yAO8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our favourite restaurant.  Stuff are very welcoming and nice . The food amaaaaazing .when we need to take a family nice time we not thinking along we directly go to choosing this resturant.. just soo good 👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOa5aEe7WpLvXSATCi3zXSrklPN9vmzWHWbBppB"],"When":"2024-1-19"},{"Name":"Adriana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXv2ejEjeevexwaK1W8vWkHDyz4X6Z8mmRP733c4Wapw8Sa4jX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food, caring and attentive staff. The service was quite fast, and the atmosphere was exceptional.

I attended with a Turkish friend, and she was delighted. The Turkish pizza is highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQzpdnpkVuwYQ8DEJdlmhf_rF4USS2J9lJ0u1P"],"When":"2024-4-5"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ellen Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoDUpJ6MSYySSJlKJkkRaFEKDaTE-JPf_XKNwubaF9_WrYfkce=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my partner visited here countless times. The best service in Brisbane!
Everyone is very attentive and always checking tables.
Food is amazing. Of course they look good too. I don’t have photo of it but try T-bone steak. It is really good. It comes with different sauces!! (Recommend if u are w group of 4 or more)
Nice river view😁","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-ho6efLdLoJ9JKMrrU0bgld5NZH6mgVoN1FTX"],"When":"2024-2-14"},{"Name":"kylie shannon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuGW-z2AGQLBGfaO5b5z4svOzg6Y2tFRtlXCB2ZO-InlZZJYY9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Took part in the "Buns and Bubbles" lunch on Saturday. For two hours, we enjoyed bottomless wines and an incredible banquet menu. Staff were attentive and friendly. Food was 10/10. We grabbed a few desserts on top of the banquet but definitely didn't need to as we were filled right up. I'd say best value for money bottomless lunch I've been to.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoI8Wt-t8TDB2ib2hYvmfyq_i9yQsPyyqDxcey"],"When":"2024-3-23"},{"Name":"A. Moe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLgl8gg4ZmRP-JAr0ZqTN466F1eQGD1JcQgW6TGHBXyOhsk6bS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Sashimi was below expectations. Other dishes went okay. The place was really crowded during the weekend and the hostess was a bit mean to everyone who did not have a reservation. We did not have a reservation :-(.
The servers were well trained and the vibe is nice. Everyone seemed to enjoy the sunny day, good food and good companies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxwSbO8gwBilSGYyqilta3JifMpUEkT4ARS72v"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"Queenie Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDl8YsCM_Mc1v9SkG1HsdgUWDV0jwiTZQocw4j19vx3YUrDwUo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my sister went for lunch on Easter Monday with my 2 kids. We had great time there. Kids enjoy food, special and delicious, especially spicy pork udon, its kids acceptable. Me and my sister has enjoy special Sake set, it’s lovely. Staff are very friendly and respond our request very quick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnTgT0_Wx-UznW7_cn4eibHx2Nq8xIW8WRc85T"],"When":"2024-4-1"},{"Name":"Annie Van","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzj0p8MG2U_J-qYAjkFG2p1WnZUc2xcj-lMoWKgB8_DxsgrA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great spot for a day out. Was a tad anxious when I first booked Yoko after reading others reviews.  But if you're happy to spend money on good food, good service and a beautiful location, this is your place. We decided to go with the al la carte menu, best decision ever. Choosing foods we enjoyed. The grilled prawns and wagyu kushiyaki is a must try. And the staff are very attentive and welcoming.
Thank you for the amazing experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuq6q7oGjdRutRVNONhIe6QC6I7mjIwytP4lg_"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Gigi T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwVB42SXD3xFVSLwZELM2cJCX5gR0zN5c3-a20z0uy_RBJfzyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yoko Dining in Brisbane impressed with its contemporary Japanese cuisine. The dishes were artfully crafted. The service was attentive, and the staff was knowledgeable about the menu. The river and Story Bridge view added to the overall charm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZB-pIIv_r4k0FlryOiX3NwEAA7Wvjs-ibtcyf"],"When":"2024-3-3"},{"Name":"Bex Beavan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBe26yjs5oEzubdf4wH94dLS3YncqS2QLUvhYGfU8EJJhRfoHq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great atmosphere, beautiful food and drinks and outstanding service, made us feel right at home and like we were already friends which I always appreciate!

Sat at the bar which was comfortable and still intimate enough.

Fab river views and top location for further adventures into the night…

Keep it up! 👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUQ11FQE_OqtGcu8l9EK7Gd5357kYmSTmHOcDA"],"When":"2024-5-12"},{"Name":"Phyllis Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5FczMFVRE3N5DpwW3qygdQAieXpxp3ddRvUQTHXtV2oGxUfjqFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a beautiful lunch here.
Eggplant sticks: eggplant was soft and the batter was very crispy.
Tuna rice crisps: great texture - had a beautiful bite to it.
Kingfish goma: exquisite and favourite of the day! The fish was fresh and the sesame sauce with chilli oil was smooth and full of flavour.
Grilled prawns: nicely cooked, flavours weren't as pronounced as I would've liked.
Chicken karaage with mango hot sauce: the batter was crunchy and seasoned well. Wish the sauce was hotter!
Hibachi chicken with red pepper and torikawa: most of the meat was tender with some bits slightly dry. The sauce had great flavour.
Orange and lemon myrtle sorbet: fragrant and not too sweet.
Fried bread with Yuzu curd: super delicious! Great texture and flavours.
Mochi: the texture of the mochi was perfect - thin and soft with a bit of a bite.

The river views were beautiful and the service was attentive. Great spot for lunch!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDbELGYKlTKvPgBa6xvYeXfyau5fPx0u58FrDU"],"When":"2024-4-26"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Charlotte M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxMFfOpW3n170UedK-nfZxEmZQeTPh5IPhoQMVTlx2FbRatGw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered the banquet. The food was amazing. My only criticism was that it came out very fast, we had so many plates as we couldn’t keep up with the pace the dishes were delivered. The view of the river was beautiful. For the amount of food, the location and view, the quality of food - I thought it was great value too! Would definitely go back and recommend to friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-qJ0_ukNcQ229IMU3zboDefMPxfqB3WXjxaXE"],"When":"2024-1-6"},{"Name":"Frank Joris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMYYgve4QC8RcjWyhBZJNLFCc3cbGrpDzhdm89GgeeYOxdaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service from the moment we walked in by Lizzie was amazing but unfortunately the food compared to what it was some time ago wasn’t as good. The portions were huge but lacked in quality with way too much batter on the chicken and the dumplings whilst tasted good were smothered by a heavy mayonnaise type sauce rather than a light dressing as an example, the other dishes were ok but we were way too full to go any further. Unfortunately this place has opted for massive portions rather than lower fat clean flavours like it used to be. Overall a pleasant place overlooking the beautiful Brisbane river with lovely wine and service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFf_qvR5mTwbGk5pk8TEs0ENKA00Yx-EDpmEEQ"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Charles Niautou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVB0OxyUSPK5tQEviy43vIj2rsIXMRUcCiqI9t6mxBDg6DDiN_c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had dinner at Madam Wu last night and the food was amazing. The presentation of the food was exceptional and all the food tasted great. We had the 1/2 duck for mains and it was melt-in-your-mouth delicious. Best place to eat is outside with views of the Story Bridge","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN67QizCRePaGQbXl4p5z3dJfn6icw6dOatRcl9"],"When":"2024-4-4"},{"Name":"Bree de Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8kH-Tl6EEFlpcOXd-pQlwCp3_hbrQIK9yfQEeNkTRaaJgXJJq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The location, vibe  and ambience of the restaurant was brilliant. The staff were attentive and friendly but if I were to comment on anything, it would be the serviettes/napkins. For a place like that, it didn’t seem right to have disposable ones that kept flying off one’s lap whilst seated on the terrace. Portions of the tasty food were big, so it’s good to share!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO68BGI9fnPpHTA213x2yQDqOJcmp7Mweftuzi7"],"When":"2024-2-2"},{"Name":"Hans Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiJKl0Q2nSmcFoGyc0otcVbK2UtvmJs28dtJp9_A3UU66lxw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We decided to dine at Madame Wu due to the reviews on the internet. Nonetheless, the food wasn’t there for the price, especially the pork and prawn dumplings when the skin is not hot and a bit thick when it arrived at the table. The most disappointed point is that we need to wait for more than 30 mins for the first dish to arrive. Turning to the main dishes, the most decent ones was the fried rice, the duck meat is cooked well, but the sauce is too salty, while the sauce for the barramundi was a bland combination of cream and chili oil while the fish is not seasoned well to paired the sauce off. Hope that they will do better for a place with good atmosphere and great view of the lake.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9A6NiMOIhP3pc6-5OS7mZjH5OzYrQRfGmZ66M"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Bonnie Becker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIxxMLS4Ej-Kd3eQqnIqYvCYvl5D_2pWP-teFqS1efOVyGTog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Celebrated our wedding anniversary here. Service was amazing; they made it so special. Great food & the view is beautiful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRJ-dB58V5i-XTygzWEHh52KXAEtnKyrOj9E_1"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Steve Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL7SQidKu0Y4zRaxzB67iURxcvbhZNzX76KJ_FVy_aRxW43mg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"WOW - We had the most amazing experience. The extraordinary Emma looked after us and ensured the meal came out in a timely manner. The food was hot, wonderfully tasty and served with a smile. The atmosphere and view over the river just add to a remarkable evening. Emma is an amazing ambassador for the restaurant. Thank you Emma","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0pj4s0sWwRuo538_RjY8kKjzphkA94HRDKC3R"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Kimmy D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKFf2t_AsgA-qUkm2uOJip3uh4N3NQvUkW1aZOT6euJHADhL5_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you're after more of an intimate dinner, dining here in a Thursday night is a "must do".

Being able to soak up the warm sunset view of our calm Brissie River, it was a lovely experience to share with the girls.

If you can't decide on what to get, their Banquets are a great option.

My Photos are from Banquet #1 at $79 pp.

Top dishes:
- Tang Sui Chicken Ribs - the sauce, crunch and flavours was good! (Note its not boneless)
- Smoked Ocean Trout - fresh, delicious and light
- Lamb Breast - very tender and the chilli sauce complimented the dish well.

I will be returning again, thanks guys for the experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWnkDla_it314IFaDdYAydD4I1C9pmJDUHZRr0"],"When":"2024-1-4"}]

[{"Name":"Russell Sturgess","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuo8PJOgNAh8K3raso610vRsr2-48JrWiFIwUiAhpao_bhqMfu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Have been here on several occasions over the last decade. It is an easy walk if you are staying in Brisbane city. Always has good food and good service. Busy on the weekends a tad quieter through the week.
It’s classic Italian, you won’t be disappointed. Pizzas are typical of Naples. Arancini is great. Never been disappointed with any food I’ve had here. Enjoy!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqObQ-BDFGReN7DGsERu6BzDhFNx452toIAbre"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"Julian Seow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOHN_tH_MxidGDy1ze2P3kwHFQ3E7H-eZYyIvDb4pX3OtRCM4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Decent pizzas, they were alright. We ordered their special flavours but didn’t really like the sauce on it and probably should have ordered some of their classic pizzas instead. Truffle mushroom gnocchi was pretty nice, liked the texture of the gnocchi but couldn’t really taste much of a truffle flavour. Staff were really welcoming and friendly, beer was good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8aYEEJOjR0JSWBGqJRgicogn1oasnmCJzJIaa"],"When":"2024-1-3"},{"Name":"Vivian Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_Ujv6v5hLAhgAIsV7t5zwWdIzvCb4cU9wlN_RfaTysMwMow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food is nice and has great portions size.
Staff is very friendly and quick to service.
The atmosphere is good for a nice catch up.
It was a bit humid in the restaurant when I dined, so the guests were a bit uncomfortable, but we enjoyed the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVtOniNci8gwN0M8QfPahPT47JyF54knz698u-"],"When":"2024-1-9"},{"Name":"Reecie Boii","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdFgTGoqZyWHhjdNB1mBsQ_IYNjoMOasO-FMXccfn0jzxqDZo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to enjoy going out to. Went to grab some food stayed for a few drinks. Drinks were amazing and food was just as good. Service was quick for being nearly full I'd say. Best to make a reservation but we were able to be seated outside which didn't bother us. Will be back :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVsWr1-UOUwS9P4khXFFICFr2ZpelktORwhUiF"],"When":"2024-3-15"},{"Name":"ozmacguyver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQd7hy6VeIWHNYwklMoXOKTxNF9dwCfMHdqBJRFebRGGiOSCTD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super chill place to dine and have a few drinks. The alley is awesome, nice and quiet but lighting cool. Even Teddy was chill (Pomeranian)

Visited last week, on a Thursday, and again today. I eBike ride in from Eat Street, the regular waiter dude is super nice and friendly, so will be back for sure. [{"Name":"Terri Michelle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_GNO5EiZxezS_m1c2UuW00aPtii-rlQL9TGgS-VjXAZaIZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for a high tea, staff were attentive and lovely, food was fresh and tasty.  Was well priced for a high tea experience. We were there for 3 hours and had an enjoyable afternoon. Will definitely go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCOpYlE3HIZIfqfmsAXRumpZjFfaHE18SU5Rzx"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Lucas Haines","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNgvSj1j1HHugJ1jfzACH4Qf1X7s0cm3RY6vv3Nzj62OWnhlWkVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Elegant and warm atmosphere. Classic and well executed dishes. The staff were attentive and friendly and overall had a relaxing and enjoyable evening. The wine list and menu match well.

Will be back for sure","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlllybYKuZbqTv7FvGvpyg17RfBi79DiXZzjkO"],"When":"2023-8-22"},{"Name":"Eva Gu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeRODgH_c_BUBhGntkJNiV-nA1XTDxLAAmxsdXdlhElyHQ1KA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here in Feb and had a super experience with my friend. Very nice service with great dishes, you would sit in a old fashioned room and enjoy your time here. Still remember the fish and the impressive crab salad as the side.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYhluGwAMunYIsZ82uV_FhvSLA0c7tyXcO8FsY"],"When":"2021-11-21"},{"Name":"Bhagya S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIm5zFZm5_6fwKTiOvHiFglqBKbDV8TuMo2qIvyvyT6x_OeMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My partner and I had dinner here for our anniversary. The food was divine. We recommend the lamb shanks and the steak. The desserts were so lovely too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMRNNi5Y7iKQcQglbemJPQMx3_XRvj91u_nG6n"],"When":"2023-7-22"},{"Name":"Jonathan Law","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_bZRFoxEy763DYEfOvPGtKhlr_w2yewek1PagbrkcCJnbYlvm1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is situated opposite to the Botanical Gardens and within the Royal on the Park Hotel.

I came here during the The Fork 50% promotions and was drawn to the many positive reviews on Google.

All I can say is that the food we tried were absolutely amazing. The food portions were very generous. I highly recommend the duck breast and seared scallops.

This is a fine dining restaurant so expect to wait a while for the food to be served but was worth every second for the wait.

Staff were very friendly and the restaurant was very clean. Definitely would be back. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMigJN1xZZzYfGGufejKAxAZf-4ILbfdAe3e6WS"],"When":"2021-3-19"},{"Name":"Victor Tan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6bajTHoa1EBZqxqMtT23Jtr8gkzMnjpQCiPcpy6XlD_Ik_x0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The service was really good with a rustic wooden ambience. The chairs were comfortable and the waiting time for our food wasn't long either. The dishes were well presented and tasted amazing. Recommended to have their duck confit and crab spaghettini. The oysters were really fresh as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwZXnE2rrgl4T1lNByNTShqeOmmkev0BS0HsM"],"When":"2019-7-2"},{"Name":"Kristy F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFAWenLrFWb2C-rVC1D8ghE718tSOHjkSCCsLlzZr6tkYEeg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We stayed at the hotel in November 2020 but we didn't eat at the restaurant. A year later, in November 2021, we booked in at the Walnut. I had the char-grilled 180g pasture fed eye fillet, rare. It was perfect. The vegetables are a nice accompaniment to the dish. The meal portion is perfect for me. My husband had the char-grilled 300g scotch fillet, rare. He enjoyed his meal but was not an enthused as I was about my meal. We dined here again between Christmas and the New Year with a friend. My husband and I ordered the eye fillet. Our friend ordered the special. This visit we had dessert: one caramel tart brulee and one bombe Alaska. Both desserts were devine. Good portions for such rich and sweet desserts. Service was excellent on both visits. We'll be back again soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqzR0pfgqDwBq_UdEi-KXU7yOrxQRNj0fHS_G8"],"When":"2021-11-21"},{"Name":"Fortune R Music","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTGpQ55y5Grpq5-5LL446S1Pc5ocEsxOlcOkaVVUPbYBX9BIqL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve dined here a handful of times is not more. The atmosphere keeps me coming back. It’s very cosy and classy. The food is amazing. My favourite being the gnocchi. As someone who does not have a sweet tooth at all and usually doesn’t have dessert, I have to say they have the best desserts which are not overwhelmingly sweet.

I’ve never been disappointed and highly recommend this restaurant.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jing Yellow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmPgIURwP6R6yOLck_lsy6fpJzmNGRReu5JR0cbIqTG7Mbp8kD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A fantastic FINE dining experience in Brisbane🍾 Strongly recommended to book a reservation in advance!!

The atmosphere and environment were amazing and high class. According to the cuisine,  it’s fantastic!! You could feel how carefully the chef prepared the meals🧑‍🍳Duck and pork were so perfect!! ( You could enjoy the cooking show through the kitchen tho lmao)

The service was kind and friendly. The last but not least, don’t forget to order some cocktails for the night!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODQ0YI94eLogb6W8rSfqX_BFTw7dSBCGZ08Jqh"],"When":"2023-12-27"},{"Name":"Lily Andrews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXvitoM-6RilmICGDJJt3cAPCLHDRhmTtjM40U_mS4l8VK3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a beautiful restaurant with great quality service and food. Service was prompt and professional. We were served by Vita who made our dining experience enjoyable with her warm presence and great hospitality. It was great to be taken through the menu when initially being seated. We were also welcomed with a complimentary beef taster on the table which was highly enjoyable. Scallops and oysters were absolutely incredible and some of the best we have ever tried. Would highly recommend this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYyBqe4PIqUf6U2UGTk0lQv1mCVGNE3O1cbOrn"],"When":"2024-1-13"},{"Name":"Pia Cristina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlVrGRDYPjQhHq4iPgz0qsSqZGcybqHr3HRyUHOgr45gjdRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Large selection of Wagyu and Angus beef.
The preparation process for the meat is pure perfectionism, the meat melts in your mouth.
The wine list is quite extensive, the staff are knowledgeable and can help find the perfect wine for the meal.
Booking in advance is recommended if you want to be sure to get a taste of the food in this beef paradise","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0hLMFxR8GNgAShX6cFF-tnfSxTNJZKw4-Bf9S"],"When":"2024-3-16"},{"Name":"Matt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdIe3VRrTDNmICmphhzQPI536wETlqeamse205oaDkoVwpIr2L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I'm going to be a little controversial here. I don't think the food is worth the price. It does however make up for it with the incredible setting. Privacy while dining in a room as majestic as this is an incomparable experience in Brisbane.

The Sides are well made, but there's nothing spectacular about them.

The signature steak, the pure Wagu A9 was probably the most tender piece of meat I've ever put in my mouth, but, it was so heavily seasoned I was forced to scrape it off. It really did ruin the texture of such a special cut of meat.

Personally I wasn't a fan of the desert either.

However, the cocktails were phenomenal as were the wait staff.

Strangely, if you asked whether I would return to a restaurant where I didn't like the food I'd usually laugh at you and say no. Moo Moo's would be the exception here though. Regardless of a less than ideal first experience I would eagerly return. Perhaps ordering something a little more ordinary to see if the food can live up to the hype.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMh1eUtieSZ0ebpDku74EzaSmxy3vMFoHfDbKLF"],"When":"2023-12-23"},{"Name":"Peter Lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjE5Fl2y819M8UI7DFlNMFmcBrQRGtaQ6P0pEH5cNn_8ndWxSc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A dining experience that's 100% worth revisiting. The staff were attentive and approachable and the menu hit the spot. It was my first time here so the waiter walked me through the menu, and even offered half portion sides so that, as a single diner, I could endulge in some variety.

Every just, sauce, cultured/truffle butter and side harmonised with the juicy cut of med rare Angus I ordered, and I gobbled it all down.

Bring a mate have a nice catch up over meat!

The one comment I have for the team at moo moos would be that the experience eating at the bar would be even more elevated if the down lights were warmer in tone.

Thank you for the lovely meal","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvporbymZAKf3bJSunHnYKX_e1vUK8TNRR_RLs"],"When":"2024-4-17"},{"Name":"Cameron Stacey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVOQ1suNFIctE--VVidvU9h4Rj5DzkouL65qOAN6CNO2R9BSdX-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is definitely the best steak restaurant in Brisbane. It's not just the high-end quality steaks, the massive wine list or the beautiful heritage building that makes it the best, but the service. From the very first time I came to Moo Moos, the staff have treated my guests and myself like family. If you want to impress a client, your partner or a first date, This is the place. While you're there you have to try to Purebred Wagyu A11 Striploin. This has got to be in my opinion, the best cut of meat in Australia.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiwH2yrA-G4KteJ8c2g_V74G3FoPsUWc4XAiOJ"],"When":"2023-11-10"},{"Name":"Kally Teo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQk80l1Sfjz_sVYaCaNHAmRFZV9JcQ-n1f9ncxb5OYyHfI5K1m=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fresh oysters, clean-tasting steak, great mustard and awesome service.
Everyone that served us were amazing and friendly. Happy to be here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLLz2zXEBhtETV2ftbETSe61ucgWnJxxBMWNph"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"Col Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxez0MsAZV64AM7VwVc1ilbNLPvpPu-K6XShbxoPwqSYgt2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great atmosphere and amazing service by our waitress. Kindly explained everything on the menu, not pushy at all. Amazing atmosphere for a celebration. The steak we got was absolute divine!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTZW-dEjZQaAopIVJA_GyAlqOtaXGflx4s994D"],"When":"2024-4-20"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Omar H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZKk0xLFf20TYcx5z2H-yG7w31iHyOS9jPmPngL2qwEfYRxNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lucky enough to sneak in here on a Monday night and was happily surprised with how authentic some dishes were - and also with how tasty and fresh others were.

The mushroom buns were amazing and look fantastic.

Service was charming, friendly and well paced. Atmosphere is elegant but approachable.

Will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtgeYIIJ_TWd0HdHdCHetz1-UxK-NDQQEEDrH7"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"Saw Yu Mon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHYFAh49eH6U0KDL5-qgVFNkSzYyLFvh2pMuOQues42zFMpQOr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Beautiful classy building and nicely decorated restaurant.

Cocktails are a miss for us, ordered 3, and did not like any.  The food, however, was great. Our favourite would have been the fish and lamb ribs, but the rest of the dishes are also lovely.

Service could be improved. We find ourselves constantly trying to make eye contact with the staff but unsuccessful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVZs8BbjwBOhg0VQ5xS6aF8U6ZuSPcQQ1mJuri"],"When":"2024-4-24"},{"Name":"Vivian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmTNlSJ6dcOU2VxSNjR4svU-6Q_NPfLw0wW9ymzvGJIKTzNM25=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The atmosphere is very formal. The tables for 2 people are fairly close together so not much privacy and space. The staff are friendly and very helpful answering questions. I also ordered the peach oolong tea which was very tasty however you could only smell the peach and the oolong flavour is muted. The scallop and prawn wontons were my favourite.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5ngcbycULy3FJaR_GNyeQjfFb-er9s3Vq5g5R"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Andrew Chee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIF42QhsaxoN0aqQPjXkzg8JueqArjsB2_YH1XB2Sp9Fp9NtA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here a couple months ago for dinner and it has truly changed my standards on dining. I am from NZ and nothing here compares to Donna Chang. The food was incredible, the aesthetic was classy and the service was impeccable. Highly recommend this restaurant- make sure to try out the lamb ribs!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipME6quRCfoYo-sG31VHPSc8EC870Nkdb7XpFz2V"],"When":"2024-2-3"},{"Name":"Suzie Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXx7ZHPZRN0bsJIxDUWdxmQTwEO3DMTPOQcwGCaNN65SHXUGgz2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious food
We had lunch at this beautiful heritage listed restaurant in the old  Queensland Government Insurance Office.  The food was a level up from the standard Chinese restaurant offering and the service was excellent.  Nicey but pricey!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaVM8l2PyK4_UH_HlnVKxmTtYoifKuewXObrG9"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"Leah Halliwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVw5FeD-R8a5isVRCAb7MQZesEmUVfUE7xLGgElifODLEZzbaY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I booked my son’s 18th birthday at Donna Chang, firstly they gave us a free upgrade to the private dining room upstairs. The room was SPECTACULAR! Adi our waitress was an incredible addition to the night, superior customer service with a beautiful smile! Your beautiful sommelier recommended a great wine (we definitely drank too many bottles of it) and the Boom Boom room downstairs was the perfect end to a fantastic night. We will definitely be doing this whole experience again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPel2xH0Jg3QAnZ_CM0LPIwzbF9NSYG3xFg8va"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Reagan Raj Kumar Chennama Reddi Vincent","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW12D7HDxIJPvs3Kzwce2cvWDsCOv9SJQ4Elwy17IRLPrg3P0sV2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food  full of flavours ,fantastic service and wines are a bit expensive. My favourite is Lamb ribs , Stir-fry beef &.  lamb bun with house chilli sauce.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZGl0IKtoiuZM0OEWOVyD2nGSyZcbdp_9mGX89"],"When":"2024-5-24"},{"Name":"Lewi Hirvela","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVk6UBcpyfP5zvCHgZL8me2cgKDD-Mi-eJCqsWcaPBnCPfXMXv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It wasn’t until after we left did it click that this is a gimmick restaurant, what with us both getting the exact same damn Jerry Seinfeld quote fortune cookie. That’s when I realised this is named after Donna Chang from Seinfeld. Just from that you can probably guess the quality of food. “I’m not listening to some white woman, I thought she was Chinese!” Well she definitely isn’t Chinese here. The cockroach on my friends bench seat probably didn’t help either. 2 stars including the tip.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXl6WEztJhWSx4jgOoiA9OyYg5Ys87s2lTcrzo"],"When":"2024-2-19"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"nesh mobile","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-LszUHEhMDA9FZVEtADQjZG6SUcurEj8HDnaMSCGYMHgj-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Opa Bar with my wife, and our experience was exceptional. The service was outstanding, and we thoroughly enjoyed the food. We opted for six banquet meals, each costing $60. From the moment we started with the pita bread and dipping sauce, we knew we were in for a treat. The starters were a delightful introduction to the meal, setting high expectations for what was to come.

The highlight of the evening was the lamb shoulder, which was incredibly juicy and flavorful. It was cooked to perfection and left us wanting more. Additionally, I ordered grilled prawns as an extra dish, and they were simply delicious. The prawns were fresh and perfectly grilled, adding a wonderful variety to our meal.

The ambiance of Opa Bar further enhanced our dining experience. The atmosphere was pleasant and welcoming, making it an ideal place to enjoy a meal. The combination of great food, excellent service, and a lovely environment makes Opa Bar a must-visit.

I highly recommend Opa Bar to anyone looking for tasty food in a great setting. Whether you’re there for a special occasion or just a casual night out, you’re sure to have a memorable experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXEtyEo0RO4YJy2grQZqUFl7oVWtmppYl1DB4o"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Karen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-XSfYLNAMyy-352AJqno6Y3RxtPjvklDrdJrp-o10Tsyimw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We celebrated our significant wedding anniversary at Opa on Saturday night. The food was beautiful and good serving sizes. Sophia, our waitress, was fabulous - helping with our menu choices as first-time customers. While the restaurant was full, we didn't feel crowded in, and we could speak easily to each other. The Opa parking deal was also good value!! Thanks for a lovely night. 🌟","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIKXkytdK4R84YkkYs34jlns8x-kasv7PX4Z33"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"Tabby Cat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoHaWadI7qrhpsBaGHwTHfG7J1wNZdTuvpgGW2IDGRxBfhfh58_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you want Greek food, you can't go wrong here. The Lamb shoulder was soooo good. Country salad, lemon potatoes, stuffed capsicum. Waiting now for dessert, which will absolutely be good. Definitely on my must return list.
The staff, especially Lea, are so friendly and and helpful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2f_T86EozS49W2V7WXcDQkRlI5xy9nCHuKYiJ"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"Tl92","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrZXVo9x7yc1YQzCesmY0QWCrgUJxwKThL721IJuoDn9Ytfg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Dined in and ordered the “First in Greek” menu which is a $60pp banquet before 6pm. The banquet was great value with a lot of food - we had so much of every dish. We did order some additional sides including the saganaki which was good however not as tasty as another famous saganaki up the river. The calamari was alright, nothing to rave about however the lemon potatoes, lamb shoulder and Greek salad was delicious!  We were celebrating a special occasion and the little surprise dish was appreciated.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP17TRiF0SUcxb2SeWf8uuNGACrR8wHBK4UdNLF"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Kristen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjojMlSBfHXDRxvJDdVLShUTJuVBaViWrw08FLx6PRd2zM2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a great restaurant located right on the Brisbane River. It doesn’t matter what you order, everything is absolutely delicious. We dined here for dinner with another couple and had a really nice evening. We ordered a bit of everything, dips & pita, saganaki calamari, spanakopita, and lamb to name a few, with wine to complement. After dinner we had a nice stroll along the boardwalk and it was the perfect way to end the evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQAddvsvOB9of6N9gvx7w8cv-8lox_-S6Q2eVC"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"Patricia Gibbons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmPZOszW7kafXqdIDIzuBuwa2O0AN7E_cHWel9mlcHmVvItOrs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible food, beautiful location.  Exceptional service.  A group of friends attended for lunch and we ordered the smaller banquet and couldn’t finish it!  Every mouthful was delicious - highlight was the peas!!  A great venue for a special occasion or just to indulge.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKLo6hOBeVMi1QGjzKIjpebSItb0-s6GORMmE4"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Kartya Wunderle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6Y0PL-JzxPizFxizNCIrBQI11eQzklxu33z5XT3H4EUTfdA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was amazing!  We usually go to another Greek restaurant in Brisbane that is highly rated but this one takes the cake! The staff and service were super attentive. Couldn’t fault anything. Will definitely be back! Everyone at our table loved the food! The lamb shoulder was the softest we’ve ever eaten. The spicy sausage was to die for! The manager went above and beyond. Thank you for such a great afternoon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPg22oI744Ji-PAlTxyATNe1vxOjEDxAmXZhggg"],"When":"2024-4-6"},{"Name":"Shawn Wilmoth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSLt4k8dU7KIfiSA1FnZuHWhRnoSp6dXMwm68nVh9vPa0dQy7eBg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dinner here was excellent. They were very accommodating to food allergies in the quality of the staff was excellent as well. The Greek salad was good though it could be a little bit larger portions. The steak, though was very large and so big I could not finish.  Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHk_cSMNXfbNaMaKtrHYEQQLoFCU6JMjwi3cQr"],"When":"2024-1-22"}]

[{"Name":"EdenApparelBoutique","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPI_s5Hn6l_pRzKXmy5UuGKm4prZCn11H-thkd3fRBO5PI3He5mA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful spot in the middle of the city near the Botanical gardens. We went there as a freshly married couple and after a stroll through the gardens for a small afternoon snack.

Shared the antipasti platter for two and I had a limoncello spritz.

Good selection of wines, prices are more than adequate for the quality of the food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAPjUKZvvMv8MshrNPglRRXCxI6QSKjv8_6Uz4"],"When":"2024-4-5"},{"Name":"Lainey Sioux","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHMCjzRQVzGomY-D3QZR0XZFTjInECzOl3nh_U1YsqQ_wpEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A stroll down to the Brisbane Botanic Garden end of Edward Street where we dined at the charming Olive and Angelo.

We had a selection of shared antipasti including bruschetta and octopus salad, followed by mains of marinara on freshly made pasta and veal scallopine.

To end the evening on a sweet note, we savoured cups of coffee alongside a heavenly plate of pasta angeli - delicate fried dough pillows generously topped with oozing nutella.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7Bg2mlAE4dU-4x4K-4-pq1ZLzdJGN8JLMCYQI"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Spoorthy Reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6O7t1sIhwXmK_LINdo4G1h53_WYKHn1Wm98XaArAhReWOc7K_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Great ambience and vibe. Was packed, but we managed to get a table without booking. Some nice wine options. The food was alright, but not worth the price point. Service was disappointing. They never checked if we wanted to order more. After indicating twice if we could have a look at the dessert menu, they brought it to us after good 15 mins, although the place was half empty by then. Expected better experience and service","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKoRMWbseBTMjbrHGpjx8fX7YtsqKSUTz9EHEZ"],"When":"2024-1-1"},{"Name":"Jonathan Noble","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIO8AfkOhP9aGPXr_a7FvyRGasct62NV2nh-DM8vDfUkif8LA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food was great. Service was beyond terrible.
Took my family to dinner for my daughter’s 16th birthday celebration. When booking on the website they ask whether it was a special event to which I selected Birthday. After ordering dessert my wife discreetly went to the bathroom and asked the waiter whether they could put a candle on my daughter’s dessert or write a message in chocolate. (As wanted it to be a surprise) Waiter said he’d ask the kitchen. Waiter then came back to the table and whispered in my wife’s ear in front of my family. Naturally all were curious as to what was going on so my wife had to explain that she had asked for a candle or message, but the response had been that they were too busy. Following this the waiter charged us for the wrong table (overcharge of $200 and we learnt you are unable to pay without giving a minimum of 5% tip) He was very remorseful but it was a shame we had to have those experiences. UPDATE: the restaurant charged a $120 ‘no show’ fee 🙃 all was fixed and reimbursed 3 business days and a phone call later.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwiHMK51FILaYyefSPdF-bZVgbNKanbDq2kNEB"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Doreen Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItJMg42NtLyI8Rax6czmLPMeI9yeM79KUZhtu5WTCwSdJ8_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A little gem in the city. We were looking for lunch places on a whim and this one came up as it has high 5 star reviews.  It intrigued us so we went.
The moment we got there, Seymour's friendly smile greeted us and took us to our table.
He's very knowledgeable in recommending the right dishes for us, so we ordered the prawn pizza, and duck fat roasted potatoes. Yummm! 😋
I would give Seymour 5 stars for his amazing customer service. Always kind enough to accommodate any needs that we have and checking if we needed anything else. What a humble asks hard-working guy.
Well done Seymour!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtUPZHV_XzTOqI14EzseITkUPnuw27_s3gMgRz"],"When":"2024-3-24"},{"Name":"Todd Burton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNU7LAlV6f12X9xwI8ztu4pCxvt6AKU2TxGpSF1bxiBCxAHn3n=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have been here a few times now and it is exceptional Italian, in a beautiful atmosphere with great top notch service and recommendation’s.

Try one of the pasta dishes. You won’t be disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhZSJy2TjaKxYpSGrzohLbBJ78PJltNDiqIOds"],"When":"2024-3-24"},{"Name":"Rohit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXr4coJOTJYF8XEqfU59VcZ5P2jECs5tkO51r0YaD3fSAlbE508=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were welcomed by Seymouir,
He is very honest and sincere. A pure gentleman and a great host. We really liked his humble nature, and he suggested food dishes to us and they were fabulous.

Guys please retain this great host and promote him as he can be  a great mentor for juniors resources maube

Very Good Restaurant
Their food is always fresh and tasty
Ambience is great
Waiters are lovely
Have been visiting this place since many years, never regretted

Highly recommended.
Definitely 5 stars ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ for these guys","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmLKHOXJBi56CSNJFKQx9vgBk4AbTkri9L4tWz"],"When":"2024-3-30"},{"Name":"Bill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVp-LS8fTgDLaKs54cCZe3g27n2yhQcQX89Hx7E3jJDJ4vgMjHWxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice afternoon lunch at Olive & Angelo. We had a variety of dishes. An antipasti plate, patates, vegetarian pizza, mussels ans zucchini flowers. All the food was fresh and served promptly.
A decent Italian wine list is offer, but it is limited. There are digestives and amaros as well.
Recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM74TNXp83BnmNoSIu9Po_wVMBY3NZ_8-Csjfgg"],"When":"2024-1-13"}]

[{"Name":"Jennifer Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcYUa3GR5XJ9GAPVBKRheWaEiwzrAOyb52Ur4LU2bGDJan8j-6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a fantastic date night here. So definitely no complaints there after eating such amazing food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7PHqunW02u922ZFAIFTqIC5b1p2MGIGz2BFIq"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Darren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvm7I8OFs8G44HVqZHPQwkoUBiB0EnedFQESCXZaTGC_lzsZEmjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I enjoyed dinner here with a group of colleagues. From the presentation to the amazing flavours I can only recommended this restaurant as a wonderful place to dine. Service was good and drinks reasonably priced.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0S4anVufzmzOf1L7V5RYj26orwT-xfU_lkh0y"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"Sam Graham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJdCoai1saKlhMSXkAKTdqHwQNXEUND1BxJZgtJdlCkXJOcg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved it. We had a set menu banquet and there was so much delicious food. Cocktails were very good and a bit unusual which is nice. Wine is sold by the small glass, the large glass and the carafe.
All staff were really accommodating and friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsx08luhQUKAbEg07ySkHPBHReebV3gB6ckLAb"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Jazz Canny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmT4LEj82gfgNn98nUrO8yrUzoOmJnwsTt_aAboABN5-dNMtE_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"After visiting last year for valentines when it was newly opened, this venue has since established itself in Brisbane extremely well. We were seated in the main dining area which had a lovely vibe. It was dimly lit apart from one extremely bright light above us that was slightly off-putting, but otherwise the restaurant is on theme, well done and fairly comfortable for an intimate dinner.
We opted for the taste menu ($79pp) which we were extremely happy was an option for two diners. The meals came out quick and timely in their respective courses and were fresh and delicious, and the cocktails and cocktail menu was great! A standout for us was definitely the fried cauliflower which was served with the main of chicken, which we unfortunately found a little dry and lacking flavour. Overall this banquet option was definitely worth the price in comparison to other restaurants and we left very full and satisfied.
Our only complaint was our waiter, who unfortunately was quite abrupt and passive aggressive to us which was unusual considering all the other staff were lovely.
Overall so glad we returned, the banquet was totally worth the cost and made it an easy night and will definitely be returning again in the future!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwQqWCgEnDAfkYvz4yed8cYwF4e-khy1QpSJNr"],"When":"2024-2-10"},{"Name":"Manufit326","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMmHZetnpskOZr9GbLYg_vXFlyqFmnXDSsd0o_QNbHvIyf5bw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s becoming our favourite restaurant, starting because the place is perfectly decorated with a warm welcome. But what we love the most is the food, we have tried the deluxe and premium taste. Everything is mouthwatering, the combination of different flavours, and the presentation are unmatchable!!! Congratulations to the chef… well done guys.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMI90GRrlDb7Liy7kSoI6di-Uq80L0uJrbUi5MG"],"When":"2024-3-31"},{"Name":"Leoni van Nieuwenhuizen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgsUsRPLE_Gbvo9w_7gmMSCOda2mcna18xxm3BnNhSoeS3tvvj-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was spectacular! Had a tasting menu with each dish better than the one before. Great view, atmosphere, service and food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkO0-6d5znpveRLMV8FANM50qV-kWfsWW_SCWv"],"When":"2024-4-15"},{"Name":"kezia yepes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLU3N3jujgs6w-jtsBUrC2kRfHGEtsTsRLdxK0Q6ZQZzudqhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The atmosphere was nice, the place is well decorated and does have river views. The food was honestly a little bland. I wasn’t a big fan of the sauce with the oyster, but the oysters themselves were nice. The duck was cooked really well but was quite bland, and I feel that the sauce didn’t really match the duck. The short rib aswell was bland and a little dry. The octopus however was definitely my favourite it was very good. The food being a little bland would be somewhat acceptable if it wasn’t very expensive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMysvi2NCU-tNVGi6O6uo9-g-p4Je4X7ROWPtho"],"When":"2024-2-13"},{"Name":"Cherie KH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7_L6eWne63QIo1ar5iFtUv--hwX6_OHtLS6X7xItv_rKSZqE9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a beautiful spot along Eagle Street, views are amazing and very well setup and presented. Food was delicious and fresh, bar staff were amazing, very friendly and accommodating, especially James & Savio from the garden bar, top quality service and really looked after us. Would definitely come back and visit again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrIWz7iCGsuSDWC2SKG54XcM_5iH4KzZR-JQea"],"When":"2024-6-4"}]

[{"Name":"Su Jiahui (Chanelle)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYfkINro41tJh9k2s1BMLLy5XjMwTln65Y50SpGXqB7KngHhkD3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing location by the river! Had the Super Greek banquet and it was marvellous!! However, the lamb was too dry. This is definitely worth the $75 as me and my partner could not even finish it. Service was amazing, everyone was fun and friendly! (dessert not in picture because we got it to go but it was amazing!)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVZttX0JcTrNe586fSR6XHROI4-dbmZ-gh_4Eq"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Lambo Blair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCHeowVirg-4pQAdT3hKpP3DSCttPp4l_pjCF6213DwnFURDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visited GRECA on Saturday night, and the food was very tasty. We had the lamb shoulder which was so incredibly tender and tasty.
We also had the moussaka which also had amazing flavour.
The lemon potatoes were superb, too.
All the staff were friendly and service was fantastic.
The restaurant does get very busy and can be quite noisy but still very enjoyable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-FWLW8fzvr4Ydt6FV-NJ_eF2gGh5rd0xN8mQQ"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Yeganeh Hallaj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfia3uuvxy2uAwNzWUFjWy5Zsia4OcTS4KaFmCgkXC3_XPoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You would experience a very delicious and different taste from Greece. The service is really good they would help you with the menu and give you good recommendations. We tried their two most popular dishes, the octopus with hummus was tasty and the chicken was juicy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0XIf-Y6n9drE_MwWXn-bv5p7vAkK8BIjuxvnl"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"Bene Laurie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9nabIoz1hsfCXEE23Y8TofTVs-G7db2szR5JkfOJxL8rhGpUP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing🙌 service. Had my birthday here. Friendly staff, fast service and stunning view of the Story Bridge. Midst of winter but the cold didn’t bother us cause we were sitted next to a gas heater. Made it warm and cosy.

We chose the Super Greek banquet and it did not disappoint, WORTH it!  Also added a birthday cocktail on arrival. Highly recommended Greek restaurant in Brisbane✨⭐️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLiOd8M2oVzD8NQ8p5IOR62genCZ20J_1oWgNg"],"When":"2024-5-30"},{"Name":"Zeta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJC_pSqKi55d_WV9-p7VKkTmculY-wEty42UtHKl_u2PcY14Bnc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went to celebrate my friend’s birthday, and the service was outstanding! The staff were very hospitable, and the food was great value. We enjoyed our time there!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjwbze0V620hFTzcqUbsSXwzymj6Wz-ER5oCj5"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"Alex Sebeschuk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfUx3rCiv3K__F4wijAn1WXpGCJOOwfM405mu4ocgUUvrpTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I choose the restaurant to dine in for my birthday. Even tho we didn‘t have a reservation the staff still managed to get us seated (upstairs). We took the Full Greek menu and were surprised by the high variety of delicious food. For the desert we asked for the Katoumari without walnuts because of allergies what was no problem. Additionally we got the Ouzo Watermelon which tasted even better as we could have imagined! The staff was very friendly and ensured we are happy all the time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfkzMFHvP9CKPBQFV8d0YrpEKPLXzmNCpQ9sdz"],"When":"2024-4-17"},{"Name":"S Andrews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLa0wjDm-EbBZzXLFbSuLAGgr3znwyXyQKMxyWagft0L61JLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Entree - Moussaka was ok just lacked flavour.
Honey cheese - first few bites were amazing shared between two but was a mission to finish because it was very sweet. Would be good if you had a table of four.
Lamb Shoulder - amazing, can’t fault this dish
Desserts -lemon meringue was delicious

Service was lovely.

Atmosphere - mezzanine area - lacking and music too noisey.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRg-EXb3ohxTANJ7OcyyZPeDiNfGok9x67bJhZ"],"When":"2024-3-27"},{"Name":"Tiapye Saal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTg3ezqBta9mwq-AN1Vy1eosnz7YLRFhvBl2YWZ_EmjTUPHmixbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my loved ones had a really special time at Greca. It’s beautiful location draws you in, add the amazing food, drinks and service and you’re set for an amazing experience. The food couldn’t be faulted and our wait staff were so attentive and looked after us from beginning to end. If you’re visiting the area it’s absolutely worth getting amongst this beautiful venue.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1s-VFzEZ6YsoieL15GxS0esx12jqaPsRgS1oJ"],"When":"2024-2-29"}]
