[{"Name":"Carl Sullivan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW36noN8KlmRK9NP99bF92fRnSvPlh7YvRcm5uz2WjS00u_VH1z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My fav coffee spot in the city. The owner roasts his own beans every week so the coffee is always fresh and tasty. Has nice hides holes to hang out in and a take away window plus a simple but tasty food menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAuF6SBpNjOCiDHEWvYB5Qk13rXVTiZwGhQKVu"],"When":"2022-5-3"},{"Name":"Irene","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvweA8HODofn7v8KWpCWF_2pEzL3ABUSUYRJbOlQKPpQTjjXOpcg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee roasted in-house. Jazz music. Great sitting spots - cool, funky and informal vibe. Generous toast with ricotta, honey and cinnamon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNS3CVFGL2p9K3Lk-0rFzHmY3RwoITZ7b9Au2Y2"],"When":"2022-9-14"},{"Name":"George Forgan-Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEi8DQNSmTKTnE8vGDT6TpzWr4p0OyUd2Owum7iO9mXLdYUkil=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Micro cafe just behind the Q.V. building in the CBD.
Menu was limited but tasty. Seating in limited with 2 small 2 seaters. Visiting during non busy times you should be fine.
Coffee was great as was my smoked salmon on toast.
Great spot for a quick snack or coffee on the go.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO47d4PqvLj5Iv1SM2QXhjVnieQ64n68AP5k6r5"],"When":"2018-8-6"},{"Name":"Dean Paradise","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFpSzALQFl0h2CL0ILCsDiw6QPcbaUsqkLoGDvu91Af7s9Si5t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A place for serious drinkers of coffee. I’ve never had a bad coffee in this place. Strong, dark roast. Staff this morning were helpful, and friendly, offering me water and also table service. Quick service and nice environment. Luckily there was a free table, as this place gets very busy in the mornings 9.30-11.30am.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyZdajq16GKE99zQHWHfOI0XQ4aMV0hjn6e_Y6"],"When":"2018-3-27"},{"Name":"Donal Evans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBOgMjOoj9wRjD80ZPWSE0u9yPvEF6hzfKn_JwIBBUU5tWdg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Really good coffee. I’ve just had it on the go, but great coffee and friendly staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"NAMYOUNG KIM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOx2sqAf5jAtiqSiF0skGtYenuw2Xhff_YhGaM3AIdvWg-mQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely place! I really loved coffee and ricotta toast. Definitely will visit again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMw3rDUU6I6Md_bbFovYgE45fOJEB5XTDpsMy1h"],"When":"2022-8-5"},{"Name":"doktor cinta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGbfzWoy5ORRz1CfyGA25Hwt8p-MeqDoJ31FQPQhzGdi2jS7wg4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Smooth easy jazz at the background, a space with character and a good coffee .. what else can you ask for? A hidden gem.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMZVNMQyFH7EkiSDjJtamRwri00PnCkDFYKYG_"],"When":"2022-9-5"},{"Name":"C C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOJ9B3R1DXO2miTSc7BvxgJWRFRQEXHo3l16aZMSTmTVUVYw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice hideaway to enjoy your coffee","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPelz1SWXlcWkRu-8VDmAGCJ7Hdn39VrjzZZMhj"],"When":"2024-6-3"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Traveller Me","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMTG4ze20ybx-eNQnd8mxhl12mQ8LBubeqI1I-_XCWoE0Tt8Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you looking for slow bar ,chilling ,chit chat and relaxing ~
Here is Amazing hidden gem of specialty coffee
So many coffee beans all around  the world
but already drop here  in Sydney !! 🇦🇺👍👍👍

It's not only coffee but It's mean coffee,people,sharing and community
Great ambience. Good service

Cake and cookies was so tasty.
And House made Hot Chocolate was amazing also!!
You should try !!! 😊😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIPeLJSLYHg6NlUZIyiXFq2LEas_We39Vd6dbC"],"When":"2022-6-3"},{"Name":"Carolyne Kramar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXx14Oy71LdMxbrXxLd_D34RaRgpHKoLaQdu4d0ORrOMAH90fEOSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a find!
Open Saturday and Sunday- a little out of the way, but full nevertheless, and with good reason.
These guys and girls know their stuff, and my double espresso was rich, flavourful and smooth with no bitter or burnt aftertaste.

Cold brew and pour over are also available, along with milk and iced coffees.

Music was great and not overbearing, service from all the staff was exceptional.  A small space, but it works and the patrons, both regulars and those who had the fortune to find this, are happy to shuffle and smile to make it work.

The coffee really shines though - well worthwhile seeking out if in this sector or the city.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdKJpyB7-qp-6CZGWGyeLWB8wIIVDNQzSaN-ty"],"When":"2024-2-24"},{"Name":"S A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqgcHhBPoJHjRetn6I5i2LbcmDzIgYe3HX5JQsFjQ4yu1JxQI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Discover this hidden gem filled with amazing individuals possessing extensive knowledge about coffees from all corners of the globe. Though it may be elusive to locate, once found, it promises a delightful experience. The coffee is sensational, complemented by exceptional service in a welcoming atmosphere. Despite its small size, the cafe boasts a great space that is perfectly curated. Indulge in rich, flavorful, and smooth coffee without any hint of bitterness or burnt aftertaste.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxTUnLPIu3YdXqArZ6H9onRps-DQhss3wYWX7w"],"When":"2024-2-24"},{"Name":"Sam Mastine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs3kpJDKO73ym9leCBMB4N6HmqRGTDDCkmjnp6YiB-tQntnqcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great spot tucked away down the end of Region Food Arcade. Super yummy coffee, great staff, cute eclectic atmosphere which is very relaxed. Food looked delish as well, going to have to go back! If you’re up for a chat, try and find a seat at the filter bar! Perfect spot to watch all the action.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKgr_lsTQJK3ePYO29GNC7XxRBC3s2pU2AuwpQ"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Tiffany Cheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjZXqsUiv_h5jf7q5Rr2Quf9V-ycJ6ppb9TLJetZSD1J8WlG0x=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stayed in Sydney for 5 days and came back twice already. Easily become my favourite coffee place in the city👍🏻 Was hard to find it in the first place as it is hidden in a rather gloomy-looking food arcade. Entry via backdoor on weekends / holidays.

Tried a good variety of coffee - pourovers, espresso, flat white, all of them done right! They use beans from a various roasters around the world. The bar table setup is great for having a chat with the baristas. Barista is super friendly and funny, and very, very knowledgeable about coffee, which explains why most of the customers are frequent goers / coffee snobs. Will definitely come back again for my next visit to Sydney!😀","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoRZtZFA2V7dCkG_NxYs3cgunV7T9XQUojUz2r"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Sam and Benny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLktsfIBWgl4_Plechd05IxmMCS-DhjNWILddYMHDZ95FifoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent cafe, although it appears to be intentionally hidden away. Otherwise, it is ideally located off Bridge Street. The staff were super friendly and even educated us on the coffee. The general demeanor of everyone around created a very pleasant atmosphere indeed. We like how Diggy do.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMw1DkLU5ZQQ6kKgC-hNKgH3JPfc7aWXtgaqCUl"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Shenny Bhuwani Cili","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9s0s4LARYKkn5v6l9MNxecZBbC_gawfJcUvEyIzUqzfmpx_bO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dare I say the best coffee on the planet. I kept looking at the coffee cup in my hand after every sip, amazed at how a cup of mocha coffee could taste so good. 😂 In the pictures: mocha coffee with oatmilk and kimchi toastie.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnDTAXzGz8xdP0Zr9PXo64JJpEhGQNCYENPk00"],"When":"2024-5-27"},{"Name":"OvrlndHI Pohaku","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjPLak-7xj7ahZ7AFsICD6D7zAoOm8OEvq7CeyNPYw6aQuXPFlOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We only had pour overs, which were all done very well. But the extensive selection and homely atmosphere is what has won me over as the best pour over & single origin selection in Sydney. You need to come in to check the amazing selection","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNu0kDlGEwl_21dYKs3I3_qom2Rvq1YG_hIQQti"],"When":"2024-6-8"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kristina M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0nx4k_a9nlK4tb-VV-1pP95WmxR2t9SsKJ7x8AVvYe049AQ-Zqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Syrniki is divine! ✨
The vibe here is awesome and the service is spot-on. It's the perfect hangout to sip tea, dive into a good book or enjoy some people watching from the cozy upstairs nook.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSg_DYoeGi7EJju8n1TX4WABDESGygzI1xZTNz"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Kai Ran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKpflOyCBsAcSq6lvy8sEztlmI-CZR4wzoUjXYFXvSaN7JQrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was an amazing find. Eastern European bent on the menu, which is not easy to find, and very delicious. The servers are always friendly and smiling. Love that the menu is all days so it suits if you happen to need a proper meal at an unusual time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMR7rhp9gxlKNgmkHBzGZ3uCU_gsD9Tw3UWUs5U"],"When":"2024-2-3"},{"Name":"Dmitry Sadovnikov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVk7TBpd8y8RancUc4SGwpggljecasJlBahteSOcuAg7LjzrPnj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dymocks Cafe is my favourite place in Sydney. The staff are friendly. I've tried different food and can recommend Borsch with lots of meat, Beef Stroganoff, Beef Goulash, Syrniki, Honey Cake. Will come back to this place again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRzZZdd11E_GRYQ_YDUdxZTbbd6EtgeUfiu0yd"],"When":"2024-4-10"},{"Name":"Pauline O'Keeffe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5winGYqyapeQFiHCf67b6quwDPIuLK6lb_k6n2nvucjidl7g9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Didn’t see the entrance to the cafe as it’s a little hidden upstairs against the balcony. You will have to wait to be seated and it builds up quickly. The prices for the food is a little on the higher side but lots of choices. Very narrow to get to the seats and pay so
not suitable for buggies or wheelchair. Delicious ricotta strawberry pancakes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiO8HJPg2h4tor3lPN4Kuz7EVdF-YM0tL7nhWY"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"Bee Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWg68SqnDfr7ivin7Qgm7zHQo-MPf3-hujsARw2YUx4RGl5QIhd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic Cafe with extensive menu. I highly recommend going but also to book it gets quite busy and for good reason. Vegetarian crepe and salmon crepe were excellent. Will go again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTOtVTdt16aiQlHXiDbwpIE92VdwBeBBbRZ--Q"],"When":"2024-3-16"},{"Name":"Ayushma Dwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpD_Ppf4STLC9GFJE5WVKnVH64qg1_I1hyFh3h6Y5DU4d1fAhH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A beautiful little gem in town. I was looking for cafés in town because I wanted something like a sandwich. I found this place. I ordered a takeaway salmon and avocado croissant. One of the google review photos looked so yum that I had to give it a try. Have to say, looks don’t lie. Definitely going back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPv2hbODMCbZlRuLVP5ikMzcG2bJVvCb_J5kdcG"],"When":"2024-1-9"},{"Name":"Greg Sharpe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXyzayukVsmS5Cj0LipmUA7SBw0HbOP2zIG0iH6M6TyUwiTlUo2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice drinks and an amazing cake selection. Located on the 1st floor of Dymocks, seating is a little cramped, but you'll get some views over the Dymocks shopping floor. Enjoyed a hot chocolate and a vanilla slice","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKs1JLdV2sXBU9lca00LuuoL0krnqknCJafuvn"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Mia Duong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqsSZegbTdo1Hm6pyYQKR-QomlpHSsOSeQ10E30vlen9a9f-yg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is delicious and visually beautiful .

However I think they can do better with service . There are quite a few vacant tables but we have to wait a bit before we got seated . I have seen later some customers waited but did not get acknowledge so they walked away .

When our food was served , we tried to ask for extra cutlery but after trying to get attention from waiter and get no luck , my friend walked over to the counter and asked for it . Then someone brought it to us after . May be it was a busy period for them and lack of staff , otherwise good location and atmosphere is good .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2KnYSPBz7xlzT2cFFr8_hC1kq9wEyr6BDiwc0"],"When":"2023-12-28"}]

[{"Name":"A L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbG4Uovod39icBTUGTFjHt_xR14j4Ui5Ztp6f2KVXGtLNexA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great cafe, with a great variety of options.  Sarah was our server, and hands down she made the experience great.  She was very friendly and cheerful.  She was exceptional, we will be back and hope to have Sarah as our server again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsZMrEmGYWwlWt04YXeD8I2qCrRX2QDboJD3zv"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Gbyepain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDh2I33LQ97OVb5s868wcBWiXKO2vr3hIzqDXWtqst2xfU6HMe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best coffee and chicken sandwich in town. Must try the soup of the day and the cold brew ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMf0h2CtzhdpaUSL8OCX117267zQodEeEbc9Q4O"],"When":"2024-4-3"},{"Name":"Meredith Epp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJH6irUacMwHgD3m-JnDVdYYZmMQFlrlfqfqpt4KCsNIINWv8H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Big fan of this place for breakfast and lunch meetings. A wide range of healthy options in a nice really open and airy setting. Been here about 10 times over the last few years. Consistently good coffee and food. Went yesterday and had a wonderful server. Will be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmBdMLzb6-YLFYkpioR-afLXY2R-wE7tIgjvwmJb6R5MUTUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cafe is cute, but I am giving this raving reviewing based off of one server alone, Sarah.  She was the best server I have ever had, made recommendations, was patient with ordering, and to top it off she was so friendly and always smiling.  She made this the best cafe experience, and for that alone I would recommend this cafe, and hope you get the best server Sarah.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K Prince","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiPTBCQlXcsGCnpmUUg1yxDk3KlsCxbsBeLhk7IZFVsxtUTP8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A really test for a cafe is the simple poached egg.

I’m always recommending this fantastic cafe.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"doktor cinta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGbfzWoy5ORRz1CfyGA25Hwt8p-MeqDoJ31FQPQhzGdi2jS7wg4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Spacious cafe with a lot of healthy options. [{"Name":"Adam Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXPQrtVBtf87kNlfyRELbPXi54_KhEn3LGUdXqeWYDa-w1Jwx_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Overall: 5/7
Nice place to grab some reasonably priced toasties that deliver strong flavours and show off a variety of combinations.

The migoreng one is quite good and the egg is perfectly cooked. Last time I went it was saltier though…","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-w38277zKo7rnLLiGTL4D3aLo7dzSmjP1_dde"],"When":"2024-3-15"},{"Name":"Razel Navarro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXK7RyhsU1CNv4z0r7pnA8OHiWKDA6QqKdhfd6e-UImBjcZ1v2b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our favourite cafe for toasties and iced tea (and coffee) The Mi Goreng Toastie of course is very good but try their other toasties as well because they are equally delicious. Mushroom Truffle, Nachos, Rueben are my other faves from them.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIYklsru9gsD13HuQNVgev2IIfCRXgcZrUfv78"],"When":"2024-2-4"},{"Name":"Randy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpBzB5mI0gSMErSbx1qCuB4-5Lsv332ewg8H7CkEuHqR-5Pu73=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dutch smuggler george street. Equip with la marzocco kb90, mahlkonig e80,ek43 and mazzer kony. Collaborative roast under the same brand. Brew method mostly espresso. Because its open outdoor seating, will be challenging in the winter, so many wind 🥶","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNndnzmEB0JthnarYb1YurvLWrNw42ilKF5tY7K"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"Melissa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNm7vsX1Mnp6LdE7r0IlZzBSlmo865p_AdyLQckZhVPTFUUMNx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A small little cafe with limited outdoor seating. Friendly staff, and the toasts tasted great indeed. We enjoyed our oat mocha and oat sticky chai as well. Highly recommended if you would just like to have a quick bite (with good quality coffee).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyr66j_Mbq2QUs9Si-UuKMXERjgaHhWizU8bQQ"],"When":"2023-11-11"},{"Name":"Alex Svensson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzGV5VZWQOIDARNbZDQuQ340CD_vLgvGBHKCKVJY6mJBPi59U3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A secret hideout in Sydney cbd with the most delicious toasties and coffee! We happened to pick a wonderful sunny day, suitable for their outdoor seating among other restaurants.

We tried their coffee flight, which provided us a white coffee, espresso and batch brew, all of which were super flavoursome. Highly recommend their kimchi toastie too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaZrtm-3QocCRLOYmtIYtXpbWGl8_QrcJJtvZ-"],"When":"2023-12-17"},{"Name":"Pliyakamol Akkharajittanon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyA0qvd0_hHwXHcSgLKNiOGJM89amZ8EIEi8B2tfBW016CSBPs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good to go / sit in Breakfast
Good iced latte
I love their bacon & egg roll!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPelSWjVdZPuVQj6LaGTwTZAaXwDh8R16XfZqSf"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"S A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqgcHhBPoJHjRetn6I5i2LbcmDzIgYe3HX5JQsFjQ4yu1JxQI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Searching for an extraordinary café experience? Look no further than Dutch Smuggler! This charming establishment has swiftly become my top choice for a delectable cup of coffee and a mouthwatering toastie. The coffee they serve is truly exceptional—always fresh, brimming with flavor, and brewed with expertise. On vivid Sydney’s cold evening, we were pleasantly surprised by their delightful offering of freshly made tacos. The flavors were a burst of deliciousness that left us craving for more. Whether you're a regular patron or a first-time visitor, you'll feel immediately at ease in this cozy and welcoming space.

All in all, I cannot emphasize enough how strongly I recommend Dutch Smuggler. If you happen to be in the vicinity, make sure to drop by and savor their outstanding coffee and toasties firsthand!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO65dlpvBTMnQoETIgH6rELAuv-39Crj8J-3a5E"],"When":"2023-6-26"},{"Name":"Alberto Rascon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi27jlBjtO1vKkBx9E62M8u9E79ddd481IhUP3HhfMjrvYVz1W=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first experience with a toastie was delicious. We ordered the croque monsieur, and everything was heavenly with just the right amount of "toastieness" to it. Easily my favorite toasties in Sydney. We also ordered a flat white and a chai latte, which were the cherry on top of our breakfast. The cafe is situated at the bottom of an office building, which was a bit challenging to find at first. The service was amazing, and the baristas were super friendly, providing us with recommendations around the CBD. They have only a small, limited outdoor seating area. Such a solid place for some coffee and toasties!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSv02-2KCxZhNKHJxoL2R0U4jaMJDhsy-8YpXn"],"When":"2023-11-19"}]

Coffee by welcome dose.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvyB3FflGbmXp3msIZHBRK_B64nuxinwc4VZ_9"],"When":"2024-5-30"},{"Name":"Leonard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXM5zYQL_rs11ZsXmJxIzKfTMONMHBcwkRpVyqmptW1t3UCBEhnzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered a dirty decaf chai latte here and it was really good.

They use real chai and not a sugar powder mix. They have decaf coffee for those who want a cup later in the day. And they have oat milk for those with lactose intolerance.

They're also super friendly.

Note: the place doesn't have wifi and seating is limited. Not good for working.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUaftx5wtJf9fmV-rix4cK77m9OGyWySK1BRBg"],"When":"2024-1-4"},{"Name":"Sid Rev","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZQxifvvjUJN2uq4Tm2D5WCGgP-e_47oj8nY2wSPwqPY0ljEUs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cabrito Cafe is located on the alleyway of historical buildings. Had to ask which coffee brand they use, and was told they roast their own.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRBEDki9S-2nkxAvq94Bbb73om6zQi02TzAAfd"],"When":"2023-9-6"},{"Name":"Sami Makelainen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxMa_WOHZv-3uoFhSDrp0SMZg7neb-BBQHc4FJUBZbTmUinDxcGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Charming place with excellent coffee. Has a bit of a Melbourne-vibe to it, which, let's be honest, is always a good thing in this genre.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaImymArE8VoftP2jGdVZ1d2vAXfMAJhHH5YcP"],"When":"2023-11-28"},{"Name":"Julia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJm2zKCC22dgtsJALLJUmiaTMTrygtxMaaLbCOP89Hll6a2LTsG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The staff acted weirdly when taking my order and sounded like he didn't want to serve me. The coffee tasted watery after all. The barista made multiple cups of coffee at the same time but clearly poured less milk into my cup compared to the others of the same size.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carlito","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNCAyEL2NiKi7Dd_v-VyPcaF4PTFQJzgDdlWXi5U2mmPX1sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a great hole in the wall joint down a little alleyway. [{"Name":"Gary J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKystsZeWe2yZ9Y_xBwoCZPvQsJlYu-zhjPjCfwzpof4MsrpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So good I had to have two orders of the lamb. Wade, Rudy, Miguel and Junior showed true passion in what they do and it shows in not just their food but their drinks as well. The quality of their food and drinks(all made from scratch) were mind blowing. It shows true love of what they do and would recommend them first to anyone visiting the Gold Coast. Rarely do we visit the same place twice during our travels but we were dreaming about returning and did two days later. You can tell that they choose the best sources and recipes carried down through the generations of the Rabbath family. We definitely will come back here on our next trip. Thank you so much for a great meal, drinks and experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNV8QprQW2CNoDo-forvBAiXDLdTxmkoyDnuexY"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Lorraine Wienand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2TikJs8uL7AuQGfsYefkFwKmVIUO-sLtb8DmkUfDSOx5-3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We all really enjoyed the variety and the quality was excellent.
Angus steak was the best I have had and the soft drinks were absolutely amazing.
The Turkish delight desert and the spiced coffee was exceptional. Great selection and variety especially for gluten free and vegeyarian meals.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOB5BiSjBXrmR86IrCdt8an5NQeaxwSiC4Fq1Lu"],"When":"2024-3-6"},{"Name":"Rosa Villar Montero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICwpWjxaSIcp1VPfCKeay9KEg9NW6VNkjuOJZvttXkdUqfNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food. The flavours make you feel you're not in Australia.
Rudy was so nice and friendly.  Service 10/10.
Can't wait to come back thanks :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEQJbnIRAtkc4rbuTXun7IZZLnN9AGTilJAosi"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Anthony Elmore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8684YjFkkHcgHZYgIJ_4Z6_ZlurCqdlyljl-IPP1AWehg1A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding!  What more can I say... We enjoyed a magnificent lunch, fantastic service from front of house staff and the two extremely friendly chefs.  We were there for a Tuesday lunch and the atmosphere was spot on for a relaxed lunch.  All the food was amazing, but the absolute highlight dish was the salmon, with the lamb very close second!  The salads were also so fresh and tasty.  Would ABSOLUTELY recommend this restaurant to others!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTWtZiy__8q169kdL7XOOrb5hxP_Fx6ujhmrAT"],"When":"2023-12-12"},{"Name":"Alice is eating","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCMxNpqkIupS4iilOmyGQdMXPhESX54QTEMsrmEhdBKWAqxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was the only group dining at that time
So we enjoyed the Aces hospitality from the manager and chefs.
A must come place if u r around and not dislike this type of food.
If the manager saw my review, could u tell me again what is the area you said deserve to explore restaurants in Perth please?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVdQWmomU0SbA9xOoFARstdZ-1LzbYBlPuXKw"],"When":"2023-6-5"},{"Name":"Lilly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCgXn6t3rU3m-dN_lC8PTtDUBM1SH5XSUb8gNCYze55lG3ogA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My new no.1 on the coast for dining. Service atmosphere and food are all top tier. This venue did not disappoint. Perfect for a cosy date, family dinner or girls night escapades.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSsWJ9M-w7RfZNNa5Phr8vBFdguUwTmt0IUOxf"],"When":"2024-4-9"},{"Name":"Ellie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZOp3w17SCmnIs9b65HJszRyBrkthYM3XqkRz_3YQuHtsYtUX5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came here last night with no booking & high hopes for a table - we had a short 30min wait & wow was it worth it! We absolutely loved this friendly & welcoming restaurant. Highly recommend their 3 course menu with wine pairing, such good value & really DELICIOUS food. Each course was full of flavour & the service was outstanding. If we’re in Burleigh Heads again we will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSLEi34jQsHnXVabCRsy-b-WIqmpqTOLuQruma"],"When":"2024-1-4"},{"Name":"Luke Olsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJh7fi9etObZhtolOjOzyLls8oIxWJm0ugLjczKJ8nafELFsw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place and very authentic Lebanese cuisine, would highly recommend and look forward to going back.

Highlights were the lamb and chicken skewers, fries with toum (garlic dip) and the Fattoush salad!

Also, love the selection of wines and the Pinot noir served cold. They also have a great selection of Lebanese wines and local beer.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWt89ZY-G7CAKTgVweyryPI0WV40uayJnXX36T"],"When":"2024-1-26"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Juan Rincon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK8JQWLmpqLQamQ5TL14VN0iq1GZIXlljNotQ4ZLHIZFOIxAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an absolutely fantastic dining experience at Omeros! From the moment we walked in, the atmosphere was inviting and cozy. We started off with a delightful array of appetizers including succulent scallops, flavorful mussels, and perfectly cooked garlic prawns. Each bite was bursting with fresh, delicious seafood goodness.

For our mains, we indulged in the salmon and ravioli dishes, both of which were absolute showstoppers. The salmon was cooked to perfection, flaky on the inside with a crispy skin on the outside, while the ravioli was filled with rich, creamy goodness that melted in our mouths.

To accompany our meal, we enjoyed a selection of wines and cocktails that perfectly complemented our dishes. The staff “Michael” was incredibly professional and attentive ensuring that our glasses were never empty.

Overall, Omeros exceeded our expectations in every way. The food was top-notch, the drinks were divine, and the service was impeccable. I can't wait to return for another memorable dining experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOciF3TKhoMNnmZuHRvY_ieu1YwgimCJwavxyAp"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"John Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIbWfbqFsqC3eUEkVXF5I6EASBRK7W4TWcrREcgr1v6TX-y3t28=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Under the slanting rays of the evening sun, the reflection of the yacht forms a beautiful scenery on the water. It's truly wonderful to dine at a riverside restaurant like this! The service staff are friendly, and the taste of the dishes is good. The only downside is that the freshness of the fish is not quite up to par.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNJ5df0jv_F6AA7r9I3LvlmGhYycoM5p74wi-X"],"When":"2024-1-5"},{"Name":"Clint Palmer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCOPiReRHV0S7Gxc7k64fAd3iSU1713iDABUJJuMETptBM5WaD4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Omeros brothers is a well-known establishment at Marina Mirage that offers plenty of options for fresh seafood as well as other fare such as steak and pasta. The restaurant has a great view and offers internal and external dining. It's a casual yet fancier place, a lot of people will go here to celebrate events and large bookings are well accomadated for. The servers are friendly and attentive and always go the extra effort. The food speaks for itself, mostly basic cuisine, yet always well cooked and tasty. Their consistency for a high-quality dining experience means they are a must try for anyone on the Gold Coast who enjoys seafood. Yes, they are relatively expensive. However, the produce is always high-end. Surf and Turf is the go-to for lovers of steak and seafood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgM0i-vYkfGN0YUh9ExU9fGwiRlblWfWnkAr51"],"When":"2024-1-10"},{"Name":"Clinton Moore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9lAD3Lq6mS6VXLtffO7UfAD1O1GAaXR-pKfsLwZaC2-5mdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I don't eat seafood so this place really isn't for me anyway, but this was a family occasion so I went with the cumin spiced vegetable gratin. Unfortunately, it had no flavour. It did have some nice textures though. Those who ordered seafood said it was nice but bones were found in two separate fish dishes. Our waiter was efficient but it isn't the type of place where they talk to you too much. Entrees (which were only slices of garlic bread) came out quickly, but mains then took almost an hour to arrive. Overall, just not worth the cost.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2wFKl6SuMsFnrg8MsJN2DeBOrO674LrbIPxxz"],"When":"2024-5-25"},{"Name":"Big Hungry Papa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3OEyYJntrYo5sJeZ5-arDxJFfsakwMm-Hscl1oxxFSkrG2S4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Offering spectacular Broadwater views, this restaurant serves the freshest Australian seafood at the Marina Mirage’s boardwalk.

Food is incredible, the atmosphere is superb and service is excellent.

We loved that the place is so well presented, it’s elegant but casual and cosy at the same time.

We found it hard to decide on the drinks(they have such an extensive drinks menu). so we asked our wait staff to help us in choosing, paired really well with our food. 🤌🏻👍🏻🍷

We will definitely be back, this place is highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIQKPlv835_2Sa8KaDLNu_jpUP5GMmClWG9udv"],"When":"2023-10-5"},{"Name":"Lisa Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSbAiThpiI6DRIW3lhMHl7vSoBw-4hvr5mrRFyEljiTlXLQ9ujow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Special occasions or making memories the best in the GC for a menu that’s lasted over 40 years untouched.

Best choice - Beef & Reef 🪸 better than any I’ve had in my lifetime.
❤️🍷🎁✨🌙","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxRoPcsdcDbw_nBqHOJNHsM0Tj7ugHfIhB5yhv"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Faye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrv-8fSne5_lz79mBAE7NxF0u-ayTS4QHQWQHZkgwLQrLVVHI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This use to be one of my favourite places on the coast for a nice seafood meal but after revisiting it from being away for a few years…I must say they need to up their game on their menu. Bring more to the table than what other seafood restaurants are offering.

Food aside, the inside of the restaurant is in need of a good Reno, the carpet floors are just screaming (90’s dining) 😆although the food is still on point, they could do more with creating a better ambience with updated decor as it can feel a little stuffy inside the way the seating is organised.

The garlic prawns I ordered with the rice for my mains was great! We got a range of entrees - the bread with dips (yum) the calamari also amazing, the seafood chowder - always good! And my friend got the fish of the day which she enjoyed. We also got a bottle of wine to share and had some drinks.

At the end of the night (2 couples) the bill added up to just over $500. I find this quite expensive and I think the quality is great but not $500 great. I still enjoy this place but it’s definitely not the most wallet friendly 😂
I’d recommend it for more a daytime long lunch and to sit outside for the view.

Still a nice restaurant but it looks really worn out inside and should deliver a more 5 star dining ambience if they are aiming for a sophisticated overall fine dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgsydgBJDDSJSE24suN_9N-YYCepKeJXoh6x-y"],"When":"2023-10-15"},{"Name":"Ivana G.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnzAR1cDUosvjuArS9sf_qdzBVfaJQQ5D_Fb39oW4kDbTKEiR9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful Restaurant with nice views. Quite busy restaurant, fast service, waiter was looking after us well. Prices were ok as this fine restaurant. Portions quite big for entrees menu. It was husbands birthday and I have asked if I can have something special for him, so they did sparkling candle on the desert, which was very nice. I really appreciated that they filled my request. Beautiful deserts and plenty of free parking. I would recommend to everyone this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5wHZ7cGIRC--6h9UiR0-a_2p5D8fOcAXkiwBs"],"When":"2023-10-20"}]

[{"Name":"Tony","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEFVXOWo46WP_5jkfSx3VEIuk9bI_YuJfSTWHRarS18ChBmJ8G=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A great casual dining experience. The food was outstanding yet simple enough. The service was very good. Not over the top, but attentive when needed, and able to go through the menu and provide insight into it and recommend complimentary dishes and wines. Would return and would certainly recommend it as a dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWBBvByx3IqPSaVO7XnJPxxZR4scJ7Fo3iVjLf"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Deborah Lowe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkmTiMqev6QPs0Vb-465nMF3x3et7OG73mpPIdJBcXdDoL6RM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sensational food and service. We ended up eating way too much because the food was so delicious! Standouts were the pork belly and the pancake. The vegan menu is extensive and excellent. My vegan husband wouldn't share. He said it's the best tasting vegan meals he's ever had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOS3n2elVCX_L2-EUymx5owxEVU_eL3ZzCjOjU1"],"When":"2024-4-30"},{"Name":"L T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpgDkZAxszZQjpeub1F32QyAcnQtyixDzLdsd2Q0NJQw9UqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing service and delicious food!

The staff here were incredible, especially a friendly staff from the Netherlands (sorry I forgot his name!).

The food was equally impressive. I highly recommend the Barramundi yellow curry and the tempura oysters.

We’ll definitely be back to try more dishes on the menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXaj1BCvnipsmm6P-Dp31_-m3OPI-nHhU7KTJ8"],"When":"2024-4-30"},{"Name":"Luke Olsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJh7fi9etObZhtolOjOzyLls8oIxWJm0ugLjczKJ8nafELFsw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jimmy Wah's in Burleigh Heads offers a fantastic dining experience with mouthwatering dishes like tempura snapper on betel leaves and tempura oysters. The sticky pork ribs are a must-try, and the wine selection adds to the overall enjoyment. It's a casual spot with exceptional food and drinks, perfect for a relaxed evening out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkaM9l01kd-lutXdqx1DNmOLhDLwkM3IoJYK53"],"When":"2024-3-9"},{"Name":"S R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUp7ljV-mM8HdUgSEcG9gwumQtBmCORdf8hfEilnR6fqKd9qQB_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is amazing. 10/10 for all dishes we have. Except the pancake 9/10 (bit too greasy).

One of the best dining experience in Australia.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_h9HTZzrfHbgR1yVC9qOvauLeKgCHFjR1FJLb"],"When":"2024-4-7"},{"Name":"Bevin Rijkaart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhogjPShd2Gx6wE0ReFrpFs5ghPwStkGfoEGVsDrAlW-JFUA2b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jimmy’s lived up to its reputation with our recent visit. Food was Devine, no complaints from me.
Check out my reel at @SensorySavours","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcGZBhtvpXqsY1nLnLj6YGQ8aO6z6_fSaT4c8_"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"summer zhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_x1xlOjfKtzcJVA0lx363YmNjXK25kYeHZ6c7Dy65yTZ50w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jimmy Wah's is my favorite restaurant on the Gold Coast. I visited once in 2018, and the memory has lingered ever since. Returning during this New Year holiday, the food is as delicious as ever, the cocktails are superb, and the service is top-notch. To me immy Wah's is my favorite restaurant across Australia 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlAVCiYBa7FqeBpXs4CpVnLiQVMfxltrjE_N9K"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Cameron Murphy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJodoNGrYbtLY_uYuRJppns3y4njjkvVa7wXQ_lc1XrKfN0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a favourite of ours on the Gold Coast. Great modern Vietnamese cuisine with an interesting wine list of domestic and imports that pair well with the menu. Such a pleasure to consistently experience great food, hospitality & service from the team that go the extra yards, unprompted 😁.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5oIuGbDK_hp7PahFoicRIckqvh3an-1uAIE21"],"When":"2024-1-6"}]

[{"Name":"JUNO KANG (가즈아앗)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMFxe6D4tCgPIksVi5Hr0zUWwBCnvp5I1oAdHvBXr6QIG9Kg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was our first meal at Gold Coast, and it was just amazing. We ordered 4 different kind of dish, and everything was absolutely fabulous.  Quite reasonable price. Nice servers. Highly recommended if u are wandering what to eat near mermaid beach.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPeDEsxM6Yumsz4exQe68z3jN_N_OAueMb5MhK"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Andrew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMfg_Xb7s1hxfNbbnVFCoSIcXq_-EPKegQ5k6ADk9JvczWWs_hXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food and fast service. The stir-fry was a flavor explosion! The combination of fresh basil and chilies created a perfect balance between sweet, savory, and spicy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuxdX8Wwkmj0gh2V-0um5x6NjAfeKapP8UbO40"],"When":"2024-5-25"},{"Name":"Mona k","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjkbv2L--8C6g1gt6dz53xz1X7No0NvfRn0Gm7beiaC8UZNrKk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Real Thai Taste in Gold Coast! Reasonable price, cozy environment, and friendly staff

Recommended: Crispy pork menu and tom yum fried rice","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZpXDtDc-r7lwVbaMfkj7Ic1b1ipatsM4a69F4"],"When":"2024-2-6"},{"Name":"Carl Bronkhorst","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXz9HZvIgrcIMl0C72dfSzae2-63ohTU6TELfn1i3EsQZuVUfIqEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Thai was grouse, and the best iv had on a while. The price and serving sizes were awesome. Authentic flavours and ingredients. There were just so many levels to theses meals, like the crispy chicken was so good, but then you dip in in the Thai sweet chilli sauce and the flavours explode in you mouth, even black to the basic coconut rice, it was just creamy and delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtlg1N4ikgkkVlJ_4EHCEO5WTT4tk7_V1qRS2D"],"When":"2023-10-17"},{"Name":"Yuri Verboog","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlSEPhQFM2Aej-mykU3xaWIklPoawsRO8mSgpXWb9caQT7mn1f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Thai street food on the Gold Coast! If you're looking for the authentic flavours of Thai street food you will not be disappointed. It is absolutely spot on, and I know because my partner is a Thai chef! Great portion sizing, delicious food and good atmosphere - this place gets a huge thumbs-up👌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORo4xGBGoT7i8MSiRrvFW4vspcI9aMbGNEyLR0"],"When":"2023-9-27"},{"Name":"Shannon Jackson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_aCaM82SqfxnuO9e6XYTR_WXpVzQIANptDn-uKE585Al6TA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A locals little secret. Book ahead on a weekend. Here’s why. Always consistently beautiful traditional yet humble Thai food. We were seated outside with a smile, because all the tables were taken. Food is always awesome. Despite being busy, super organised and though super busy, staff are friendly helpful and nice. The food is always fresh, and authentic. Wonderful little family business, who takes pride in every aspect of the business and shares their beautiful culture with us.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXmKupdFQKe91v1qnWmuZ-TZnCMEp09ZzsWEQK"],"When":"2023-11-24"},{"Name":"Narrapat Suparangsri (Gunn)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_zPdRYtGm_uz4_xUKDYA6wDA9P7CyLxgucc3yV8XugS64WnS9ng=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lucky Buddha Thai Restaurant is a fantastic place to savour authentic and delicious Thai street food. The restaurant is located in Mermaid Beach, on the Gold Coast Highway. The staff are friendly and helpful, and the service is fast and professional. The menu offers a wide range of dishes, from soups and salads to stir-fries and curries. The portions are ample and the prices are fair. I recommend the tom yum soup, the massaman beef and the pineapple fried rice. The food is fresh and tasty, with the perfect balance of sweet, sour, salty and spicy. The restaurant has a cozy and inviting atmosphere, with a modern decor and a lucky Buddha statue. It is a popular spot for locals and visitors alike, so it can get crowded at peak times.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPVndyvFAk2spUyp9i8uvkmianD2kkTsHmStfZ"],"When":"2023-5-5"},{"Name":"Yuka L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS3iNi9PKtzF2eP7Y1K4et2T2v8i6ZtAx9QslT7gN6kIX_zX8A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A month later🙂
I had Boat noodle $12.9 and Steamed Dim Sim $9.9 (homemade)😋
Dim Sim was very nice 😍
Noodle soup made me uplifted 💪🏻😁
I wanted to try Prawn cake but they didn’t have it today 😢
I need to come again and try it 😋😋😋

It’s my first visit for lunch 😋
I had Yen Ta Fo seafood $16.9 and mixed entree $10.9.
I got there 2:30pm then they closed 3pm.
I needed to rush to have them a little bit.
It’s pink soup noodle 😳😳😳
It’s very interesting for me😁
It’s not spicy 😊I put some spicy vinegar (?) later, I liked it 🥰
It’s difficult to explain how it tasted like again 😅
I love to try the Thai street food 😁👍🏻
It’s so much fun trying food which I never had 🤩🤩🤩","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPX8SGKhBBbnr5utFFFTeHD492u8oaUFVIZhtWz"],"When":"2022-7-6"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ward Purcell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiXXqQwd1lGyDQ8y_LwgP0aE_9Zcw8xkdVWgV-e9TJPCa8FRxR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We saved the best for last. On our last night on holidays we visited Georges on Broadbeach having walked past it on our way to the awesome Pink Flamingo. The food is exceptional, the staff were amazing and the atmosphere cool and family friendly. Highly recommend and the best garlic prawns we had on the Gold coast including 2, 5 star restaurants. Well done guys and girls and we are definitely looking forward to dining there again next year. Thank you 😁","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSckzzAf2AfHEo6toEkUERJSiNyDTZSUpK-zhj"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"Jade Waldron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5TbpCyEe0rach84w1pf9WVwZhQJHZjQUG5vogtwByyiqD6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When arriving to the restaurant, my partner and I were greeted by hard working, focused yet kind and friendly smiles, being told they would only be a moment as they had finished with their previous customers. I would like to take a second to show my appreciation for how uplifted and generous the crew were making us feel accepted and comfortable before taking even one step into their establishment. Upon being seated our waiter Alberto Greeted us with a smile and filled our water without us having to ask whenever we were empty. The atmosphere was friendly, fun and welcoming, and it only got better with the 5 star rating food they put out in front of us. With the perfect amount to not be too filling yet filling enough, and the balance of flavours which made my smile grow bigger with every bite I had. I recommend coming here, we will definitely be back ourselves!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIa6mdW87eXGRCz2-gtvwxK7QDsDqQWr94cDGp"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Phillip Yee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUuU1yoL-hnUQ0XuKY0lNfIyfaicTW_-LW7xNFlqk-DqezTKMWHoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food last night was very good, especially the scallops entree which was delicious!! . Everyone enjoyed themselves!!
Our waiter was friendly and efficient, though not quite so friendly at the end, when I didn't add anything extra to the bill when requested.
This was a disappointing ending to otherwise an enjoyable evening!!
I also couldn't understand why they would charge us $11. 90 for tap water!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1fGSl_xmg3acCPdXV8NKq0MoyUOQ58T2UJcEw"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Liam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYLy6HT0n2_hawpIDy0ieJaHP_Dp02lwUurquL89LSKi5GJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stumbled across this beautiful restaurant glad we stopped to eat as the food was incredible and the waitstaff were very friendly and the service was fantastic, this was the best seafood I have had hands down and will not hesitate to re visit, if you want to eat the most fresh oysters and delicious octopus eat here! Scollops we had to re order after eating because they were so good we needed more ! 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJtwXSwO7PwDVQ4ISbwXmxcW-m4yY37bgCfzHN"],"When":"2024-5-6"},{"Name":"Justan Knoff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDfQaXvDFULHdb8UU0vtRnDAAZR949XOE_UgqGYb2iDK1w-YatIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely beautiful dining experience on our holiday.
Ordered their hot & cold seafood platter & wasn't disappointed.
Plenty of seafood & other items to tuck into. Served on a bed of rice & surrounded by leafy greens & salad, it satisfies even the hungriest soul.
At $200 a throw it's not cheap, but it's a well prepared & presented meal.
The only complaint, and it cist them a perfect score, once they gave us water, they never came to refill our glasses.
Overall, a fantastic dining experience that capped off a great day.
Come & try, you won't be disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2ChsKFseKCUtSibJ6lY3R-1l8UsH3VyXzNAFa"],"When":"2024-2-12"},{"Name":"V B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-ubFJiGwoihkJZq50aLwnnXt-xmW2DExlZzUmt_6BOu2N8Pel=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic seafood, fantastic ambience, and atmosphere. Great service and perfect advice. Highly recommend oysters, garlic prawns, and Baramindi! I've stayed in Gold Cost only for 2 evenings, and we selected George's randomly - this was a great choice. Came here next evening as well. Big thanks for our waiter from Spain (sorry, couldn't recall the name).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCkU0VAotx1-TjZ5NnJCxUJ_lVoPE2SIlyHYvd"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"Karen Betancourt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtMe1oFTmt0jcrR8mSU_kkqXKyB5qZEPnMRKY1UQuy7PYqabjpfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is really nice! The food is good and the service is amazing! Susana was amazing, with exceptional customer service skills. I would come back for sure!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEiOjIFEBPwzH9RbCOwc2WH_lLBslG1B0Vxci1"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"J V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXYN4IqfEau6i2LWtEWoR0Z13edZeBgGB3DEfaPtwvg6_bcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love the food here: it is fresh and cooked to perfection. Much better than Georges in Sanctuary Cove, a little bit more expensive, but 10x the quality, and the service is excellent, I am very impressed. If I could improve anything, I'd say they need more staff on the weekends as it can get quite busy, and I can see the guys struggling to keep up with demand. Other than that, 10/10.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNh3hQQ_hqlQIpvbPfAPdpncg1hyoxv-Gsbs4ZA"],"When":"2024-2-16"}]

[{"Name":"Zureen Prasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBL9PBKiA7iA93DBJkUgSc6zElv-n7M7Vt9v2AsHDy_GGAsA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was one of the best meals of our trip. Everything was delicious and cooked to perfection. Shout out to the chef's for preparing the amazing meals and a special thanks to our server Isa. She was lovely and made sure we had a great dining experience. All n all a 5 star experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0MoiO4mTSyA8Okq-e2fM24JJAtQZwmu3zy_OS"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"Tanya Butenko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXS0Y_bOe2yONowA4K03kaaSDH8D1Tw0hgcr7qrmxQKQMlfPLJU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our first try of Persian cuisine and it was mouthwatering. We are meat lovers and our taste buds were satisfied beyond the mention.
Service was great and place had a nice ambience.
We had Meateterian platter and traditional desert and everything was very good and some new flavours for us.
Pity it was rain so we couldn’t enjoy outside sitting.
Looking forward to visit again and try more dishes","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOle7Wg48pByMfejSFBWUXSJH9Bh_T5snlz5CO"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Irina Sultani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPdK546h9YKyS7cSz0qJDS8CXxXOO6PzK9AHSaPgZmYnfQPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service and food. We often have Persian food at home, so it was nice to eat at a restaurant with good food quality and variety of dishes. We ordered Persian Feast Banquet ($79 per person , min 4 ppl) , Ash & Jo soup - everything was delicious. Ash and Persian tea were the highlights of my dinner. Service was great. I loved seeing  Shiraz’s multicultural team 😊. Overall we had a great experience, thank you all!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-DPHNGwB74AcvBjZIlDdJwnUA3uczodhr_XA2"],"When":"2024-1-29"},{"Name":"Jheniffer Lourenço","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBAUnBtm2JqOy7L7d6CY7-SvyiCLMKKrpXC0XBiQoJZszF_23A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was my first time at the restaurant and I was surprised by how delicious the food was. Isa's service was impeccable, she explained the dishes to me very well and thanks to her I chose a marvellous dish. I'll definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPQi327x-BJvPDvpTd1DBywWcShgXk3NVbtb4s"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Izabela Marczyk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnUbC58TMMy6myJgJRLRXMu0qXQ0ucPyeVL6e2JkhMe2ffkp0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Followed the reviews and was amazed by the results. Delicious food, we had a banquet and could not finish any of the plates, having only breakfast that day we were very hungry which didn't help as the portions are super generous. All other quests were leaving with bags to finish at home. Happy to have yummy leftovers for lunch today.
Family friendly with lots of seating inside and out

I would maybe suggest some entertainment on weekends as we usually experience in Persian restaurants. Even without that we would be back again,","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSbpAQrCCjfgIX8KTsYXy-rnxx7qlyzkj1RJgT"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Amin Ghadersohi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbG08HYnTxsJM3cmvGujY3A_06WTkOkZ9WF7LE1ojFU3byVQ9d3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the lamb shank, zereshk polo and the soltani so far. They were absolutely delicious and so much food. I loved how each meal has a small shirazi salad and yogurt too. Highly recommend this place. Also stay at the Langham if you are visiting gold coast.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOoHcMowN88Hth-7nzdOmxlGpypdWPSBGJsPvjS"],"When":"2024-4-10"},{"Name":"Leanne Towns","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqesERU8YTBY3NPXVBinBVuX8bQOA0y_cIlhUk8L5VnoIldQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such delicious food and extremely large serving sizes!! We could have easily shared the ‘standard’ size meal with its very generous portions of meat, delicious rice and side condiments.
The service was good and all staff were welcoming. Decor and ambience was smart, casual and very relaxing.
Prices were very good especially considering quantity and quality of food provided.
I would definitely recommend and we will return as I really want to try the delicious desserts (but just couldn’t fit it in this time around!)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnsyJVyPkq8NMiOtyo38AvbkM4FxVujCW0V1Yd"],"When":"2024-1-11"},{"Name":"Susan Austin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2k_qNJnOwHijT9CIMDhZ5whn5jrW9Foz7auCK_NNMTvTGjdI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We stumbled across this place and are so glad we did. Having never dined at a Persian Restaurant before, the menu was a bit overwhelming, however the waiter Waa a great help 🙏 Everything was delicious and we can recommend the Salmon & rice dish & the slow cooked beef 😋 We will be back 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhdUuXUM5OJujZaExKEicyzFQ-L7jTXBsxXNpF"],"When":"2024-6-1"}]

[{"Name":"Leo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTy4-LRa6mGoEmf1XQB7ihuXBVtgGUfP3mEulIEKLd5lA5dhouuw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Situated nicely on the corner, it gives you a view of the street atmosphere

Waitresses had exotic ascents, very friendly, mocktails were good

Meal sizes for their pastas were small (but tasty), we left semi-hungry, and would recommend 1 or 2 entrees before mains","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMi42v3IsxJT4pEwQg3phtIUS-PAoW1iBcgbv4M"],"When":"2023-11-21"},{"Name":"Ric Pale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICGmQNozrWS6EsY3bOQNJXyZtyiJpUX2AwoaZJ9ho12PD-LQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful place, great service and great food too, regardless of some main courses and desserts not being available. Fair prices. Anyway, we enjoyed dinner at Sage Broadbeach. Highly recommended and we will surely be back there for lunch or dinner!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracey Wickham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCt4bvs4F9_9ggGpDA0flXfdzrpiNHfeMq_qYp1D1GTEvOyw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a wonderful restaurant Sage is to hold our Friends Christmas lunch at.

So friendly and easy to book with.

Extensive menu, set 2&3 course meal menus to select from and a bar where they make a might Bloody G&T !! The Sunday roast was divine !

The team couldn’t have been lovelier and everyone commented how much they enjoyed their meal and the atmosphere of Sage.

Highly recommend and we will be back next year.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHk3TDMcWEskxRQlb9w8V8haBh5sX-_2yyaWEI"],"When":"2023-12-10"},{"Name":"Christie Burgoyne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhjgJ_NmaAD7tMubRVXgVvDlheRj17MBtZP6PVrYN9bbXuweidPw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food, definitely impressed the father in law up from Sydney and looking to eat some really good seafood. Service was excellent! The staff are very welcoming and friendly and the service and meal time was really quick for Good Friday when the restaurant was full. The live music was absolutely perfect for the scene and it was an all round lovely experience. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katrina Ww","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCAOYBPen0U4pWWqMk56Rk-JeneqJJ6iiFv0nsqEFZpdjS2LQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Birthday Dinner… Very disappointed! We booked a table for 7 people for family birthday celebrations . The cocktails were wonderful and that’s where it stopped!
The waitress did not mention a number of items were unavailable that evening and we had to reevaluate our order.
The main courses - two of us chose the rump steak- unavailable!  and had option 2.  sirloin steak. Ordered medium well. It came out more than well done. At almost $50 for the meal they were sent back to kitchen. The 2nd round they came out served medium with a blood ring on the table. These steaks were not sirloin but thin fatty cuts of meat.
We had to ask twice for the drink menu to order wine with food. Very unattentive staff. We told the waitress we didnot want anything else for the main. She didn’t even say Happy Birthday to my brother. We spend $350 plus ! Won’t return.
We were told when we went to pay the bill that the chef said it wasn’t good meat not his cooking and we could have the sirloin at the rump price.. seriously disrespectful those two meals should have been foc !
Never again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8PAzmljwgfJiR40uOoHTWuZk0VGmYU4XdcWkb"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Ricardo Martins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_stXfECBkI9eB-_pZDj3vsrnf1OknCbTm2tyXMUrlxAiumHn3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here for a Sunday lunch with my little girls and loved it. Big portion of the kids calamari, and also thev spinach cannelloni was very well served. Great Veneto pro seco and fair priced as well(in comparison to the region).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cindy Chang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk46bYITiTJspyrhUY74-1I73xX6tR9gxh8hMctNtGVmzKvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We had cold & hot combined seafood platter. The seafood was ok fresh. I found the cuddlefish a bit too rich, and got a upset stomach after the meal. The bugs were not much taste. Overall food was ok, not as good as we remembered, quite disappointed. But I understand the cost of the food has gone up. The staff were very friendly and service was good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKj-wWKs0WzFh6Q-gqt-v8CS8aFGsDvGfkmrqx"],"When":"2023-4-6"},{"Name":"Esta Mostert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFO-auqLWpFZ0mX0NA_j3VXDNpGXnhP4EBmh-aNZHE3j7HzS8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I was looking forward to an exquisite evening for our wedding anniversary. We were welcomed by the staff who seemed to have difficulties finding our bookings. The food was well prepared and tasty. I think that what we expérienced could be an effect of the Covid19 outbreak. The staff with exception of two servers, were either inexperienced or not very well trained. As the restaurant boasted with so many accolades, I would urged the owner to save what he can. The food was very tasty. I take my hat off to the chef.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuYYj7W6eJQBd082K5XuT0IOJkzuqjjzqflCRl"],"When":"2021-12-30"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Cherie H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUL9f5-eZHWGJ54NuEnDfvBVrPc7h3LPry0a6TswDMdXQqOvnYy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Popular Asian fusion restaurant with a great modern vibe. Service was good, we had to leave by a certain time and they easily accommodated this. We ordered the banquet menu and it did not disappoint! The highlight was the fried squid, it was tender and delicious with the sauce. I found all the dishes to be tasty but on the salty side. The beef in the curry was a bit stringy as the beef was cut with the grain not against it. Overall a lovely dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1g0TSntxetgAhTieXt58CZUQaJhIIRFKyHocd"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"Sarah Higgins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUqQmcBLBPrDGYs3sUIjEZktgKB7zJDxAevr4ym181xqOwTZTR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sensational food packed with powerful flavour, brilliant waiters with a sense of humour, elegant but relaxed environment. The lamb fell off the bone, pork was like butter, pulled beef curry was delicious & consistently soft… Hands down the most memorable meal to date. Thank you Mamasan Kitchen! 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvwvECD5UACtgW37Hk3MMfg7aOpyMNZ91dWqGb"],"When":"2024-3-28"},{"Name":"Lambo Blair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCHeowVirg-4pQAdT3hKpP3DSCttPp4l_pjCF6213DwnFURDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazingly good food here, super tasty and presented very nicely.
Service was excellent and the restaurant itself was very nice 👌.
Definitely a cool Asian fusion restaurant worth visiting.
We had the lobster entree, the short ribs, the wagyu beef and the fried. Everything was super tasty.
Keen to visit again to try some of the other dishes on the menu.
Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxx3I5VHqMImzMT-YmOv4X1ro5L-lHxXUOyWP0"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"Damien Lynch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmXDR-PpKMl-apII8a38eegZKwkZkBL2ViAr2ZY0KSeCSR5dIG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staying on the Gold Coast for a week and walked past Mamasan Kitchen a few times. Decided to give it a try and it was delightful. Very busy for a Monday night but got a table. Would suggest making a reservation however as some people were turned away after us. Had the soft shell crab bao, followed by the waygu red curry and Mamasan fried rice, washed down with some cocktails, my favorite being Good Morning Vietnam sour. Food looked and tasted great, atmosphere was relaxed but classy and the service was fantastic, big shout out to Max who looked after us with some great recommendations and brought great energy. Would recommend to anyone in the mood for Asian fusion.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyrW8oMBxiPudAsue21tGqsmDeIdQSdjcMnyVT"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Emmy Than","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLtJWdq1MKKyVcaur3I-MedYUyyjhQNIHf5Up21k33emYFZVOW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice to be sitting outdoor having beer and champagne with friends and family :) the Asian fusion foods are very nice. We enjoyed it so much ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPn-v7PAszh7oJeaQbHHPJgDENpvQCX2a_O6lFn"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Phillip Louey2","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3tGG5-SfhtsA9Zi7ctQ_A0zGs2EYsEspg-RTEmzxHJmXYkA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every visit is special warm friendly atmosphere, sensational food , we love spice and wow everything is a mouth sensation. The cocktails are amazing, for a couple or a friends get together wow service first class many thanks for making my birthday special .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP32lR6v_jORBaSJUpMvHA7LMblB7MSkfaQExiY"],"When":"2024-3-9"},{"Name":"Mandy Krause","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPEeUSDS2XKuvzGe97VPb5bC1GqyKr9cy1mqsfbQg0C4y1HQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered a number of dishes from the menu for appetizer, main and desert and couldn't pick a favourite! Incredible food and service, the best we have had on the GoldCoast and the best pork belly and Thai green fish curry we have had. The service was also exceptional!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3rB1s4Lh-WD5Pzx7l-Jyn4leYw8XYlDlu4ZKE"],"When":"2024-6-6"},{"Name":"M C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLd7zWjcv0S6Q8_7kK5VnL2fiXAxCKY_vjV-dvF6KVJS68dsA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The ambiance and staff at this place are impressive, and friendly.

However, the signature dish,  4 pcs spanner crab ravioli dumplings  fell short of expectations for its  $40 price tag. The wagyu beef red curry and panko-fried squid were just okay, with the squid being a bit dry, though my daughter enjoyed it.

The standout dish was the tuna tartare. The duck pancake lacked moisture and failed to impress; I'd opt for the duck pancakes from Aldi or Costco over this. Despite the average food, combined with alcohol and good service, my overall experience was okay.

While I don't mind splurging on food, Asian fusion cuisine should pack a punch of flavour, and some dish lack  both taste and value for money. If not for the attentive staff and the cocktail experience, I would rate it lower, but considering we enjoyed the overall night, I'm giving it 3 stars.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyjpDtNS_yxm7QxsEXnTfrGtwnLA43fI1iTQk_"],"When":"2024-1-20"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"A Bez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBQeW-Qp-nXi4i2ToWqaviTG6vcqI10Sk4u7ppAHs4eZ4rUg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Fine dining at a different level. Stunning setting for just a casual day dining however it must be quite a stunning setting for a night private dining. Only downside could be the walk through of over indulged people in evening. Food in a different class, presentation of is expected of a establishment at that level. We were even honoured with the presence of a dolphin cruising past our table. Really stunning place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIWXMiCPLuPKStXwleeaOrOdfx65MgB51F8lWy"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"Justin Weekes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWe1t8ROe-DdbdayoTXhEzTijQ1MH2QffuSgJ-ksS_XEqD85wJj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My partner and I enjoyed a lovely dinner here for her birthday. We were seated outside with a lovely water and boat view with lovely low lit lights to set the mood. We both had an amazing steak dinner with a lovely red wine sauce and a couple of cocktails each, which were all very lovely. The food was great, and so was the service.  It can be a little difficult to find the place, but it is just located at the very end right next to the marina.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONM_KximOZGR-P-BexHj8eS_DC1uQdT5x6qDfB"],"When":"2024-2-21"},{"Name":"il.c il.c","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhryPW5PtUmznqU8X_J7rW7ZEjcvO29IWEFaIExOnmpJWSEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an absolutely fantastic dining experience at Glass Dining & Lounge Bar! From the moment we walked in, the atmosphere was inviting and cozy. We started off with a Warm Mediterranean Olives, Byron Bay Burrata &San Daniele, baby squid, Tartare and Warmed Turkish Bread. Everything was delicious.
I can't wait to return for another memorable dining experience❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYna8M8j6lCYG_hcBqW33pdkFzHbDHafVrc0wk"],"When":"2024-5-29"},{"Name":"Mr Pickle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNhZ6aPunT4yxCLYSDSz7uIyY9I8EVvyF90Lu17NX7NQEWcAHq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice food and the person serving us was amazing and very nice (Sebastian). Perfect for a special occasion. It has amazing view.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO26GFLeXSBB3YoLG6jWuc2g-kj3eM74IsGfId7"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Helena Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKcomyx_oPsrsBHPDMt0pdz6h_9JtitaKoiKFZvMDkd-dmbFKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice waterfront restaurant with decent food

Our favourite dish was the seafood linguine - the pasta had a nice texture, the sauce was savoury and seafoody and the lobster in it was very nice! The barramundi was nice with a very tasty sauce, but the overall dish was underwhelming for the price. The shoestring fries were good but $14 is quite expensive for it. The duck liver & plum pate was a very nice starter but, similarly, quite expensive for what we get.

Overall, the food wasn’t out of this world; so it didn’t really justify their price point. But the restaurant being waterfront does give a really nice atmosphere and the service was pretty good.

Also, if you stay at the Sheraton, it’s only a couple minutes walk from there!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7En_OectZ26T0PDFQDNokGHLFzOHcojKp_ICO"],"When":"2023-10-14"},{"Name":"Jason Butterworth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZ-cPlXAQZy6V7ROoBtMpMRcZP21Xbzye26picm_QcEYaj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful spot on the marina. The wait staff were very knowledgeable and friendly.  The food was exceptional. I had the seafood linguine, and my partner had the aged rib fillet with a Moreton Bay Bug and Local Prawns. We live an hour and a half from Glass and both agree its well worth the drive  This is now one of our most favourite restaurants. We cant wait to get back and try some other things on the menu.  Oh... and the Naked Margarita was amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLiypnr3PixmrPs41kXj_ZWUcAWJXthWn6F88"],"When":"2023-3-23"},{"Name":"Phil Spence","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHIR_4qrFS4clRcAgSYi5xHOWlcdqF_scunSz7BX4rn5l32g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First of all, I just wanna say this restaurant they serve happiness on a plate, Jesus Christ. What a great restaurant great service fantastic wine list from Sydney. It’s hard to find a decent restaurant in the Gold Coast. I’ve eaten at various places. This place leaves them for  dead
The chef is  from Wales talented chef","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dollypop Southern","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUY2qHbHgmkDsj7WEvoSTjj7ZtpTIzIOtbTR6UjYJjthi9tghU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Got the lunch menu which was very good value at $65 for 3 courses. We were all really impressed with our meal choices. Would go back for the same again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNx28dfUTun521k77N_UCvF93YETdfN8lHBo_tA"],"When":"2023-12-12"}]
