[{"Name":"Yes I will marry you! Liz Pforr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWNpciTCeNA3Z-0Sfp6YIi3SUkpXyaOe9EmvK07eTlI5H7hB23-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Was so looking forward to lunch here as I’d heard so many good reports only to be extremely disappointed. We waited well over an hour & a half for our meals, one of which had to be sent back as it was seared charcoal on the outside and raw on the inside! My salmon was very oily and the service left a lot to be desired. The saving grace was the view and the chips but won’t be going back for them!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxGYRFYq7peqicJrZRpIdD5U7DNHse1RXfHR8j"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"K M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkFwuSbSOPGV04NiXW0BK1jIjBQ1oV8rtwI9cdptc_gnBGCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food here was beautiful, absolutely delicious.
Service was very friendly and attentive. They go above and beyond other restaurants I’ve been to.
My only issue was how long it took someone to come back to take our order. People were sat down after us and their orders taken before ours without them having to call someone over like we did.
Gorgeous scenery, really nice location. We will be back.
The banana piña colada was delicious and I haven’t found a nicer drink elsewhere!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNL1E6CtpbX-P8V6dVgQYoXffqN490E4BlriZKO"],"When":"2024-1-3"},{"Name":"Peter Scanlon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrcOb4Y8Tg4woLk3jUGRq0hPvEqrE7RZpf1dXJKIiI-pmKK4ju0g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Scollops excellent
Calamari not do good. Funny taste, perhaps the oil
Prawn hubs, awful
Skin on chips/fries, actually fries. OK
Service excellent
Atmosphere excellent
Overall just a pass.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCerZxTlJRGnK05fiqclAicxLK1wDAOASh8vhP"],"When":"2024-4-10"},{"Name":"Cheryl Adams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkKUhLREhdwuMZu035KJW9cSauu2BwboNUI1tHcedjynZ1lnnvaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Edgewater is always a wonderful dining experience with its stunning canal views, excellent food and service. Perfect for a large family group - we were 10. Highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUsX-uQsOXK3Oe5dVnCTdWWR_3iBP3MoJiC0c_"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Rachel Permalloo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLh5f9zhEWUnVf5CajQ2rG9WaubUaFZ75dRBXu1nZLxQDQ1SgA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent experience! Went there for a birthday dinner and did not regret! Staff was super friendly, atmosphere was amazing and food was delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaKrNXix2zXeprDAGDLDplYhulxXWozPlxdeZ0"],"When":"2024-2-24"},{"Name":"Putu Devi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3sqMjuaYrbIBUIn1HjvdJ-4BjDdwUX9_Ntl2x5kQm9WsKkUfW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Five stars for everything! Love the food, staffs are friendly. Although, a bit long wait for the food, but still reasonable. They are children-friendly! They take a great care of customers with children, bonus gift for my kid too, so she is not too bored waiting. Staffs were so attentive trying to give the best service, we were asking for a place close to a view, and they are willing to accommodate. There is one staff very professional, friendly, and I think he is really passionate with his job. Will be back again trying other menus!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3vKJD1pwZEpn0iKEqVX8WyhmHzyIXw1AimJVa"],"When":"2023-7-15"},{"Name":"Dilini Navarathne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPiQU_xhOsg_FliFyjMq0s6GAVnEZCNn5kb3Ysq8R44wAMxsI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the food we had here was really good..would definitely recommend.
Didn't really like the banana Colada and the expresso martini blonde.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1oINPSe77JaMXiYhT0eUZa-bCbUcfi6f35JSs"],"When":"2024-3-16"},{"Name":"Steve Carr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeizvS_79yq6Muc7rYo0JwOQuXAPJsyZjwLXL_1A48hOTA_S8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome dining experience for Lunch. We had fantastic service and amazing meals. The food was delicious, all servers attentive and lovely, we had a great time. Thanks all for a lovely meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWvO5mToVAvZIyMJJF1qwQMM3K_BAwzwU3CVwV"],"When":"2023-11-5"}]

[{"Name":"Andrew Yee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJE67VdVAEvt5G1kysIazcJzXatAJ30CeumZGwPopwFJfrWTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent restaurant. I had my best meal in Gold Coast here. The King Prawn Risotto was perfectly cooked and seasoned. Loved the slight truffle fragrance which permeates the dish. The straciatella with charred zucchini and pickled squash was also brilliant. I also tasted a bit of the Pork Tomahawk and it was divine. Finally, service was top notch. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcZq990JCSrAKdlzMVhjdKunP5UrHBtV482C9l"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"Paulyn Dy (paulyndy)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjOBPej64Pt2jkmA7zpVQ-ErLM4VANjIamXSOTRfVCwlfTP7IaMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Social Eating House + Bar is undoubtedly a gem in the Gold Coast dining scene. With its inviting ambiance, delectable cuisine, and impeccable service, it's a place we'll eagerly return to. If you're in the area, don't miss the opportunity to dine at this fantastic establishment.

Overall Experience:Our experience at Social Eating House + Bar was nothing short of exceptional. From the moment we stepped in, we were greeted with warmth and hospitality.

Food: We embarked on a culinary journey by ordering nearly every dish from the menu, and each one surpassed our expectations. Every bite was a delightful explosion of flavors, leaving us feeling both satisfied and content.

Service: The attentive and knowledgeable staff, particularly our waitress, elevated our dining experience. Their dedication to ensuring every guest's needs were met added to the overall ambiance of the restaurant.

👌🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-tPaOVlAkpWOMlENwaCehFlV6-UqADNF-Hr-x"],"When":"2024-3-10"},{"Name":"Camila Rossi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsP5PdRtVqUDlYcPHNsUNWqDVmtZpPRZbkETPEGnoBGM1Sd6db=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"beef carpaccio flavours were delightful! octopus was a little bit overcooked but as soon as we reported to our waitress, she promptly notified her manager who apologised and replaced the dish. house cocktails were good, but nothing very special. beautiful service and food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXop5UMu-4MtbMYh7ICCChPU9sm1Z_DMwyebS0"],"When":"2023-12-8"},{"Name":"Felitciana Zsha'Mirzze","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4RcWiOvuxUf4zs4MH782tHnnhMdOQRd7kdYChRAGiL9K3E0E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eat here you will not regret it. Food is top tier and the cocktails are delicious. Good service and cozy atmosphere. One of my favourites.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYqjeWDIRSP9pG18qF_eK0Rvtgk1qV--mDgI0d"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"Eva H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkKoFwS299ZiKOksvHDjYZBpBQ69HnBhPGs9pfl1S6Do3q5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible dinner ..one of the best meals I've ever had 🤩 If you're visiting the area, I highly recommend this as your 'special occasion' place.

We ordered:

🔹 Seared scallop with seaweed butter.
MUST ORDER ITEM. Plump juicy scallops and the sauce is amazing. Everyone who ordered this loved it, and the one person who didn't, regretted their decision.

🔹 Sashimi of the day.
Very nice but nothing really special. Could order something else

🔹Burrata, figs, grapes
It was good, but burrata is always good

🔹BBQ octopus with txistorra sausage
Very delicious. Recommend

🔹 King prawn risotto, black truffle, caviar
MUST ORDER ITEM. Absolutely divine. The best risotto I've ever had. It's rich and comforting, but also bright with pops of caviar.

🔹Slow cooked lamb shoulder
Honestly a bit mid. It was tasty but you could get this at other places

🔹SIDES: crispy potatoes and broccolini
As advertised. Nothing showstopping

Service was very good until they got our order wrong (we ordered brussel sprouts and they mistakenly gave us the broccolini).

Instead of apologising and offering to go back to the kitchen to make the food we ordered, they made us feel like we were the ones inconveniencing them since they've already made it. "Do you still want it?"","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPj6QVN90WUn969Y8gfBUHmafmVGgjFQRauGs6A"],"When":"2023-11-14"},{"Name":"Agata Kania","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIa2d4hceUOCEt5WSSnvoygjIjR5H5gMEBYANlyR7m8Tattdg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I couldn't be more delighted with my visit to this restaurant! We ordered scallops, burrata, and octopus for starters, and each dish delighted us with perfectly balanced flavors and high-quality ingredients. For the main course, we had shrimp risotto, which was intensely flavorful, definitely something intriguing. The crab pasta was perfectly spicy, with juicy and fresh crab. The presentation of the whole dish was surprising due to its unconventional form of serving pasta. The entire dining experience was heavenly! I highly recommend this restaurant, and the price for such quality is truly reasonable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNbxRUyx4kVtyzyGvZ2AiIsb1qiGIqS9gbXS5U"],"When":"2024-1-3"},{"Name":"Symone Mercuri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV164Rp_GEW7UndmU6fpj9cxm2S2wuW719H0lclXuf1Q8Tl-GFBZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":""Social in Broadbeach exceeded my expectations in every way! The service was truly top-notch, with attentive staff who made us feel welcomed from the moment we walked in. The food was exceptional – fresh, flavorful, and beautifully presented. I couldn't fault a single thing about our dining experience. Highly recommend to anyone looking for a fantastic meal and great service!"","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5NsepwXy7mFR75VIFogxKn1frWR-uGnjFbEO4"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Jennifer 寶 明 Chang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXcYSJA8EgQ5gZek2qzVwWgG8RTZ9HwTy4Gg6ZxRkCK3cdnp0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Our dining experience was delightful; however, we're reluctant to revisit due to subpar customer service. Serendipitously discovering this restaurant during our time in Broad Beach, we consulted Google reviews, which were generally positive. Despite the excellent food, our enthusiasm waned when we uncovered a hair beneath the steak. Despite my attempt to gracefully address the issue with the lady in her late 30s or early 40s of Middle Eastern or Indian descent, the reaction was less than amiable. Although I reassured her that the flavorful cuisine compensated for the oversight, an apology was noticeably absent.

Upon settling the lunch bill at the register, totaling $210, the same lady conducted the transaction. Regrettably, any expectation of a conciliatory gesture vanished as she briskly concluded the payment process without offering a simple apology. The lack of remorse left us disheartened; surely, expressing a single word of regret is not an arduous task?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_BqFHuK3WZvvVDv1ppu6Jx1JNlXQ-gBNN49JQ"],"When":"2024-1-1"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Louie W Ong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCDS1ROuQN6MfkgWxUnJrdoXHObH_ZXUYFKCsp4BGeWD8uyv5S=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A cozy place to grab a few bites and some drinks with your mates.

They alter their menu from time to time and it’s worth checking The Star app for their monthly dining promos.

This place has opportunity to up their game. I still think The Star Sydney has better dining deals and quality. The sportsbar is just as great to order their pub food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPq59vueoiPA7K77ZaACE8cHYbAcRDLhsCgS0fd"],"When":"2022-11-7"},{"Name":"C Pal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5-50OkqVMygPD4SQOXzDe00dwdTrus0267tjHSyUI5ZabuENR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Can be hit or miss here depending on what you order. We go on a weekly basis before a movie or after a UFC fight. We have Star platinum, gold and bronze members in our family. Staff have been mostly friendly and accommodating, except when I was told it would cost a dollar when I asked for basic hot sauce, and we had just paid for a large meal (we usually go with 4 to 6 people). What a bunch of penny pinching nonsense.

Here's what we found has been good:

Spicy Buffalo crispy fried wings & blue cheese dip are on point, we have 2 Americans in our family and you guys have got this down to a T, so keep it up!

The pumpkin salad and caesar salad are winners!

The Singapore style Lobster special with fried rice was delicious, can you please do more of this dish as it is underrated.

The meat lovers pizza, supreme pizza, chicken parmesan, chicken schnitzel with gravy, corned beef special, chicken burger, spring rolls, butter chicken, pumpkin soup, onion rings, wedges and roast beef plate have all been very good.

The vanilla slices and other cakes have all been great. No complaints.

What's been mediocre and inconsistent:

The calamari was good one time and overcooked, almost burnt another time. Same with the t-bone steak and the beef burger. Also one time you had horseradish, another time you did not. Some consistency would be nice.

What's been a disappointment:

The steak and bugs special was bad, nothing good to say about it but bland, dry, and overcooked, some steak sauce and garlic butter would've been nice. The side salads that come with a meal are tiny and barely have any dressing on them and are mostly tasteless (perhaps offer other dressings too for some variety), they're more like a garnish than anything. The lobster mornay special was overcooked and pretty awful, we left still hungry. The roast lamb special was tough, overcooked and barely had any gravy on it and was super bland. Don't ever skimp on gravy with the roast dinner plates!! May I suggest adding herbs, garlic & olive oil to the vegetables? Or at least lemon pepper seasoning or something. It's like eating cubes of water.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3JliQmYEtyif1TuiRqZlKzHimB8Jb5Wu20_Qh"],"When":"2022-5-8"},{"Name":"Lisa Kingsbeer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXr7ekLIkMC-MoJWRXRCgcbBE5wY0ydLQN45kx1NdUJy4vJh0o_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A family lunch at Food Quarter was a pleasant surprise. A nice variety of meals on the menu, reasonable prices and fast and friendly service made for a lovely lunch enjoyed by all. We will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMku3hXaBYdcCpFjwBLmjG4QK_B9Ceh7SqBmXSp"],"When":"2023-10-24"},{"Name":"Chris St Clair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlfh5QN55FyiEDgtLlAEFmHyrmJY3h-0WrVhLAyFZYkw0iqA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They really do the best members specials here and the food is always superb","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWx3ah3cGW1V4grXgT29Cs9TeA4RJGRTz8NczL"],"When":"2024-2-6"},{"Name":"Astrid Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyQCnWaiQkMCvuhc4Cv1rqIY4zL-s6ZrD9MFDuuf1IM1Cn4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food always rubbish at the Food Quarter Casino. Every time I’m disappointed here, the food is so bland. It’s inedible and some food tastes frozen.

Undercooked mushrooms on my pizza and no flavour. Burger and chips below average.

Never going to that restaurant again.

Only will go to Kiyomi from now on which is upstairs. Or the nice Chinese restaurant there.

All of us were disappointed in our food.

0/5 wouldn’t recommend, be warned don’t go here. Food is expensive for what it is too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpi1tMNYgQMMYkoo2WYqIZPUVKodJk5vQmrOhX"],"When":"2023-8-21"},{"Name":"CC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZnBbcsCEXbEpBSB1c4sdoIQV0H7QXWUAr-yKKlgal9n6cUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had the grilled chicken burger and chips, it was delicious the sauce was nice, hubby had the stir fried noodles, noodles were a bit cold but it was nice","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwTyB0EzmB8igxQIZMV0dGTEW8ucnCMpvHdctg"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Craig Lawrence","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRTsYStnxdLD7xZ6uK15jOHVCchkwwZjAT-792mReu5kYBE5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great roast for $12, in a busy cafeteria style venue. Order, grab a table and wait for your buzzer to sound before you go to the collection area to pick up your meals. There’s a high volume of meals being pumped out as this place is popular with the keno crowd. They do well given the massive amount of food they dish out and the low prices.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0hU2pDT3NjisTn56muTYWT5_ZnUJYyJ__dJ2H"],"When":"2018-10-13"},{"Name":"Juanita Sumner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaNiqEo9mam7pwA0yfj09fEiS9VXsJ8txrr2Y5Z3vZSQGSLrfZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time I have had a meal here and it was great. Staff were helpful in explaining how things worked. I had the lamb roast, which came promptly. A generous serve with tender lamb and lots of nice vegetables. Excellent value for money and I look forward to trying other meals there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8VUgRSw1dOXWAzingaLGZYY2GHDhf9OWjRx6J"],"When":"2023-9-15"}]

[{"Name":"W W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUghDTTpx0c_wmizR16d8L-nLN64V9aSzP7yBtFPOL4KLA8T0wHxA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Huge portions of sweet potato chips and fries for what we paid for! The live music was nice. Colouring pencils and papers were provided for kids. We had the pork ribs which were delicious. The half a kilo of chicken wings weren't too bad either. Overall it was a nice dinner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiaaQ8ofrWdxMerZPhhVfwPthYQOBJQjZiiQnq"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"DNA K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPczgPokE0Pkt4l2VWG0sfxQ8bG6fg3ZfOCoqpNb7oC_Tpmc4ZLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had a pleasant afternoon here. I had a few nice cocktails during the happy hour and then dinner afterwards. The fish of the day was salt water barramundi, so I ordered it. It was not great. It came with a lot of different condiments/sauces, which were nice but not very  complementary with the fish, and the fish and prawns were bland, unfortunately. The broccolini were undercooked, so I couldn't eat it. Again, if you are charging the premium price, the dish should be premium. I was hungry after dinner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqOdwdgzH6ovYEZgMAxakiWww4VgCYE1CmS8w5"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Brooklyn Review","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYXyzPtXZitxU-kOx9YK8FAObAUW_4LE4zPN6W5CNMhpWT0fe1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful restaurant with amazing selection food and drinks. The cocktails are fantastic and made by the pro Chris Lisala himself. During evening time you can listen to live music which really sets a good vibe and being by the beach the atmosphere is relaxing and exciting at the same time.

The food is really yummy and fulfilling. We ordered the fried squid which came with hot sauce that is just too good. The burgers are amazing ordered garden salad on the side as well which was nice👌 Try the onion rings and the Tacos as well! They are a mouthfull and the portions are so good to fill up your tummy!

The service is really good and the staff are very cordial, helpful and friendly. Amy, Olivia and Val all looked after us well and made sure we had everything.

Definitely coming back here soon!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSY41LCFjyRWV3Zta-kl4JCU7zPCFTPchpT3Gy"],"When":"2024-2-27"},{"Name":"David Dalton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGkznTUFhCPVt624ojmVCaubZXXBoJC7uvxUHFlO8cADTVxaZn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service and food for dinner.  Had the calamari to start which melted in the mouth.  Followed up with a generous pour negroni and that set the scene for the mains.  Applied myself had had the rib eye steak and it was cooked to perfection.. accompanied with a mushroom gravy that smashed the dish out of the park.  Big shout out to Chris for making our dinner that little bit more special.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFJJ3a-lOuOLsA6TJS2lh1nEPexpTdz3Q2YgCL"],"When":"2024-2-11"},{"Name":"Zoe L'AOT","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqhDctyaeOhlv_AKsJZGA5va_eD5OZbL4rnN2vMM5TjUZL5QQ8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s an amazing restaurant and coffee shop. The coffee and the bacon eggs muffin are so good ! I recommend you this restaurant ! You have a good vue, close to the beach. The waitress Scarlett is so nice and really welcoming !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNn5OfpNADqqHFgxpu_P1N0oQCNGyDfOBwctzn6"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Tshering Druk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXT_D_nfAjFtfkBhSmC5cImaAFwMzn1dIqoq4oTC_1hnOZvEkqe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":""I bring my resident here every Saturday, and we both love it! The staff are always so welcoming and accommodating, making us feel right at home. The food consistently tastes amazing, and the location couldn't be better. It's become our favorite spot to unwind and enjoy a delicious meal together!" Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7wp6q5NDxuMv8f7rqQbHdwIlZ9FwnnCggTiZx"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Jonjo Borrill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhlaZBpdQSVC6r02ptOo6O25l4RP4YOTMs2CyCpcZrvvdiQCj2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Can’t comment on the food but the coffee and smoothies are unreal.
Lovely staff and actually know a bit about coffee. Instead of rushing a drink out they took their time to fine tune the extraction and get a good espresso out.

The food I did see others ordering looked great!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7MuUZhAmA5vY6G0Ir6jxF1dnq1MbVtGx9TG_4"],"When":"2024-1-11"},{"Name":"Shah akshay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjXJ953ZvMC3qanrWsx6e9etw8NnqdWft4SOXPO_qBVwbHJmw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visited First time to Gold Coast and visited Elston Restaurant & Bar. The best Bar I have seen and enjoyed exactly in front of the Surfers Paradise Beach.

They have got a Vast range of Drinks, especially the cocktails made by “DOM” and a variety of food which suit Vegetarian as well as Non Vegetarian people.

I would highly recommend if you guys visiting Gold Coast please go once and I’m sure you will visit again.

Spacial thanks to “Clara” for an amazing customer experience. No doubt to give you 5***** stars for the way you looked after us. She is so humble, kind and supportive. Lovely to meet you and will meet you all soon once again.

Special thanks to “DOM” for an amazing cocktails you have made for us with lots of love. He is very kind and supportive. Thanks so much for your best Cocktails.

Thanks to Chris for your great service and hospitality.

Overall, 5 STAR without any doubt. If you guys visiting Gold Coast then I would highly recommend you guys to visit this place and you will definitely addicted to this place for sure.

Thanks once again Clara, Dom & Chris.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNHnYT3hEHfUWwiuK-DtL1i7hWbXmmITme5X5D"],"When":"2023-12-24"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sharon S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUao7dCW8T0Nw2iaVOuwBqZqVfUX6lvlrlUwjNjJdVT8RF4AGes=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"For what we paid compared to others, we definitely got a lot less. As other reviews mentioned, oysters are very small, desserts taste the same and the hot food was cold which a few people raised that night but chef wasn’t bothered. When asked if I could get the oysters done a bit differently, a very stern response was received by stating, ‘what you see is what you get’. Won’t be back, The Star offers much more variety for less the price","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP648ei7vbbwkTxbGWnZC0q69ZNTZLyfzkOywW2"],"When":"2024-5-25"},{"Name":"Nancy Allan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTaZFf2OOvTIqsnUdEwPFDo9br6tc9S7wr0922MXUnpA2s0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Seafood buffet was very good, but the size of the oysters let the whole thing down. The oysters are the smallest  I have ever seen. The meat was slightly bigger than a 5c piece. It’s an embarrassment that they served these. I guess they are purchased as they are rejected by every other restaurant. They were fresh though, but you could barely taste them due to the minuscule size. I think there should be a few bowls with dressings to go with the oysters. Kilpatrick oysters are served also at the carvery, but also teeny tiny. The Crab legs were froze and watery. The scallops were large and plump, but were not replenished fast enough. They were served with a tarty dressing with fish roe, I believe. Often there were empty platters. When we first arrived, there was a whole fish looking dish, which had already been eaten. This was not replaced at all. Instead there were two platters of the same dish. Hey also bought out a second mussels dish instead of the scallops. I asked if there were scallops on the buffet, I got told yes. I asked where, and the lad said did I check the salad side. Yes I did, there were no scallops. I then asked the staff to bring some out, but customers should not have to. At this time two of the platters were empty, the soft cheese was empty and not replaced quickly either. The prawns were king prawns, not tiger which was a nice surprise. These were on the small size too, but acceptable. The bugs were also on the small side. The crabs too were small, and you could barely get any meat out, as again they were not very fresh or again frozen.
Salads were uninspiring, and not many people ate those, similar to the hot food. There was a pasta made in a cheese wheel which was very nice, as was the chicken roll.
The desserts were very very pretty, but they were all similar with a mousse type cake with a different flavour.
Breakfast buffet was a let down, for $52, I was expecting it all. There was so smoked salmon, no prosciutto, no avocado. None of the high priced items you expect at $52. The star has all of these. A whole side of the buffet is for fruity. You don’t need 9 different plates of fruit, you can condense this and put on a platter, but it seems they just needed to fill the space. None of the fruits are exotic either, which should be expected on the GC and at $52. Buy some dragon or star fruit which is currently in season. No one seemed interested in the wilted salad and vegetables in oil. It is advertised as table service omelette, but this wasn’t offered to us. What they did well was the sweets, but again, not the same as on the menu online. The sweets were the best of any buffet I have had, as were the juices. The orange juice seemed real, with pith, whereas the star seems to have watered down juice. The trail mix and macadamia, was a small nod to local produce. There was a small gluten free area too, which seemed to be better than other hotel buffets. Coffee was included , which was great. The girls working today were very busy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEv63sjFf0hl1r1MaiuXGuseEqbtYhtLfV3ufY"],"When":"2024-3-10"},{"Name":"Enyi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-Tl-GeRIyDQUvRtgLxfCCH76Sja8WJcB2J1afgeVuJrUhh_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Luxury hotel dining setting. Good service! The food variety is not the most abundant but enough. They do make it up with the high quality of items provided. I had to especially point out the desserts are very good! I could still demolish a lot of them after boat load of seafood because how light they are. Both sparkling and still water are bill shock items. Juices and ice creams are chargeable items. Tea, coffee and hot choc are not. Hot choc is really good! This could have been a 5 star rating if not for the watery crab legs and briney prawns. Bit of a let down for I had high hopes in the better part of seafood selection. Bugs are the saving grace. Recommend parking is marina mirage under cover parking next door. (3 hours free).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyviPzR8yPiphu-wiRCUdJnJMSLKTm0FYqVzq6"],"When":"2024-1-21"},{"Name":"Chris Ellenby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7kQ3zdQFPYzjGHW5D-Mh4dcbXm0eFXpp8XxlNqQcrwGKk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This magnificent spread of high quality food in a premium location with superb service is hard to beat. There is no shortage of any food as the buffet is constantly replenished especially the highly popular seafood and dessert. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwNbGUtJ3YLapnJA-CWe8GMa--hz0gFfB1nmc"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Kiara Borgonha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKoocTxnOnBSx1lrEC5Op0LL1xpmabxxfaS49kwsI56Z6ii7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was incredible. We dined here for lunch having the al a carte menu and it was so luxurious. Very fancy, yet the meals were substantial and satisfying, while being full of flavour. This is rare as we were expecting small meals as it sounded like another one of those over priced fine dining restaurants, but no! We highly recommend the risotto and pasta. Add some fries too, the focaccia they give you at the start is divine! Fresh and hot out of the oven.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrD6OwYvqck3_0-GMEvpB1v3aGyMcf4gy9k7bA"],"When":"2024-2-10"},{"Name":"Julie Saville","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImKRUdO1mAGmyEsb-uey0SKpHPuQ9wERpMLFzwaKeWRxupug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We took some friends out for a celebratory lunch and we definitely chose the right restaurant. One of our party has quite restrictive dietary needs and the chef was very accommodating, even cooking her chips in separate oil. The food was fabulous. I had an eye fillet that was cooked superbly, my husband had pork that melted in your mouth and the seafood pasta looked wonderful. We all had the prawns for entree and they did not disappoint. The icing on the cake was the service. Jimmy was wonderful. Understanding and funny. The setting was lovely - perhaps a little more separation from the lobby might be good. But really, absolutely nothing to complain about and plenty to rave about.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Lister","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIgie3dV2Q4RcDMJd2q4J3iKCECdubjpo-UxikFpXC6hL_O_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The lamb shoulder was outstanding. Enough food (in a share plate) for 6 people! Nice quiet atmosphere and good service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-7anpbB92_X0vZ31WeaytXzy3gBaAffhXDk9j"],"When":"2024-2-14"},{"Name":"K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKS_fcsffDzaDxQ6idF7O5hCStHPi1utzBrZUwYjSuwKFYIYM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The selection of food is adequate, we were expecting more options available at this buffet.
The food itself was satisfactory, the seafood being the saving grace
The staff were not readily available and would only come over to the table on occasion
The environment is nice and inviting","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMa6xFoAjveoILsV77xTDfQl2CZI_wtuNtKJHgi"],"When":"2023-8-19"}]

[{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW55WYME_Lq5IFdQf0AhN9NLTAsjcPJzRy2bC8_KyEYpgc891yX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The cuisine was satisfactory considering the price, and the five-course tasting menu dishes were mostly adequate. The service was also commendable. Additionally, the ambiance was pleasantly calm, a delightful dining atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP779I2blQvB-7Lm2AGyw5fNLBswvv1Oba-LfTW"],"When":"2024-1-28"},{"Name":"d388y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXACCLnlQ33_x9HBhVlTLEHmXbfb0gHtaiuSX0QXMgwcmzZkys_mQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely delicious dishes from start to finish!
You can really tell the quality of produce is top notch and cooked so well.
A great buzz of energy in the atmosphere so it didn’t matter having my 2 preschool children there as it wouldn’t disturb other guests.
Drinks selection was broad and there was something to satisfy all tastes.
Definitely coming back when we’re visiting Queensland again.
One downside was the toilets which were public ones outside of the restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpwaEK2dFg6Aw-nGJkzgyRAAFSTAdhC0anyH7L"],"When":"2023-8-4"},{"Name":"Mark Just","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHQrW6nR-01F9jyMqtnO06O9YcrpirV1E0qlaQYcV61YgWuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good food, I have had a lot of Italian food in my time and this is up there with some of the high end ones, menu offerings are quite good. The price is up there with other high end restaurants and is somewhat worth it. Quite a few options were not available when we ordered but they were very upfront about it. Would go again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBqs3KJX25xRPllSHwffzZzHPmiWyC7fBgNs-J"],"When":"2024-1-3"},{"Name":"Avez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjRliIZyGshvu0Xx7zuVnFt62vvKZSA1nA0MWuv_lh3-cUx4s=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic for a date night! Insanely good food, really friendly/knowledgeable staff. Book in advance is best bet to guarantee a table. It is slightly expensive, but I think it was absolutely worth it. The quality of the food/drinks aligns with this so i wouldn't expect any different. Keen to go back soon!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vee H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHTXUInpTLFBfvh--TkvJqKPESaJAtHMj6DTNbo0AUUUrXwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I couldn't decide on a few items so ended up getting the chef's tasting menu 5 courses. Extremely good value with very generous portions. Pasta texture was excellent. Food tasted very fresh and full of flavour. It's been a while since I've had pasta in Australia and walked away happy! Waiters were very helpful in explaining the menu, describing the flavours and picking out the perfect wine.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kayne Croft","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBAxV4Sk6KXyxYKhIpwHMzyjC9a9HiSBBSukVw1GvvD87X7ye4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is in my top 2 on the Gold Coast! Good for lunch or dinner and never disappoints. Standouts: focaccia to start is a must! And Truffle Gnocchi was god tier. Their wine list is incredible too so spend some money and pick a bottle for your meal. I love that their menu changes frequently and keeps me coming back for more","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM35oV4Cz4kIjQb_knI3gpNVcOFLQPCQpKxK6eY"],"When":"2022-11-20"},{"Name":"Kaige Silcock (Mozart)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYZoTWKBKaIxBpM1TCmjZ5dzeS9WuBUeGINrALCvaa1btqkdjD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The wait staff we amazing and attentive although the entrees came out really quick, witch isn’t the worst thing if your hungry but for the occasion we weren’t in a rush and it was kind of abrupt but food was exceptional the scallops where are stand out for the starters..
The mains where beautiful and outstanding. The nunjda pasta was the outstanding dish for me !

Definitely recommend this place to anyone wanting to try proper Italian food !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLbD7qGbRlN9olJ1Lh_2jpWTg5I6v7ZX-7iLtp"],"When":"2023-4-13"},{"Name":"Vincent Bugeja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBtXN20nyoKv9dkAV1aE6CLHPxBP_Xas81y3Kd91WHisCkdYWd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stunning. Exceeded our expectations in every way. The food was perfect. Flavour, texture and presentation.
Tuna crodo and Wagyu Carpaccio with a Radicchio salad to start. Generous portions for entrees and amazing flavours.
Linguine with seafood had beautifully cooked fish portions as well as mussels and prawns. Cavatelli with sausage was divine. Both pastas cooked perfectly.
Then the finale. For me, I'm lactose free, I copied this off the menu....

Dark chocolate + banana parfait, cacao biscuit, macadamia ice-cream, caramelized banana

And it's vegan and delicious. I was blown away. So rare for me to get something so delicious for dessert. We also had a cheese platter with a pecorino and the accompanying crackers, toasted bread, fig, honey and fruit will bring me back. Easily the best cheese platter I've ever seen.

As you can tell we were seriously impressed. Great evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXOhY_ZYZlDt-KVCkE7lIv1GsFKZdMy5LiM-2q"],"When":"2023-11-18"}]

[{"Name":"Alison O'Neill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwnvpJd5Rs9Zgt4ivmQrpCcAmwiHyCRECR1R8Bb5Sgvv7S-XEHOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a really cool restaurant. It is situated at the front/bottom of the Q1 accommodation. The food is very very good. The cocktails and bar are awesome. The vibe is fun, outdoorsy and upbeat. Pricing is really pretty reasonable. Recommend a visit here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ1SlRFO7E6OAjvxBIXfYw9wA39wKPnRE8TRmI"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"James Curtin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSMg4VKwv3zy5YbfSK6o8Ghr-yO34UqfJHDL2nHIX0q45gHNfoyw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It is hard to to make chips poor - but this place finds a way. The calamari was OK but if you are thinking of coming for the food - you can do much better. The photo is super complimentary of the meal but shows a dismal calamari ratio. The high ratings cam really only be from overlooking a pool","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNws4qW-VI8hlLpOuOyq9bR0cxtVVzfUiPauukQ"],"When":"2024-3-6"},{"Name":"Dianne Caine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgIy2DIIELJjnxWCz1f75acJmxW9qHek8P5ClG063Jvo2BhLk4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an amazing dinner here
The food was delicious
Cocktails were amazing
Staff were super friendly and helpful
Highly recommended
Loved the way it was decorated awesome location and really nice with the pool","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_Mih2SJ08QAH4Ga9e651JvpptzGzpMD958c4p"],"When":"2024-3-1"},{"Name":"Alex Patty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhSoMbYmOep4IvcG19sHfpBhMp6jFuH9si1Tq5Uwf2VVehtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had some great servers. A young man and an English fella that were amazing, hilarious and were incredible to deal with. The burgers were amazing and the service was even better. Couldn’t recommend this place more. I’m sorry for not remember the names, the burger/beer crawl limited my ability to remember names but they were awesome.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rilee Perry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3VQsh9Zqr0y2bqAQ-lcmkPyR1mEacIQLWxIu4zhbckaJ049g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cannot recommend this place enough!

The foods here is fantastic, hot and fresh when it comes to your table and in good quantity for the pricing. Some of the best burgers and chips we’ve ever had.

The staff here are the most friendly, ready to help people you’ll ever meet. They really go above and beyond for you and we really appreciate it. The food and drink came out quick which was great considering we had a large group (11).

The atmosphere is awesome, good music playing at a level that you can hear the people you’re eating with and also enjoy what you’re listening to. Easy to find/access location, we walked to and from both times we ate here for dinner and lunch.

Must go to when in the Gold Coast,
Thankyou to the team here, you’re doing amazing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephen Verrall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2uOE11DOeJE-EtD2fo0G61Mvhl13rQ-uUExeYC4k9lPfXBOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You can not make a better chicken burger, and their chips are fresh, hot, and spiced just right. My son had the beef burger, which he really enjoyed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCpzBDblLwODvKQLHzatOa9MM0nlCpn79GDeuw"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Kelly Lun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxxfKwPpYMG_zo-XUuFm35WyZoJP4zi3k9V8uteFWUzGMJzL1G=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Longboards is great. Stayed in the Gold Coast for a week and this was honestly one of the best meals we had. We got the slider taster with 3 of their popular burger flavours which were all really tasty, their sweet potato fries that were nice and crisp, and the chicken wings that came with ranch. Food was delicious and the ambience had that nice 'laidback' feel to it, perfect to go before heading down to the beach. Cocktails were also good. You can either order by scanning the QR code at the table or going to the bar.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoW_Jd6GKegluGmWwJW1qcWgZQnPQmjiO6GD-c"],"When":"2023-1-13"},{"Name":"Enduro Shredders","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8TpcPLZQ-6bVB9gpZqggoIkMPAQY0Z8-2nSIjP4nfYBH5erk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10, food was very good. There is something in the fried that is really good.

Ringer Burger
- chicken was perfectly crunchy, pineapple was a great compliment
- it wasnt really spicy as advertised

Chicken Caesar Salad
- lots of chicken
- lettuce was fresh and tasty
- Garlic Croutons were amazing

They have lots of deals on throughout the week, we went on Sunday and the love music was fantastic, will be back again soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMr5BhxH4QSym8c9XUNVpYkq3CU_l6vumceooCp"],"When":"2022-7-24"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"jaime","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJkPPcLBEJAH8upWKwub9lDOo3kDHMOlT_22aZtHCJK0ZZQnbU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Loved the atmosphere. Was cute and unique. The food came out quickly and taste amazing. Heaps of flavour and meat was tender. Majority of the service was really good. Seating and waiter staff was super friendly and helpful but the lady at reception was pretty rude when we paid last night.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMq6VWtzXuvCUSKxXjnUKfUZD0OEoadtsWnl7yM"],"When":"2024-3-20"},{"Name":"Tanya Smithwick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYiFRkLXX_CuoeevPHSFpVt2tpAgYo768-Uj9tkTSB31DOG70Sgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went here for dinner last night and omg the food was amazing! Not only the food was amazing but our wonderful Claudia who looked after us for the night. She was so friendly and helpful when we asked about the dishes. She was A++ The food came out quickly and was so fresh and delicious and so were the cocktails. We will definitely be back!!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4mqNUr0rlAifaTjTmbDZuYEccrvyk78Vj41mx"],"When":"2024-5-25"},{"Name":"Naomi Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIW8Pfn2UiKRBEqiQ2RbH-j93mzyU1tM9hpvrrqTSM3O2Y4yg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hosted a Christmas party at Hideaway Kitchen \u0026 Bar and could not recommend them highly enough. The entire team could not have been more amazing.\nThe food was absolutely incredible (The crispy bug rolls are a MUST!!!).  The staff went above and beyond to help us enjoy our day.  The cocktails were creative and delicious (and really well priced) and the atmosphere was, as always, just gorgeous.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMz612BRQ9tu57M-LOlBQaYln8aYcIaDaaryK_T"],"When":"2023-12-18"},{"Name":"Mikayla Hayes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWULv9wMiFzEUtWrPFR2qNuApFYj3YqcLpZKGfdc3co1SMz7T-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staying nearby, walked past and decided we would try for dinner. Booked in not long before going and so thankful we did! What a hidden gem, great atmosphere, great service but this food was hands down delicious. One of the best meals and cocktails we have had in our time on the Gold Coast","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhfVTYzSsiuL-ab0UFH_v6L2WGie3KzMvcqPaF"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"Shaun Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTsCo-u9KFH8IzOZVypbuofBjdaQXZyl2MIrL-Rbqgv3D351a7gQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place mightn't look like much from the outside, but once you get inside, it's got quite the atmosphere, with a good amount of indoor seating and a plesant outdoor courtyard.  Admittedly, we had one the best steaks we've ever had here. The pleasant service is also a bonus. Our waitress was lovely.  Had the gyoza dumplings, special fried rice and wok fried beef with veg.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1qxPY2G1DzP0x3pUOMU5NtUBsbMXGrHtUJVgA"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"Emanuel Heil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5JlvbsOkJ1Hu24ipXI2HjN9RTemrbMTJWSoD7KKsq195PLbFW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dinner at Hideaway Kitchen was great! We loved the concept of the street feast: choose a variety of small and big platters and get them served one after the other to share with your friends and family. Service was very polite and professional, drinks average with the exception of the Kaffir Lime Vodka. It is a must try and exceptional tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGVbRqfbTtBBTYfegWKobfwowzx04vvrayn-1r"],"When":"2024-4-12"},{"Name":"Lauren Helena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVi13sadfGoVJfd96kifLPyDFSq9MTywDR2sqJEHqjmlJNs3cCS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing amazing amazing. Best food and service on the GC, we’re from Melbourne but deliberately make an effort to come here every time we visit. Incredible food, incredible service and fantastic value. The chilli beef is out of this world.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOih16IrUig7DteFkPhyYk5xRcZJfIa57Ay6VNy"],"When":"2024-4-29"},{"Name":"Monica Cheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdWjQURuydIIHMrG_MKIzcqU8zCz8T1ho8up_dktXcPrvibKE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time in the area, walked by and walk in on a Saturday 6pmish, and get a nice seat by myself. I was not particularly hungry, after consulting the waitor(he's such an excellent help) and observing other tables, I ordered duck spring rolls - devine when serving fresh from the kitchen, chilli beef and a glass of Shiraz. The chilli is full of flavors and texture. But the shiraz did not impress me. But all in all, beautifulfood, nice breeaze and the atmosphere delights me to no end. A definite recommendation from me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLVX0jfoTjxB_z65RY17z3xjYlTuyJokqRAw1Q"],"When":"2024-2-17"}]

[{"Name":"sabella green","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKm0FJ6kI3EesugjuShoiQnaHEyxAtITl7fg4jb0rMwzzMV8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Celebrated my mother’s 50th at The Surfers Pavilion, And had the most amazing experience! Not only with a staff so attentive and lovely the staff were so quick to get our orders through and come out, And on top of that the atmosphere was incredible. The music was such a vibe and we had such a great time! My mum was so happy with how the night turned out, We ordered The surf and turf platter as well as the Oceanside seafood platter and they were both so amazing! The seafood was so fresh and all the food was so enjoyable. Highly recommend celebrating any occasion here! Best venue out!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUYAnLBPKptV3bVQmo7LXJxzaWjdcfv6Fyt5s"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"DNA K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPczgPokE0Pkt4l2VWG0sfxQ8bG6fg3ZfOCoqpNb7oC_Tpmc4ZLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Great location, but food and service were ordinary. The tables were not cleaned after people had left. They had attractive and interesting menus, but the quality/flavour were not that great. Still, it is a lovely location and had nice atmosphere!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHDI96mg4vG3vPXIzZ5o7IOLmBSyf1wO4oQZhg"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Nikki Prime (Ocean)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUijZORNgLD9MVrka6aaqRVCUdJIGTIP_2OruMCMMEN4hWsP9XbYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I was here for a women's event which was lots of fun. Unfortunately included wasn't vegan friendly, apart from the hot chips, but I knew this when booking my ticket
I've ordered a vegan salad from here previously which was pretty good.
Great atmosphere at any time of the day or early evening. We worth a drink or two and lunch or an early dinner before it kicks off with the younger crowd wanting to party, unless that's your thing of course!
You can dock your boat or jetski and wander up from the water for lunch and a few drinks, I absolutely love this!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmATeHPcHAJ05jJG1t8_8Z2EbzYU9z_26gZeC3"],"When":"2024-5-11"},{"Name":"P S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNHwxSsvuVsrtsyUJihMPD8HMtZl-usxYjfVGsjlhZpwfPLxx8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently visited this restaurant for breakfast and, despite not having a reservation, we were promptly seated. The food was reasonably priced, offering good value for money. The view from the restaurant was absolutely amazing, adding to the overall enjoyable experience. The staff were exceptionally friendly and accommodating, making our visit even more pleasant.
We will definitely be coming back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFfSwJ44I61sly5igDphZ1DMP3jb1andEFTDT9Zxj8MuWNktBU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A local pub with a nice view of the river, a decent menu, and friendly helpful staff. Attended this evening for a meal. The Mexican schnitzel was delicious and a good sized portion. The kingfish cevice was nice but the fish flavour was overpowered by the mayonnaise/dressing. The mushroom lasagne was okay.
The staff went above and beyond so we could have a good meal. We had a pram, and discovered a large set of stairs leading up into the pub, but after enquiring with staff we were led to a lift for wheelchairs, prams, accessibility. The manager (?) helped us use the lift, and even led us to a quieter area of the pub and turned down the music (for our child).
Worth attending for a meal and a drink.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNP_4LdXU4NgMYc6NwY22TCce_DYnLRhW0ZEtKG"],"When":"2024-3-12"},{"Name":"Jason Hansen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3TMAjuJfo-3riVxyoHf-Jbi68HoWlhq0tXG9iya0FSPC6UA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Greeted and welcomed  by very friendly enthusiastic staff.
Cold water for table delivered upon sit.down
Atmosphere and view of Nerang river was second to none.
Barister delivered on incredible  coffee 10/10.
We had the corn frittas and chilli crab scrambled eggs. Amazing  incredible flavors, served promptly, chef takes pride in beautiful presentation. Magnificent.
Do yourself a favor and go to Surfers Pav.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLsI-_SoADw8JSWrK9RRGaRWAnBHEv9RP_qRW-"],"When":"2024-3-22"},{"Name":"Vivian Megumi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVy7q43VHzqN3MAYZpefMT3hS7GDn4zBI4F3U3Gl8Q0Z5-K4Whw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a great breakfast experience there. The service was top-notch - friendly, attentive, and truly made me feel welcomed. The coffee was exceptional, and sipping it with the best view was the highlight of the day. The Biscoff Pancakes were recommended to me, and they did not disappoint! I highly recommend this place for a delicious breakfast with great service and an unbeatable view. Can't wait to come back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2dKMpd4tEf5mwGnL9nAzW_zu2B7c-g_YWIjrHlkEH_bwHRw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I came here for our 1 year wedding anniversary and it was honestly amazing. The staff were all so friendly and accommodating. The food was delicious and came out quickly. Cocktails were to die for, and we loved the atmosphere of the DJ and live saxophone.
The views of the water were beautiful, and it was nice to just sit back and relax.
We can't wait to come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGIQDHmE2ixnS02qydGqyc6CcbZA0FtvkT-vA4"],"When":"2023-9-16"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Mel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWVbVDK-OSSJ0aAzAEw_a_ocj2sJ_VL-kh8Nin3-KHEXok0P0KMw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A cute little cafe I stumbled upon on Google. The atmosphere in the place was welcoming and we were greeted by a lovely waiter.

The menu had a variety of unique options. We shared a meal and ordered a cup of tea each. They both came out at the same time which was nice.

The serving size is decent and more than enough to fill up.

The staff were friendly and checked in we were all sorted a few times. The place had some unique items to look at which was handy when the conversation ran dry.

If I'm ever back in Adelaide, I will come back to Peter Rabbit.

Thanks for a great breakfast!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIPlQuUWMFI_FT66_5PuVjqcG_MH_QnW7jno7N"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Madhawa Perera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkswqvYLMDpqttTrNR9w1UoSs12nCTHu4HkaGXJeH-ZNbIbazP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's a really nice little restaurant with a great atmosphere. I enjoyed having breakfast there, and the food was delicious. Unfortunately, they didn't have the pistachio and matcha hot chocolate, but the fig French toast (in the photos) was amazing. I highly recommend trying out this restaurant if you're visiting this area in Adelaide.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3jOazMhvu_K-zCQjW8hmMBJ555NstUNWlAyIC"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"Shilpi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvjHlfGGYUkyPF_w6NZGsKLzaDKpUW4sb2DlNVZmhdqhONgwBS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recommended by a friend, a beautiful garden cafe with good vegan options. The interiors are really pretty & the service is good. We went there for a Sunday breakfast and ordered Avocado Smash & vegan mushroom bowl with English Breakfast Tea. The portion size was really good, and both the items tasted good. Would definitely recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNl1344v2Peg5jCbElkGLNaMYE5sYTaHoV1ZYIO"],"When":"2024-4-14"},{"Name":"Russell King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUT4Q2KnQAmXAZLuO7lI-ihV5xEBG7iNGhAs0I9IT1J7e0NQw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice little spot, outside open area with shaded areas and spaced out enough you arent on top of each other. Food is very unique, and all presented in really nice ways. Serves are quite large as well so you wont be disappointed if you are hungry!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9r1kwMwxPDU0rsM7WLQpcTgcGJj_ZM3LgIq0"],"When":"2024-3-20"},{"Name":"Justine Terese","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLS79FivVrTFf3_dr55B8_OSUl1Fwog1afFHwIjlp48UvS02K5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely adore everything about this place. Food is delicious. Coffee is consistently good. Staff are lovely.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGeOL-IKKXfHzcgIX1T9l8UG8GTXf4rQr2CeI7"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"Niloufar Ansari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUn0LEZs4CAWaqzePhN6WLyoWftuE-cVYMLBaAq-9DCwW9qIZhxzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Weekends at this cafe? Prepare for a long wait to be seated, and a long queue for ordering! It took them about 20 minutes to bring us our coffees. Prices are a bit steep. Nice decorations, but not exactly the cozy spot for catching up with friends. Overall, it had nice decoration, and was ok to try once. Going back? Probably no!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiXZ9-vVbdhIBU6hvAO_O4bDXSZ0D_1Lj189Id"],"When":"2024-3-30"},{"Name":"Courtney Jess","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5xugfKxulDecp3GrOFZh1tRtN-cVAf_flmxdzAGZ_X_9Swg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had breakfast here recently and it was amazing. I stumbled across it by accident as it was near my hotel. Food was great. Coffee was great (the most important thing) ans the staff were very friendly. I was dining alone and the waiter set my table up for me while I ordered at the counter. Really happy with my experience. Definitely recommend for breakfast, lunch or just a coffee!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvP88ZqntbWV07a-bBlMkm4VId0cxqoaFXhjQv"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Charlene and Ronny (Fitness Foodies)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzmw9UDsD5isHrR7ARD6-HRqJH0vx9M35mieydr3B9woLP75wmqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great breakfast as soon as we landed and got to town. The chilli scramble with the pork sausages hit the spot and the wife enjoyed the tuna soba noodles. Can’t go wrong. Atmosphere was excellent and turned out to be perfect on a sunny morning sitting outside. Lovely place. Highly recommend it. Oh and coffee was excellent too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4KVAoiu8WsQJvMYC-a_9D8pdBz99ljStux5Pe"],"When":"2024-3-28"}]

[{"Name":"Wendy Luu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgPTIn1KOx9O4Y4uEi62IGmnHar4z_cPqTFCzA9TAMLvGhZJ3y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place so much! The decor is impressive with every single detail is touched up - from the soap container to the coffee cup.
They also offer a wide range of vegan options.
Love their macadamia smoothies - add a turmeric shot to spice it up. :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNJFpcbo-Rshkjq8w2gXvzB3dS2TTEJxHJRUH1"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"Adhi Sappareng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFRDA4enBPCcEh7eQVh09kUg2UxbkMSJqxZ-IpnZ29lOUEqoEm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The place is really cute, around the corner, we were sitting outside, and we love the spot. We always wanted to visit this place and finally we can make it. I think they made their own bakery, so many bakery display there. The customer service was quick, but the food a bit pricey for the waffle. Unfortunately $26 for 1 pcs of waffle. The taste 7.5/10 but we love the juice. Sooo fresh. The place like really beautiful","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8IEg7-p9C6rMQDGc2bmLQNgAN6dC87H0INuQ1"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Charissa Davies","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrsRCUtneU65ttjtaitHm4MYn-Y29TiVhyFg5gG9_gstZNUrrwcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is excellent. Recommend the GFO flower power dish and add an egg. Great textures and flavours. The gluten free bread is one of the best I’ve had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6qR8UePDTWQlaFcU3SymboIl6NahrCS4Jz8Q-"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"Lewis Noyes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWeDA7TEVkUmOJLsu95po5kbW-jasBDdKXEqYafaI6xTUrdNkK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"such a bougie, hip, earthly vibe to the place and above all else comes the exceptional food and coffee!!

i had the spring waffle which i highly recommend, it’s not just a waffle, it’s not just honey and it’s not just egg it’s so much more with fragrant herbs and well balanced sweet & salty aspects. will be coming back for the food and experience! 🤌🤌🤌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGuGWxuYVcUhVTtCjeNifi6kDQR5TmGILKvRo9"],"When":"2024-4-25"},{"Name":"Charlene and Ronny (Fitness Foodies)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzmw9UDsD5isHrR7ARD6-HRqJH0vx9M35mieydr3B9woLP75wmqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There’s a reason this cafe is highly rated and that is because the food is amazing, from flavours to presentation to portion size. Service was great and the place has a distinctive charm. Great breakfast and will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5s6knmQhUXcdkB_a9-HSOJGa1lYxZPY2pp83s"],"When":"2023-12-6"},{"Name":"Mark Mywords","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUm26HIy9BxR6ol3yU5_3Dyn2i8dg6LlLdIwwi4x3gukPAZk29V=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A garden cafe in the heart of the city.

Sitting inside or outside, this serene and wonderful cafe has the envy of being in the city, but with the feel of a chilled backyard garden. The wide open doors and rustic interior with homemade jars of pickles, fresh produce in wooden crates, cakes, breads and olive oil in longneck beer bottles, all help set the mood, and that mood is - relax, take a deep breath and enjoy something special.
The staff here were exceptionally friendly and care about their food, which comes across in their enthusiastic approach.

I started with a Bloody Mary that was garnished with in-house, homemade pickles, fresh cracked pepper and a fresh lemon wedge, excellent! My only misdemeanour, I forgot to ask for it 'extra' spicy.
A green juice for my 'partner in dine' (sorry) Both 'green and red juices'' were quality and freshly made.

We ordered the Spring Waffle and the Pickleman's Platter - with the latter being basically a deconstructed, albeit, hearty sandwich.
Both plates were quickly and wholly demolished with almost no conversion between us, yes, that good.
My only gripe, the whites on my poached egg, on my waffle, was a little "snotty." (undercooked) luckily I like a runny yolk, so this didn't deter me in the least, but may bother others.
Weekends here can be a very busy affair, so midweek lunch is where it's at for a no fuss experience.
The carrot and walnut cake is a must buy. A generous serve, sinfully moist, with crunchy walnuts and super fresh with no fridge smell/taste.

Various homemade pickles, chilli sauces, chutneys and olive oil are available to purchase, so be sure to load up, if that's your thing.

All in all, one of the best cafes in Adelaide.

Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9AmfDRNcYK3XAjoJQ0XJh9JkYuhI3v_JrEQGV"],"When":"2024-3-1"},{"Name":"Chrissy Masters","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8s5wEaFAjA2_hJgdpQgz--DfDaShYB2VWletqPGUwiuar2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place is sensational. Real fresh delicious food. Great cute outdoor tables too. Pick a sunny day and you’ll love it .. had the chilli scramble and Flower power","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpgahJLma9PXf0OkzI18ggW87YPLyUslvaYkd-"],"When":"2024-4-5"},{"Name":"q q","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcobdqZsLozGu2ouoDtEKJvNBAc3Y3B_4RZ2IqrhPSfD2OEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Green waffle was delicious. I love the inside interior and the atmosphere of sitting outside. Staff were really friendly too. Will come again. Thanks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVKf0jPD6hIVY7T2O8fkLjt8Lzox_zSQVTG7z1"],"When":"2024-6-7"}]

If anyone asks about brunch spots in the city, I'd recommend this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Charlene and Ronny (Fitness Foodies)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzmw9UDsD5isHrR7ARD6-HRqJH0vx9M35mieydr3B9woLP75wmqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"An overall great breakfast. We arrived in  Adelaide and needed somewhere to eat. Found this place and wasn’t disappointed. Food was overall great and so was the coffee.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3fdql7M_ksvGGrVxjqheyeXLdX3EsQ6a5f--Q"],"When":"2023-11-4"},{"Name":"samapti ch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4SXNKkvnvqftrnw__mhXwRjtlq-SXJN1KkLlPAC57Xk-78r1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great Coffee every time. Have tasted quite a number of cakes and pastries as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZWrF12Q9hIhe7KnAvbuBo7K9X1U4ZkskzcC-n"],"When":"2024-5-12"},{"Name":"n s","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwR-Ix7jy98ay-YWmz3o_nvrQJmrriI0FMqP1e4ZMe_yn7uw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The high ratings brought us here. The atmosphere \u0026 service was great. Unfortunately, the food wasn’t too special. I ordered the egg \u0026 swiss cheese sandwich. The bread was dry and stale and the cheese was still cold. I couldn’t even eat the crust \u0026 I don’t usually leave stuff on my plate. It only came with one hash brown which was a bit sad :( The iced latte was OK. Cost $24.50 in total which I would’ve rather spent somewhere else.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5LPEmySqMznifud5eauaEPgnlkhhG_Kr36VDO"],"When":"2023-10-9"},{"Name":"Alysha Rosly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_HGZNUZdVEP-5I2UknT-bvYzeA7O4Fxs_F_W8nePBLEgOSk0Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They offer a good range of breakfast options. The atmosphere was cozy and the staff were friendly. We tried the Grilled Haloumi Burger and Egg Benedict. The food was good but it didnt reach the level of being mind-blowing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMC4n7eYDz91tcsZJJexFqn_XEKFxpjQkfC8LiS"],"When":"2023-9-16"},{"Name":"Kristen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjojMlSBfHXDRxvJDdVLShUTJuVBaViWrw08FLx6PRd2zM2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place for lunch. We had the halloumi veggie burger, fried chicken salad and a cappuccino. Ingredients were fresh and the serving size was perfect for lunch. Venue is nice and the waitstaff were attentive. Next time will try the breakfast menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWzugENJXZ4JmaVEL0-Pjs8jHXhTkCUYvz9QaB"],"When":"2023-11-7"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Steve K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZpYXA2OCqUnSeBnG6Anj266ptA-RhEKn5NCpYwVLtOTRbuILn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As always, food was spot on.
Love the classic pastrami Reuben from  my previous visits, but tried the slow cooked lamb Reuben today. Juicy and dissolved in my mouth. Definitely recommend.
The shakshuka was tasty with a great combination of flavours and colours.
Hit the spot!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPj3Dms-i-p8Q3PmffvXnhmhNstembn8knxbPPH"],"When":"2024-3-27"},{"Name":"Adhi Sappareng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFRDA4enBPCcEh7eQVh09kUg2UxbkMSJqxZ-IpnZ29lOUEqoEm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Went there for the 3rd time after 1-2 years. I was surprise with menu price. The food was pricey but worth to try.

We ordered original reuben for $25 and french toast for $23 luckily the taste was really good. I love the reuben and the french toast. The cold fresh juice also taste really good.

The place and the customer always nice. They were really good on customer service.

If you like reuben, may be its the place to try. I love it","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9nCSbzKx1VQIk0zzjdPtTfaqGsrDFXdrttNBn"],"When":"2024-2-3"},{"Name":"Heidi I","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFrKv2eZ-EAMqOhDzN071xE79f8Rx2OjodRrNe1y3KeQOe6Wo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the most unique eateries in Adelaide! Authentic Jewish food in the heart of North Adelaide with great coffee, unique dishes, and a range of groceries too!

I’ve lost count of how many times I’ve been here but it is one of my favourites. The team are always friendly and welcoming, and they have creative specials each week. The bagels are excellent of course, and they have other classics like Matzo Ball Soup. My husband’s fave is the Pastrami Rueben and it never disappoints!

Definitely worth booking if visiting on a weekend as it can be a very popular place!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK7KdCI-Vknrg0YzD0NC8EOwagxv3e1daaz8FA"],"When":"2023-12-15"},{"Name":"Ian Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTkxy3E1sidmuZY-XxJWjYjJIZfUsKMZYhz568e2jlsqLFWKZEhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food…

Malawach: Jewish flatbread, served with poached eggs, spinach, grated tomato (garlic and olive oil), schug,

broccolini, beetroot hummus, hazelnut dukkha and fresh chilli.

The Lamb Reuben - Grilled - A 24 hour slow cooked lamb shoulder, halloumi, house -made cabbage, kohlrabi and carraway sauerkraut, Swiss cheese and our Russian dressing on dark rye.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNi1K-yAi1zDsMhvAmUCc5FJbPmZsfRWD24FQrf"],"When":"2024-1-24"},{"Name":"Pejman Babaei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYl_zJGvyaaz5Z9O07F4kxFMDS1XbqcxtlxVjO_nmeusDGRL2N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited this charming local cafe on a rainy weekend morning and relished our breakfast by the window. The food and coffee were delightful, and the excellent customer service left us quite satisfied. We look forward to returning soon for another enjoyable meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPttfpmfb0vGi3D5pDFhjW5Kgab7XgT-1Vma1wr"],"When":"2024-1-5"},{"Name":"Kristine A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNeKEeZnrL5B14Ii8TCqdlb7R5kih3sln2P18qkMCddg1MtVsg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food here was so good, I forgot to take a photo before we dug in. The lox bagel was a flavour explosion, and both bagels were the freshest we’ve ever had in SA. Sitting in the sun on a Sunday morning was perfect, but there was heaps of seating both inside and out. The staff were so friendly and organised. Excellent coffee too 👌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqZEkNYFXSe4ZIsg-pGqKDiMIAiwWzuKjcPFoo"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Paul Griffin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_AooHF2CHKeR08BtQwn-9cu0OsyZKLe_vzBfQTB79PStl3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Unique food and drinks. Classic Bagel combinations with quality ingredients. Middle Eastern Eggs provided a new (delicious) experience. Excellent location. We’re coming back here again (and again). Cherry pie to die for. Love it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBQX2XIyEE5LIpw5rpKywIl7xD3aZiBRvXzwQx"],"When":"2024-1-14"},{"Name":"Bear and Dad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVba8fKnEaBIOygWQfKpJVxFskG-W2W7-tD4GbH3G8Tg4lJ_9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommended if you are in North Adelaide. If you have never been to a Jewish Deli, this would be a great place to go to experience that, and we would consider it a destination spot. It is located on a quiet street in North Adelaide, with plenty of seating outdoors and inside buzzes with a tradition deli feel.

(Note: We only review a spot after two visits to be fair on judgement) The service has always been friendly and accommodating. However when they are busy the service level is the same, but be prepared for a delay on food coming out of the kitchen which would be expected.  Our first  visit the food came out quickly was to a very high standard. A huge bonus for the fact they make their own bagels in house each day. (Which you can buy to take away when not sold out.) The menu does blend traditional jewish food with their own inventive twist.

The baked eggs were perfect and full of flavour. I you have never had a Reuben you must go to this place. The bagels very much reminded us of New York style bagels, and we loved the bagel and smoked salmon. We would rate it as a 4.5, due to some of the delays in food, but still an amazing place and a 5 is not that far of a stretch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNTqGplabG2pso3gHUl-LItzND9q8oQU1asuLw"],"When":"2023-12-3"}]
